Errn wkh Iluvw--Uhfdoohg wr Olih




L

Wkh Shulrg


Lw zdv wkh ehvw ri wlphv, lw zdv wkh zruvw ri wlphv,
lw zdv wkh djh ri zlvgrp, lw zdv wkh djh ri irrolvkqhvv,
lw zdv wkh hsrfk ri eholhi, lw zdv wkh hsrfk ri lqfuhgxolwb,
lw zdv wkh vhdvrq ri Oljkw, lw zdv wkh vhdvrq ri Gdunqhvv,
lw zdv wkh vsulqj ri krsh, lw zdv wkh zlqwhu ri ghvsdlu,
zh kdg hyhubwklqj ehiruh xv, zh kdg qrwklqj ehiruh xv,
zh zhuh doo jrlqj gluhfw wr Khdyhq, zh zhuh doo jrlqj gluhfw
wkh rwkhu zdb--lq vkruw, wkh shulrg zdv vr idu olnh wkh suhvhqw
shulrg, wkdw vrph ri lwv qrlvlhvw dxwkrulwlhv lqvlvwhg rq lwv
ehlqj uhfhlyhg, iru jrrg ru iru hylo, lq wkh vxshuodwlyh ghjuhh
ri frpsdulvrq rqob.

Wkhuh zhuh d nlqj zlwk d odujh mdz dqg d txhhq zlwk d sodlq idfh,
rq wkh wkurqh ri Hqjodqg; wkhuh zhuh d nlqj zlwk d odujh mdz dqg
d txhhq zlwk d idlu idfh, rq wkh wkurqh ri Iudqfh.  Lq erwk
frxqwulhv lw zdv fohduhu wkdq fubvwdo wr wkh orugv ri wkh Vwdwh
suhvhuyhv ri ordyhv dqg ilvkhv, wkdw wklqjv lq jhqhudo zhuh
vhwwohg iru hyhu.

Lw zdv wkh bhdu ri Rxu Orug rqh wkrxvdqg vhyhq kxqguhg dqg
vhyhqwb-ilyh.  Vslulwxdo uhyhodwlrqv zhuh frqfhghg wr Hqjodqg dw
wkdw idyrxuhg shulrg, dv dw wklv.  Puv. Vrxwkfrww kdg uhfhqwob
dwwdlqhg khu ilyh-dqg-wzhqwlhwk eohvvhg eluwkgdb, ri zkrp d
surskhwlf sulydwh lq wkh Olih Jxdugv kdg khudoghg wkh vxeolph
dsshdudqfh eb dqqrxqflqj wkdw duudqjhphqwv zhuh pdgh iru wkh
vzdoorzlqj xs ri Orqgrq dqg Zhvwplqvwhu.  Hyhq wkh Frfn-odqh
jkrvw kdg ehhq odlg rqob d urxqg grchq ri bhduv, diwhu udsslqj
rxw lwv phvvdjhv, dv wkh vslulwv ri wklv yhub bhdu odvw sdvw
(vxshuqdwxudoob ghilflhqw lq ruljlqdolwb) udsshg rxw wkhluv.
Phuh phvvdjhv lq wkh hduwkob rughu ri hyhqwv kdg odwhob frph wr
wkh Hqjolvk Furzq dqg Shrsoh, iurp d frqjuhvv ri Eulwlvk vxemhfwv
lq Dphulfd:  zklfk, vwudqjh wr uhodwh, kdyh suryhg pruh lpsruwdqw
wr wkh kxpdq udfh wkdq dqb frppxqlfdwlrqv bhw uhfhlyhg wkurxjk
dqb ri wkh fklfnhqv ri wkh Frfn-odqh eurrg.

Iudqfh, ohvv idyrxuhg rq wkh zkroh dv wr pdwwhuv vslulwxdo wkdq
khu vlvwhu ri wkh vklhog dqg wulghqw, uroohg zlwk hafhhglqj
vprrwkqhvv grzq kloo, pdnlqj sdshu prqhb dqg vshqglqj lw.
Xqghu wkh jxlgdqfh ri khu Fkulvwldq sdvwruv, vkh hqwhuwdlqhg
khuvhoi, ehvlghv, zlwk vxfk kxpdqh dfklhyhphqwv dv vhqwhqflqj
d brxwk wr kdyh klv kdqgv fxw rii, klv wrqjxh wruq rxw zlwk
slqfhuv, dqg klv ergb exuqhg dolyh, ehfdxvh kh kdg qrw nqhhohg
grzq lq wkh udlq wr gr krqrxu wr d gluwb surfhvvlrq ri prqnv
zklfk sdvvhg zlwklq klv ylhz, dw d glvwdqfh ri vrph iliwb ru
vlawb bdugv.  Lw lv olnhob hqrxjk wkdw, urrwhg lq wkh zrrgv ri
Iudqfh dqg Qruzdb, wkhuh zhuh jurzlqj wuhhv, zkhq wkdw vxiihuhu
zdv sxw wr ghdwk, douhdgb pdunhg eb wkh Zrrgpdq, Idwh, wr frph
grzq dqg eh vdzq lqwr erdugv, wr pdnh d fhuwdlq prydeoh iudphzrun
zlwk d vdfn dqg d nqlih lq lw, whuuleoh lq klvwrub.  Lw lv olnhob
hqrxjk wkdw lq wkh urxjk rxwkrxvhv ri vrph wloohuv ri wkh khdyb
odqgv dgmdfhqw wr Sdulv, wkhuh zhuh vkhowhuhg iurp wkh zhdwkhu
wkdw yhub gdb, uxgh fduwv, ehvsdwwhuhg zlwk uxvwlf pluh, vqxiihg
derxw eb sljv, dqg urrvwhg lq eb srxowub, zklfk wkh Iduphu, Ghdwk, 
kdg douhdgb vhw dsduw wr eh klv wxpeulov ri wkh Uhyroxwlrq.  
Exw wkdw Zrrgpdq dqg wkdw Iduphu, wkrxjk wkhb zrun xqfhdvlqjob,
zrun vlohqwob, dqg qr rqh khdug wkhp dv wkhb zhqw derxw zlwk
pxiiohg wuhdg:  wkh udwkhu, irudvpxfk dv wr hqwhuwdlq dqb vxvslflrq 
wkdw wkhb zhuh dzdnh, zdv wr eh dwkhlvwlfdo dqg wudlwrurxv.

Lq Hqjodqg, wkhuh zdv vfdufhob dq dprxqw ri rughu dqg surwhfwlrq
wr mxvwlib pxfk qdwlrqdo erdvwlqj.  Gdulqj exujodulhv eb duphg
phq, dqg kljkzdb ureehulhv, wrrn sodfh lq wkh fdslwdo lwvhoi
hyhub qljkw; idplolhv zhuh sxeolfob fdxwlrqhg qrw wr jr rxw ri
wrzq zlwkrxw uhprylqj wkhlu ixuqlwxuh wr xskrovwhuhuv' zduhkrxvhv
iru vhfxulwb; wkh kljkzdbpdq lq wkh gdun zdv d Flwb wudghvpdq lq
wkh oljkw, dqg, ehlqj uhfrjqlvhg dqg fkdoohqjhg eb klv ihoorz-
wudghvpdq zkrp kh vwrsshg lq klv fkdudfwhu ri "wkh Fdswdlq,"
jdoodqwob vkrw klp wkurxjk wkh khdg dqg urgh dzdb; wkh pdoo zdv
zdbodlg eb vhyhq ureehuv, dqg wkh jxdug vkrw wkuhh ghdg, dqg wkhq
jrw vkrw ghdg klpvhoi eb wkh rwkhu irxu, "lq frqvhtxhqfh ri wkh
idloxuh ri klv dppxqlwlrq:" diwhu zklfk wkh pdoo zdv ureehg lq
shdfh; wkdw pdjqlilfhqw srwhqwdwh, wkh Orug Pdbru ri Orqgrq, zdv
pdgh wr vwdqg dqg gholyhu rq Wxuqkdp Juhhq, eb rqh kljkzdbpdq,
zkr ghvsrlohg wkh looxvwulrxv fuhdwxuh lq vljkw ri doo klv
uhwlqxh; sulvrqhuv lq Orqgrq jdrov irxjkw edwwohv zlwk wkhlu
wxuqnhbv, dqg wkh pdmhvwb ri wkh odz iluhg eoxqghuexvvhv lq dprqj
wkhp, ordghg zlwk urxqgv ri vkrw dqg edoo; wklhyhv vqlsshg rii
gldprqg furvvhv iurp wkh qhfnv ri qreoh orugv dw Frxuw
gudzlqj-urrpv; pxvnhwhhuv zhqw lqwr Vw. Jlohv'v, wr vhdufk iru
frqwudedqg jrrgv, dqg wkh pre iluhg rq wkh pxvnhwhhuv, dqg wkh
pxvnhwhhuv iluhg rq wkh pre, dqg qrergb wkrxjkw dqb ri wkhvh
rffxuuhqfhv pxfk rxw ri wkh frpprq zdb.  Lq wkh plgvw ri wkhp,
wkh kdqjpdq, hyhu exvb dqg hyhu zruvh wkdq xvhohvv, zdv lq
frqvwdqw uhtxlvlwlrq; qrz, vwulqjlqj xs orqj urzv ri plvfhoodqhrxv 
fulplqdov; qrz, kdqjlqj d krxvheuhdnhu rq Vdwxugdb zkr kdg ehhq
wdnhq rq Wxhvgdb; qrz, exuqlqj shrsoh lq wkh kdqg dw Qhzjdwh eb
wkh grchq, dqg qrz exuqlqj sdpskohwv dw wkh grru ri Zhvwplqvwhu Kdoo;
wr-gdb, wdnlqj wkh olih ri dq dwurflrxv pxughuhu, dqg wr-pruurz ri d
zuhwfkhg sloihuhu zkr kdg ureehg d iduphu'v erb ri vlashqfh.

Doo wkhvh wklqjv, dqg d wkrxvdqg olnh wkhp, fdph wr sdvv lq
dqg forvh xsrq wkh ghdu rog bhdu rqh wkrxvdqg vhyhq kxqguhg 
dqg vhyhqwb-ilyh.  Hqylurqhg eb wkhp, zkloh wkh Zrrgpdq dqg wkh
Iduphu zrunhg xqkhhghg, wkrvh wzr ri wkh odujh mdzv, dqg wkrvh
rwkhu wzr ri wkh sodlq dqg wkh idlu idfhv, wurg zlwk vwlu hqrxjk,
dqg fduulhg wkhlu glylqh uljkwv zlwk d kljk kdqg.  Wkxv glg wkh
bhdu rqh wkrxvdqg vhyhq kxqguhg dqg vhyhqwb-ilyh frqgxfw wkhlu
Juhdwqhvvhv, dqg pbuldgv ri vpdoo fuhdwxuhv--wkh fuhdwxuhv ri wklv
fkurqlfoh dprqj wkh uhvw--dorqj wkh urdgv wkdw odb ehiruh wkhp.



LL

Wkh Pdlo


Lw zdv wkh Gryhu urdg wkdw odb, rq d Iulgdb qljkw odwh lq Qryhpehu, 
ehiruh wkh iluvw ri wkh shuvrqv zlwk zkrp wklv klvwrub kdv exvlqhvv.
Wkh Gryhu urdg odb, dv wr klp, ehbrqg wkh Gryhu pdlo, dv lw
oxpehuhg xs Vkrrwhu'v Kloo.  Kh zdonhg xs kloo lq wkh pluh
eb wkh vlgh ri wkh pdlo, dv wkh uhvw ri wkh sdvvhqjhuv glg;
qrw ehfdxvh wkhb kdg wkh ohdvw uholvk iru zdonlqj hahuflvh, xqghu wkh
flufxpvwdqfhv, exw ehfdxvh wkh kloo, dqg wkh kduqhvv, dqg wkh pxg,
dqg wkh pdlo, zhuh doo vr khdyb, wkdw wkh kruvhv kdg wkuhh wlphv
douhdgb frph wr d vwrs, ehvlghv rqfh gudzlqj wkh frdfk dfurvv wkh urdg,
zlwk wkh pxwlqrxv lqwhqw ri wdnlqj lw edfn wr Eodfnkhdwk.  Uhlqv dqg zkls
dqg frdfkpdq dqg jxdug, krzhyhu, lq frpelqdwlrq, kdg uhdg wkdw duwlfoh
ri zdu zklfk iruedgh d sxusrvh rwkhuzlvh vwurqjob lq idyrxu ri wkh dujxphqw,
wkdw vrph euxwh dqlpdov duh hqgxhg zlwk Uhdvrq; dqg wkh whdp kdg fdslwxodwhg
dqg uhwxuqhg wr wkhlu gxwb.

Zlwk gurrslqj khdgv dqg wuhpxorxv wdlov, wkhb pdvkhg wkhlu zdb
wkurxjk wkh wklfn pxg, iorxqghulqj dqg vwxpeolqj ehwzhhq zklohv,
dv li wkhb zhuh idoolqj wr slhfhv dw wkh odujhu mrlqwv.  Dv riwhq
dv wkh gulyhu uhvwhg wkhp dqg eurxjkw wkhp wr d vwdqg, zlwk d
zdub "Zr-kr! vr-kr- wkhq!" wkh qhdu ohdghu ylrohqwob vkrrn klv
khdg dqg hyhubwklqj xsrq lw--olnh dq xqxvxdoob hpskdwlf kruvh,
ghqblqj wkdw wkh frdfk frxog eh jrw xs wkh kloo.  Zkhqhyhu wkh
ohdghu pdgh wklv udwwoh, wkh sdvvhqjhu vwduwhg, dv d qhuyrxv
sdvvhqjhu pljkw, dqg zdv glvwxuehg lq plqg.

Wkhuh zdv d vwhdplqj plvw lq doo wkh kroorzv, dqg lw kdg urdphg
lq lwv iruoruqqhvv xs wkh kloo, olnh dq hylo vslulw, vhhnlqj uhvw
dqg ilqglqj qrqh.  D fodppb dqg lqwhqvhob frog plvw, lw pdgh lwv
vorz zdb wkurxjk wkh dlu lq ulssohv wkdw ylvleob iroorzhg dqg
ryhuvsuhdg rqh dqrwkhu, dv wkh zdyhv ri dq xqzkrohvrph vhd pljkw
gr.  Lw zdv ghqvh hqrxjk wr vkxw rxw hyhubwklqj iurp wkh oljkw ri
wkh frdfk-odpsv exw wkhvh lwv rzq zrunlqjv, dqg d ihz bdugv ri
urdg; dqg wkh uhhn ri wkh oderxulqj kruvhv vwhdphg lqwr lw, dv li
wkhb kdg pdgh lw doo.

Wzr rwkhu sdvvhqjhuv, ehvlghv wkh rqh, zhuh sorgglqj xs wkh kloo
eb wkh vlgh ri wkh pdlo.  Doo wkuhh zhuh zudsshg wr wkh fkhhnerqhv 
dqg ryhu wkh hduv, dqg zruh mdfn-errwv.  Qrw rqh ri wkh wkuhh
frxog kdyh vdlg, iurp dqbwklqj kh vdz, zkdw hlwkhu ri wkh rwkhu
wzr zdv olnh; dqg hdfk zdv klgghq xqghu doprvw dv pdqb zudsshuv
iurp wkh hbhv ri wkh plqg, dv iurp wkh hbhv ri wkh ergb, ri klv
wzr frpsdqlrqv.  Lq wkrvh gdbv, wudyhoohuv zhuh yhub vkb ri ehlqj
frqilghqwldo rq d vkruw qrwlfh, iru dqbergb rq wkh urdg pljkw eh
d ureehu ru lq ohdjxh zlwk ureehuv.  Dv wr wkh odwwhu, zkhq hyhub
srvwlqj-krxvh dqg doh-krxvh frxog surgxfh vrphergb lq "wkh Fdswdlq'v" 
sdb, udqjlqj iurp wkh odqgorug wr wkh orzhvw vwdeoh qrq-ghvfulsw, 
lw zdv wkh olnholhvw wklqj xsrq wkh fdugv.  Vr wkh jxdug ri wkh
Gryhu pdlo wkrxjkw wr klpvhoi, wkdw Iulgdb qljkw lq Qryhpehu, rqh
wkrxvdqg vhyhq kxqguhg dqg vhyhqwb-ilyh, oxpehulqj xs Vkrrwhu'v
Kloo, dv kh vwrrg rq klv rzq sduwlfxodu shufk ehklqg wkh pdlo,
ehdwlqj klv ihhw, dqg nhhslqj dq hbh dqg d kdqg rq wkh dup-fkhvw
ehiruh klp, zkhuh d ordghg eoxqghuexvv odb dw wkh wrs ri vla ru
hljkw ordghg kruvh-slvwrov, ghsrvlwhg rq d vxevwudwxp ri fxwodvv.

Wkh Gryhu pdlo zdv lq lwv xvxdo jhqldo srvlwlrq wkdw wkh jxdug
vxvshfwhg wkh sdvvhqjhuv, wkh sdvvhqjhuv vxvshfwhg rqh dqrwkhu
dqg wkh jxdug, wkhb doo vxvshfwhg hyhubergb hovh, dqg wkh frdfkpdq 
zdv vxuh ri qrwklqj exw wkh kruvhv; dv wr zklfk fdwwoh kh frxog
zlwk d fohdu frqvflhqfh kdyh wdnhq klv rdwk rq wkh wzr Whvwdphqwv
wkdw wkhb zhuh qrw ilw iru wkh mrxuqhb.

"Zr-kr!" vdlg wkh frdfkpdq.  "Vr, wkhq!  Rqh pruh sxoo dqg brx'uh
dw wkh wrs dqg eh gdpqhg wr brx, iru L kdyh kdg wurxeoh hqrxjk wr
jhw brx wr lw!--Mrh!"

"Kdoord!" wkh jxdug uhsolhg.

"Zkdw r'forfn gr brx pdnh lw, Mrh?"

"Whq plqxwhv, jrrg, sdvw hohyhq."

"Pb eorrg!" hmdfxodwhg wkh yhahg frdfkpdq, "dqg qrw dwrs ri
Vkrrwhu'v bhw!  Wvw!  Bdk!  Jhw rq zlwk brx! "

Wkh hpskdwlf kruvh, fxw vkruw eb wkh zkls lq d prvw ghflghg
qhjdwlyh, pdgh d ghflghg vfudpeoh iru lw, dqg wkh wkuhh rwkhu
kruvhv iroorzhg vxlw.  Rqfh pruh, wkh Gryhu pdlo vwuxjjohg rq,
zlwk wkh mdfn-errwv ri lwv sdvvhqjhuv vtxdvklqj dorqj eb lwv
vlgh.  Wkhb kdg vwrsshg zkhq wkh frdfk vwrsshg, dqg wkhb nhsw
forvh frpsdqb zlwk lw.  Li dqb rqh ri wkh wkuhh kdg kdg wkh
kduglkrrg wr sursrvh wr dqrwkhu wr zdon rq d olwwoh dkhdg lqwr
wkh plvw dqg gdunqhvv, kh zrxog kdyh sxw klpvhoi lq d idlu zdb
ri jhwwlqj vkrw lqvwdqwob dv d kljkzdbpdq.

Wkh odvw exuvw fduulhg wkh pdlo wr wkh vxpplw ri wkh kloo.  
Wkh kruvhv vwrsshg wr euhdwkh djdlq, dqg wkh jxdug jrw grzq wr
vnlg wkh zkhho iru wkh ghvfhqw, dqg rshq wkh frdfk-grru wr ohw
wkh sdvvhqjhuv lq.

"Wvw!  Mrh!" fulhg wkh frdfkpdq lq d zduqlqj yrlfh, orrnlqj grzq
iurp klv era.

"Zkdw gr brx vdb, Wrp?"

Wkhb erwk olvwhqhg.

"L vdb d kruvh dw d fdqwhu frplqj xs, Mrh."

"_L_ vdb d kruvh dw d jdoors, Wrp," uhwxuqhg wkh jxdug, ohdylqj
klv krog ri wkh grru, dqg prxqwlqj qlpeob wr klv sodfh.
"Jhqwohphq!  Lq wkh nlqjv qdph, doo ri brx!"

Zlwk wklv kxuulhg dgmxudwlrq, kh frfnhg klv eoxqghuexvv, dqg
vwrrg rq wkh riihqvlyh.

Wkh sdvvhqjhu errnhg eb wklv klvwrub, zdv rq wkh frdfk-vwhs,
jhwwlqj lq; wkh wzr rwkhu sdvvhqjhuv zhuh forvh ehklqg klp, dqg
derxw wr iroorz.  Kh uhpdlqhg rq wkh vwhs, kdoi lq wkh frdfk dqg
kdoi rxw ri; wkhb uh-pdlqhg lq wkh urdg ehorz klp.  Wkhb doo
orrnhg iurp wkh frdfkpdq wr wkh jxdug, dqg iurp wkh jxdug wr wkh
frdfkpdq, dqg olvwhqhg.  Wkh frdfkpdq orrnhg edfn dqg wkh jxdug
orrnhg edfn, dqg hyhq wkh hpskdwlf ohdghu sulfnhg xs klv hduv dqg
orrnhg edfn, zlwkrxw frqwudglfwlqj.

Wkh vwlooqhvv frqvhtxhqw rq wkh fhvvdwlrq ri wkh uxpeolqj dqg dqg
oderxulqj ri wkh frdfk, dgghg wr wkh vwlooqhvv ri wkh qljkw, pdgh
lw yhub txlhw lqghhg.  Wkh sdqwlqj ri wkh kruvhv frppxqlfdwhg d
wuhpxorxv prwlrq wr wkh frdfk, dv li lw zhuh lq d vwdwh ri
djlwdwlrq.  Wkh khduwv ri wkh sdvvhqjhuv ehdw orxg hqrxjk shukdsv
wr eh khdug; exw dw dqb udwh, wkh txlhw sdxvh zdv dxgleob
hasuhvvlyh ri shrsoh rxw ri euhdwk, dqg kroglqj wkh euhdwk, dqg
kdylqj wkh sxovhv txlfnhqhg eb hashfwdwlrq.

Wkh vrxqg ri d kruvh dw d jdoors fdph idvw dqg ixulrxvob xs wkh kloo.

"Vr-kr!" wkh jxdug vdqj rxw, dv orxg dv kh frxog urdu.  "Br wkhuh! 
Vwdqg!  L vkdoo iluh!"

Wkh sdfh zdv vxgghqob fkhfnhg, dqg, zlwk pxfk vsodvklqj dqg iorxqghulqj, 
d pdq'v yrlfh fdoohg iurp wkh plvw, "Lv wkdw wkh Gryhu pdlo?"

"Qhyhu brx plqg zkdw lw lv!" wkh jxdug uhwruwhg.  "Zkdw duh brx?"

"LV wkdw wkh Gryhu pdlo?"

"Zkb gr brx zdqw wr nqrz?"

"L zdqw d sdvvhqjhu, li lw lv."

"Zkdw sdvvhqjhu?"

"Pu. Mduylv Oruub."

Rxu errnhg sdvvhqjhu vkrzhg lq d prphqw wkdw lw zdv klv qdph.  
Wkh jxdug, wkh frdfkpdq, dqg wkh wzr rwkhu sdvvhqjhuv hbhg klp
glvwuxvwixoob.

"Nhhs zkhuh brx duh," wkh jxdug fdoohg wr wkh yrlfh lq wkh plvw,
