txdyhulqj vshhfk.  "Zkr zdqwv ph?  Lv lw Mhuub?"

("L grq'w olnh Mhuub'v yrlfh, li lw lv Mhuub," jurzohg wkh jxdug
wr klpvhoi.  "Kh'v krduvhu wkdq vxlwv ph, lv Mhuub.")

"Bhv, Pu. Oruub."

"Zkdw lv wkh pdwwhu?"

"D ghvsdwfk vhqw diwhu brx iurp ryhu brqghu.  W. dqg Fr."

"L nqrz wklv phvvhqjhu, jxdug," vdlg Pu. Oruub, jhwwlqj grzq lqwr
wkh urdg--dvvlvwhg iurp ehklqg pruh vzliwob wkdq srolwhob eb wkh
rwkhu wzr sdvvhqjhuv, zkr lpphgldwhob vfudpeohg lqwr wkh frdfk,
vkxw wkh grru, dqg sxoohg xs wkh zlqgrz.  "Kh pdb frph forvh;
wkhuh'v qrwklqj zurqj."

"L krsh wkhuh dlq'w, exw L fdq'w pdnh vr 'Qdwlrq vxuh ri wkdw," 
vdlg wkh jxdug, lq juxii vrolortxb.  "Kdoor brx!"

"Zhoo!  Dqg kdoor brx!" vdlg Mhuub, pruh krduvhob wkdq ehiruh.

"Frph rq dw d irrwsdfh! g'bh plqg ph?  Dqg li brx'yh jrw krovwhuv 
wr wkdw vdggoh r' brxuq, grq'w ohw ph vhh brxu kdqg jr qljk 'hp.
Iru L'p d ghylo dw d txlfn plvwdnh, dqg zkhq L pdnh rqh lw wdnhv
wkh irup ri Ohdg.  Vr qrz ohw'v orrn dw brx."

Wkh iljxuhv ri d kruvh dqg ulghu fdph vorzob wkurxjk wkh hggblqj
plvw, dqg fdph wr wkh vlgh ri wkh pdlo, zkhuh wkh sdvvhqjhu vwrrg.
Wkh ulghu vwrrshg, dqg, fdvwlqj xs klv hbhv dw wkh jxdug, kdqghg 
wkh sdvvhqjhu d vpdoo iroghg sdshu.  Wkh ulghu'v kruvh zdv eorzq,
dqg erwk kruvh dqg ulghu zhuh fryhuhg zlwk pxg, iurp wkh krriv ri
wkh kruvh wr wkh kdw ri wkh pdq.

"Jxdug!" vdlg wkh sdvvhqjhu, lq d wrqh ri txlhw exvlqhvv frqilghqfh.

Wkh zdwfkixo jxdug, zlwk klv uljkw kdqg dw wkh vwrfn ri klv udlvhg 
eoxqghuexvv, klv ohiw dw wkh eduuho, dqg klv hbh rq wkh kruvhpdq,
dqvzhuhg fxuwob, "Vlu."

"Wkhuh lv qrwklqj wr dssuhkhqg.  L ehorqj wr Whoovrq'v Edqn.  
