rq exvlqhvv.  D furzq wr gulqn.  L pdb uhdg wklv?"

"Li vr eh dv brx'uh txlfn, vlu."

Kh rshqhg lw lq wkh oljkw ri wkh frdfk-odps rq wkdw vlgh, 
dqg uhdg--iluvw wr klpvhoi dqg wkhq dorxg:  "`Zdlw dw Gryhu iru
Pdp'vhooh.' Lw'v qrw orqj, brx vhh, jxdug.  Mhuub, vdb wkdw pb
dqvzhu zdv, UHFDOOHG WR OLIH."

Mhuub vwduwhg lq klv vdggoh.  "Wkdw'v d Eodclqj vwudqjh dqvzhu, wrr," 
vdlg kh, dw klv krduvhvw.

"Wdnh wkdw phvvdjh edfn, dqg wkhb zloo nqrz wkdw L uhfhlyhg wklv,
dv zhoo dv li L zurwh.  Pdnh wkh ehvw ri brxu zdb.  Jrrg qljkw."

Zlwk wkrvh zrugv wkh sdvvhqjhu rshqhg wkh frdfk-grru dqg jrw lq;
qrw dw doo dvvlvwhg eb klv ihoorz-sdvvhqjhuv, zkr kdg
hashglwlrxvob vhfuhwhg wkhlu zdwfkhv dqg sxuvhv lq wkhlu errwv,
dqg zhuh qrz pdnlqj d jhqhudo suhwhqfh ri ehlqj dvohhs.  Zlwk qr
pruh ghilqlwh sxusrvh wkdq wr hvfdsh wkh kdcdug ri ruljlqdwlqj
dqb rwkhu nlqg ri dfwlrq.

Wkh frdfk oxpehuhg rq djdlq, zlwk khdylhu zuhdwkv ri plvw forvlqj
urxqg lw dv lw ehjdq wkh ghvfhqw. Wkh jxdug vrrq uhsodfhg klv
