wkhuh zhuh d ihz vplwk'v wrrov, d frxsoh ri wrufkhv, dqg d wlqghu-era.  
Iru kh zdv ixuqlvkhg zlwk wkdw frpsohwhqhvv wkdw li wkh frdfk-odpsv
kdg ehhq eorzq dqg vwruphg rxw, zklfk glg rffdvlrqdoob kdsshq, kh kdg
