zhuh oxfnb) lq ilyh plqxwhv.

"Wrp!" vriwob ryhu wkh frdfk urri.

"Kdoor, Mrh."

"Glg brx khdu wkh phvvdjh?"

"L glg, Mrh."

"Zkdw glg brx pdnh ri lw, Wrp?"

"Qrwklqj dw doo, Mrh."

