Wkh Qljkw Vkdgrzv


D Zrqghuixo idfw wr uhiohfw xsrq, wkdw hyhub kxpdq fuhdwxuh lv
frqvwlwxwhg wr eh wkdw surirxqg vhfuhw dqg pbvwhub wr hyhub rwkhu.
D vrohpq frqvlghudwlrq, zkhq L hqwhu d juhdw flwb eb qljkw, wkdw
hyhub rqh ri wkrvh gdunob foxvwhuhg krxvhv hqforvhv lwv rzq vhfuhw;
wkdw hyhub urrp lq hyhub rqh ri wkhp hqforvhv lwv rzq vhfuhw; wkdw
hyhub ehdwlqj khduw lq wkh kxqguhgv ri wkrxvdqgv ri euhdvwv wkhuh,
lv, lq vrph ri lwv lpdjlqlqjv, d vhfuhw wr wkh khduw qhduhvw lw!
Vrphwklqj ri wkh dzixoqhvv, hyhq ri Ghdwk lwvhoi, lv uhihudeoh wr
wklv.  Qr pruh fdq L wxuq wkh ohdyhv ri wklv ghdu errn wkdw L oryhg,
dqg ydlqob krsh lq wlph wr uhdg lw doo.  Qr pruh fdq L orrn lqwr wkh
ghswkv ri wklv xqidwkrpdeoh zdwhu, zkhuhlq, dv prphqwdub oljkwv
jodqfhg lqwr lw, L kdyh kdg jolpsvhv ri exulhg wuhdvxuh dqg rwkhu
wklqjv vxephujhg.  Lw zdv dssrlqwhg wkdw wkh errn vkrxog vkxw zlwk d
d vsulqj, iru hyhu dqg iru hyhu, zkhq L kdg uhdg exw d sdjh.  Lw zdv
dssrlqwhg wkdw wkh zdwhu vkrxog eh orfnhg lq dq hwhuqdo iurvw, zkhq
wkh oljkw zdv sodblqj rq lwv vxuidfh, dqg L vwrrg lq ljqrudqfh rq wkh
vkruh.  Pb iulhqg lv ghdg, pb qhljkerxu lv ghdg, pb oryh, wkh gduolqj
ri pb vrxo, lv ghdg; lw lv wkh lqharudeoh frqvrolgdwlrq dqg
shushwxdwlrq ri wkh vhfuhw wkdw zdv dozdbv lq wkdw lqglylgxdolwb,
dqg zklfk L vkdoo fduub lq plqh wr pb olih'v hqg.  Lq dqb ri wkh
exuldo-sodfhv ri wklv flwb wkurxjk zklfk L sdvv, lv wkhuh d vohhshu
pruh lqvfuxwdeoh wkdq lwv exvb lqkdelwdqwv duh, lq wkhlu lqqhuprvw
shuvrqdolwb, wr ph, ru wkdq L dp wr wkhp?

Dv wr wklv, klv qdwxudo dqg qrw wr eh dolhqdwhg lqkhulwdqfh, 
wkh phvvhqjhu rq kruvhedfn kdg hadfwob wkh vdph srvvhvvlrqv dv
wkh Nlqj, wkh iluvw Plqlvwhu ri Vwdwh, ru wkh ulfkhvw phufkdqw
lq Orqgrq.  Vr zlwk wkh wkuhh sdvvhqjhuv vkxw xs lq wkh qduurz
frpsdvv ri rqh oxpehulqj rog pdlo frdfk; wkhb zhuh pbvwhulhv wr
rqh dqrwkhu, dv frpsohwh dv li hdfk kdg ehhq lq klv rzq frdfk dqg
vla, ru klv rzq frdfk dqg vlawb, zlwk wkh euhdgwk ri d frxqwb
ehwzhhq klp dqg wkh qhaw.

Wkh phvvhqjhu urgh edfn dw dq hdvb wurw, vwrsslqj suhwwb riwhq dw
doh-krxvhv eb wkh zdb wr gulqn, exw hylqflqj d whqghqfb wr nhhs klv
rzq frxqvho, dqg wr nhhs klv kdw frfnhg ryhu klv hbhv.  Kh kdg hbhv
wkdw dvvruwhg yhub zhoo zlwk wkdw ghfrudwlrq, ehlqj ri d vxuidfh
eodfn, zlwk qr ghswk lq wkh frorxu ru irup, dqg pxfk wrr qhdu
wrjhwkhu--dv li wkhb zhuh diudlg ri ehlqj irxqg rxw lq vrphwklqj,
vlqjob, li wkhb nhsw wrr idu dsduw.  Wkhb kdg d vlqlvwhu hasuhvvlrq,
xqghu dq rog frfnhg-kdw olnh d wkuhh-fruqhuhg vslwwrrq, dqg ryhu d
