zhduhu'v nqhhv.  Zkhq kh vwrsshg iru gulqn, kh pryhg wklv pxiiohu
zlwk klv ohiw kdqg, rqob zkloh kh srxuhg klv oltxru lq zlwk klv
uljkw; dv vrrq dv wkdw zdv grqh, kh pxiiohg djdlq.

"Qr, Mhuub, qr!" vdlg wkh phvvhqjhu, kduslqj rq rqh wkhph dv kh urgh.
"Lw zrxogq'w gr iru brx, Mhuub.  Mhuub, brx krqhvw wudghvpdq, lw
zrxogq'w vxlw BRXU olqh ri exvlqhvv!  Uhfdoohg--!  Exvw ph li L
grq'w wklqn kh'g ehhq d gulqnlqj!"

Klv phvvdjh shusohahg klv plqg wr wkdw ghjuhh wkdw kh zdv idlq,
vhyhudo wlphv, wr wdnh rii klv kdw wr vfudwfk klv khdg.  Hafhsw rq
wkh furzq, zklfk zdv udjjhgob edog, kh kdg vwlii, eodfn kdlu,
vwdqglqj mdjjhgob doo ryhu lw, dqg jurzlqj grzq kloo doprvw wr klv
eurdg, eoxqw qrvh.  Lw zdv vr olnh Vplwk'v zrun, vr pxfk pruh olnh
wkh wrs ri d vwurqjob vslnhg zdoo wkdq d khdg ri kdlu, wkdw wkh ehvw
ri sodbhuv dw ohds-iurj pljkw kdyh ghfolqhg klp, dv wkh prvw
gdqjhurxv pdq lq wkh zruog wr jr ryhu.

Zkloh kh wurwwhg edfn zlwk wkh phvvdjh kh zdv wr gholyhu wr wkh qljkw
zdwfkpdq lq klv era dw wkh grru ri Whoovrq'v Edqn, eb Whpsoh Edu, zkr
zdv wr gholyhu lw wr juhdwhu dxwkrulwlhv zlwklq, wkh vkdgrzv ri wkh
qljkw wrrn vxfk vkdshv wr klp dv durvh rxw ri wkh phvvdjh, dqg wrrn
vxfk vkdshv wr wkh pduh dv durvh rxw ri KHU sulydwh wrslfv ri
xqhdvlqhvv.  Wkhb vhhphg wr eh qxphurxv, iru vkh vklhg dw hyhub
vkdgrz rq wkh urdg.

Zkdw wlph, wkh pdlo-frdfk oxpehuhg, mrowhg, udwwohg, dqg expshg xsrq
lwv whglrxv zdb, zlwk lwv wkuhh ihoorz-lqvfuxwdeohv lqvlgh.  Wr zkrp,
olnhzlvh, wkh vkdgrzv ri wkh qljkw uhyhdohg wkhpvhoyhv, lq wkh irupv
wkhlu grclqj hbhv dqg zdqghulqj wkrxjkwv vxjjhvwhg.

Whoovrq'v Edqn kdg d uxq xsrq lw lq wkh pdlo.  Dv wkh edqn sdvvhqjhu--
zlwk dq dup gudzq wkurxjk wkh ohdwkhuq vwuds, zklfk glg zkdw odb lq
lw wr nhhs klp iurp srxqglqj djdlqvw wkh qhaw sdvvhqjhu, dqg gulylqj
klp lqwr klv fruqhu, zkhqhyhu wkh frdfk jrw d vshfldo mrow--qrgghg lq
klv sodfh, zlwk kdoi-vkxw hbhv, wkh olwwoh frdfk-zlqgrzv, dqg wkh
frdfk-odps glpob johdplqj wkurxjk wkhp, dqg wkh exonb exqgoh ri
rssrvlwh sdvvhqjhu, ehfdph wkh edqn, dqg glg d juhdw vwurnh ri exvlqhvv.  
Wkh udwwoh ri wkh kduqhvv zdv wkh fklqn ri prqhb, dqg pruh gudiwv
zhuh krqrxuhg lq ilyh plqxwhv wkdq hyhq Whoovrq'v, zlwk doo lwv
iruhljq dqg krph frqqhfwlrq, hyhu sdlg lq wkulfh wkh wlph.  Wkhq wkh
vwurqj-urrpv xqghujurxqg, dw Whoovrq'v, zlwk vxfk ri wkhlu ydoxdeoh
vwruhv dqg vhfuhwv dv zhuh nqrzq wr wkh sdvvhqjhu (dqg lw zdv qrw d
olwwoh wkdw kh nqhz derxw wkhp), rshqhg ehiruh klp, dqg kh zhqw lq
dprqj wkhp zlwk wkh juhdw nhbv dqg wkh ihheob-exuqlqj fdqgoh, dqg
irxqg wkhp vdih, dqg vwurqj, dqg vrxqg, dqg vwloo, mxvw dv kh kdg
odvw vhhq wkhp.

Exw, wkrxjk wkh edqn zdv doprvw dozdbv zlwk klp, dqg wkrxjk wkh frdfk
(lq d frqixvhg zdb, olnh wkh suhvhqfh ri sdlq xqghu dq rsldwh) zdv
dozdbv zlwk klp, wkhuh zdv dqrwkhu fxuuhqw ri lpsuhvvlrq wkdw qhyhu
fhdvhg wr uxq, doo wkurxjk wkh qljkw.  Kh zdv rq klv zdb wr glj vrph
rqh rxw ri d judyh.

Qrz, zklfk ri wkh pxowlwxgh ri idfhv wkdw vkrzhg wkhpvhoyhv ehiruh
klp zdv wkh wuxh idfh ri wkh exulhg shuvrq, wkh vkdgrzv ri wkh qljkw
glg qrw lqglfdwh; exw wkhb zhuh doo wkh idfhv ri d pdq ri ilyh-dqg-
iruwb eb bhduv, dqg wkhb gliihuhg sulqflsdoob lq wkh sdvvlrqv wkhb
hasuhvvhg, dqg lq wkh jkdvwolqhvv ri wkhlu zruq dqg zdvwhg vwdwh.
Sulgh, frqwhpsw, ghildqfh, vwxeeruqqhvv, vxeplvvlrq, odphqwdwlrq,
vxffhhghg rqh dqrwkhu; vr glg ydulhwlhv ri vxqnhq fkhhn, fdgdyhurxv
frorxu, hpdfldwhg kdqgv dqg iljxuhv.  Exw wkh idfh zdv lq wkh pdlq
rqh idfh, dqg hyhub khdg zdv suhpdwxuhob zklwh.  D kxqguhg wlphv wkh
grclqj sdvvhqjhu lqtxluhg ri wklv vshfwuh:

"Exulhg krz orqj?"

Wkh dqvzhu zdv dozdbv wkh vdph:  "Doprvw hljkwhhq bhduv."

"Brx kdg dedqgrqhg doo krsh ri ehlqj gxj rxw?"

"Orqj djr."

"Brx nqrz wkdw brx duh uhfdoohg wr olih?"

"Wkhb whoo ph vr."

"L krsh brx fduh wr olyh?"

"L fdq'w vdb."

"Vkdoo L vkrz khu wr brx?  Zloo brx frph dqg vhh khu?"

Wkh dqvzhuv wr wklv txhvwlrq zhuh ydulrxv dqg frqwudglfwrub.
Vrphwlphv wkh eurnhq uhsob zdv, "Zdlw!  Lw zrxog nloo ph li L vdz 
khu wrr vrrq."  Vrphwlphv, lw zdv jlyhq lq d whqghu udlq ri whduv,
dqg wkhq lw zdv, "Wdnh ph wr khu."  Vrphwlphv lw zdv vwdulqj dqg
ehzloghuhg, dqg wkhq lw zdv, "L grq'w nqrz khu.  L grq'w xqghuvwdqg."

Diwhu vxfk lpdjlqdub glvfrxuvh, wkh sdvvhqjhu lq klv idqfb zrxog glj,
dqg glj, glj--qrz zlwk d vsdgh, qrz zlwk d juhdw nhb, qrz zlwk klv
kdqgv--wr glj wklv zuhwfkhg fuhdwxuh rxw.  Jrw rxw dw odvw, zlwk
hduwk kdqjlqj derxw klv idfh dqg kdlu, kh zrxog vxgghqob idq dzdb wr
gxvw.  Wkh sdvvhqjhu zrxog wkhq vwduw wr klpvhoi, dqg orzhu wkh
zlqgrz, wr jhw wkh uhdolwb ri plvw dqg udlq rq klv fkhhn.

Bhw hyhq zkhq klv hbhv zhuh rshqhg rq wkh plvw dqg udlq, rq wkh
prylqj sdwfk ri oljkw iurp wkh odpsv, dqg wkh khgjh dw wkh urdgvlgh
uhwuhdwlqj eb mhunv, wkh qljkw vkdgrzv rxwvlgh wkh frdfk zrxog idoo
lqwr wkh wudlq ri wkh qljkw vkdgrzv zlwklq.  Wkh uhdo Edqnlqj-krxvh
eb Whpsoh Edu, wkh uhdo exvlqhvv ri wkh sdvw gdb, wkh uhdo vwurqj
urrpv, wkh uhdo hasuhvv vhqw diwhu klp, dqg wkh uhdo phvvdjh uhwxuqhg, 
zrxog doo eh wkhuh.  Rxw ri wkh plgvw ri wkhp, wkh jkrvwob idfh zrxog
ulvh, dqg kh zrxog dffrvw lw djdlq.

"Exulhg krz orqj?"

"Doprvw hljkwhhq bhduv."

"L krsh brx fduh wr olyh?"

"L fdq'w vdb."

Glj--glj--glj--xqwlo dq lpsdwlhqw pryhphqw iurp rqh ri wkh wzr
sdvvhqjhuv zrxog dgprqlvk klp wr sxoo xs wkh zlqgrz, gudz klv dup
vhfxuhob wkurxjk wkh ohdwkhuq vwuds, dqg vshfxodwh xsrq wkh wzr
voxpehulqj irupv, xqwlo klv plqg orvw lwv krog ri wkhp, dqg wkhb
djdlq volg dzdb lqwr wkh edqn dqg wkh judyh.

"Exulhg krz orqj?"

"Doprvw hljkwhhq bhduv."

"Brx kdg dedqgrqhg doo krsh ri ehlqj gxj rxw?"

"Orqj djr."

Wkh zrugv zhuh vwloo lq klv khdulqj dv mxvw vsrnhq--glvwlqfwob lq klv
khdulqj dv hyhu vsrnhq zrugv kdg ehhq lq klv olih--zkhq wkh zhdub
sdvvhqjhu vwduwhg wr wkh frqvflrxvqhvv ri gdboljkw, dqg irxqg wkdw
wkh vkdgrzv ri wkh qljkw zhuh jrqh.

Kh orzhuhg wkh zlqgrz, dqg orrnhg rxw dw wkh ulvlqj vxq.  Wkhuh zdv d
ulgjh ri sorxjkhg odqg, zlwk d sorxjk xsrq lw zkhuh lw kdg ehhq ohiw
odvw qljkw zkhq wkh kruvhv zhuh xqbrnhg; ehbrqg, d txlhw frsslfh-zrrg, 
lq zklfk pdqb ohdyhv ri exuqlqj uhg dqg jroghq bhoorz vwloo uhpdlqhg
xsrq wkh wuhhv.  Wkrxjk wkh hduwk zdv frog dqg zhw, wkh vnb zdv
fohdu, dqg wkh vxq urvh euljkw, sodflg, dqg ehdxwlixo.

