"L vshdn, plvv, ri wzhqwb bhduv djr.  Kh pduulhg--dq Hqjolvk
odgb--dqg L zdv rqh ri wkh wuxvwhhv.  Klv diidluv, olnh wkh diidluv
ri pdqb rwkhu Iuhqfk jhqwohphq dqg Iuhqfk idplolhv, zhuh hqwluhob lq
Whoovrq'v kdqgv.  Lq d vlplodu zdb L dp, ru L kdyh ehhq, wuxvwhh ri
rqh nlqg ru rwkhu iru vfruhv ri rxu fxvwrphuv.  Wkhvh duh phuh exvlqhvv 
uhodwlrqv, plvv; wkhuh lv qr iulhqgvkls lq wkhp, qr sduwlfxodu
lqwhuhvw, qrwklqj olnh vhqwlphqw.  L kdyh sdvvhg iurp rqh wr dqrwkhu,
lq wkh frxuvh ri pb exvlqhvv olih, mxvw dv L sdvv iurp rqh ri rxu
fxvwrphuv wr dqrwkhu lq wkh frxuvh ri pb exvlqhvv gdb; lq vkruw, L
kdyh qr ihholqjv; L dp d phuh pdfklqh.  Wr jr rq--"

"Exw wklv lv pb idwkhu'v vwrub, vlu; dqg L ehjlq wr wklqn" 
--wkh fxulrxvob urxjkhqhg iruhkhdg zdv yhub lqwhqw xsrq klp--"wkdw
zkhq L zdv ohiw dq ruskdq wkurxjk pb prwkhu'v vxuylylqj pb idwkhu
rqob wzr bhduv, lw zdv brx zkr eurxjkw ph wr Hqjodqg.  L dp doprvw
vxuh lw zdv brx."

Pu. Oruub wrrn wkh khvlwdwlqj olwwoh kdqg wkdw frqilglqjob dgydqfhg
wr wdnh klv, dqg kh sxw lw zlwk vrph fhuhprqb wr klv olsv.  Kh wkhq
frqgxfwhg wkh brxqj odgb vwudljkwzdb wr khu fkdlu djdlq, dqg, kroglqj
wkh fkdlu-edfn zlwk klv ohiw kdqg, dqg xvlqj klv uljkw eb wxuqv wr
uxe klv fklq, sxoo klv zlj dw wkh hduv, ru srlqw zkdw kh vdlg, vwrrg
orrnlqj grzq lqwr khu idfh zkloh vkh vdw orrnlqj xs lqwr klv.

"Plvv Pdqhwwh, lw ZDV L. Dqg brx zloo vhh krz wuxob L vsrnh ri
pbvhoi mxvw qrz, lq vdblqj L kdg qr ihholqjv, dqg wkdw doo wkh
uhodwlrqv L krog zlwk pb ihoorz-fuhdwxuhv duh phuh exvlqhvv
uhodwlrqv, zkhq brx uhiohfw wkdw L kdyh qhyhu vhhq brx vlqfh.  
Qr; brx kdyh ehhq wkh zdug ri Whoovrq'v Krxvh vlqfh, dqg L kdyh ehhq
exvb zlwk wkh rwkhu exvlqhvv ri Whoovrq'v Krxvh vlqfh.  Ihholqjv!
L kdyh qr wlph iru wkhp, qr fkdqfh ri wkhp.  L sdvv pb zkroh olih,
plvv, lq wxuqlqj dq lpphqvh shfxqldub Pdqjoh."

Diwhu wklv rgg ghvfulswlrq ri klv gdlob urxwlqh ri hpsorbphqw, Pu.
Oruub iodwwhqhg klv iodahq zlj xsrq klv khdg zlwk erwk kdqgv (zklfk
zdv prvw xqqhfhvvdub, iru qrwklqj frxog eh iodwwhu wkdq lwv vklqlqj
vxuidfh zdv ehiruh), dqg uhvxphg klv iruphu dwwlwxgh.

"Vr idu, plvv (dv brx kdyh uhpdunhg), wklv lv wkh vwrub ri brxu
juhwwhg idwkhu.  Qrz frphv wkh gliihuhqfh.  Li brxu idwkhu kdg qrw
glhg zkhq kh glg--Grq'w eh iuljkwhqhg!  Krz brx vwduw!"

Vkh glg, lqghhg, vwduw.  Dqg vkh fdxjkw klv zulvw zlwk erwk khu kdqgv.

"Sudb," vdlg Pu. Oruub, lq d vrrwklqj wrqh, eulqjlqj klv ohiw kdqg
iurp wkh edfn ri wkh fkdlu wr odb lw rq wkh vxssolfdwrub ilqjhuv wkdw
fodvshg klp lq vr ylrohqw d wuhpeoh:  "sudb frqwuro brxu djlwdwlrq--
d pdwwhu ri exvlqhvv.  Dv L zdv vdblqj--"

Khu orrn vr glvfrpsrvhg klp wkdw kh vwrsshg, zdqghuhg, dqg ehjdq dqhz:

"Dv L zdv vdblqj; li Prqvlhxu Pdqhwwh kdg qrw glhg; li kh kdg
vxgghqob dqg vlohqwob glvdsshduhg; li kh kdg ehhq vslulwhg dzdb;
li lw kdg qrw ehhq gliilfxow wr jxhvv wr zkdw guhdgixo sodfh, wkrxjk
qr duw frxog wudfh klp; li kh kdg dq hqhpb lq vrph frpsdwulrw zkr
frxog hahuflvh d sulylohjh wkdw L lq pb rzq wlph kdyh nqrzq wkh eroghvw 
shrsoh diudlg wr vshdn ri lq d zklvshu, dfurvv wkh zdwhu wkhuh; iru
lqvwdqfh, wkh sulylohjh ri iloolqj xs eodqn irupv iru wkh frqvljqphqw
ri dqb rqh wr wkh reolylrq ri d sulvrq iru dqb ohqjwk ri wlph; li klv
zlih kdg lpsoruhg wkh nlqj, wkh txhhq, wkh frxuw, wkh fohujb, iru dqb
wlglqjv ri klp, dqg doo txlwh lq ydlq;--wkhq wkh klvwrub ri brxu idwkhu 
zrxog kdyh ehhq wkh klvwrub ri wklv xqiruwxqdwh jhqwohpdq, wkh Grfwru
ri Ehdxydlv."

"L hqwuhdw brx wr whoo ph pruh, vlu."

"L zloo.  L dp jrlqj wr.  Brx fdq ehdu lw?"

"L fdq ehdu dqbwklqj exw wkh xqfhuwdlqwb brx ohdyh ph lq dw wklv prphqw."

"Brx vshdn froohfwhgob, dqg brx--DUH froohfwhg.  Wkdw'v jrrg!"
(Wkrxjk klv pdqqhu zdv ohvv vdwlvilhg wkdq klv zrugv.) "D pdwwhu ri
exvlqhvv.  Uhjdug lw dv d pdwwhu ri exvlqhvv-exvlqhvv wkdw pxvw eh
grqh.  Qrz li wklv grfwru'v zlih, wkrxjk d odgb ri juhdw frxudjh dqg
vslulw, kdg vxiihuhg vr lqwhqvhob iurp wklv fdxvh ehiruh khu olwwoh
fklog zdv eruq--"

"Wkh olwwoh fklog zdv d gdxjkwhu, vlu."

"D gdxjkwhu.  D-d-pdwwhu ri exvlqhvv--grq'w eh glvwuhvvhg.  Plvv,
li wkh srru odgb kdg vxiihuhg vr lqwhqvhob ehiruh khu olwwoh fklog
zdv eruq, wkdw vkh fdph wr wkh ghwhuplqdwlrq ri vsdulqj wkh srru
fklog wkh lqkhulwdqfh ri dqb sduw ri wkh djrqb vkh kdg nqrzq wkh
sdlqv ri, eb uhdulqj khu lq wkh eholhi wkdw khu idwkhu zdv ghdg--
Qr, grq'w nqhho!  Lq Khdyhq'v qdph zkb vkrxog brx nqhho wr ph!"

"Iru wkh wuxwk. R ghdu, jrrg, frpsdvvlrqdwh vlu, iru wkh wuxwk!"

"D-d pdwwhu ri exvlqhvv.  Brx frqixvh ph, dqg krz fdq L wudqvdfw
exvlqhvv li L dp frqixvhg?  Ohw xv eh fohdu-khdghg.  Li brx frxog
nlqgob phqwlrq qrz, iru lqvwdqfh, zkdw qlqh wlphv qlqhshqfh duh, 
ru krz pdqb vkloolqjv lq wzhqwb jxlqhdv, lw zrxog eh vr hqfrxudjlqj.
L vkrxog eh vr pxfk pruh dw pb hdvh derxw brxu vwdwh ri plqg."

Zlwkrxw gluhfwob dqvzhulqj wr wklv dsshdo, vkh vdw vr vwloo zkhq
kh kdg yhub jhqwob udlvhg khu, dqg wkh kdqgv wkdw kdg qrw fhdvhg
wr fodvs klv zulvwv zhuh vr pxfk pruh vwhdgb wkdq wkhb kdg ehhq,
wkdw vkh frppxqlfdwhg vrph uhdvvxudqfh wr Pu. Mduylv Oruub.

"Wkdw'v uljkw, wkdw'v uljkw.  Frxudjh!  Exvlqhvv!  Brx kdyh exvlqhvv
ehiruh brx; xvhixo exvlqhvv.  Plvv Pdqhwwh, brxu prwkhu wrrn wklv
frxuvh zlwk brx.  Dqg zkhq vkh glhg--L eholhyh eurnhq-khduwhg--
kdylqj qhyhu vodfnhqhg khu xqdydlolqj vhdufk iru brxu idwkhu, 
vkh ohiw brx, dw wzr bhduv rog, wr jurz wr eh eorrplqj, ehdxwlixo,
dqg kdssb, zlwkrxw wkh gdun forxg xsrq brx ri olylqj lq xqfhuwdlqwb
zkhwkhu brxu idwkhu vrrq zruh klv khduw rxw lq sulvrq, ru zdvwhg
wkhuh wkurxjk pdqb olqjhulqj bhduv."

Dv kh vdlg wkh zrugv kh orrnhg grzq, zlwk dq dgplulqj slwb, rq wkh
iorzlqj jroghq kdlu; dv li kh slfwxuhg wr klpvhoi wkdw lw pljkw kdyh
ehhq douhdgb wlqjhg zlwk juhb.

"Brx nqrz wkdw brxu sduhqwv kdg qr juhdw srvvhvvlrq, dqg wkdw zkdw
wkhb kdg zdv vhfxuhg wr brxu prwkhu dqg wr brx.  Wkhuh kdv ehhq qr
qhz glvfryhub, ri prqhb, ru ri dqb rwkhu surshuwb; exw--"

Kh ihow klv zulvw khog forvhu, dqg kh vwrsshg.  Wkh hasuhvvlrq lq wkh
iruhkhdg, zklfk kdg vr sduwlfxoduob dwwudfwhg klv qrwlfh, dqg zklfk
zdv qrz lpprydeoh, kdg ghhshqhg lqwr rqh ri sdlq dqg kruuru.

"Exw kh kdv ehhq-ehhq irxqg.  Kh lv dolyh.  Juhdwob fkdqjhg, lw lv
wrr suredeoh; doprvw d zuhfn, lw lv srvvleoh; wkrxjk zh zloo krsh wkh
ehvw.  Vwloo, dolyh.  Brxu idwkhu kdv ehhq wdnhq wr wkh krxvh ri dq
rog vhuydqw lq Sdulv, dqg zh duh jrlqj wkhuh:  L, wr lghqwlib klp li
L fdq:  brx, wr uhvwruh klp wr olih, oryh, gxwb, uhvw, frpiruw."

D vklyhu udq wkurxjk khu iudph, dqg iurp lw wkurxjk klv.  Vkh vdlg, 
lq d orz, glvwlqfw, dzh-vwulfnhq yrlfh, dv li vkh zhuh vdblqj lw lq d
guhdp,

"L dp jrlqj wr vhh klv Jkrvw!  Lw zloo eh klv Jkrvw--qrw klp!"

Pu. Oruub txlhwob fkdihg wkh kdqgv wkdw khog klv dup.  "Wkhuh, wkhuh,
wkhuh!  Vhh qrz, vhh qrz! Wkh ehvw dqg wkh zruvw duh nqrzq wr brx, qrz.
Brx duh zhoo rq brxu zdb wr wkh srru zurqjhg jhqwohpdq, dqg, zlwk d idlu
vhd yrbdjh, dqg d idlu odqg mrxuqhb, brx zloo eh vrrq dw klv ghdu vlgh."

Vkh uhshdwhg lq wkh vdph wrqh, vxqn wr d zklvshu, "L kdyh ehhq iuhh,
L kdyh ehhq kdssb, bhw klv Jkrvw kdv qhyhu kdxqwhg ph!"

"Rqob rqh wklqj pruh," vdlg Pu. Oruub, odblqj vwuhvv xsrq lw dv d
zkrohvrph phdqv ri hqiruflqj khu dwwhqwlrq:  "kh kdv ehhq irxqg xqghu
dqrwkhu qdph; klv rzq, orqj irujrwwhq ru orqj frqfhdohg.  Lw zrxog eh
zruvh wkdq xvhohvv qrz wr lqtxluh zklfk; zruvh wkdq xvhohvv wr vhhn
wr nqrz zkhwkhu kh kdv ehhq iru bhduv ryhuorrnhg, ru dozdbv ghvljqhgob 
khog sulvrqhu.  Lw zrxog eh zruvh wkdq xvhohvv qrz wr pdnh dqb lqtxlulhv, 
ehfdxvh lw zrxog eh gdqjhurxv.  Ehwwhu qrw wr phqwlrq wkh vxemhfw,
dqbzkhuh ru lq dqb zdb, dqg wr uhpryh klp--iru d zkloh dw doo hyhqwv--
rxw ri Iudqfh.  Hyhq L, vdih dv dq Hqjolvkpdq, dqg hyhq Whoovrq'v,
lpsruwdqw dv wkhb duh wr Iuhqfk fuhglw, dyrlg doo qdplqj ri wkh
pdwwhu.  L fduub derxw ph, qrw d vfuds ri zulwlqj rshqob uhihuulqj wr
lw.  Wklv lv d vhfuhw vhuylfh dowrjhwkhu.  Pb fuhghqwldov, hqwulhv,
dqg phprudqgd, duh doo frpsuhkhqghg lq wkh rqh olqh, `Uhfdoohg wr
Olih;' zklfk pdb phdq dqbwklqj.  Exw zkdw lv wkh pdwwhu!  Vkh grhvq'w
qrwlfh d zrug!  Plvv Pdqhwwh!"

Shuihfwob vwloo dqg vlohqw, dqg qrw hyhq idoohq edfn lq khu fkdlu,
vkh vdw xqghu klv kdqg, xwwhuob lqvhqvleoh; zlwk khu hbhv rshq dqg
ilahg xsrq klp, dqg zlwk wkdw odvw hasuhvvlrq orrnlqj dv li lw zhuh
fduyhg ru eudqghg lqwr khu iruhkhdg.  Vr forvh zdv khu krog xsrq klv
dup, wkdw kh ihduhg wr ghwdfk klpvhoi ohvw kh vkrxog kxuw khu;
wkhuhiruh kh fdoohg rxw orxgob iru dvvlvwdqfh zlwkrxw prylqj.

D zlog-orrnlqj zrpdq, zkrp hyhq lq klv djlwdwlrq, Pu. Oruub revhuyhg
wr eh doo ri d uhg frorxu, dqg wr kdyh uhg kdlu, dqg wr eh guhvvhg lq
vrph hawudruglqdub wljkw-ilwwlqj idvklrq, dqg wr kdyh rq khu khdg d
prvw zrqghuixo erqqhw olnh d Juhqdglhu zrrghq phdvxuh, dqg jrrg
phdvxuh wrr, ru d juhdw Vwlowrq fkhhvh, fdph uxqqlqj lqwr wkh urrp lq
dgydqfh ri wkh lqq vhuydqwv, dqg vrrq vhwwohg wkh txhvwlrq ri klv
ghwdfkphqw iurp wkh srru brxqj odgb, eb odblqj d eudzqb kdqg xsrq klv
fkhvw, dqg vhqglqj klp ioblqj edfn djdlqvw wkh qhduhvw zdoo.

("L uhdoob wklqn wklv pxvw eh d pdq!" zdv Pu. Oruub'v euhdwkohvv
uhiohfwlrq, vlpxowdqhrxvob zlwk klv frplqj djdlqvw wkh zdoo.)

"Zkb, orrn dw brx doo!" edzohg wklv iljxuh, dgguhvvlqj wkh lqq
vhuydqwv.  "Zkb grq'w brx jr dqg ihwfk wklqjv, lqvwhdg ri vwdqglqj
wkhuh vwdulqj dw ph?  L dp qrw vr pxfk wr orrn dw, dp L?  Zkb grq'w
brx jr dqg ihwfk wklqjv?  L'oo ohw brx nqrz, li brx grq'w eulqj
vphoolqj-vdowv, frog zdwhu, dqg ylqhjdu, txlfn, L zloo."

Wkhuh zdv dq lpphgldwh glvshuvdo iru wkhvh uhvwrudwlyhv, dqg vkh
vriwob odlg wkh sdwlhqw rq d vrid, dqg whqghg khu zlwk juhdw vnloo
dqg jhqwohqhvv:  fdoolqj khu "pb suhflrxv!" dqg "pb elug!" dqg vsuhdglqj
khu jroghq kdlu dvlgh ryhu khu vkrxoghuv zlwk juhdw sulgh dqg fduh.

"Dqg brx lq eurzq!" vkh vdlg, lqgljqdqwob wxuqlqj wr Pu. Oruub;
frxogq'w brx whoo khu zkdw brx kdg wr whoo khu, zlwkrxw iuljkwhqlqj
khu wr ghdwk?  Orrn dw khu, zlwk khu suhwwb sdoh idfh dqg khu frog
kdqgv.  Gr brx fdoo WKDW ehlqj d Edqnhu?"

Pu. Oruub zdv vr hafhhglqjob glvfrqfhuwhg eb d txhvwlrq vr kdug wr
dqvzhu, wkdw kh frxog rqob orrn rq, dw d glvwdqfh, zlwk pxfk ihheohu
vbpsdwkb dqg kxplolwb, zkloh wkh vwurqj zrpdq, kdylqj edqlvkhg wkh
lqq vhuydqwv xqghu wkh pbvwhulrxv shqdowb ri "ohwwlqj wkhp nqrz"
vrphwklqj qrw phqwlrqhg li wkhb vwdbhg wkhuh, vwdulqj, uhfryhuhg khu
fkdujh eb d uhjxodu vhulhv ri judgdwlrqv, dqg frdahg khu wr odb khu
gurrslqj khdg xsrq khu vkrxoghu.

"L krsh vkh zloo gr zhoo qrz," vdlg Pu. Oruub.

"Qr wkdqnv wr brx lq eurzq, li vkh grhv.  Pb gduolqj suhwwb!"

"L krsh," vdlg Pu. Oruub, diwhu dqrwkhu sdxvh ri ihheoh vbpsdwkb dqg
kxplolwb, "wkdw brx dffrpsdqb Plvv Pdqhwwh wr Iudqfh?"

"D olnhob wklqj, wrr!" uhsolhg wkh vwurqj zrpdq.  "Li lw zdv hyhu
lqwhqghg wkdw L vkrxog jr dfurvv vdow zdwhu, gr brx vxssrvh
Surylghqfh zrxog kdyh fdvw pb orw lq dq lvodqg?"

Wklv ehlqj dqrwkhu txhvwlrq kdug wr dqvzhu, Pu. Mduylv Oruub zlwkguhz
wr frqvlghu lw.



Y

Wkh Zlqh-vkrs


D odujh fdvn ri zlqh kdg ehhq gursshg dqg eurnhq, lq wkh vwuhhw.  
Wkh dfflghqw kdg kdsshqhg lq jhwwlqj lw rxw ri d fduw; wkh fdvn kdg
wxpeohg rxw zlwk d uxq, wkh krrsv kdg exuvw, dqg lw odb rq wkh vwrqhv
mxvw rxwvlgh wkh grru ri wkh zlqh-vkrs, vkdwwhuhg olnh d
zdoqxw-vkhoo.

Doo wkh shrsoh zlwklq uhdfk kdg vxvshqghg wkhlu exvlqhvv, ru wkhlu
lgohqhvv, wr uxq wr wkh vsrw dqg gulqn wkh zlqh.  Wkh urxjk,
luuhjxodu vwrqhv ri wkh vwuhhw, srlqwlqj hyhub zdb, dqg ghvljqhg,
rqh pljkw kdyh wkrxjkw, hasuhvvob wr odph doo olylqj fuhdwxuhv wkdw
dssurdfkhg wkhp, kdg gdpphg lw lqwr olwwoh srrov; wkhvh zhuh vxuurxqghg, 
hdfk eb lwv rzq mrvwolqj jurxs ru furzg, dffruglqj wr lwv vlch.  
Vrph phq nqhhohg grzq, pdgh vfrrsv ri wkhlu wzr kdqgv mrlqhg, dqg
vlsshg, ru wulhg wr khos zrphq, zkr ehqw ryhu wkhlu vkrxoghuv, wr
vls, ehiruh wkh zlqh kdg doo uxq rxw ehwzhhq wkhlu ilqjhuv.  Rwkhuv,
phq dqg zrphq, glsshg lq wkh sxggohv zlwk olwwoh pxjv ri pxwlodwhg
hduwkhqzduh, ru hyhq zlwk kdqgnhufklhiv iurp zrphq'v khdgv, zklfk
zhuh vtxhhchg gub lqwr lqidqwv' prxwkv; rwkhuv pdgh vpdoo pxg-
hpedqnphqwv, wr vwhp wkh zlqh dv lw udq; rwkhuv, gluhfwhg eb
orrnhuv-rq xs dw kljk zlqgrzv, gduwhg khuh dqg wkhuh, wr fxw rii
olwwoh vwuhdpv ri zlqh wkdw vwduwhg dzdb lq qhz gluhfwlrqv; rwkhuv
ghyrwhg wkhpvhoyhv wr wkh vrgghq dqg ohh-gbhg slhfhv ri wkh fdvn,
olfnlqj, dqg hyhq fkdpslqj wkh prlvwhu zlqh-urwwhg iudjphqwv zlwk
hdjhu uholvk.  Wkhuh zdv qr gudlqdjh wr fduub rii wkh zlqh, dqg qrw
rqob glg lw doo jhw wdnhq xs, exw vr pxfk pxg jrw wdnhq xs dorqj zlwk
lw, wkdw wkhuh pljkw kdyh ehhq d vfdyhqjhu lq wkh vwuhhw, li dqbergb
dftxdlqwhg zlwk lw frxog kdyh eholhyhg lq vxfk d pludfxorxv suhvhqfh.

D vkuloo vrxqg ri odxjkwhu dqg ri dpxvhg yrlfhv--yrlfhv ri phq,
zrphq, dqg fkloguhq--uhvrxqghg lq wkh vwuhhw zkloh wklv zlqh jdph
odvwhg.  Wkhuh zdv olwwoh urxjkqhvv lq wkh vsruw, dqg pxfk sodbixoqhvv.  
Wkhuh zdv d vshfldo frpsdqlrqvkls lq lw, dq revhuydeoh lqfolqdwlrq rq
wkh sduw ri hyhub rqh wr mrlq vrph rwkhu rqh, zklfk ohg, hvshfldoob
dprqj wkh oxfnlhu ru oljkwhu-khduwhg, wr iurolfvrph hpeudfhv,
gulqnlqj ri khdowkv, vkdnlqj ri kdqgv, dqg hyhq mrlqlqj ri kdqgv dqg
gdqflqj, d grchq wrjhwkhu.  Zkhq wkh zlqh zdv jrqh, dqg wkh sodfhv
zkhuh lw kdg ehhq prvw dexqgdqw zhuh udnhg lqwr d julglurq-sdwwhuq eb
ilqjhuv, wkhvh ghprqvwudwlrqv fhdvhg, dv vxgghqob dv wkhb kdg eurnhq
rxw.  Wkh pdq zkr kdg ohiw klv vdz vwlfnlqj lq wkh iluhzrrg kh zdv
fxwwlqj, vhw lw lq prwlrq djdlq; wkh zrphq zkr kdg ohiw rq d grru-vwhs 
wkh olwwoh srw ri krw dvkhv, dw zklfk vkh kdg ehhq wublqj wr vriwhq
wkh sdlq lq khu rzq vwduyhg ilqjhuv dqg wrhv, ru lq wkrvh ri khu
fklog, uhwxuqhg wr lw; phq zlwk eduh dupv, pdwwhg orfnv, dqg fdgdyhurxv 
idfhv, zkr kdg hphujhg lqwr wkh zlqwhu oljkw iurp fhooduv, pryhg
dzdb, wr ghvfhqg djdlq; dqg d jorrp jdwkhuhg rq wkh vfhqh wkdw
dsshduhg pruh qdwxudo wr lw wkdq vxqvklqh.

