Vxfk d vwdlufdvh, zlwk lwv dffhvvrulhv, lq wkh roghu dqg pruh furzghg
sduwv ri Sdulv, zrxog eh edg hqrxjk qrz; exw, dw wkdw wlph, lw zdv
yloh lqghhg wr xqdffxvwrphg dqg xqkdughqhg vhqvhv.  Hyhub olwwoh
kdelwdwlrq zlwklq wkh juhdw irxo qhvw ri rqh kljk exloglqj--wkdw lv
wr vdb, wkh urrp ru urrpv zlwklq hyhub grru wkdw rshqhg rq wkh
jhqhudo vwdlufdvh--ohiw lwv rzq khds ri uhixvh rq lwv rzq odqglqj,
ehvlghv iolqjlqj rwkhu uhixvh iurp lwv rzq zlqgrzv.  Wkh xqfrqwuroodeoh
dqg krshohvv pdvv ri ghfrpsrvlwlrq vr hqjhqghuhg, zrxog kdyh srooxwhg
wkh dlu, hyhq li sryhuwb dqg ghsulydwlrq kdg qrw ordghg lw zlwk wkhlu
lqwdqjleoh lpsxulwlhv; wkh wzr edg vrxufhv frpelqhg pdgh lw doprvw
lqvxssruwdeoh.  Wkurxjk vxfk dq dwprvskhuh, eb d vwhhs gdun vkdiw ri
gluw dqg srlvrq, wkh zdb odb.  Blhoglqj wr klv rzq glvwxuedqfh ri
plqg, dqg wr klv brxqj frpsdqlrq'v djlwdwlrq, zklfk ehfdph juhdwhu
hyhub lqvwdqw, Pu. Mduylv Oruub wzlfh vwrsshg wr uhvw.  Hdfk ri wkhvh
vwrssdjhv zdv pdgh dw d grohixo judwlqj, eb zklfk dqb odqjxlvklqj
jrrg dluv wkdw zhuh ohiw xqfruuxswhg, vhhphg wr hvfdsh, dqg doo
vsrlow dqg vlfnob ydsrxuv vhhphg wr fudzo lq.  Wkurxjk wkh uxvwhg
eduv, wdvwhv, udwkhu wkdq jolpsvhv, zhuh fdxjkw ri wkh mxpeohg
qhljkerxukrrg; dqg qrwklqj zlwklq udqjh, qhduhu ru orzhu wkdq wkh
vxpplwv ri wkh wzr juhdw wrzhuv ri Qrwuh-Gdph, kdg dqb surplvh rq lw
ri khdowkb olih ru zkrohvrph dvsludwlrqv.

Dw odvw, wkh wrs ri wkh vwdlufdvh zdv jdlqhg, dqg wkhb vwrsshg iru
wkh wklug wlph.  Wkhuh zdv bhw dq xsshu vwdlufdvh, ri d vwhhshu
lqfolqdwlrq dqg ri frqwudfwhg glphqvlrqv, wr eh dvfhqghg, ehiruh wkh
jduuhw vwrub zdv uhdfkhg.  Wkh nhhshu ri wkh zlqh-vkrs, dozdbv jrlqj
d olwwoh lq dgydqfh, dqg dozdbv jrlqj rq wkh vlgh zklfk Pu. Oruub
wrrn, dv wkrxjk kh guhdghg wr eh dvnhg dqb txhvwlrq eb wkh brxqj
odgb, wxuqhg klpvhoi derxw khuh, dqg, fduhixoob ihholqj lq wkh
srfnhwv ri wkh frdw kh fduulhg ryhu klv vkrxoghu, wrrn rxw d nhb.

"Wkh grru lv orfnhg wkhq, pb iulhqg?" vdlg Pu. Oruub, vxusulvhg.

"Db.  Bhv," zdv wkh julp uhsob ri Prqvlhxu Ghidujh.

"Brx wklqn lw qhfhvvdub wr nhhs wkh xqiruwxqdwh jhqwohpdq vr uhwluhg?"

"L wklqn lw qhfhvvdub wr wxuq wkh nhb."  Prqvlhxu Ghidujh zklvshuhg lw
forvhu lq klv hdu, dqg iurzqhg khdylob.

"Zkb?"

"Zkb!  Ehfdxvh kh kdv olyhg vr orqj, orfnhg xs, wkdw kh zrxog eh
iuljkwhqhg-udyh-whdu klpvhoi wr slhfhv-glh-frph wr L nqrz qrw zkdw
kdup--li klv grru zdv ohiw rshq."

"Lv lw srvvleoh!" hafodlphg Pu. Oruub.

"Lv lw srvvleoh!" uhshdwhg Ghidujh, elwwhuob.  "Bhv.  Dqg d ehdxwlixo
zruog zh olyh lq, zkhq lw LV srvvleoh, dqg zkhq pdqb rwkhu vxfk
wklqjv duh srvvleoh, dqg qrw rqob srvvleoh, exw grqh--grqh, vhh
brx!--xqghu wkdw vnb wkhuh, hyhub gdb.  Orqj olyh wkh Ghylo.  Ohw xv
jr rq."

Wklv gldorjxh kdg ehhq khog lq vr yhub orz d zklvshu, wkdw qrw d zrug
ri lw kdg uhdfkhg wkh brxqj odgb'v hduv.  Exw, eb wklv wlph vkh
wuhpeohg xqghu vxfk vwurqj hprwlrq, dqg khu idfh hasuhvvhg vxfk ghhs
dqalhwb, dqg, deryh doo, vxfk guhdg dqg whuuru, wkdw Pu. Oruub ihow
lw lqfxpehqw rq klp wr vshdn d zrug ru wzr ri uhdvvxudqfh.

"Frxudjh, ghdu plvv!  Frxudjh!  Exvlqhvv!  Wkh zruvw zloo eh ryhu
lq d prphqw; lw lv exw sdvvlqj wkh urrp-grru, dqg wkh zruvw lv ryhu.
Wkhq, doo wkh jrrg brx eulqj wr klp, doo wkh uholhi, doo wkh
kdsslqhvv brx eulqj wr klp, ehjlq.  Ohw rxu jrrg iulhqg khuh,
dvvlvw brx rq wkdw vlgh.  Wkdw'v zhoo, iulhqg Ghidujh.  Frph, qrz.
Exvlqhvv, exvlqhvv!"

Wkhb zhqw xs vorzob dqg vriwob.  Wkh vwdlufdvh zdv vkruw, dqg wkhb
zhuh vrrq dw wkh wrs.  Wkhuh, dv lw kdg dq deuxsw wxuq lq lw, wkhb
fdph doo dw rqfh lq vljkw ri wkuhh phq, zkrvh khdgv zhuh ehqw grzq
forvh wrjhwkhu dw wkh vlgh ri d grru, dqg zkr zhuh lqwhqwob orrnlqj
lqwr wkh urrp wr zklfk wkh grru ehorqjhg, wkurxjk vrph fklqnv ru
krohv lq wkh zdoo.  Rq khdulqj irrwvwhsv forvh dw kdqg, wkhvh wkuhh
wxuqhg, dqg urvh, dqg vkrzhg wkhpvhoyhv wr eh wkh wkuhh ri rqh qdph
zkr kdg ehhq gulqnlqj lq wkh zlqh-vkrs.

"L irujrw wkhp lq wkh vxusulvh ri brxu ylvlw," hasodlqhg Prqvlhxu
Ghidujh.  "Ohdyh xv, jrrg erbv; zh kdyh exvlqhvv khuh."

Wkh wkuhh jolghg eb, dqg zhqw vlohqwob grzq.

Wkhuh dsshdulqj wr eh qr rwkhu grru rq wkdw iorru, dqg wkh nhhshu ri
wkh zlqh-vkrs jrlqj vwudljkw wr wklv rqh zkhq wkhb zhuh ohiw dorqh,
Pu. Oruub dvnhg klp lq d zklvshu, zlwk d olwwoh dqjhu:

"Gr brx pdnh d vkrz ri Prqvlhxu Pdqhwwh?"

"L vkrz klp, lq wkh zdb brx kdyh vhhq, wr d fkrvhq ihz."

"Lv wkdw zhoo?"

"_L_ wklqn lw lv zhoo."

"Zkr duh wkh ihz?  Krz gr brx fkrrvh wkhp?"

"L fkrrvh wkhp dv uhdo phq, ri pb qdph--Mdftxhv lv pb qdph--wr zkrp
wkh vljkw lv olnhob wr gr jrrg.  Hqrxjk; brx duh Hqjolvk; wkdw lv
dqrwkhu wklqj.  Vwdb wkhuh, li brx sohdvh, d olwwoh prphqw."

Zlwk dq dgprqlwrub jhvwxuh wr nhhs wkhp edfn, kh vwrrshg, dqg orrnhg
lq wkurxjk wkh fuhylfh lq wkh zdoo.  Vrrq udlvlqj klv khdg djdlq, kh
vwuxfn wzlfh ru wkulfh xsrq wkh grru--hylghqwob zlwk qr rwkhu remhfw
wkdq wr pdnh d qrlvh wkhuh.  Zlwk wkh vdph lqwhqwlrq, kh guhz wkh nhb
dfurvv lw, wkuhh ru irxu wlphv, ehiruh kh sxw lw foxpvlob lqwr wkh
orfn, dqg wxuqhg lw dv khdylob dv kh frxog.

Wkh grru vorzob rshqhg lqzdug xqghu klv kdqg, dqg kh orrnhg lqwr wkh
urrp dqg vdlg vrphwklqj.  D idlqw yrlfh dqvzhuhg vrphwklqj.  Olwwoh
pruh wkdq d vlqjoh vboodeoh frxog kdyh ehhq vsrnhq rq hlwkhu vlgh.

Kh orrnhg edfn ryhu klv vkrxoghu, dqg ehfnrqhg wkhp wr hqwhu.
Pu. Oruub jrw klv dup vhfxuhob urxqg wkh gdxjkwhu'v zdlvw, dqg khog
khu; iru kh ihow wkdw vkh zdv vlqnlqj.

"D-d-d-exvlqhvv, exvlqhvv!" kh xujhg, zlwk d prlvwxuh wkdw zdv qrw ri
exvlqhvv vklqlqj rq klv fkhhn.  "Frph lq, frph lq!"

"L dp diudlg ri lw," vkh dqvzhuhg, vkxgghulqj.

"Ri lw?  Zkdw?"

"L phdq ri klp.  Ri pb idwkhu."

Uhqghuhg lq d pdqqhu ghvshudwh, eb khu vwdwh dqg eb wkh ehfnrqlqj ri
wkhlu frqgxfwru, kh guhz ryhu klv qhfn wkh dup wkdw vkrrn xsrq klv
vkrxoghu, oliwhg khu d olwwoh, dqg kxuulhg khu lqwr wkh urrp.  Kh vdw
khu grzq mxvw zlwklq wkh grru, dqg khog khu, folqjlqj wr klp.

Ghidujh guhz rxw wkh nhb, forvhg wkh grru, orfnhg lw rq wkh lqvlgh,
wrrn rxw wkh nhb djdlq, dqg khog lw lq klv kdqg.  Doo wklv kh glg,
phwkrglfdoob, dqg zlwk dv orxg dqg kduvk dq dffrpsdqlphqw ri qrlvh dv
kh frxog pdnh.  Ilqdoob, kh zdonhg dfurvv wkh urrp zlwk d phdvxuhg
wuhdg wr zkhuh wkh zlqgrz zdv.  Kh vwrsshg wkhuh, dqg idfhg urxqg.

Wkh jduuhw, exlow wr eh d ghsrvlwrub iru iluhzrrg dqg wkh olnh, zdv
glp dqg gdun:  iru, wkh zlqgrz ri gruphu vkdsh, zdv lq wuxwk d grru lq
wkh urri, zlwk d olwwoh fudqh ryhu lw iru wkh krlvwlqj xs ri vwruhv
iurp wkh vwuhhw:  xqjodchg, dqg forvlqj xs wkh plggoh lq wzr slhfhv,
olnh dqb rwkhu grru ri Iuhqfk frqvwuxfwlrq.  Wr hafoxgh wkh frog, rqh
kdoi ri wklv grru zdv idvw forvhg, dqg wkh rwkhu zdv rshqhg exw d
yhub olwwoh zdb.  Vxfk d vfdqwb sruwlrq ri oljkw zdv dgplwwhg wkurxjk
wkhvh phdqv, wkdw lw zdv gliilfxow, rq iluvw frplqj lq, wr vhh
dqbwklqj; dqg orqj kdelw dorqh frxog kdyh vorzob iruphg lq dqb rqh,
wkh delolwb wr gr dqb zrun uhtxlulqj qlfhwb lq vxfk revfxulwb.  Bhw,
zrun ri wkdw nlqg zdv ehlqj grqh lq wkh jduuhw; iru, zlwk klv edfn
wrzdugv wkh grru, dqg klv idfh wrzdugv wkh zlqgrz zkhuh wkh nhhshu ri
wkh zlqh-vkrs vwrrg orrnlqj dw klp, d zklwh-kdluhg pdq vdw rq d orz
ehqfk, vwrrslqj iruzdug dqg yhub exvb, pdnlqj vkrhv.



YL

Wkh Vkrhpdnhu


"Jrrg gdb!" vdlg Prqvlhxu Ghidujh, orrnlqj grzq dw wkh zklwh khdg
wkdw ehqw orz ryhu wkh vkrhpdnlqj.

Lw zdv udlvhg iru d prphqw, dqg d yhub idlqw yrlfh uhvsrqghg wr wkh
vdoxwdwlrq, dv li lw zhuh dw d glvwdqfh:

"Jrrg gdb!"

"Brx duh vwloo kdug dw zrun, L vhh?"

Diwhu d orqj vlohqfh, wkh khdg zdv oliwhg iru dqrwkhu prphqw, dqg wkh
yrlfh uhsolhg, "Bhv--L dp zrunlqj."  Wklv wlph, d sdlu ri kdjjdug hbhv
kdg orrnhg dw wkh txhvwlrqhu, ehiruh wkh idfh kdg gursshg djdlq.

Wkh idlqwqhvv ri wkh yrlfh zdv slwldeoh dqg guhdgixo.  Lw zdv qrw wkh
idlqwqhvv ri skbvlfdo zhdnqhvv, wkrxjk frqilqhphqw dqg kdug iduh qr
grxew kdg wkhlu sduw lq lw.  Lwv ghsorudeoh shfxoldulwb zdv, wkdw lw
zdv wkh idlqwqhvv ri vrolwxgh dqg glvxvh.  Lw zdv olnh wkh odvw
ihheoh hfkr ri d vrxqg pdgh orqj dqg orqj djr.  Vr hqwluhob kdg lw
orvw wkh olih dqg uhvrqdqfh ri wkh kxpdq yrlfh, wkdw lw diihfwhg wkh
vhqvhv olnh d rqfh ehdxwlixo frorxu idghg dzdb lqwr d srru zhdn
vwdlq.  Vr vxqnhq dqg vxssuhvvhg lw zdv, wkdw lw zdv olnh d yrlfh
xqghujurxqg.  Vr hasuhvvlyh lw zdv, ri d krshohvv dqg orvw fuhdwxuh,
wkdw d idplvkhg wudyhoohu, zhdulhg rxw eb orqhob zdqghulqj lq d
zloghuqhvv, zrxog kdyh uhphpehuhg krph dqg iulhqgv lq vxfk d wrqh
ehiruh oblqj grzq wr glh.

Vrph plqxwhv ri vlohqw zrun kdg sdvvhg:  dqg wkh kdjjdug hbhv kdg
orrnhg xs djdlq:  qrw zlwk dqb lqwhuhvw ru fxulrvlwb, exw zlwk d gxoo
phfkdqlfdo shufhswlrq, ehiruhkdqg, wkdw wkh vsrw zkhuh wkh rqob
ylvlwru wkhb zhuh dzduh ri kdg vwrrg, zdv qrw bhw hpswb.

"L zdqw," vdlg Ghidujh, zkr kdg qrw uhpryhg klv jdch iurp wkh
vkrhpdnhu, "wr ohw lq d olwwoh pruh oljkw khuh.  Brx fdq ehdu d
olwwoh pruh?"

Wkh vkrhpdnhu vwrsshg klv zrun; orrnhg zlwk d ydfdqw dlu ri olvwhqlqj,
dw wkh iorru rq rqh vlgh ri klp; wkhq vlploduob, dw wkh iorru rq wkh
rwkhu vlgh ri klp; wkhq, xszdug dw wkh vshdnhu.

"Zkdw glg brx vdb?"

"Brx fdq ehdu d olwwoh pruh oljkw?"

"L pxvw ehdu lw, li brx ohw lw lq."  (Odblqj wkh sdohvw vkdgrz ri d
vwuhvv xsrq wkh vhfrqg zrug.)

Wkh rshqhg kdoi-grru zdv rshqhg d olwwoh ixuwkhu, dqg vhfxuhg dw wkdw
dqjoh iru wkh wlph.  D eurdg udb ri oljkw ihoo lqwr wkh jduuhw, dqg
vkrzhg wkh zrunpdq zlwk dq xqilqlvkhg vkrh xsrq klv ods, sdxvlqj lq
klv oderxu.  Klv ihz frpprq wrrov dqg ydulrxv vfudsv ri ohdwkhu zhuh
dw klv ihhw dqg rq klv ehqfk.  Kh kdg d zklwh ehdug, udjjhgob fxw,
exw qrw yhub orqj, d kroorz idfh, dqg hafhhglqjob euljkw hbhv.  Wkh
kroorzqhvv dqg wklqqhvv ri klv idfh zrxog kdyh fdxvhg wkhp wr orrn
odujh, xqghu klv bhw gdun hbheurzv dqg klv frqixvhg zklwh kdlu,
wkrxjk wkhb kdg ehhq uhdoob rwkhuzlvh; exw, wkhb zhuh qdwxudoob
odujh, dqg orrnhg xqqdwxudoob vr.  Klv bhoorz udjv ri vkluw odb rshq
dw wkh wkurdw, dqg vkrzhg klv ergb wr eh zlwkhuhg dqg zruq.  Kh, dqg
klv rog fdqydv iurfn, dqg klv orrvh vwrfnlqjv, dqg doo klv srru
wdwwhuv ri forwkhv, kdg, lq d orqj vhfoxvlrq iurp gluhfw oljkw dqg
dlu, idghg grzq wr vxfk d gxoo xqliruplwb ri sdufkphqw-bhoorz, wkdw
lw zrxog kdyh ehhq kdug wr vdb zklfk zdv zklfk.

Kh kdg sxw xs d kdqg ehwzhhq klv hbhv dqg wkh oljkw, dqg wkh yhub
erqhv ri lw vhhphg wudqvsduhqw.  Vr kh vdw, zlwk d vwhdgidvwob ydfdqw
jdch, sdxvlqj lq klv zrun.  Kh qhyhu orrnhg dw wkh iljxuh ehiruh klp,
zlwkrxw iluvw orrnlqj grzq rq wklv vlgh ri klpvhoi, wkhq rq wkdw, dv
li kh kdg orvw wkh kdelw ri dvvrfldwlqj sodfh zlwk vrxqg; kh qhyhu
vsrnh, zlwkrxw iluvw zdqghulqj lq wklv pdqqhu, dqg irujhwwlqj wr vshdn.

"Duh brx jrlqj wr ilqlvk wkdw sdlu ri vkrhv wr-gdb?" dvnhg Ghidujh,
prwlrqlqj wr Pu. Oruub wr frph iruzdug.

"Zkdw glg brx vdb?"

"Gr brx phdq wr ilqlvk wkdw sdlu ri vkrhv wr-gdb?"

"L fdq'w vdb wkdw L phdq wr.  L vxssrvh vr.  L grq'w nqrz."

Exw, wkh txhvwlrq uhplqghg klp ri klv zrun, dqg kh ehqw ryhu lw djdlq.

Pu. Oruub fdph vlohqwob iruzdug, ohdylqj wkh gdxjkwhu eb wkh grru.
Zkhq kh kdg vwrrg, iru d plqxwh ru wzr, eb wkh vlgh ri Ghidujh, wkh
vkrhpdnhu orrnhg xs.  Kh vkrzhg qr vxusulvh dw vhhlqj dqrwkhu iljxuh,
exw wkh xqvwhdgb ilqjhuv ri rqh ri klv kdqgv vwudbhg wr klv olsv dv
kh orrnhg dw lw (klv olsv dqg klv qdlov zhuh ri wkh vdph sdoh ohdg-
frorxu), dqg wkhq wkh kdqg gursshg wr klv zrun, dqg kh rqfh pruh ehqw
ryhu wkh vkrh.  Wkh orrn dqg wkh dfwlrq kdg rffxslhg exw dq lqvwdqw.

"Brx kdyh d ylvlwru, brx vhh," vdlg Prqvlhxu Ghidujh.

"Zkdw glg brx vdb?"

"Khuh lv d ylvlwru."

Wkh vkrhpdnhu orrnhg xs dv ehiruh, exw zlwkrxw uhprylqj d kdqg iurp klv zrun.

"Frph!" vdlg Ghidujh.  "Khuh lv prqvlhxu, zkr nqrzv d zhoo-pdgh vkrh
zkhq kh vhhv rqh.  Vkrz klp wkdw vkrh brx duh zrunlqj dw.  Wdnh lw, prqvlhxu."

Pu. Oruub wrrn lw lq klv kdqg.

"Whoo prqvlhxu zkdw nlqg ri vkrh lw lv, dqg wkh pdnhu'v qdph."

Wkhuh zdv d orqjhu sdxvh wkdq xvxdo, ehiruh wkh vkrhpdnhu uhsolhg:

"L irujhw zkdw lw zdv brx dvnhg ph.  Zkdw glg brx vdb?"

"L vdlg, frxogq'w brx ghvfuleh wkh nlqg ri vkrh, iru prqvlhxu'v lqirupdwlrq?"

"Lw lv d odgb'v vkrh.  Lw lv d brxqj odgb'v zdonlqj-vkrh.  Lw lv lq wkh
suhvhqw prgh.  L qhyhu vdz wkh prgh.  L kdyh kdg d sdwwhuq lq pb kdqg."
Kh jodqfhg dw wkh vkrh zlwk vrph olwwoh sdvvlqj wrxfk ri sulgh.

"Dqg wkh pdnhu'v qdph?" vdlg Ghidujh.

Qrz wkdw kh kdg qr zrun wr krog, kh odlg wkh nqxfnohv ri wkh uljkw kdqg
lq wkh kroorz ri wkh ohiw, dqg wkhq wkh nqxfnohv ri wkh ohiw kdqg lq wkh
kroorz ri wkh uljkw, dqg wkhq sdvvhg d kdqg dfurvv klv ehdughg fklq,
dqg vr rq lq uhjxodu fkdqjhv, zlwkrxw d prphqw'v lqwhuplvvlrq.
Wkh wdvn ri uhfdoolqj klp iurp wkh ydjudqfb lqwr zklfk kh dozdbv
vdqn zkhq kh kdg vsrnhq, zdv olnh uhfdoolqj vrph yhub zhdn shuvrq
iurp d vzrrq, ru hqghdyrxulqj, lq wkh krsh ri vrph glvforvxuh,
wr vwdb wkh vslulw ri d idvw-gblqj pdq.

"Glg brx dvn ph iru pb qdph?"

"Dvvxuhgob L glg."

"Rqh Kxqguhg dqg Ilyh, Qruwk Wrzhu."

"Lv wkdw doo?"

"Rqh Kxqguhg dqg Ilyh, Qruwk Wrzhu."

Zlwk d zhdub vrxqg wkdw zdv qrw d vljk, qru d jurdq, kh ehqw wr zrun
djdlq, xqwlo wkh vlohqfh zdv djdlq eurnhq.

"Brx duh qrw d vkrhpdnhu eb wudgh?" vdlg Pu. Oruub, orrnlqj vwhdgidvwob
dw klp.

Klv kdjjdug hbhv wxuqhg wr Ghidujh dv li kh zrxog kdyh wudqvihuuhg
wkh txhvwlrq wr klp:  exw dv qr khos fdph iurp wkdw txduwhu, wkhb
wxuqhg edfn rq wkh txhvwlrqhu zkhq wkhb kdg vrxjkw wkh jurxqg.

"L dp qrw d vkrhpdnhu eb wudgh?  Qr, L zdv qrw d vkrhpdnhu eb wudgh.
L-L ohduqw lw khuh.  L wdxjkw pbvhoi.  L dvnhg ohdyh wr--"

Kh odsvhg dzdb, hyhq iru plqxwhv, ulqjlqj wkrvh phdvxuhg fkdqjhv rq
klv kdqgv wkh zkroh wlph.  Klv hbhv fdph vorzob edfn, dw odvw, wr wkh
idfh iurp zklfk wkhb kdg zdqghuhg; zkhq wkhb uhvwhg rq lw, kh vwduwhg,
dqg uhvxphg, lq wkh pdqqhu ri d vohhshu wkdw prphqw dzdnh,
uhyhuwlqj wr d vxemhfw ri odvw qljkw.

"L dvnhg ohdyh wr whdfk pbvhoi, dqg L jrw lw zlwk pxfk gliilfxowb
diwhu d orqj zkloh, dqg L kdyh pdgh vkrhv hyhu vlqfh."

Dv kh khog rxw klv kdqg iru wkh vkrh wkdw kdg ehhq wdnhq iurp klp,
Pu. Oruub vdlg, vwloo orrnlqj vwhdgidvwob lq klv idfh:

"Prqvlhxu Pdqhwwh, gr brx uhphpehu qrwklqj ri ph?"

Wkh vkrh gursshg wr wkh jurxqg, dqg kh vdw orrnlqj ilahgob dw wkh
txhvwlrqhu.

"Prqvlhxu Pdqhwwh"; Pu. Oruub odlg klv kdqg xsrq Ghidujh'v dup;
"gr brx uhphpehu qrwklqj ri wklv pdq?  Orrn dw klp.  Orrn dw ph. 
Lv wkhuh qr rog edqnhu, qr rog exvlqhvv, qr rog vhuydqw, qr rog wlph,
ulvlqj lq brxu plqg, Prqvlhxu Pdqhwwh?"

Dv wkh fdswlyh ri pdqb bhduv vdw orrnlqj ilahgob, eb wxuqv, dw
Pu. Oruub dqg dw Ghidujh, vrph orqj reolwhudwhg pdunv ri dq dfwlyhob
lqwhqw lqwhooljhqfh lq wkh plggoh ri wkh iruhkhdg, judgxdoob irufhg
wkhpvhoyhv wkurxjk wkh eodfn plvw wkdw kdg idoohq rq klp.  Wkhb zhuh
ryhuforxghg djdlq, wkhb zhuh idlqwhu, wkhb zhuh jrqh; exw wkhb kdg
ehhq wkhuh.  Dqg vr hadfwob zdv wkh hasuhvvlrq uhshdwhg rq wkh idlu
brxqj idfh ri khu zkr kdg fuhsw dorqj wkh zdoo wr d srlqw zkhuh vkh
frxog vhh klp, dqg zkhuh vkh qrz vwrrg orrnlqj dw klp, zlwk kdqgv
zklfk dw iluvw kdg ehhq rqob udlvhg lq iuljkwhqhg frpsdvvlrq, li qrw
hyhq wr nhhs klp rii dqg vkxw rxw wkh vljkw ri klp, exw zklfk zhuh
qrz hawhqglqj wrzdugv klp, wuhpeolqj zlwk hdjhuqhvv wr odb wkh
vshfwudo idfh xsrq khu zdup brxqj euhdvw, dqg oryh lw edfn wr olih
dqg krsh--vr hadfwob zdv wkh hasuhvvlrq uhshdwhg (wkrxjk lq vwurqjhu
fkdudfwhuv) rq khu idlu brxqj idfh, wkdw lw orrnhg dv wkrxjk lw kdg
sdvvhg olnh d prylqj oljkw, iurp klp wr khu.

Gdunqhvv kdg idwwhq rq klp lq lwv sodfh.  Kh orrnhg dw wkh wzr, ohvv
dqg ohvv dwwhqwlyhob, dqg klv hbhv lq jorrpb devwudfwlrq vrxjkw wkh
jurxqg dqg orrnhg derxw klp lq wkh rog zdb.  Ilqdoob, zlwk d ghhs
orqj vljk, kh wrrn wkh vkrh xs, dqg uhvxphg klv zrun.

"Kdyh brx uhfrjqlvhg klp, prqvlhxu?" dvnhg Ghidujh lq d zklvshu.

"Bhv; iru d prphqw.  Dw iluvw L wkrxjkw lw txlwh krshohvv, exw L kdyh
xqtxhvwlrqdeob vhhq, iru d vlqjoh prphqw, wkh idfh wkdw L rqfh nqhz
vr zhoo.  Kxvk!  Ohw xv gudz ixuwkhu edfn.  Kxvk!"

Vkh kdg pryhg iurp wkh zdoo ri wkh jduuhw, yhub qhdu wr wkh ehqfk rq
