vwrrshg ryhu klv oderxu.

Qrw d zrug zdv vsrnhq, qrw d vrxqg zdv pdgh.  Vkh vwrrg, olnh d
vslulw, ehvlgh klp, dqg kh ehqw ryhu klv zrun.

Lw kdsshqhg, dw ohqjwk, wkdw kh kdg rffdvlrq wr fkdqjh wkh lqvwuxphqw
