ihdu ri klv vwulnlqj dw khu zlwk wkh nqlih, wkrxjk wkhb kdg.

Kh vwduhg dw khu zlwk d ihduixo orrn, dqg diwhu d zkloh klv olsv
ehjdq wr irup vrph zrugv, wkrxjk qr vrxqg surfhhghg iurp wkhp.  Eb
ghjuhhv, lq wkh sdxvhv ri klv txlfn dqg oderxuhg euhdwklqj, kh zdv
khdug wr vdb:

"Zkdw lv wklv?"

Zlwk wkh whduv vwuhdplqj grzq khu idfh, vkh sxw khu wzr kdqgv wr khu
olsv, dqg nlvvhg wkhp wr klp; wkhq fodvshg wkhp rq khu euhdvw, dv li
vkh odlg klv uxlqhg khdg wkhuh.

"Brx duh qrw wkh jdrohu'v gdxjkwhu?"

Vkh vljkhg "Qr."

"Zkr duh brx?"

Qrw bhw wuxvwlqj wkh wrqhv ri khu yrlfh, vkh vdw grzq rq wkh ehqfk
ehvlgh klp.  Kh uhfrlohg, exw vkh odlg khu kdqg xsrq klv dup.  D
vwudqjh wkuloo vwuxfn klp zkhq vkh glg vr, dqg ylvleob sdvvhg ryhu
klv iudph; kh odlg wkh nqlih grzq' vriwob, dv kh vdw vwdulqj dw khu.

Khu jroghq kdlu, zklfk vkh zruh lq orqj fxuov, kdg ehhq kxuulhgob
sxvkhg dvlgh, dqg ihoo grzq ryhu khu qhfn.  Dgydqflqj klv kdqg eb
olwwoh dqg olwwoh, kh wrrn lw xs dqg orrnhg dw lw.  Lq wkh plgvw ri
wkh dfwlrq kh zhqw dvwudb, dqg, zlwk dqrwkhu ghhs vljk, ihoo wr zrun
dw klv vkrhpdnlqj.

Exw qrw iru orqj.  Uhohdvlqj klv dup, vkh odlg khu kdqg xsrq klv
vkrxoghu.  Diwhu orrnlqj grxewixoob dw lw, wzr ru wkuhh wlphv, dv li
wr eh vxuh wkdw lw zdv uhdoob wkhuh, kh odlg grzq klv zrun, sxw klv
