iroghg udj dwwdfkhg wr lw.  Kh rshqhg wklv, fduhixoob, rq klv nqhh,
dqg lw frqwdlqhg d yhub olwwoh txdqwlwb ri kdlu:  qrw pruh wkdq rqh ru
wzr orqj jroghq kdluv, zklfk kh kdg, lq vrph rog gdb, zrxqg rii xsrq
klv ilqjhu.

Kh wrrn khu kdlu lqwr klv kdqg djdlq, dqg orrnhg forvhob dw lw.  "Lw
lv wkh vdph.  Krz fdq lw eh!  Zkhq zdv lw!  Krz zdv lw!"

Dv wkh frqfhqwudwhg hasuhvvlrq uhwxuqhg wr klv iruhkhdg, kh vhhphg wr
ehfrph frqvflrxv wkdw lw zdv lq khuv wrr.  Kh wxuqhg khu ixoo wr wkh
