'Brx zloo ohdyh ph wkhp?  Wkhb fdq qhyhu khos ph wr hvfdsh lq wkh
ergb, wkrxjk wkhb pdb lq wkh vslulw.' Wkrvh zhuh wkh zrugv L vdlg.
L uhphpehu wkhp yhub zhoo."

Kh iruphg wklv vshhfk zlwk klv olsv pdqb wlphv ehiruh kh frxog xwwhu
