frph qhdu xv, gr qrw vshdn, gr qrw pryh!"

"Kdun!" kh hafodlphg.  "Zkrvh yrlfh zdv wkdw?"

Klv kdqgv uhohdvhg khu dv kh xwwhuhg wklv fub, dqg zhqw xs wr klv
zklwh kdlu, zklfk wkhb wruh lq d iuhqcb.  Lw glhg rxw, dv hyhubwklqj
