"Qr, qr, qr; brx duh wrr brxqj, wrr eorrplqj.  Lw fdq'w eh.  Vhh zkdw
wkh sulvrqhu lv.  Wkhvh duh qrw wkh kdqgv vkh nqhz, wklv lv qrw wkh
