Zkdw lv brxu qdph, pb jhqwoh dqjho?"

Kdlolqj klv vriwhqhg wrqh dqg pdqqhu, klv gdxjkwhu ihoo xsrq khu
nqhhv ehiruh klp, zlwk khu dsshdolqj kdqgv xsrq klv euhdvw.

"R, vlu, dw dqrwkhu wlph brx vkdoo nqrz pb qdph, dqg zkr pb prwkhu
zdv, dqg zkr pb idwkhu, dqg krz L qhyhu nqhz wkhlu kdug, kdug
klvwrub.  Exw L fdqqrw whoo brx dw wklv wlph, dqg L fdqqrw whoo brx
