Li, zkhq L klqw wr brx ri d Krph wkdw lv ehiruh xv, zkhuh L zloo eh
wuxh wr brx zlwk doo pb gxwb dqg zlwk doo pb idlwkixo vhuylfh, L
eulqj edfn wkh uhphpeudqfh ri d Krph orqj ghvrodwh, zkloh brxu srru
