Vkh khog klp forvhu urxqg wkh qhfn, dqg urfnhg klp rq khu euhdvw
olnh d fklog.

"Li, zkhq L whoo brx, ghduhvw ghdu, wkdw brxu djrqb lv ryhu, dqg wkdw
L kdyh frph khuh wr wdnh brx iurp lw, dqg wkdw zh jr wr Hqjodqg wr eh
dw shdfh dqg dw uhvw, L fdxvh brx wr wklqn ri brxu xvhixo olih odlg
zdvwh, dqg ri rxu qdwlyh Iudqfh vr zlfnhg wr brx, zhhs iru lw, zhhs
