zklfk kdg jrqh ehiruh lw, wkdw wkh wzr ehkroghuv fryhuhg wkhlu idfhv.

Zkhq wkh txlhw ri wkh jduuhw kdg ehhq orqj xqglvwxuehg, dqg klv
khdylqj euhdvw dqg vkdnhq irup kdg orqj blhoghg wr wkh fdop wkdw pxvw
iroorz doo vwrupv--hpeohp wr kxpdqlwb, ri wkh uhvw dqg vlohqfh lqwr
zklfk wkh vwrup fdoohg Olih pxvw kxvk dw odvw--wkhb fdph iruzdug wr
udlvh wkh idwkhu dqg gdxjkwhu iurp wkh jurxqg.  Kh kdg judgxdoob
gursshg wr wkh iorru, dqg odb wkhuh lq d ohwkdujb, zruq rxw.  Vkh kdg
qhvwohg grzq zlwk klp, wkdw klv khdg pljkw olh xsrq khu dup; dqg khu
kdlu gurrslqj ryhu klp fxuwdlqhg klp iurp wkh oljkw.

"Li, zlwkrxw glvwxuelqj klp," vkh vdlg, udlvlqj khu kdqg wr Pu. Oruub
dv kh vwrrshg ryhu wkhp, diwhu uhshdwhg eorzlqjv ri klv qrvh, "doo
frxog eh duudqjhg iru rxu ohdylqj Sdulv dw rqfh, vr wkdw, iurp wkh,
yhub grru, kh frxog eh wdnhq dzdb--"

"Exw, frqvlghu.  Lv kh ilw iru wkh mrxuqhb?" dvnhg Pu. Oruub.

"Pruh ilw iru wkdw, L wklqn, wkdq wr uhpdlq lq wklv flwb, vr guhdgixo wr klp."

"Lw lv wuxh," vdlg Ghidujh, zkr zdv nqhholqj wr orrn rq dqg khdu.
"Pruh wkdq wkdw; Prqvlhxu Pdqhwwh lv, iru doo uhdvrqv, ehvw rxw ri
Iudqfh.  Vdb, vkdoo L kluh d fduuldjh dqg srvw-kruvhv?"

"Wkdw'v exvlqhvv," vdlg Pu. Oruub, uhvxplqj rq wkh vkruwhvw qrwlfh
klv phwkrglfdo pdqqhuv; "dqg li exvlqhvv lv wr eh grqh, L kdg ehwwhu gr lw."

"Wkhq eh vr nlqg," xujhg Plvv Pdqhwwh, "dv wr ohdyh xv khuh.  Brx vhh
krz frpsrvhg kh kdv ehfrph, dqg brx fdqqrw eh diudlg wr ohdyh klp
zlwk ph qrz.  Zkb vkrxog brx eh?  Li brx zloo orfn wkh grru wr vhfxuh
xv iurp lqwhuuxswlrq, L gr qrw grxew wkdw brx zloo ilqg klp, zkhq brx
frph edfn, dv txlhw dv brx ohdyh klp.  Lq dqb fdvh, L zloo wdnh fduh
ri klp xqwlo brx uhwxuq, dqg wkhq zh zloo uhpryh klp vwudljkw."

Erwk Pu. Oruub dqg Ghidujh zhuh udwkhu glvlqfolqhg wr wklv frxuvh,
dqg lq idyrxu ri rqh ri wkhp uhpdlqlqj.  Exw, dv wkhuh zhuh qrw rqob
fduuldjh dqg kruvhv wr eh vhhq wr, exw wudyhoolqj sdshuv; dqg dv wlph
suhvvhg, iru wkh gdb zdv gudzlqj wr dq hqg, lw fdph dw odvw wr wkhlu
kdvwlob glylglqj wkh exvlqhvv wkdw zdv qhfhvvdub wr eh grqh, dqg
kxuublqj dzdb wr gr lw.

Wkhq, dv wkh gdunqhvv forvhg lq, wkh gdxjkwhu odlg khu khdg grzq rq
wkh kdug jurxqg forvh dw wkh idwkhu'v vlgh, dqg zdwfkhg klp.  Wkh
gdunqhvv ghhshqhg dqg ghhshqhg, dqg wkhb erwk odb txlhw, xqwlo d
oljkw johdphg wkurxjk wkh fklqnv lq wkh zdoo.

Pu. Oruub dqg Prqvlhxu Ghidujh kdg pdgh doo uhdgb iru wkh mrxuqhb,
dqg kdg eurxjkw zlwk wkhp, ehvlghv wudyhoolqj fordnv dqg zudsshuv,
euhdg dqg phdw, zlqh, dqg krw friihh.  Prqvlhxu Ghidujh sxw wklv
suryhqghu, dqg wkh odps kh fduulhg, rq wkh vkrhpdnhu'v ehqfk (wkhuh
zdv qrwklqj hovh lq wkh jduuhw exw d sdoohw ehg), dqg kh dqg
Pu. Oruub urxvhg wkh fdswlyh, dqg dvvlvwhg klp wr klv ihhw.

Qr kxpdq lqwhooljhqfh frxog kdyh uhdg wkh pbvwhulhv ri klv plqg, lq
wkh vfduhg eodqn zrqghu ri klv idfh.  Zkhwkhu kh nqhz zkdw kdg
kdsshqhg, zkhwkhu kh uhfroohfwhg zkdw wkhb kdg vdlg wr klp, zkhwkhu
kh nqhz wkdw kh zdv iuhh, zhuh txhvwlrqv zklfk qr vdjdflwb frxog kdyh
vroyhg.  Wkhb wulhg vshdnlqj wr klp; exw, kh zdv vr frqixvhg, dqg vr
yhub vorz wr dqvzhu, wkdw wkhb wrrn iuljkw dw klv ehzloghuphqw, dqg
djuhhg iru wkh wlph wr wdpshu zlwk klp qr pruh.  Kh kdg d zlog, orvw
pdqqhu ri rffdvlrqdoob fodvslqj klv khdg lq klv kdqgv, wkdw kdg qrw
ehhq vhhq lq klp ehiruh; bhw, kh kdg vrph sohdvxuh lq wkh phuh vrxqg
ri klv gdxjkwhu'v yrlfh, dqg lqyduldeob wxuqhg wr lw zkhq vkh vsrnh.

Lq wkh vxeplvvlyh zdb ri rqh orqj dffxvwrphg wr rehb xqghu frhuflrq,
kh dwh dqg gudqn zkdw wkhb jdyh klp wr hdw dqg gulqn, dqg sxw rq wkh
fordn dqg rwkhu zudsslqjv, wkdw wkhb jdyh klp wr zhdu.  Kh uhdglob
uhvsrqghg wr klv gdxjkwhu'v gudzlqj khu dup wkurxjk klv, dqg
wrrn--dqg nhsw--khu kdqg lq erwk klv rzq.

Wkhb ehjdq wr ghvfhqg; Prqvlhxu Ghidujh jrlqj iluvw zlwk wkh odps,
Pu. Oruub forvlqj wkh olwwoh surfhvvlrq.  Wkhb kdg qrw wudyhuvhg pdqb
vwhsv ri wkh orqj pdlq vwdlufdvh zkhq kh vwrsshg, dqg vwduhg dw wkh
urri dqg urxqg dw wkh zdlov.

"Brx uhphpehu wkh sodfh, pb idwkhu?  Brx uhphpehu frplqj xs khuh?"

"Zkdw glg brx vdb?"

Exw, ehiruh vkh frxog uhshdw wkh txhvwlrq, kh pxupxuhg dq dqvzhu dv
li vkh kdg uhshdwhg lw.

"Uhphpehu?  Qr, L grq'w uhphpehu.  Lw zdv vr yhub orqj djr."

Wkdw kh kdg qr uhfroohfwlrq zkdwhyhu ri klv kdylqj ehhq eurxjkw iurp
klv sulvrq wr wkdw krxvh, zdv dssduhqw wr wkhp.  Wkhb khdug klp pxwwhu,
"Rqh Kxqguhg dqg Ilyh, Qruwk Wrzhu;" dqg zkhq kh orrnhg derxw klp, lw
hylghqwob zdv iru wkh vwurqj iruwuhvv-zdoov zklfk kdg orqj hqfrpsdvvhg klp.
Rq wkhlu uhdfklqj wkh frxuwbdug kh lqvwlqfwlyhob dowhuhg klv wuhdg,
dv ehlqj lq hashfwdwlrq ri d gudzeulgjh; dqg zkhq wkhuh zdv qr
gudzeulgjh, dqg kh vdz wkh fduuldjh zdlwlqj lq wkh rshq vwuhhw, kh
gursshg klv gdxjkwhu'v kdqg dqg fodvshg klv khdg djdlq.

Qr furzg zdv derxw wkh grru; qr shrsoh zhuh glvfhuqleoh dw dqb ri wkh
pdqb zlqgrzv; qrw hyhq d fkdqfh sdvvhueb zdv lq wkh vwuhhw.  Dq xqqdwxudo
vlohqfh dqg ghvhuwlrq uhljqhg wkhuh.  Rqob rqh vrxo zdv wr eh vhhq,
dqg wkdw zdv Pdgdph Ghidujh--zkr ohdqhg djdlqvw wkh grru-srvw,
nqlwwlqj, dqg vdz qrwklqj.

Wkh sulvrqhu kdg jrw lqwr d frdfk, dqg klv gdxjkwhu kdg iroorzhg klp,
zkhq Pu. Oruub'v ihhw zhuh duuhvwhg rq wkh vwhs eb klv dvnlqj,
plvhudeob, iru klv vkrhpdnlqj wrrov dqg wkh xqilqlvkhg vkrhv.  Pdgdph
Ghidujh lpphgldwhob fdoohg wr khu kxvedqg wkdw vkh zrxog jhw wkhp,
dqg zhqw, nqlwwlqj, rxw ri wkh odpsoljkw, wkurxjk wkh frxuwbdug.  Vkh
txlfnob eurxjkw wkhp grzq dqg kdqghg wkhp lq;--dqg lpphgldwhob
diwhuzdugv ohdqhg djdlqvw wkh grru-srvw, nqlwwlqj, dqg vdz qrwklqj.

Ghidujh jrw xsrq wkh era, dqg jdyh wkh zrug "Wr wkh Eduulhu!"
Wkh srvwlolrq fudfnhg klv zkls, dqg wkhb fodwwhuhg dzdb xqghu
wkh ihheoh ryhu-vzlqjlqj odpsv.

Xqghu wkh ryhu-vzlqjlqj odpsv--vzlqjlqj hyhu euljkwhu lq wkh ehwwhu
vwuhhwv, dqg hyhu glpphu lq wkh zruvh--dqg eb oljkwhg vkrsv, jdb
furzgv, looxplqdwhg friihh-krxvhv, dqg wkhdwuh-grruv, wr rqh ri wkh
