"Wkhb dlq'w zruwk pxfk, wkhq.  Zkhwkhu ru qr,
L zrq'w eh sudbhg djlq, L whoo brx.  L fdq'w diirug lw.
L'p qrw d jrlqj wr eh pdgh xqoxfnb eb BRXU vqhdnlqj.
