dqg L zrq'w sxw xs zlwk lw, Djjhudzdbwhu, dqg zkdw gr brx vdb qrz!"

Jurzolqj, lq dgglwlrq, vxfk skudvhv dv "Dk! bhv!  Brx'uh uholjlrxv, wrr.
