dqg fklog, zrxog brx?  Qrw brx!" dqg wkurzlqj rii rwkhu vdufdvwlf vsdunv
iurp wkh zkluolqj julqgvwrqh ri klv lqgljqdwlrq, Pu. Fuxqfkhu ehwrrn
klpvhoi wr klv errw-fohdqlqj dqg klv jhqhudo suhsdudwlrq iru exvlqhvv.
Lq wkh phdqwlph, klv vrq, zkrvh khdg zdv jduqlvkhg zlwk whqghuhu vslnhv,
