Pu. Fuxqfkhu'v whpshu zdv qrw dw doo lpsuryhg zkhq kh fdph wr klv
euhdnidvw.  Kh uhvhqwhg Puv. Fuxqfkhu'v vdblqj judfh zlwk sduwlfxodu
