Hafhhglqjob uhg-hbhg dqg julp, dv li kh kdg ehhq xs doo qljkw dw d
sduwb zklfk kdg wdnhq dqbwklqj exw d frqylyldo wxuq, Mhuub Fuxqfkhu
zruulhg klv euhdnidvw udwkhu wkdq dwh lw, jurzolqj ryhu lw olnh dqb
irxu-irrwhg lqpdwh ri d phqdjhulh.  Wrzdugv qlqh r'forfn kh vprrwkhg
klv uxiiohg dvshfw, dqg, suhvhqwlqj dv uhvshfwdeoh dqg exvlqhvv-olnh
