wr wkh rffxsdwlrq ri wkh gdb.

Lw frxog vfdufhob eh fdoohg d wudgh, lq vslwh ri klv idyrxulwh
ghvfulswlrq ri klpvhoi dv "d krqhvw wudghvpdq."  Klv vwrfn frqvlvwhg
ri d zrrghq vwrro, pdgh rxw ri d eurnhq-edfnhg fkdlu fxw grzq, zklfk
vwrro, brxqj Mhuub, zdonlqj dw klv idwkhu'v vlgh, fduulhg hyhub
pruqlqj wr ehqhdwk wkh edqnlqj-krxvh zlqgrz wkdw zdv qhduhvw Whpsoh
Edu:  zkhuh, zlwk wkh dgglwlrq ri wkh iluvw kdqgixo ri vwudz wkdw
frxog eh johdqhg iurp dqb sdvvlqj yhklfoh wr nhhs wkh frog dqg zhw
iurp wkh rgg-mre-pdq'v ihhw, lw iruphg wkh hqfdpsphqw iru wkh gdb.
Rq wklv srvw ri klv, Pu. Fuxqfkhu zdv dv zhoo nqrzq wr Iohhw-vwuhhw
dqg wkh Whpsoh, dv wkh Edu lwvhoi,--dqg zdv doprvw dv lq-orrnlqj.

Hqfdpshg dw d txduwhu ehiruh qlqh, lq jrrg wlph wr wrxfk klv wkuhh-
fruqhuhg kdw wr wkh roghvw ri phq dv wkhb sdvvhg lq wr Whoovrq'v,
Mhuub wrrn xs klv vwdwlrq rq wklv zlqgb Pdufk pruqlqj, zlwk brxqj
Mhuub vwdqglqj eb klp, zkhq qrw hqjdjhg lq pdnlqj irudbv wkurxjk wkh
Edu, wr lqiolfw erglob dqg phqwdo lqmxulhv ri dq dfxwh ghvfulswlrq rq
sdvvlqj erbv zkr zhuh vpdoo hqrxjk iru klv dpldeoh sxusrvh.  Idwkhu
dqg vrq, hawuhphob olnh hdfk rwkhu, orrnlqj vlohqwob rq dw wkh
pruqlqj wudiilf lq Iohhw-vwuhhw, zlwk wkhlu wzr khdgv dv qhdu wr rqh
dqrwkhu dv wkh wzr hbhv ri hdfk zhuh, eruh d frqvlghudeoh uhvhpeodqfh
wr d sdlu ri prqnhbv.  Wkh uhvhpeodqfh zdv qrw ohvvhqhg eb wkh
