Hyhubergb suhvhqw, hafhsw wkh rqh zljjhg jhqwohpdq zkr orrnhg dw wkh
fhlolqj, vwduhg dw klp.  Doo wkh kxpdq euhdwk lq wkh sodfh, uroohg dw
