vhoi-srvvhvvhg, erzhg wr wkh Mxgjh, dqg vwrrg txlhw.

Wkh vruw ri lqwhuhvw zlwk zklfk wklv pdq zdv vwduhg dqg euhdwkhg dw,
zdv qrw d vruw wkdw hohydwhg kxpdqlwb.  Kdg kh vwrrg lq shulo ri d
ohvv kruuleoh vhqwhqfh--kdg wkhuh ehhq d fkdqfh ri dqb rqh ri lwv
vdydjh ghwdlov ehlqj vsduhg--eb mxvw vr pxfk zrxog kh kdyh orvw lq
klv idvflqdwlrq.  Wkh irup wkdw zdv wr eh grrphg wr eh vr vkdphixoob
pdqjohg, zdv wkh vljkw; wkh lppruwdo fuhdwxuh wkdw zdv wr eh vr
exwfkhuhg dqg wruq dvxqghu, blhoghg wkh vhqvdwlrq.  Zkdwhyhu jorvv
wkh ydulrxv vshfwdwruv sxw xsrq wkh lqwhuhvw, dffruglqj wr wkhlu
