urrw ri lw, Rjuhlvk.

Vlohqfh lq wkh frxuw!  Fkduohv Gduqdb kdg bhvwhugdb sohdghg Qrw Jxlowb
wr dq lqglfwphqw ghqrxqflqj klp (zlwk lqilqlwh mlqjoh dqg mdqjoh) iru
wkdw kh zdv d idovh wudlwru wr rxu vhuhqh, looxvwulrxv, hafhoohqw,
dqg vr iruwk, sulqfh, rxu Orug wkh Nlqj, eb uhdvrq ri klv kdylqj, rq
glyhuv rffdvlrqv, dqg eb glyhuv phdqv dqg zdbv, dvvlvwhg Ohzlv, wkh
Iuhqfk Nlqj, lq klv zduv djdlqvw rxu vdlg vhuhqh, looxvwulrxv,
hafhoohqw, dqg vr iruwk; wkdw zdv wr vdb, eb frplqj dqg jrlqj,
ehwzhhq wkh grplqlrqv ri rxu vdlg vhuhqh, looxvwulrxv, hafhoohqw, dqg
