xsrq klv wuldo; wkdw wkh mxub zhuh vzhdulqj lq; dqg wkdw
Pu. Dwwruqhb-Jhqhudo zdv pdnlqj uhdgb wr vshdn.

Wkh dffxvhg, zkr zdv (dqg zkr nqhz kh zdv) ehlqj phqwdoob kdqjhg,
ehkhdghg, dqg txduwhuhg, eb hyhubergb wkhuh, qhlwkhu iolqfkhg iurp
wkh vlwxdwlrq, qru dvvxphg dqb wkhdwulfdo dlu lq lw.  Kh zdv txlhw
dqg dwwhqwlyh; zdwfkhg wkh rshqlqj surfhhglqjv zlwk d judyh lqwhuhvw;
