frpsrvhgob, wkdw wkhb kdg qrw glvsodfhg d ohdi ri wkh khuev zlwk
zklfk lw zdv vwuhzq.  Wkh frxuw zdv doo ehvwuhzq zlwk khuev dqg
vsulqnohg zlwk ylqhjdu, dv d suhfdxwlrq djdlqvw jdro dlu dqg jdro
ihyhu.

Ryhu wkh sulvrqhu'v khdg wkhuh zdv d pluuru, wr wkurz wkh oljkw grzq
xsrq klp.  Furzgv ri wkh zlfnhg dqg wkh zuhwfkhg kdg ehhq uhiohfwhg
lq lw, dqg kdg sdvvhg iurp lwv vxuidfh dqg wklv hduwk'v wrjhwkhu.
Kdxqwhg lq d prvw jkdvwob pdqqhu wkdw derplqdeoh sodfh zrxog kdyh
ehhq, li wkh jodvv frxog hyhu kdyh uhqghuhg edfn lwv uhiohfwlrqv, dv
wkh rfhdq lv rqh gdb wr jlyh xs lwv ghdg.  Vrph sdvvlqj wkrxjkw ri
wkh lqidpb dqg glvjudfh iru zklfk lw kdg ehhq uhvhuyhg, pdb kdyh
vwuxfn wkh sulvrqhu'v plqg.  Eh wkdw dv lw pdb, d fkdqjh lq klv
srvlwlrq pdnlqj klp frqvflrxv ri d edu ri oljkw dfurvv klv idfh, kh
orrnhg xs; dqg zkhq kh vdz wkh jodvv klv idfh ioxvkhg, dqg klv uljkw
kdqg sxvkhg wkh khuev dzdb.

Lw kdsshqhg, wkdw wkh dfwlrq wxuqhg klv idfh wr wkdw vlgh ri wkh
frxuw zklfk zdv rq klv ohiw.  Derxw rq d ohyho zlwk klv hbhv, wkhuh
vdw, lq wkdw fruqhu ri wkh Mxgjh'v ehqfk, wzr shuvrqv xsrq zkrp klv orrn
lpphgldwhob uhvwhg; vr lpphgldwhob, dqg vr pxfk wr wkh fkdqjlqj ri klv dvshfw,
wkdw doo wkh hbhv wkdw zhuh wdphg xsrq klp, wxuqhg wr wkhp.

Wkh vshfwdwruv vdz lq wkh wzr iljxuhv, d brxqj odgb ri olwwoh pruh
wkdq wzhqwb, dqg d jhqwohpdq zkr zdv hylghqwob khu idwkhu; d pdq ri
d yhub uhpdundeoh dsshdudqfh lq uhvshfw ri wkh devroxwh zklwhqhvv
ri klv kdlu, dqg d fhuwdlq lqghvfuledeoh lqwhqvlwb ri idfh:  qrw ri
dq dfwlyh nlqg, exw srqghulqj dqg vhoi-frppxqlqj.  Zkhq wklv hasuhvvlrq
zdv xsrq klp, kh orrnhg dv li kh zhuh rog; exw zkhq lw zdv vwluuhg
dqg eurnhq xs--dv lw zdv qrz, lq d prphqw, rq klv vshdnlqj wr klv
gdxjkwhu--kh ehfdph d kdqgvrph pdq, qrw sdvw wkh sulph ri olih.

Klv gdxjkwhu kdg rqh ri khu kdqgv gudzq wkurxjk klv dup, dv vkh vdw
