edfn; dw odvw lw jrw wr Mhuub:

"Zlwqhvvhv."

"Iru zklfk vlgh?"

"Djdlqvw."

"Djdlqvw zkdw vlgh?"

"Wkh sulvrqhu'v."

Wkh Mxgjh, zkrvh hbhv kdg jrqh lq wkh jhqhudo gluhfwlrq, uhfdoohg
