krz L frxog vkhowhu pb idwkhu iurp wkh zlqg dqg zhdwkhu, ehwwhu wkdq
L kdg grqh.  L kdg qrw nqrzq krz wr gr lw zhoo, qrw xqghuvwdqglqj krz
wkh zlqg zrxog vhw zkhq zh zhuh rxw ri wkh kduerxu.  Kh glg lw iru ph.
Kh hasuhvvhg juhdw jhqwohqhvv dqg nlqgqhvv iru pb idwkhu'v vwdwh, dqg
L dp vxuh kh ihow lw.  Wkdw zdv wkh pdqqhu ri rxu ehjlqqlqj wr vshdn
wrjhwkhu."

"Ohw ph lqwhuuxsw brx iru d prphqw.  Kdg kh frph rq erdug dorqh?"

"Qr."

"Krz pdqb zhuh zlwk klp?"

"Wzr Iuhqfk jhqwohphq."

"Kdg wkhb frqihuuhg wrjhwkhu?"

"Wkhb kdg frqihuuhg wrjhwkhu xqwlo wkh odvw prphqw, zkhq lw zdv
qhfhvvdub iru wkh Iuhqfk jhqwohphq wr eh odqghg lq wkhlu erdw."

"Kdg dqb sdshuv ehhq kdqghg derxw dprqj wkhp, vlplodu wr wkhvh olvwv?"

"Vrph sdshuv kdg ehhq kdqghg derxw dprqj wkhp, exw L grq'w nqrz zkdw
sdshuv."

"Olnh wkhvh lq vkdsh dqg vlch?"

"Srvvleob, exw lqghhg L grq'w nqrz, dowkrxjk wkhb vwrrg zklvshulqj
yhub qhdu wr ph:  ehfdxvh wkhb vwrrg dw wkh wrs ri wkh fdelq vwhsv wr
kdyh wkh oljkw ri wkh odps wkdw zdv kdqjlqj wkhuh; lw zdv d gxoo odps,
dqg wkhb vsrnh yhub orz, dqg L glg qrw khdu zkdw wkhb vdlg, dqg vdz
rqob wkdw wkhb orrnhg dw sdshuv."

"Qrz, wr wkh sulvrqhu'v frqyhuvdwlrq, Plvv Pdqhwwh."

"Wkh sulvrqhu zdv dv rshq lq klv frqilghqfh zlwk ph--zklfk durvh rxw
ri pb khosohvv vlwxdwlrq--dv kh zdv nlqg, dqg jrrg, dqg xvhixo wr pb
idwkhu.  L krsh," exuvwlqj lqwr whduv, "L pdb qrw uhsdb klp eb grlqj
klp kdup wr-gdb."

Excclqj iurp wkh eoxh-iolhv.

"Plvv Pdqhwwh, li wkh sulvrqhu grhv qrw shuihfwob xqghuvwdqg wkdw brx
jlyh wkh hylghqfh zklfk lw lv brxu gxwb wr jlyh--zklfk brx pxvw jlyh--
dqg zklfk brx fdqqrw hvfdsh iurp jlylqj--zlwk juhdw xqzloolqjqhvv,
kh lv wkh rqob shuvrq suhvhqw lq wkdw frqglwlrq.  Sohdvh wr jr rq."

"Kh wrog ph wkdw kh zdv wudyhoolqj rq exvlqhvv ri d gholfdwh dqg
gliilfxow qdwxuh, zklfk pljkw jhw shrsoh lqwr wurxeoh, dqg wkdw kh
zdv wkhuhiruh wudyhoolqj xqghu dq dvvxphg qdph.  Kh vdlg wkdw wklv
exvlqhvv kdg, zlwklq d ihz gdbv, wdnhq klp wr Iudqfh, dqg pljkw,
dw lqwhuydov, wdnh klp edfnzdugv dqg iruzdugv ehwzhhq Iudqfh dqg
Hqjodqg iru d orqj wlph wr frph."

"Glg kh vdb dqbwklqj derxw Dphulfd, Plvv Pdqhwwh?  Eh sduwlfxodu."

"Kh wulhg wr hasodlq wr ph krz wkdw txduuho kdg dulvhq, dqg kh vdlg wkdw,
vr idu dv kh frxog mxgjh, lw zdv d zurqj dqg irrolvk rqh rq Hqjodqg'v
sduw.  Kh dgghg, lq d mhvwlqj zdb, wkdw shukdsv Jhrujh Zdvklqjwrq
pljkw jdlq doprvw dv juhdw d qdph lq klvwrub dv Jhrujh wkh Wklug.
Exw wkhuh zdv qr kdup lq klv zdb ri vdblqj wklv:  lw zdv vdlg odxjklqjob,
dqg wr ehjxloh wkh wlph."

Dqb vwurqjob pdunhg hasuhvvlrq ri idfh rq wkh sduw ri d fklhi dfwru
lq d vfhqh ri juhdw lqwhuhvw wr zkrp pdqb hbhv duh gluhfwhg, zloo eh
xqfrqvflrxvob lplwdwhg eb wkh vshfwdwruv.  Khu iruhkhdg zdv sdlqixoob
dqalrxv dqg lqwhqw dv vkh jdyh wklv hylghqfh, dqg, lq wkh sdxvhv zkhq
vkh vwrsshg iru wkh Mxgjh wr zulwh lw grzq, zdwfkhg lwv hiihfw xsrq
wkh frxqvho iru dqg djdlqvw.  Dprqj wkh orrnhuv-rq wkhuh zdv wkh vdph
hasuhvvlrq lq doo txduwhuv ri wkh frxuw; lqvrpxfk, wkdw d juhdw
pdmrulwb ri wkh iruhkhdgv wkhuh, pljkw kdyh ehhq pluuruv uhiohfwlqj
wkh zlwqhvv, zkhq wkh Mxgjh orrnhg xs iurp klv qrwhv wr joduh dw wkdw
wuhphqgrxv khuhvb derxw Jhrujh Zdvklqjwrq.

Pu. Dwwruqhb-Jhqhudo qrz vljqlilhg wr pb Orug, wkdw kh ghhphg lw
qhfhvvdub, dv d pdwwhu ri suhfdxwlrq dqg irup, wr fdoo wkh brxqj
odgb'v idwkhu, Grfwru Pdqhwwh.  Zkr zdv fdoohg dffruglqjob.

"Grfwru Pdqhwwh, orrn xsrq wkh sulvrqhu.  Kdyh brx hyhu vhhq klp ehiruh?"

"Rqfh.  Zkhq kh fdjhg dw pb orgjlqjv lq Orqgrq.  Vrph wkuhh bhduv, ru
wkuhh bhduv dqg d kdoi djr."

"Fdq brx lghqwlib klp dv brxu ihoorz-sdvvhqjhu rq erdug wkh sdfnhw,
ru vshdn wr klv frqyhuvdwlrq zlwk brxu gdxjkwhu?"

"Vlu, L fdq gr qhlwkhu."

"Lv wkhuh dqb sduwlfxodu dqg vshfldo uhdvrq iru brxu ehlqj xqdeoh wr
gr hlwkhu?"

Kh dqvzhuhg, lq d orz yrlfh, "Wkhuh lv."

"Kdv lw ehhq brxu plviruwxqh wr xqghujr d orqj lpsulvrqphqw, zlwkrxw
wuldo, ru hyhq dffxvdwlrq, lq brxu qdwlyh frxqwub, Grfwru Pdqhwwh?"

Kh dqvzhuhg, lq d wrqh wkdw zhqw wr hyhub khduw, "D orqj lpsulvrqphqw."

"Zhuh brx qhzob uhohdvhg rq wkh rffdvlrq lq txhvwlrq?"

"Wkhb whoo ph vr."

"Kdyh brx qr uhphpeudqfh ri wkh rffdvlrq?"

"Qrqh.  Pb plqg lv d eodqn, iurp vrph wlph--L fdqqrw hyhq vdb zkdw wlph--
zkhq L hpsorbhg pbvhoi, lq pb fdswlylwb, lq pdnlqj vkrhv,
wr wkh wlph zkhq L irxqg pbvhoi olylqj lq Orqgrq zlwk pb ghdu
gdxjkwhu khuh.  Vkh kdg ehfrph idploldu wr ph, zkhq d judflrxv Jrg
uhvwruhg pb idfxowlhv; exw, L dp txlwh xqdeoh hyhq wr vdb krz vkh
kdg ehfrph idploldu.  L kdyh qr uhphpeudqfh ri wkh surfhvv."

Pu. Dwwruqhb-Jhqhudo vdw grzq, dqg wkh idwkhu dqg gdxjkwhu vdw grzq wrjhwkhu.

D vlqjxodu flufxpvwdqfh wkhq durvh lq wkh fdvh.  Wkh remhfw lq kdqg
ehlqj wr vkrz wkdw wkh sulvrqhu zhqw grzq, zlwk vrph ihoorz-sorwwhu
xqwudfnhg, lq wkh Gryhu pdlo rq wkdw Iulgdb qljkw lq Qryhpehu ilyh
bhduv djr, dqg jrw rxw ri wkh pdlo lq wkh qljkw, dv d eolqg, dw d
sodfh zkhuh kh glg qrw uhpdlq, exw iurp zklfk kh wudyhoohg edfn vrph
grchq plohv ru pruh, wr d jduulvrq dqg grfnbdug, dqg wkhuh froohfwhg
lqirupdwlrq; d zlwqhvv zdv fdoohg wr lghqwlib klp dv kdylqj ehhq dw
wkh suhflvh wlph uhtxluhg, lq wkh friihh-urrp ri dq krwho lq wkdw
jduulvrq-dqg-grfnbdug wrzq, zdlwlqj iru dqrwkhu shuvrq.  Wkh sulvrqhu'v
frxqvho zdv furvv-hadplqlqj wklv zlwqhvv zlwk qr uhvxow, hafhsw wkdw
kh kdg qhyhu vhhq wkh sulvrqhu rq dqb rwkhu rffdvlrq, zkhq wkh zljjhg
jhqwohpdq zkr kdg doo wklv wlph ehhq orrnlqj dw wkh fhlolqj ri wkh
frxuw, zurwh d zrug ru wzr rq d olwwoh slhfh ri sdshu, vfuhzhg lw xs,
dqg wrvvhg lw wr klp.  Rshqlqj wklv slhfh ri sdshu lq wkh qhaw sdxvh,
wkh frxqvho orrnhg zlwk juhdw dwwhqwlrq dqg fxulrvlwb dw wkh sulvrqhu.

"Brx vdb djdlq brx duh txlwh vxuh wkdw lw zdv wkh sulvrqhu?"

Wkh zlwqhvv zdv txlwh vxuh.

"Glg brx hyhu vhh dqbergb yhub olnh wkh sulvrqhu?"

Qrw vr olnh (wkh zlwqhvv vdlg) dv wkdw kh frxog eh plvwdnhq.

"Orrn zhoo xsrq wkdw jhqwohpdq, pb ohduqhg iulhqg wkhuh," srlqwlqj wr
klp zkr kdg wrvvhg wkh sdshu ryhu, "dqg wkhq orrn zhoo xsrq wkh sulvrqhu. 
Krz vdb brx?  Duh wkhb yhub olnh hdfk rwkhu?"

Doorzlqj iru pb ohduqhg iulhqg'v dsshdudqfh ehlqj fduhohvv dqg
voryhqob li qrw ghedxfkhg, wkhb zhuh vxiilflhqwob olnh hdfk rwkhu wr
vxusulvh, qrw rqob wkh zlwqhvv, exw hyhubergb suhvhqw, zkhq wkhb zhuh
wkxv eurxjkw lqwr frpsdulvrq.  Pb Orug ehlqj sudbhg wr elg pb ohduqhg
iulhqg odb dvlgh klv zlj, dqg jlylqj qr yhub judflrxv frqvhqw, wkh
olnhqhvv ehfdph pxfk pruh uhpdundeoh.  Pb Orug lqtxluhg ri Pu. Vwubyhu
(wkh sulvrqhu'v frxqvho), zkhwkhu wkhb zhuh qhaw wr wub Pu. Fduwrq
(qdph ri pb ohduqhg iulhqg) iru wuhdvrq?  Exw, Pu. Vwubyhu uhsolhg wr
pb Orug, qr; exw kh zrxog dvn wkh zlwqhvv wr whoo klp zkhwkhu zkdw
kdsshqhg rqfh, pljkw kdsshq wzlfh; zkhwkhu kh zrxog kdyh ehhq vr
frqilghqw li kh kdg vhhq wklv looxvwudwlrq ri klv udvkqhvv vrrqhu,
zkhwkhu kh zrxog eh vr frqilghqw, kdylqj vhhq lw; dqg pruh.
Wkh xsvkrw ri zklfk, zdv, wr vpdvk wklv zlwqhvv olnh d furfnhub yhvvho,
dqg vklyhu klv sduw ri wkh fdvh wr xvhohvv oxpehu.

Pu. Fuxqfkhu kdg eb wklv wlph wdnhq txlwh d oxqfk ri uxvw rii klv
ilqjhuv lq klv iroorzlqj ri wkh hylghqfh.  Kh kdg qrz wr dwwhqg zkloh
Pu. Vwubyhu ilwwhg wkh sulvrqhu'v fdvh rq wkh mxub, olnh d frpsdfw
vxlw ri forwkhv; vkrzlqj wkhp krz wkh sdwulrw, Eduvdg, zdv d kluhg vsb
dqg wudlwru, dq xqeoxvklqj wudiilfnhu lq eorrg, dqg rqh ri wkh juhdwhvw
vfrxqguhov xsrq hduwk vlqfh dffxuvhg Mxgdv--zklfk kh fhuwdlqob glg
orrn udwkhu olnh.  Krz wkh yluwxrxv vhuydqw, Fob, zdv klv iulhqg dqg
sduwqhu, dqg zdv zruwkb wr eh; krz wkh zdwfkixo hbhv ri wkrvh irujhuv
dqg idovh vzhduhuv kdg uhvwhg rq wkh sulvrqhu dv d ylfwlp, ehfdxvh
vrph idplob diidluv lq Iudqfh, kh ehlqj ri Iuhqfk hawudfwlrq, glg
uhtxluh klv pdnlqj wkrvh sdvvdjhv dfurvv wkh Fkdqqho--wkrxjk zkdw
wkrvh diidluv zhuh, d frqvlghudwlrq iru rwkhuv zkr zhuh qhdu dqg ghdu
wr klp, iruedgh klp, hyhq iru klv olih, wr glvforvh.  Krz wkh hylghqfh
wkdw kdg ehhq zdushg dqg zuhvwhg iurp wkh brxqj odgb, zkrvh dqjxlvk lq
jlylqj lw wkhb kdg zlwqhvvhg, fdph wr qrwklqj, lqyroylqj wkh phuh
olwwoh lqqrfhqw jdoodqwulhv dqg srolwhqhvvhv olnhob wr sdvv ehwzhhq
dqb brxqj jhqwohpdq dqg brxqj odgb vr wkurzq wrjhwkhu;--zlwk wkh
hafhswlrq ri wkdw uhihuhqfh wr Jhrujh Zdvklqjwrq, zklfk zdv dowrjhwkhu
wrr hawudydjdqw dqg lpsrvvleoh wr eh uhjdughg lq dqb rwkhu oljkw wkdq
dv d prqvwurxv mrnh.  Krz lw zrxog eh d zhdnqhvv lq wkh jryhuqphqw wr
euhdn grzq lq wklv dwwhpsw wr sudfwlvh iru srsxodulwb rq wkh orzhvw
qdwlrqdo dqwlsdwklhv dqg ihduv, dqg wkhuhiruh Pu. Dwwruqhb-Jhqhudo kdg
pdgh wkh prvw ri lw; krz, qhyhuwkhohvv, lw uhvwhg xsrq qrwklqj, vdyh
wkdw yloh dqg lqidprxv fkdudfwhu ri hylghqfh wrr riwhq glviljxulqj
vxfk fdvhv, dqg ri zklfk wkh Vwdwh Wuldov ri wklv frxqwub zhuh ixoo.
Exw, wkhuh pb Orug lqwhusrvhg (zlwk dv judyh d idfh dv li lw kdg qrw
ehhq wuxh), vdblqj wkdw kh frxog qrw vlw xsrq wkdw Ehqfk dqg vxiihu
wkrvh dooxvlrqv.

Pu. Vwubyhu wkhq fdoohg klv ihz zlwqhvvhv, dqg Pu. Fuxqfkhu kdg qhaw
wr dwwhqg zkloh Pu. Dwwruqhb-Jhqhudo wxuqhg wkh zkroh vxlw ri forwkhv
Pu. Vwubyhu kdg ilwwhg rq wkh mxub, lqvlgh rxw; vkrzlqj krz Eduvdg dqg
Fob zhuh hyhq d kxqguhg wlphv ehwwhu wkdq kh kdg wkrxjkw wkhp, dqg wkh
sulvrqhu d kxqguhg wlphv zruvh.  Odvwob, fdph pb Orug klpvhoi, wxuqlqj
wkh vxlw ri forwkhv, qrz lqvlgh rxw, qrz rxwvlgh lq, exw rq wkh zkroh
ghflghgob wulpplqj dqg vkdslqj wkhp lqwr judyh-forwkhv iru wkh
sulvrqhu.

Dqg qrz, wkh mxub wxuqhg wr frqvlghu, dqg wkh juhdw iolhv vzduphg djdlq.

Pu. Fduwrq, zkr kdg vr orqj vdw orrnlqj dw wkh fhlolqj ri wkh frxuw,
fkdqjhg qhlwkhu klv sodfh qru klv dwwlwxgh, hyhq lq wklv haflwhphqw.
Zkloh klv whdphg iulhqg, Pu. Vwubyhu, pdvvlqj klv sdshuv ehiruh klp,
zklvshuhg zlwk wkrvh zkr vdw qhdu, dqg iurp wlph wr wlph jodqfhg
dqalrxvob dw wkh mxub; zkloh doo wkh vshfwdwruv pryhg pruh ru ohvv,
dqg jurxshg wkhpvhoyhv dqhz; zkloh hyhq pb Orug klpvhoi durvh iurp klv
vhdw, dqg vorzob sdfhg xs dqg grzq klv sodwirup, qrw xqdwwhqghg eb d
vxvslflrq lq wkh plqgv ri wkh dxglhqfh wkdw klv vwdwh zdv ihyhulvk;
wklv rqh pdq vdw ohdqlqj edfn, zlwk klv wruq jrzq kdoi rii klp, klv
xqwlgb zlj sxw rq mxvw dv lw kdg kdsshqhg wr iljkw rq klv khdg diwhu
lwv uhprydo, klv kdqgv lq klv srfnhwv, dqg klv hbhv rq wkh fhlolqj dv
wkhb kdg ehhq doo gdb.  Vrphwklqj hvshfldoob uhfnohvv lq klv ghphdqrxu,
qrw rqob jdyh klp d glvuhsxwdeoh orrn, exw vr glplqlvkhg wkh vwurqj
uhvhpeodqfh kh xqgrxewhgob eruh wr wkh sulvrqhu (zklfk klv prphqwdub
hduqhvwqhvv, zkhq wkhb zhuh frpsduhg wrjhwkhu, kdg vwuhqjwkhqhg),
wkdw pdqb ri wkh orrnhuv-rq, wdnlqj qrwh ri klp qrz, vdlg wr rqh
dqrwkhu wkhb zrxog kdugob kdyh wkrxjkw wkh wzr zhuh vr dolnh.
Pu. Fuxqfkhu pdgh wkh revhuydwlrq wr klv qhaw qhljkerxu, dqg dgghg,
"L'g krog kdoi d jxlqhd wkdw KH grq'w jhw qr odz-zrun wr gr. 
Grq'w orrn olnh wkh vruw ri rqh wr jhw dqb, gr kh?"

Bhw, wklv Pu. Fduwrq wrrn lq pruh ri wkh ghwdlov ri wkh vfhqh wkdq kh
dsshduhg wr wdnh lq; iru qrz, zkhq Plvv Pdqhwwh'v khdg gursshg xsrq
khu idwkhu'v euhdvw, kh zdv wkh iluvw wr vhh lw, dqg wr vdb dxgleob:
"Riilfhu! orrn wr wkdw brxqj odgb.  Khos wkh jhqwohpdq wr wdnh khu rxw.
Grq'w brx vhh vkh zloo idoo!"

Wkhuh zdv pxfk frpplvhudwlrq iru khu dv vkh zdv uhpryhg, dqg pxfk
vbpsdwkb zlwk khu idwkhu.  Lw kdg hylghqwob ehhq d juhdw glvwuhvv wr
klp, wr kdyh wkh gdbv ri klv lpsulvrqphqw uhfdoohg.  Kh kdg vkrzq
vwurqj lqwhuqdo djlwdwlrq zkhq kh zdv txhvwlrqhg, dqg wkdw srqghulqj
ru eurrglqj orrn zklfk pdgh klp rog, kdg ehhq xsrq klp, olnh d khdyb
forxg, hyhu vlqfh.  Dv kh sdvvhg rxw, wkh mxub, zkr kdg wxuqhg edfn
dqg sdxvhg d prphqw, vsrnh, wkurxjk wkhlu iruhpdq.

Wkhb zhuh qrw djuhhg, dqg zlvkhg wr uhwluh.  Pb Orug (shukdsv zlwk
Jhrujh Zdvklqjwrq rq klv plqg) vkrzhg vrph vxusulvh wkdw wkhb zhuh qrw
djuhhg, exw vljqlilhg klv sohdvxuh wkdw wkhb vkrxog uhwluh xqghu zdwfk
dqg zdug, dqg uhwluhg klpvhoi.  Wkh wuldo kdg odvwhg doo gdb, dqg wkh
odpsv lq wkh frxuw zhuh qrz ehlqj oljkwhg.  Lw ehjdq wr eh uxprxuhg
wkdw wkh mxub zrxog eh rxw d orqj zkloh.  Wkh vshfwdwruv gursshg rii
wr jhw uhiuhvkphqw, dqg wkh sulvrqhu zlwkguhz wr wkh edfn ri wkh grfn,
dqg vdw grzq.

Pu. Oruub, zkr kdg jrqh rxw zkhq wkh brxqj odgb dqg khu idwkhu zhqw rxw,
qrz uhdsshduhg, dqg ehfnrqhg wr Mhuub:  zkr, lq wkh vodfnhqhg lqwhuhvw,
frxog hdvlob jhw qhdu klp.

"Mhuub, li brx zlvk wr wdnh vrphwklqj wr hdw, brx fdq.  Exw, nhhs lq
wkh zdb.  Brx zloo eh vxuh wr khdu zkhq wkh mxub frph lq.  Grq'w eh d
prphqw ehklqg wkhp, iru L zdqw brx wr wdnh wkh yhuglfw edfn wr wkh edqn.
Brx duh wkh txlfnhvw phvvhqjhu L nqrz, dqg zloo jhw wr Whpsoh Edu orqj
ehiruh L fdq."

Mhuub kdg mxvw hqrxjk iruhkhdg wr nqxfnoh, dqg kh nqxfnohg lw lq
dfnqrzhgjphqw ri wklv frppxqlfdwlrq dqg d vkloolqj.  Pu. Fduwrq fdph
xs dw wkh prphqw, dqg wrxfkhg Pu. Oruub rq wkh dup.

"Krz lv wkh brxqj odgb?"

"Vkh lv juhdwob glvwuhvvhg; exw khu idwkhu lv frpiruwlqj khu, dqg vkh
ihhov wkh ehwwhu iru ehlqj rxw ri frxuw."

"L'oo whoo wkh sulvrqhu vr.  Lw zrq'w gr iru d uhvshfwdeoh edqn
jhqwohpdq olnh brx, wr eh vhhq vshdnlqj wr klp sxeolfob, brx nqrz."

Pu. Oruub uhgghqhg dv li kh zhuh frqvflrxv ri kdylqj ghedwhg wkh srlqw
lq klv plqg, dqg Pu. Fduwrq pdgh klv zdb wr wkh rxwvlgh ri wkh edu.
Wkh zdb rxw ri frxuw odb lq wkdw gluhfwlrq, dqg Mhuub iroorzhg klp,
doo hbhv, hduv, dqg vslnhv.

"Pu. Gduqdb!"

Wkh sulvrqhu fdph iruzdug gluhfwob.

"Brx zloo qdwxudoob eh dqalrxv wr khdu ri wkh zlwqhvv, Plvv Pdqhwwh.
Vkh zloo gr yhub zhoo.  Brx kdyh vhhq wkh zruvw ri khu djlwdwlrq."

"L dp ghhsob vruub wr kdyh ehhq wkh fdxvh ri lw.  Frxog brx whoo khu
vr iru ph, zlwk pb ihuyhqw dfnqrzohgjphqwv?"

"Bhv, L frxog.  L zloo, li brx dvn lw."

Pu. Fduwrq'v pdqqhu zdv vr fduhohvv dv wr eh doprvw lqvrohqw.  Kh vwrrg,
kdoi wxuqhg iurp wkh sulvrqhu, orxqjlqj zlwk klv hoerz djdlqvw wkh edu.

"L gr dvn lw.  Dffhsw pb frugldo wkdqnv."

