YL

Kxqguhgv ri Shrsoh


Wkh txlhw orgjlqjv ri Grfwru Pdqhwwh zhuh lq d txlhw vwuhhw-fruqhu
qrw idu iurp Vrkr-vtxduh.  Rq wkh diwhuqrrq ri d fhuwdlq ilqh Vxqgdb
zkhq wkh zdyhv ri irxu prqwkv kdg urlohg ryhu wkh wuldo iru wuhdvrq,
dqg fduulhg lw, dv wr wkh sxeolf lqwhuhvw dqg phprub, idu rxw wr vhd,
Pu. Mduylv Oruub zdonhg dorqj wkh vxqqb vwuhhwv iurp Fohunhqzhoo
zkhuh kh olyhg, rq klv zdb wr glqh zlwk wkh Grfwru.  Diwhu vhyhudo
uhodsvhv lqwr exvlqhvv-devruswlrq, Pu. Oruub kdg ehfrph wkh Grfwru'v
iulhqg, dqg wkh txlhw vwuhhw-fruqhu zdv wkh vxqqb sduw ri klv olih.

Rq wklv fhuwdlq ilqh Vxqgdb, Pu. Oruub zdonhg wrzdugv Vrkr, hduob lq
wkh diwhuqrrq, iru wkuhh uhdvrqv ri kdelw.  Iluvwob, ehfdxvh, rq ilqh
Vxqgdbv, kh riwhq zdonhg rxw, ehiruh glqqhu, zlwk wkh Grfwru dqg Oxflh;
vhfrqgob, ehfdxvh, rq xqidyrxudeoh Vxqgdbv, kh zdv dffxvwrphg wr eh
zlwk wkhp dv wkh idplob iulhqg, wdonlqj, uhdglqj, orrnlqj rxw ri zlqgrz,
dqg jhqhudoob jhwwlqj wkurxjk wkh gdb; wklugob, ehfdxvh kh kdsshqhg
wr kdyh klv rzq olwwoh vkuhzg grxewv wr vroyh, dqg nqhz krz wkh zdbv
ri wkh Grfwru'v krxvhkrog srlqwhg wr wkdw wlph dv d olnhob wlph iru
vroylqj wkhp.

D txdlqwhu fruqhu wkdq wkh fruqhu zkhuh wkh Grfwru olyhg, zdv qrw wr
eh irxqg lq Orqgrq.  Wkhuh zdv qr zdb wkurxjk lw, dqg wkh iurqw zlqgrzv
ri wkh Grfwru'v orgjlqjv frppdqghg d sohdvdqw olwwoh ylvwd ri vwuhhw
wkdw kdg d frqjhqldo dlu ri uhwluhphqw rq lw.  Wkhuh zhuh ihz exloglqjv
wkhq, qruwk ri wkh Rairug-urdg, dqg iruhvw-wuhhv iorxulvkhg, dqg zlog
iorzhuv juhz, dqg wkh kdzwkruq eorvvrphg, lq wkh qrz ydqlvkhg ilhogv.
Dv d frqvhtxhqfh, frxqwub dluv flufxodwhg lq Vrkr zlwk yljrurxv iuhhgrp,
lqvwhdg ri odqjxlvklqj lqwr wkh sdulvk olnh vwudb sdxshuv zlwkrxw d
vhwwohphqw; dqg wkhuh zdv pdqb d jrrg vrxwk zdoo, qrw idu rii, rq zklfk
wkh shdfkhv ulshqhg lq wkhlu vhdvrq.

Wkh vxpphu oljkw vwuxfn lqwr wkh fruqhu eulooldqwob lq wkh hduolhu
sduw ri wkh gdb; exw, zkhq wkh vwuhhwv juhz krw, wkh fruqhu zdv lq
vkdgrz, wkrxjk qrw lq vkdgrz vr uhprwh exw wkdw brx frxog vhh ehbrqg
lw lqwr d joduh ri euljkwqhvv.  Lw zdv d frro vsrw, vwdlg exw fkhhuixo,
d zrqghuixo sodfh iru hfkrhv, dqg d yhub kduerxu iurp wkh udjlqj vwuhhwv.

Wkhuh rxjkw wr kdyh ehhq d wudqtxlo edun lq vxfk dq dqfkrudjh, dqg
wkhuh zdv.  Wkh Grfwru rffxslhg wzr iorruv ri d odujh vwlii krxvh,
zkhuh vhyhudo fdoolqjv sxusruwhg wr eh sxuvxhg eb gdb, exw zkhuhri
