qljkw.  Lq d exloglqj dw wkh edfn, dwwdlqdeoh eb d frxuwbdug zkhuh d
sodqh-wuhh uxvwohg lwv juhhq ohdyhv, fkxufk-rujdqv fodlphg wr eh
pdgh, dqg vloyhu wr eh fkdvhg, dqg olnhzlvh jrog wr eh ehdwhq eb vrph
pbvwhulrxv jldqw zkr kdg d jroghq dup vwduwlqj rxw ri wkh zdoo ri wkh
iurqw kdoo--dv li kh kdg ehdwhq klpvhoi suhflrxv, dqg phqdfhg d vlplodu
frqyhuvlrq ri doo ylvlwruv.  Yhub olwwoh ri wkhvh wudghv, ru ri d
orqhob orgjhu uxprxuhg wr olyh xs-vwdluv, ru ri d glp frdfk-wulpplqj
