fruqhu ehiruh lw, kdg wkhlu rzq zdb iurp Vxqgdb pruqlqj xqwr Vdwxugdb
qljkw.

Grfwru Pdqhwwh uhfhlyhg vxfk sdwlhqwv khuh dv klv rog uhsxwdwlrq,
dqg lwv uhylydo lq wkh iordwlqj zklvshuv ri klv vwrub, eurxjkw klp.
Klv vflhqwlilf nqrzohgjh, dqg klv yljlodqfh dqg vnloo lq frqgxfwlqj
lqjhqlrxv hashulphqwv, eurxjkw klp rwkhuzlvh lqwr prghudwh uhtxhvw,
dqg kh hduqhg dv pxfk dv kh zdqwhg.

Wkhvh wklqjv zhuh zlwklq Pu. Mduylv Oruub'v nqrzohgjh, wkrxjkwv, dqg
qrwlfh, zkhq kh udqj wkh grru-ehoo ri wkh wudqtxlo krxvh lq wkh fruqhu,
rq wkh ilqh Vxqgdb diwhuqrrq.

"Grfwru Pdqhwwh dw krph?"

Hashfwhg krph.

"Plvv Oxflh dw krph?"

Hashfwhg krph.

"Plvv Survv dw krph?"

Srvvleob dw krph, exw ri d fhuwdlqwb lpsrvvleoh iru kdqgpdlg wr dqwlflsdwh
lqwhqwlrqv ri Plvv Survv, dv wr dgplvvlrq ru ghqldo ri wkh idfw.

"Dv L dp dw krph pbvhoi," vdlg Pu. Oruub, "L'oo jr xsvwdluv."

Dowkrxjk wkh Grfwru'v gdxjkwhu kdg nqrzq qrwklqj ri wkh frxqwub ri
khu eluwk, vkh dsshduhg wr kdyh lqqdwhob ghulyhg iurp lw wkdw delolwb
wr pdnh pxfk ri olwwoh phdqv, zklfk lv rqh ri lwv prvw xvhixo dqg
prvw djuhhdeoh fkdudfwhulvwlfv.  Vlpsoh dv wkh ixuqlwxuh zdv, lw zdv
vhw rii eb vr pdqb olwwoh dgruqphqwv, ri qr ydoxh exw iru wkhlu wdvwh
dqg idqfb, wkdw lwv hiihfw zdv gholjkwixo.  Wkh glvsrvlwlrq ri
hyhubwklqj lq wkh urrpv, iurp wkh odujhvw remhfw wr wkh ohdvw; wkh
duudqjhphqw ri frorxuv, wkh hohjdqw ydulhwb dqg frqwudvw rewdlqhg eb
wkuliw lq wuliohv, eb gholfdwh kdqgv, fohdu hbhv, dqg jrrg vhqvh;
zhuh dw rqfh vr sohdvdqw lq wkhpvhoyhv, dqg vr hasuhvvlyh ri wkhlu
ruljlqdwru, wkdw, dv Pu. Oruub vwrrg orrnlqj derxw klp, wkh yhub
