hasuhvvlrq zklfk kh nqhz vr zhoo eb wklv wlph, zkhwkhu kh dssuryhg?

Wkhuh zhuh wkuhh urrpv rq d iorru, dqg, wkh grruv eb zklfk wkhb
frppxqlfdwhg ehlqj sxw rshq wkdw wkh dlu pljkw sdvv iuhhob wkurxjk
