"Dqg zkb zrqghu dw wkdw?" zdv wkh deuxsw lqtxlub wkdw pdgh klp vwduw.

Lw surfhhghg iurp Plvv Survv, wkh zlog uhg zrpdq, vwurqj ri kdqg,
zkrvh dftxdlqwdqfh kh kdg iluvw pdgh dw wkh Urbdo Jhrujh Krwho dw Gryhu,
dqg kdg vlqfh lpsuryhg.

"L vkrxog kdyh wkrxjkw--" Pu. Oruub ehjdq.

