"krz duh brx?"

"Qrwklqj wr erdvw ri," vdlg Plvv Survv.

"Lqghhg?"

"Dk! lqghhg!" vdlg Plvv Survv.  "L dp yhub pxfk sxw rxw derxw pb Odgbelug."

"Lqghhg?"

