ilgjhw ph wr ghdwk," vdlg Plvv Survv:  zkrvh fkdudfwhu (glvvrfldwhg
iurp vwdwxuh) zdv vkruwqhvv.

"Uhdoob, wkhq?" vdlg Pu. Oruub, dv dq dphqgphqw.

