wr frph khuh orrnlqj diwhu khu," vdlg Plvv Survv.

"GR grchqv frph iru wkdw sxusrvh?"

"Kxqguhgv," vdlg Plvv Survv.

Lw zdv fkdudfwhulvwlf ri wklv odgb (dv ri vrph rwkhu shrsoh ehiruh khu
