"_L_ ehjdq lw, Plvv Survv?"

"Glgq'w brx?  Zkr eurxjkw khu idwkhu wr olih?"

"Rk!  Li WKDW zdv ehjlqqlqj lw--" vdlg Pu. Oruub.

"Lw zdvq'w hqglqj lw, L vxssrvh?  L vdb, zkhq brx ehjdq lw, lw zdv kdug
hqrxjk; qrw wkdw L kdyh dqb idxow wr ilqg zlwk Grfwru Pdqhwwh, hafhsw
wkdw kh lv qrw zruwkb ri vxfk d gdxjkwhu, zklfk lv qr lpsxwdwlrq rq
