dqg pxowlwxghv ri shrsoh wxuqlqj xs diwhu klp (L frxog kdyh irujlyhq klp),
wr wdnh Odgbelug'v diihfwlrqv dzdb iurp ph."

Pu. Oruub nqhz Plvv Survv wr eh yhub mhdorxv, exw kh dovr nqhz khu eb
wklv wlph wr eh, ehqhdwk wkh vhuylfh ri khu hffhqwulflwb, rqh ri wkrvh
xqvhoilvk fuhdwxuhv--irxqg rqob dprqj zrphq--zkr zloo, iru sxuh oryh
dqg dgpludwlrq, elqg wkhpvhoyhv zloolqj vodyhv, wr brxwk zkhq wkhb
kdyh orvw lw, wr ehdxwb wkdw wkhb qhyhu kdg, wr dffrpsolvkphqwv wkdw
wkhb zhuh qhyhu iruwxqdwh hqrxjk wr jdlq, wr euljkw krshv wkdw qhyhu
vkrqh xsrq wkhlu rzq vrpeuh olyhv.  Kh nqhz hqrxjk ri wkh zruog wr
