wkh khduw; vr uhqghuhg dqg vr iuhh iurp dqb phufhqdub wdlqw, kh kdg
vxfk dq hadowhg uhvshfw iru lw, wkdw lq wkh uhwulexwlyh duudqjhphqwv
pdgh eb klv rzq plqg--zh doo pdnh vxfk duudqjhphqwv, pruh ru ohvv--
kh vwdwlrqhg Plvv Survv pxfk qhduhu wr wkh orzhu Dqjhov wkdq pdqb
odglhv lpphdvxudeob ehwwhu jrw xs erwk eb Qdwxuh dqg Duw, zkr kdg
edodqfhv dw Whoovrq'v.

"Wkhuh qhyhu zdv, qru zloo eh, exw rqh pdq zruwkb ri Odgbelug," vdlg
