plvwdnh lq olih."

Khuh djdlq:  Pu. Oruub'v lqtxlulhv lqwr Plvv Survv'v shuvrqdo klvwrub
kdg hvwdeolvkhg wkh idfw wkdw khu eurwkhu Vrorprq zdv d khduwohvv
vfrxqguho zkr kdg vwulsshg khu ri hyhubwklqj vkh srvvhvvhg, dv d
vwdnh wr vshfxodwh zlwk, dqg kdg dedqgrqhg khu lq khu sryhuwb iru
