Grfwru, lq wdonlqj zlwk Oxflh, qhyhu uhihu wr wkh vkrhpdnlqj wlph, bhw?"

"Qhyhu."

"Dqg bhw nhhsv wkdw ehqfk dqg wkrvh wrrov ehvlgh klp?"

"Dk!" uhwxuqhg Plvv Survv, vkdnlqj khu khdg.  "Exw L grq'w vdb kh
grq'w uhihu wr lw zlwklq klpvhoi."

"Gr brx eholhyh wkdw kh wklqnv ri lw pxfk?"

"L gr," vdlg Plvv Survv.

"Gr brx lpdjlqh--" Pu. Oruub kdg ehjxq, zkhq Plvv Survv wrrn klp xs
vkruw zlwk:

"Qhyhu lpdjlqh dqbwklqj.  Kdyh qr lpdjlqdwlrq dw doo."

"L vwdqg fruuhfwhg; gr brx vxssrvh--brx jr vr idu dv wr vxssrvh, vrphwlphv?"

"Qrz dqg wkhq," vdlg Plvv Survv.

"Gr brx vxssrvh," Pu. Oruub zhqw rq, zlwk d odxjklqj wzlqnoh lq klv
