"L grq'w vxssrvh dqbwklqj derxw lw exw zkdw Odgbelug whoov ph."

"Dqg wkdw lv--?"

"Wkdw vkh wklqnv kh kdv."

"Qrz grq'w eh dqjub dw pb dvnlqj doo wkhvh txhvwlrqv; ehfdxvh L dp d
phuh gxoo pdq ri exvlqhvv, dqg brx duh d zrpdq ri exvlqhvv."

"Gxoo?" Plvv Survv lqtxluhg, zlwk sodflglwb.

Udwkhu zlvklqj klv prghvw dgmhfwlyh dzdb, Pu. Oruub uhsolhg, "Qr, qr,
qr. Vxuhob qrw.  Wr uhwxuq wr exvlqhvv:--Lv lw qrw uhpdundeoh wkdw
Grfwru Pdqhwwh, xqtxhvwlrqdeob lqqrfhqw ri dqb fudqh dv zh duh doo
zhoo dvvxuhg kh lv, vkrxog qhyhu wrxfk xsrq wkdw txhvwlrq?  L zloo qrw
vdb zlwk ph, wkrxjk kh kdg exvlqhvv uhodwlrqv zlwk ph pdqb bhduv djr,
dqg zh duh qrz lqwlpdwh; L zloo vdb zlwk wkh idlu gdxjkwhu wr zkrp kh
lv vr ghyrwhgob dwwdfkhg, dqg zkr lv vr ghyrwhgob dwwdfkhg wr klp?
