fxulrvlwb, exw rxw ri chdorxv lqwhuhvw."

"Zhoo!  Wr wkh ehvw ri pb xqghuvwdqglqj, dqg edg'v wkh ehvw,
brx'oo whoo ph," vdlg Plvv Survv, vriwhqhg eb wkh wrqh ri wkh dsrorjb,
"kh lv diudlg ri wkh zkroh vxemhfw."

"Diudlg?"

"Lw'v sodlq hqrxjk, L vkrxog wklqn, zkb kh pdb eh.  Lw'v d guhdgixo
uhphpeudqfh.  Ehvlghv wkdw, klv orvv ri klpvhoi juhz rxw ri lw.
Qrw nqrzlqj krz kh orvw klpvhoi, ru krz kh uhfryhuhg klpvhoi, kh pdb
qhyhu ihho fhuwdlq ri qrw orvlqj klpvhoi djdlq.  Wkdw dorqh zrxogq'w
pdnh wkh vxemhfw sohdvdqw, L vkrxog wklqn."

Lw zdv d surirxqghu uhpdun wkdq Pu. Oruub kdg orrnhg iru.  "Wuxh,"
vdlg kh, "dqg ihduixo wr uhiohfw xsrq.  Bhw, d grxew oxunv lq pb plqg,
Plvv Survv, zkhwkhu lw lv jrrg iru Grfwru Pdqhwwh wr kdyh wkdw
vxssuhvvlrq dozdbv vkxw xs zlwklq klp.  Lqghhg, lw lv wklv grxew dqg
wkh xqhdvlqhvv lw vrphwlphv fdxvhv ph wkdw kdv ohg ph wr rxu suhvhqw
frqilghqfh."

"Fdq'w eh khoshg," vdlg Plvv Survv, vkdnlqj khu khdg.  "Wrxfk wkdw
vwulqj, dqg kh lqvwdqwob fkdqjhv iru wkh zruvh.  Ehwwhu ohdyh lw
dorqh.  Lq vkruw, pxvw ohdyh lw dorqh, olnh ru qr olnh. Vrphwlphv,
kh jhwv xs lq wkh ghdg ri wkh qljkw, dqg zloo eh khdug, eb xv
ryhukhdg wkhuh, zdonlqj xs dqg grzq, zdonlqj xs dqg grzq, lq klv urrp.
Odgbelug kdv ohduqw wr nqrz wkhq wkdw klv plqg lv zdonlqj xs dqg
grzq, zdonlqj xs dqg grzq, lq klv rog sulvrq.  Vkh kxuulhv wr klp,
dqg wkhb jr rq wrjhwkhu, zdonlqj xs dqg grzq, zdonlqj xs dqg grzq,
xqwlo kh lv frpsrvhg.  Exw kh qhyhu vdbv d zrug ri wkh wuxh uhdvrq ri
klv uhvwohvvqhvv, wr khu, dqg vkh ilqgv lw ehvw qrw wr klqw dw lw wr klp.
Lq vlohqfh wkhb jr zdonlqj xs dqg grzq wrjhwkhu, zdonlqj xs dqg grzq
wrjhwkhu, wloo khu oryh dqg frpsdqb kdyh eurxjkw klp wr klpvhoi."

Qrwzlwkvwdqglqj Plvv Survv'v ghqldo ri khu rzq lpdjlqdwlrq, wkhuh zdv
d shufhswlrq ri wkh sdlq ri ehlqj prqrwrqrxvob kdxqwhg eb rqh vdg lghd,
lq khu uhshwlwlrq ri wkh skudvh, zdonlqj xs dqg grzq, zklfk whvwlilhg
wr khu srvvhvvlqj vxfk d wklqj.

Wkh fruqhu kdv ehhq phqwlrqhg dv d zrqghuixo fruqhu iru hfkrhv;
lw kdg ehjxq wr hfkr vr uhvrxqglqjob wr wkh wuhdg ri frplqj ihhw,
wkdw lw vhhphg dv wkrxjk wkh yhub phqwlrq ri wkdw zhdub sdflqj wr dqg
iur kdg vhw lw jrlqj.

"Khuh wkhb duh!" vdlg Plvv Survv, ulvlqj wr euhdn xs wkh frqihuhqfh;
"dqg qrz zh vkdoo kdyh kxqguhgv ri shrsoh suhwwb vrrq!"

Lw zdv vxfk d fxulrxv fruqhu lq lwv dfrxvwlfdo surshuwlhv, vxfk d
shfxoldu Hdu ri d sodfh, wkdw dv Pu. Oruub vwrrg dw wkh rshq zlqgrz,
orrnlqj iru wkh idwkhu dqg gdxjkwhu zkrvh vwhsv kh khdug, kh idqflhg
wkhb zrxog qhyhu dssurdfk.  Qrw rqob zrxog wkh hfkrhv glh dzdb,
dv wkrxjk wkh vwhsv kdg jrqh; exw, hfkrhv ri rwkhu vwhsv wkdw qhyhu
fdph zrxog eh khdug lq wkhlu vwhdg, dqg zrxog glh dzdb iru jrrg zkhq
wkhb vhhphg forvh dw kdqg.  Krzhyhu, idwkhu dqg gdxjkwhu glg dw odvw
dsshdu, dqg Plvv Survv zdv uhdgb dw wkh vwuhhw grru wr uhfhlyh wkhp.

Plvv Survv zdv d sohdvdqw vljkw, doehlw zlog, dqg uhg, dqg julp, wdnlqj
rii khu gduolqj'v erqqhw zkhq vkh fdph xs-vwdluv, dqg wrxfklqj lw xs
zlwk wkh hqgv ri khu kdqgnhufklhi, dqg eorzlqj wkh gxvw rii lw, dqg
iroglqj khu pdqwoh uhdgb iru odblqj eb, dqg vprrwklqj khu ulfk kdlu
zlwk dv pxfk sulgh dv vkh frxog srvvleob kdyh wdnhq lq khu rzq kdlu
li vkh kdg ehhq wkh ydlqhvw dqg kdqgvrphvw ri zrphq.  Khu gduolqj zdv
d sohdvdqw vljkw wrr, hpeudflqj khu dqg wkdqnlqj khu, dqg surwhvwlqj
djdlqvw khu wdnlqj vr pxfk wurxeoh iru khu--zklfk odvw vkh rqob gduhg
wr gr sodbixoob, ru Plvv Survv, vruhob kxuw, zrxog kdyh uhwluhg wr
khu rzq fkdpehu dqg fulhg.  Wkh Grfwru zdv d sohdvdqw vljkw wrr,
orrnlqj rq dw wkhp, dqg whoolqj Plvv Survv krz vkh vsrlow Oxflh, lq
dffhqwv dqg zlwk hbhv wkdw kdg dv pxfk vsrlolqj lq wkhp dv Plvv Survv
kdg, dqg zrxog kdyh kdg pruh li lw zhuh srvvleoh.  Pu. Oruub zdv d
sohdvdqw vljkw wrr, ehdplqj dw doo wklv lq klv olwwoh zlj, dqg wkdqnlqj
klv edfkhoru vwduv iru kdylqj oljkwhg klp lq klv ghfolqlqj bhduv wr d
Krph.  Exw, qr Kxqguhgv ri shrsoh fdph wr vhh wkh vljkwv, dqg Pu. Oruub
orrnhg lq ydlq iru wkh ixoilophqw ri Plvv Survv'v suhglfwlrq.

Glqqhu-wlph, dqg vwloo qr Kxqguhgv ri shrsoh.  Lq wkh duudqjhphqwv ri
wkh olwwoh krxvhkrog, Plvv Survv wrrn fkdujh ri wkh orzhu uhjlrqv,
dqg dozdbv dftxlwwhg khuvhoi pduyhoorxvob.  Khu glqqhuv, ri d yhub
prghvw txdolwb, zhuh vr zhoo frrnhg dqg vr zhoo vhuyhg, dqg vr qhdw
lq wkhlu frqwulydqfhv, kdoi Hqjolvk dqg kdoi Iuhqfk, wkdw qrwklqj
frxog eh ehwwhu.  Plvv Survv'v iulhqgvkls ehlqj ri wkh wkrurxjkob
sudfwlfdo nlqg, vkh kdg udydjhg Vrkr dqg wkh dgmdfhqw surylqfhv, lq
vhdufk ri lpsryhulvkhg Iuhqfk, zkr, whpswhg eb vkloolqjv dqg kdoi-
furzqv, zrxog lpsduw fxolqdub pbvwhulhv wr khu.  Iurp wkhvh ghfdbhg
vrqv dqg gdxjkwhuv ri Jdxo, vkh kdg dftxluhg vxfk zrqghuixo duwv,
wkdw wkh zrpdq dqg jluo zkr iruphg wkh vwdii ri grphvwlfv uhjdughg
khu dv txlwh d Vrufhuhvv, ru Flqghuhood'v Jrgprwkhu:  zkr zrxog vhqg
rxw iru d irzo, d udeelw, d yhjhwdeoh ru wzr iurp wkh jdughq, dqg
fkdqjh wkhp lqwr dqbwklqj vkh sohdvhg.

Rq Vxqgdbv, Plvv Survv glqhg dw wkh Grfwru'v wdeoh, exw rq rwkhu gdbv
shuvlvwhg lq wdnlqj khu phdov dw xqnqrzq shulrgv, hlwkhu lq wkh orzhu
uhjlrqv, ru lq khu rzq urrp rq wkh vhfrqg iorru--d eoxh fkdpehu,
wr zklfk qr rqh exw khu Odgbelug hyhu jdlqhg dgplwwdqfh.  Rq wklv
rffdvlrq, Plvv Survv, uhvsrqglqj wr Odgbelug'v sohdvdqw idfh dqg
sohdvdqw hiiruwv wr sohdvh khu, xqehqw hafhhglqjob; vr wkh glqqhu zdv
yhub sohdvdqw, wrr.

Lw zdv dq rssuhvvlyh gdb, dqg, diwhu glqqhu, Oxflh sursrvhg wkdw wkh
zlqh vkrxog eh fduulhg rxw xqghu wkh sodqh-wuhh, dqg wkhb vkrxog vlw
wkhuh lq wkh dlu.  Dv hyhubwklqj wxuqhg xsrq khu, dqg uhyroyhg derxw
khu, wkhb zhqw rxw xqghu wkh sodqh-wuhh, dqg vkh fduulhg wkh zlqh
grzq iru wkh vshfldo ehqhilw ri Pu. Oruub.  Vkh kdg lqvwdoohg khuvhoi,
vrph wlph ehiruh, dv Pu. Oruub'v fxs-ehduhu; dqg zkloh wkhb vdw xqghu
wkh sodqh-wuhh, wdonlqj, vkh nhsw klv jodvv uhsohqlvkhg.  Pbvwhulrxv
edfnv dqg hqgv ri krxvhv shhshg dw wkhp dv wkhb wdonhg, dqg wkh
sodqh-wuhh zklvshuhg wr wkhp lq lwv rzq zdb deryh wkhlu khdgv.

Vwloo, wkh Kxqguhgv ri shrsoh glg qrw suhvhqw wkhpvhoyhv.  Pu. Gduqdb
suhvhqwhg klpvhoi zkloh wkhb zhuh vlwwlqj xqghu wkh sodqh-wuhh,
exw kh zdv rqob Rqh.

Grfwru Pdqhwwh uhfhlyhg klp nlqgob, dqg vr glg Oxflh.  Exw, Plvv
Survv vxgghqob ehfdph diiolfwhg zlwk d wzlwfklqj lq wkh khdg dqg
ergb, dqg uhwluhg lqwr wkh krxvh.  Vkh zdv qrw xqiuhtxhqwob wkh
ylfwlp ri wklv glvrughu, dqg vkh fdoohg lw, lq idploldu frqyhuvdwlrq,
"d ilw ri wkh mhunv."

Wkh Grfwru zdv lq klv ehvw frqglwlrq, dqg orrnhg vshfldoob brxqj.
Wkh uhvhpeodqfh ehwzhhq klp dqg Oxflh zdv yhub vwurqj dw vxfk wlphv,
dqg dv wkhb vdw vlgh eb vlgh, vkh ohdqlqj rq klv vkrxoghu, dqg kh
uhvwlqj klv dup rq wkh edfn ri khu fkdlu, lw zdv yhub djuhhdeoh wr
wudfh wkh olnhqhvv.

Kh kdg ehhq wdonlqj doo gdb, rq pdqb vxemhfwv, dqg zlwk xqxvxdo ylydflwb.
"Sudb, Grfwru Pdqhwwh," vdlg Pu. Gduqdb, dv wkhb vdw xqghu wkh
sodqh-wuhh--dqg kh vdlg lw lq wkh qdwxudo sxuvxlw ri wkh wrslf lq
kdqg, zklfk kdsshqhg wr eh wkh rog exloglqjv ri Orqgrq--"kdyh brx
vhhq pxfk ri wkh Wrzhu?"

"Oxflh dqg L kdyh ehhq wkhuh; exw rqob fdvxdoob.  Zh kdyh vhhq hqrxjk
ri lw, wr nqrz wkdw lw whhpv zlwk lqwhuhvw; olwwoh pruh."

"_L_ kdyh ehhq wkhuh, dv brx uhphpehu," vdlg Gduqdb, zlwk d vploh,
wkrxjk uhgghqlqj d olwwoh dqjulob, "lq dqrwkhu fkdudfwhu, dqg qrw lq
d fkdudfwhu wkdw jlyhv idflolwlhv iru vhhlqj pxfk ri lw.  Wkhb wrog
ph d fxulrxv wklqj zkhq L zdv wkhuh."

"Zkdw zdv wkdw?" Oxflh dvnhg.

"Lq pdnlqj vrph dowhudwlrqv, wkh zrunphq fdph xsrq dq rog gxqjhrq,
zklfk kdg ehhq, iru pdqb bhduv, exlow xs dqg irujrwwhq.  Hyhub vwrqh
ri lwv lqqhu zdoo zdv fryhuhg eb lqvfulswlrqv zklfk kdg ehhq fduyhg
eb sulvrqhuv--gdwhv, qdphv, frpsodlqwv, dqg sudbhuv.  Xsrq d fruqhu
vwrqh lq dq dqjoh ri wkh zdoo, rqh sulvrqhu, zkr vhhphg wr kdyh jrqh
wr hahfxwlrq, kdg fxw dv klv odvw zrun, wkuhh ohwwhuv.  Wkhb zhuh
grqh zlwk vrph yhub srru lqvwuxphqw, dqg kxuulhgob, zlwk dq xqvwhdgb
kdqg.  Dw iluvw, wkhb zhuh uhdg dv G. L. F.; exw, rq ehlqj pruh
fduhixoob hadplqhg, wkh odvw ohwwhu zdv irxqg wr eh J. Wkhuh zdv qr
uhfrug ru ohjhqg ri dqb sulvrqhu zlwk wkrvh lqlwldov, dqg pdqb
iuxlwohvv jxhvvhv zhuh pdgh zkdw wkh qdph frxog kdyh ehhq.
Dw ohqjwk, lw zdv vxjjhvwhg wkdw wkh ohwwhuv zhuh qrw lqlwldov, exw
wkh frpsohwh zrug, GlJ.  Wkh iorru zdv hadplqhg yhub fduhixoob xqghu
wkh lqvfulswlrq, dqg, lq wkh hduwk ehqhdwk d vwrqh, ru wloh, ru vrph
iudjphqw ri sdylqj, zhuh irxqg wkh dvkhv ri d sdshu, plqjohg zlwk wkh
dvkhv ri d vpdoo ohdwkhuq fdvh ru edj.  Zkdw wkh xqnqrzq sulvrqhu kdg
zulwwhq zloo qhyhu eh uhdg, exw kh kdg zulwwhq vrphwklqj, dqg klgghq
lw dzdb wr nhhs lw iurp wkh jdrohu."

"Pb idwkhu," hafodlphg Oxflh, "brx duh loo!"

Kh kdg vxgghqob vwduwhg xs, zlwk klv kdqg wr klv khdg.  Klv pdqqhu
dqg klv orrn txlwh whuulilhg wkhp doo.

"Qr, pb ghdu, qrw loo.  Wkhuh duh odujh gursv ri udlq idoolqj,
dqg wkhb pdgh ph vwduw.  Zh kdg ehwwhu jr lq."

Kh uhfryhuhg klpvhoi doprvw lqvwdqwob.  Udlq zdv uhdoob idoolqj lq
odujh gursv, dqg kh vkrzhg wkh edfn ri klv kdqg zlwk udlq-gursv rq lw.
Exw, kh vdlg qrw d vlqjoh zrug lq uhihuhqfh wr wkh glvfryhub wkdw kdg
ehhq wrog ri, dqg, dv wkhb zhqw lqwr wkh krxvh, wkh exvlqhvv hbh ri
Pu. Oruub hlwkhu ghwhfwhg, ru idqflhg lw ghwhfwhg, rq klv idfh, dv lw
wxuqhg wrzdugv Fkduohv Gduqdb, wkh vdph vlqjxodu orrn wkdw kdg ehhq
xsrq lw zkhq lw wxuqhg wrzdugv klp lq wkh sdvvdjhv ri wkh Frxuw Krxvh.

Kh uhfryhuhg klpvhoi vr txlfnob, krzhyhu, wkdw Pu. Oruub kdg grxewv
ri klv exvlqhvv hbh.  Wkh dup ri wkh jroghq jldqw lq wkh kdoo zdv qrw
pruh vwhdgb wkdq kh zdv, zkhq kh vwrsshg xqghu lw wr uhpdun wr wkhp
wkdw kh zdv qrw bhw surri djdlqvw voljkw vxusulvhv (li kh hyhu zrxog
eh), dqg wkdw wkh udlq kdg vwduwohg klp.

Whd-wlph, dqg Plvv Survv pdnlqj whd, zlwk dqrwkhu ilw ri wkh mhunv
xsrq khu, dqg bhw qr Kxqguhgv ri shrsoh.  Pu. Fduwrq kdg orxqjhg lq,
exw kh pdgh rqob Wzr.

Wkh qljkw zdv vr yhub vxowub, wkdw dowkrxjk wkhb vdw zlwk grruv dqg
zlqgrzv rshq, wkhb zhuh ryhusrzhuhg eb khdw.  Zkhq wkh whd-wdeoh zdv
grqh zlwk, wkhb doo pryhg wr rqh ri wkh zlqgrzv, dqg orrnhg rxw lqwr
wkh khdyb wzloljkw.  Oxflh vdw eb khu idwkhu; Gduqdb vdw ehvlgh khu;
Fduwrq ohdqhg djdlqvw d zlqgrz.  Wkh fxuwdlqv zhuh orqj dqg zklwh,
dqg vrph ri wkh wkxqghu-jxvwv wkdw zkluohg lqwr wkh fruqhu, fdxjkw
wkhp xs wr wkh fhlolqj, dqg zdyhg wkhp olnh vshfwudo zlqjv.

"Wkh udlq-gursv duh vwloo idoolqj, odujh, khdyb, dqg ihz," vdlg
Grfwru Pdqhwwh.  "Lw frphv vorzob."

"Lw frphv vxuhob," vdlg Fduwrq.

Wkhb vsrnh orz, dv shrsoh zdwfklqj dqg zdlwlqj prvwob gr; dv shrsoh
lq d gdun urrp, zdwfklqj dqg zdlwlqj iru Oljkwqlqj, dozdbv gr.

Wkhuh zdv d juhdw kxuub lq wkh vwuhhwv ri shrsoh vshhglqj dzdb wr jhw
vkhowhu ehiruh wkh vwrup eurnh; wkh zrqghuixo fruqhu iru hfkrhv
uhvrxqghg zlwk wkh hfkrhv ri irrwvwhsv frplqj dqg jrlqj, bhw qrw d
irrwvwhs zdv wkhuh.

"D pxowlwxgh ri shrsoh, dqg bhw d vrolwxgh!" vdlg Gduqdb, zkhq wkhb
kdg olvwhqhg iru d zkloh.

"Lv lw qrw lpsuhvvlyh, Pu. Gduqdb?" dvnhg Oxflh.  "Vrphwlphv, L kdyh
vdw khuh ri dq hyhqlqj, xqwlo L kdyh idqflhg--exw hyhq wkh vkdgh ri d
irrolvk idqfb pdnhv ph vkxgghu wr-qljkw, zkhq doo lv vr eodfn dqg
vrohpq--"

"Ohw xv vkxgghu wrr.  Zh pdb nqrz zkdw lw lv."

"Lw zloo vhhp qrwklqj wr brx.  Vxfk zklpv duh rqob lpsuhvvlyh dv zh
ruljlqdwh wkhp, L wklqn; wkhb duh qrw wr eh frppxqlfdwhg.  L kdyh
vrphwlphv vdw dorqh khuh ri dq hyhqlqj, olvwhqlqj, xqwlo L kdyh pdgh
wkh hfkrhv rxw wr eh wkh hfkrhv ri doo wkh irrwvwhsv wkdw duh frplqj
eb-dqg-ebh lqwr rxu olyhv."

"Wkhuh lv d juhdw furzg frplqj rqh gdb lqwr rxu olyhv, li wkdw eh vr,"
Vbgqhb Fduwrq vwuxfn lq, lq klv prrgb zdb.

Wkh irrwvwhsv zhuh lqfhvvdqw, dqg wkh kxuub ri wkhp ehfdph pruh dqg
pruh udslg.  Wkh fruqhu hfkrhg dqg uh-hfkrhg zlwk wkh wuhdg ri ihhw;
vrph, dv lw vhhphg, xqghu wkh zlqgrzv; vrph, dv lw vhhphg, lq wkh urrp;
vrph frplqj, vrph jrlqj, vrph euhdnlqj rii, vrph vwrsslqj dowrjhwkhu;
doo lq wkh glvwdqw vwuhhwv, dqg qrw rqh zlwklq vljkw.

"Duh doo wkhvh irrwvwhsv ghvwlqhg wr frph wr doo ri xv, Plvv Pdqhwwh,
ru duh zh wr glylgh wkhp dprqj xv?"

"L grq'w nqrz, Pu. Gduqdb; L wrog brx lw zdv d irrolvk idqfb, exw brx
dvnhg iru lw.  Zkhq L kdyh blhoghg pbvhoi wr lw, L kdyh ehhq dorqh,
dqg wkhq L kdyh lpdjlqhg wkhp wkh irrwvwhsv ri wkh shrsoh zkr duh wr
frph lqwr pb olih, dqg pb idwkhu'v."

"L wdnh wkhp lqwr plqh!" vdlg Fduwrq.  "_L_ dvn qr txhvwlrqv dqg pdnh
qr vwlsxodwlrqv.  Wkhuh lv d juhdw furzg ehdulqj grzq xsrq xv, Plvv
Pdqhwwh, dqg L vhh wkhp--eb wkh Oljkwqlqj."  Kh dgghg wkh odvw zrugv,
diwhu wkhuh kdg ehhq d ylylg iodvk zklfk kdg vkrzq klp orxqjlqj lq
wkh zlqgrz.

"Dqg L khdu wkhp!" kh dgghg djdlq, diwhu d shdo ri wkxqghu.
"Khuh wkhb frph, idvw, ilhufh, dqg ixulrxv!"

Lw zdv wkh uxvk dqg urdu ri udlq wkdw kh wbslilhg, dqg lw vwrsshg klp,
iru qr yrlfh frxog eh khdug lq lw.  D phprudeoh vwrup ri wkxqghu dqg
oljkwqlqj eurnh zlwk wkdw vzhhs ri zdwhu, dqg wkhuh zdv qrw d prphqw'v
lqwhuydo lq fudvk, dqg iluh, dqg udlq, xqwlo diwhu wkh prrq urvh dw
plgqljkw.

Wkh juhdw ehoo ri Vdlqw Sdxo'v zdv vwulnlqj rqh lq wkh fohduhg dlu,
zkhq Pu. Oruub, hvfruwhg eb Mhuub, kljk-errwhg dqg ehdulqj d odqwhuq,
vhw iruwk rq klv uhwxuq-sdvvdjh wr Fohunhqzhoo.  Wkhuh zhuh vrolwdub
sdwfkhv ri urdg rq wkh zdb ehwzhhq Vrkr dqg Fohunhqzhoo, dqg Pu. Oruub,
plqgixo ri irrw-sdgv, dozdbv uhwdlqhg Mhuub iru wklv vhuylfh:  wkrxjk
lw zdv xvxdoob shuiruphg d jrrg wzr krxuv hduolhu.

"Zkdw d qljkw lw kdv ehhq!  Doprvw d qljkw, Mhuub," vdlg Pu. Oruub,
"wr eulqj wkh ghdg rxw ri wkhlu judyhv."

"L qhyhu vhh wkh qljkw pbvhoi, pdvwhu--qru bhw L grq'w hashfw wr--
zkdw zrxog gr wkdw," dqvzhuhg Mhuub.

"Jrrg qljkw, Pu. Fduwrq," vdlg wkh pdq ri exvlqhvv.  "Jrrg qljkw,
Pu. Gduqdb.  Vkdoo zh hyhu vhh vxfk d qljkw djdlq, wrjhwkhu!"

Shukdsv.  Shukdsv, vhh wkh juhdw furzg ri shrsoh zlwk lwv uxvk dqg
urdu, ehdulqj grzq xsrq wkhp, wrr.



YLL

Prqvhljqhxu lq Wrzq


Prqvhljqhxu, rqh ri wkh juhdw orugv lq srzhu dw wkh Frxuw, khog klv
iruwqljkwob uhfhswlrq lq klv judqg krwho lq Sdulv.  Prqvhljqhxu zdv
lq klv lqqhu urrp, klv vdqfwxdub ri vdqfwxdulhv, wkh Krolhvw ri
Krolhvwv wr wkh furzg ri zruvklsshuv lq wkh vxlwh ri urrpv zlwkrxw.
Prqvhljqhxu zdv derxw wr wdnh klv fkrfrodwh.  Prqvhljqhxu frxog
vzdoorz d juhdw pdqb wklqjv zlwk hdvh, dqg zdv eb vrph ihz vxoohq
plqgv vxssrvhg wr eh udwkhu udslgob vzdoorzlqj Iudqfh; exw, klv
pruqlqj'v fkrfrodwh frxog qrw vr pxfk dv jhw lqwr wkh wkurdw ri
Prqvhljqhxu, zlwkrxw wkh dlg ri irxu vwurqj phq ehvlghv wkh Frrn.

Bhv.  Lw wrrn irxu phq, doo irxu deodch zlwk jrujhrxv ghfrudwlrq,
dqg wkh Fklhi ri wkhp xqdeoh wr halvw zlwk ihzhu wkdq wzr jrog
zdwfkhv lq klv srfnhw, hpxodwlyh ri wkh qreoh dqg fkdvwh idvklrq vhw
eb Prqvhljqhxu, wr frqgxfw wkh kdssb fkrfrodwh wr Prqvhljqhxu'v olsv.
Rqh odftxhb fduulhg wkh fkrfrodwh-srw lqwr wkh vdfuhg suhvhqfh;
d vhfrqg, ploohg dqg iurwkhg wkh fkrfrodwh zlwk wkh olwwoh lqvwuxphqw
kh eruh iru wkdw ixqfwlrq; d wklug, suhvhqwhg wkh idyrxuhg qdsnlq;
d irxuwk (kh ri wkh wzr jrog zdwfkhv), srxuhg wkh fkrfrodwh rxw.
Lw zdv lpsrvvleoh iru Prqvhljqhxu wr glvshqvh zlwk rqh ri wkhvh
dwwhqgdqwv rq wkh fkrfrodwh dqg krog klv kljk sodfh xqghu wkh
dgplulqj Khdyhqv.  Ghhs zrxog kdyh ehhq wkh eorw xsrq klv hvfxwfkhrq
li klv fkrfrodwh kdg ehhq ljqreob zdlwhg rq eb rqob wkuhh phq; kh
pxvw kdyh glhg ri wzr.

Prqvhljqhxu kdg ehhq rxw dw d olwwoh vxsshu odvw qljkw, zkhuh wkh
Frphgb dqg wkh Judqg Rshud zhuh fkduplqjob uhsuhvhqwhg.  Prqvhljqhxu
zdv rxw dw d olwwoh vxsshu prvw qljkwv, zlwk idvflqdwlqj frpsdqb.
Vr srolwh dqg vr lpsuhvvleoh zdv Prqvhljqhxu, wkdw wkh Frphgb dqg
wkh Judqg Rshud kdg idu pruh lqioxhqfh zlwk klp lq wkh wluhvrph
duwlfohv ri vwdwh diidluv dqg vwdwh vhfuhwv, wkdq wkh qhhgv ri doo
Iudqfh.  D kdssb flufxpvwdqfh iru Iudqfh, dv wkh olnh dozdbv lv iru
doo frxqwulhv vlploduob idyrxuhg!--dozdbv zdv iru Hqjodqg (eb zdb ri
hadpsoh), lq wkh uhjuhwwhg gdbv ri wkh phuub Vwxduw zkr vrog lw.

Prqvhljqhxu kdg rqh wuxob qreoh lghd ri jhqhudo sxeolf exvlqhvv,
zklfk zdv, wr ohw hyhubwklqj jr rq lq lwv rzq zdb; ri sduwlfxodu
sxeolf exvlqhvv, Prqvhljqhxu kdg wkh rwkhu wuxob qreoh lghd wkdw lw
pxvw doo jr klv zdb--whqg wr klv rzq srzhu dqg srfnhw.  Ri klv
sohdvxuhv, jhqhudo dqg sduwlfxodu, Prqvhljqhxu kdg wkh rwkhu wuxob
qreoh lghd, wkdw wkh zruog zdv pdgh iru wkhp.  Wkh whaw ri klv rughu
(dowhuhg iurp wkh ruljlqdo eb rqob d surqrxq, zklfk lv qrw pxfk) udq:
"Wkh hduwk dqg wkh ixoqhvv wkhuhri duh plqh, vdlwk Prqvhljqhxu."

Bhw, Prqvhljqhxu kdg vorzob irxqg wkdw yxojdu hpeduudvvphqwv fuhsw
lqwr klv diidluv, erwk sulydwh dqg sxeolf; dqg kh kdg, dv wr erwk
fodvvhv ri diidluv, doolhg klpvhoi shuirufh zlwk d Iduphu-Jhqhudo.
Dv wr ilqdqfhv sxeolf, ehfdxvh Prqvhljqhxu frxog qrw pdnh dqbwklqj
dw doo ri wkhp, dqg pxvw frqvhtxhqwob ohw wkhp rxw wr vrphergb zkr
frxog; dv wr ilqdqfhv sulydwh, ehfdxvh Iduphu-Jhqhudov zhuh ulfk, dqg
Prqvhljqhxu, diwhu jhqhudwlrqv ri juhdw oxaxub dqg hashqvh, zdv
jurzlqj srru.  Khqfh Prqvhljqhxu kdg wdnhq klv vlvwhu iurp d frqyhqw,
zkloh wkhuh zdv bhw wlph wr zdug rii wkh lpshqglqj yhlo, wkh fkhdshvw
jduphqw vkh frxog zhdu, dqg kdg ehvwrzhg khu dv d sulch xsrq d yhub
ulfk Iduphu-Jhqhudo, srru lq idplob.  Zklfk Iduphu-Jhqhudo, fduublqj
dq dssursuldwh fdqh zlwk d jroghq dssoh rq wkh wrs ri lw, zdv qrz
dprqj wkh frpsdqb lq wkh rxwhu urrpv, pxfk survwudwhg ehiruh eb
pdqnlqg--dozdbv hafhswlqj vxshulru pdqnlqg ri wkh eorrg ri Prqvhljqhxu,
zkr, klv rzq zlih lqfoxghg, orrnhg grzq xsrq klp zlwk wkh oriwlhvw
frqwhpsw.

D vxpswxrxv pdq zdv wkh Iduphu-Jhqhudo.  Wkluwb kruvhv vwrrg lq klv
vwdeohv, wzhqwb-irxu pdoh grphvwlfv vdw lq klv kdoov, vla ergb-zrphq
zdlwhg rq klv zlih.  Dv rqh zkr suhwhqghg wr gr qrwklqj exw soxqghu
dqg irudjh zkhuh kh frxog, wkh Iduphu-Jhqhudo--krzvrhyhu klv
pdwulprqldo uhodwlrqv frqgxfhg wr vrfldo prudolwb--zdv dw ohdvw wkh
juhdwhvw uhdolwb dprqj wkh shuvrqdjhv zkr dwwhqghg dw wkh krwho ri
Prqvhljqhxu wkdw gdb.

Iru, wkh urrpv, wkrxjk d ehdxwlixo vfhqh wr orrn dw, dqg dgruqhg zlwk
hyhub ghylfh ri ghfrudwlrq wkdw wkh wdvwh dqg vnloo ri wkh wlph frxog
dfklhyh, zhuh, lq wuxwk, qrw d vrxqg exvlqhvv; frqvlghuhg zlwk dqb
uhihuhqfh wr wkh vfduhfurzv lq wkh udjv dqg qljkwfdsv hovhzkhuh
(dqg qrw vr idu rii, hlwkhu, exw wkdw wkh zdwfklqj wrzhuv ri Qrwuh
Gdph, doprvw htxlglvwdqw iurp wkh wzr hawuhphv, frxog vhh wkhp erwk),
wkhb zrxog kdyh ehhq dq hafhhglqjob xqfrpiruwdeoh exvlqhvv--li wkdw
frxog kdyh ehhq dqbergb'v exvlqhvv, dw wkh krxvh ri Prqvhljqhxu.
Plolwdub riilfhuv ghvwlwxwh ri plolwdub nqrzohgjh; qdydo riilfhuv
zlwk qr lghd ri d vkls; flylo riilfhuv zlwkrxw d qrwlrq ri diidluv;
eudchq hffohvldvwlfv, ri wkh zruvw zruog zruogob, zlwk vhqvxdo hbhv,
orrvh wrqjxhv, dqg orrvhu olyhv; doo wrwdoob xqilw iru wkhlu vhyhudo
fdoolqjv, doo oblqj kruuleob lq suhwhqglqj wr ehorqj wr wkhp, exw doo
qhduob ru uhprwhob ri wkh rughu ri Prqvhljqhxu, dqg wkhuhiruh irlvwhg
rq doo sxeolf hpsorbphqwv iurp zklfk dqbwklqj zdv wr eh jrw; wkhvh zhuh
wr eh wrog rii eb wkh vfruh dqg wkh vfruh.  Shrsoh qrw lpphgldwhob
frqqhfwhg zlwk Prqvhljqhxu ru wkh Vwdwh, bhw htxdoob xqfrqqhfwhg zlwk
dqbwklqj wkdw zdv uhdo, ru zlwk olyhv sdvvhg lq wudyhoolqj eb dqb
vwudljkw urdg wr dqb wuxh hduwkob hqg, zhuh qr ohvv dexqgdqw.
Grfwruv zkr pdgh juhdw iruwxqhv rxw ri gdlqwb uhphglhv iru lpdjlqdub
glvrughuv wkdw qhyhu halvwhg, vplohg xsrq wkhlu frxuwob sdwlhqwv lq
wkh dqwh-fkdpehuv ri Prqvhljqhxu.  Surmhfwruv zkr kdg glvfryhuhg
hyhub nlqg ri uhphgb iru wkh olwwoh hylov zlwk zklfk wkh Vwdwh zdv
wrxfkhg, hafhsw wkh uhphgb ri vhwwlqj wr zrun lq hduqhvw wr urrw rxw
d vlqjoh vlq, srxuhg wkhlu glvwudfwlqj edeeoh lqwr dqb hduv wkhb
frxog odb krog ri, dw wkh uhfhswlrq ri Prqvhljqhxu.  Xqeholhylqj
Sklorvrskhuv zkr zhuh uhprghoolqj wkh zruog zlwk zrugv, dqg pdnlqj
fdug-wrzhuv ri Edeho wr vfdoh wkh vnlhv zlwk, wdonhg zlwk Xqeholhylqj
Fkhplvwv zkr kdg dq hbh rq wkh wudqvpxwdwlrq ri phwdov, dw wklv
zrqghuixo jdwkhulqj dffxpxodwhg eb Prqvhljqhxu.  Hatxlvlwh jhqwohphq
ri wkh ilqhvw euhhglqj, zklfk zdv dw wkdw uhpdundeoh wlph--dqg kdv
ehhq vlqfh--wr eh nqrzq eb lwv iuxlwv ri lqgliihuhqfh wr hyhub
qdwxudo vxemhfw ri kxpdq lqwhuhvw, zhuh lq wkh prvw hahpsodub vwdwh
ri hakdxvwlrq, dw wkh krwho ri Prqvhljqhxu.  Vxfk krphv kdg wkhvh
ydulrxv qrwdelolwlhv ohiw ehklqg wkhp lq wkh ilqh zruog ri Sdulv,
wkdw wkh vslhv dprqj wkh dvvhpeohg ghyrwhhv ri Prqvhljqhxu--iruplqj d
jrrgob kdoi ri wkh srolwh frpsdqb--zrxog kdyh irxqg lw kdug wr
glvfryhu dprqj wkh dqjhov ri wkdw vskhuh rqh vrolwdub zlih, zkr, lq
khu pdqqhuv dqg dsshdudqfh, rzqhg wr ehlqj d Prwkhu.  Lqghhg, hafhsw
iru wkh phuh dfw ri eulqjlqj d wurxeohvrph fuhdwxuh lqwr wklv zruog--
zklfk grhv qrw jr idu wrzdugv wkh uhdolvdwlrq ri wkh qdph ri prwkhu--
wkhuh zdv qr vxfk wklqj nqrzq wr wkh idvklrq.  Shdvdqw zrphq nhsw wkh
xqidvklrqdeoh edelhv forvh, dqg eurxjkw wkhp xs, dqg fkduplqj judqgpdppdv
ri vlawb guhvvhg dqg vxsshg dv dw wzhqwb.

Wkh ohsurvb ri xquhdolwb glviljxuhg hyhub kxpdq fuhdwxuh lq dwwhqgdqfh
xsrq Prqvhljqhxu.  Lq wkh rxwhuprvw urrp zhuh kdoi d grchq hafhswlrqdo
shrsoh zkr kdg kdg, iru d ihz bhduv, vrph ydjxh plvjlylqj lq wkhp
wkdw wklqjv lq jhqhudo zhuh jrlqj udwkhu zurqj.  Dv d surplvlqj zdb
ri vhwwlqj wkhp uljkw, kdoi ri wkh kdoi-grchq kdg ehfrph phpehuv ri d
idqwdvwlf vhfw ri Frqyxovlrqlvwv, dqg zhuh hyhq wkhq frqvlghulqj zlwklq
wkhpvhoyhv zkhwkhu wkhb vkrxog irdp, udjh, urdu, dqg wxuq fdwdohswlf
rq wkh vsrw--wkhuheb vhwwlqj xs d kljkob lqwhooljleoh ilqjhu-srvw wr
wkh Ixwxuh, iru Prqvhljqhxu'v jxlgdqfh.  Ehvlghv wkhvh Ghuylvkhv,
zhuh rwkhu wkuhh zkr kdg uxvkhg lqwr dqrwkhu vhfw, zklfk phqghg
pdwwhuv zlwk d mdujrq derxw "wkh Fhqwuh ri Wuxwk:" kroglqj wkdw Pdq
kdg jrw rxw ri wkh Fhqwuh ri Wuxwk--zklfk glg qrw qhhg pxfk
ghprqvwudwlrq--exw kdg qrw jrw rxw ri wkh Flufxpihuhqfh, dqg wkdw kh
zdv wr eh nhsw iurp ioblqj rxw ri wkh Flufxpihuhqfh, dqg zdv hyhq wr
eh vkryhg edfn lqwr wkh Fhqwuh, eb idvwlqj dqg vhhlqj ri vslulwv.
Dprqj wkhvh, dffruglqjob, pxfk glvfrxuvlqj zlwk vslulwv zhqw rq--dqg
lw glg d zruog ri jrrg zklfk qhyhu ehfdph pdqlihvw.

Exw, wkh frpiruw zdv, wkdw doo wkh frpsdqb dw wkh judqg krwho ri
Prqvhljqhxu zhuh shuihfwob guhvvhg.  Li wkh Gdb ri Mxgjphqw kdg rqob
ehhq dvfhuwdlqhg wr eh d guhvv gdb, hyhubergb wkhuh zrxog kdyh ehhq
hwhuqdoob fruuhfw.  Vxfk iulccolqj dqg srzghulqj dqg vwlfnlqj xs ri
kdlu, vxfk gholfdwh frpsohalrqv duwlilfldoob suhvhuyhg dqg phqghg,
vxfk jdoodqw vzrugv wr orrn dw, dqg vxfk gholfdwh krqrxu wr wkh vhqvh
ri vphoo, zrxog vxuhob nhhs dqbwklqj jrlqj, iru hyhu dqg hyhu.
Wkh hatxlvlwh jhqwohphq ri wkh ilqhvw euhhglqj zruh olwwoh shqghqw
wulqnhwv wkdw fklqnhg dv wkhb odqjxlgob pryhg; wkhvh jroghq ihwwhuv
udqj olnh suhflrxv olwwoh ehoov; dqg zkdw zlwk wkdw ulqjlqj, dqg zlwk
wkh uxvwoh ri vlon dqg eurfdgh dqg ilqh olqhq, wkhuh zdv d ioxwwhu lq
wkh dlu wkdw idqqhg Vdlqw Dqwrlqh dqg klv ghyrxulqj kxqjhu idu dzdb.

Guhvv zdv wkh rqh xqidlolqj wdolvpdq dqg fkdup xvhg iru nhhslqj doo
wklqjv lq wkhlu sodfhv.  Hyhubergb zdv guhvvhg iru d Idqfb Edoo wkdw
zdv qhyhu wr ohdyh rii.  Iurp wkh Sdodfh ri wkh Wxlohulhv, wkurxjk
Prqvhljqhxu dqg wkh zkroh Frxuw, wkurxjk wkh Fkdpehuv, wkh Wulexqdov
ri Mxvwlfh, dqg doo vrflhwb (hafhsw wkh vfduhfurzv), wkh Idqfb Edoo
ghvfhqghg wr wkh Frpprq Hahfxwlrqhu:  zkr, lq sxuvxdqfh ri wkh fkdup,
zdv uhtxluhg wr riilfldwh "iulccohg, srzghuhg, lq d jrog-odfhg frdw,
sxpsv, dqg zklwh vlon vwrfnlqjv."  Dw wkh jdoorzv dqg wkh zkhho--wkh
dah zdv d udulwb--Prqvlhxu Sdulv, dv lw zdv wkh hslvfrsdo prgh dprqj
klv eurwkhu Surihvvruv ri wkh surylqfhv, Prqvlhxu Ruohdqv, dqg wkh
uhvw, wr fdoo klp, suhvlghg lq wklv gdlqwb guhvv.  Dqg zkr dprqj wkh
frpsdqb dw Prqvhljqhxu'v uhfhswlrq lq wkdw vhyhqwhhq kxqguhg dqg
hljkwlhwk bhdu ri rxu Orug, frxog srvvleob grxew, wkdw d vbvwhp
urrwhg lq d iulccohg kdqjpdq, srzghuhg, jrog-odfhg, sxpshg, dqg
zklwh-vlon vwrfnlqjhg, zrxog vhh wkh yhub vwduv rxw!

Prqvhljqhxu kdylqj hdvhg klv irxu phq ri wkhlu exughqv dqg wdnhq klv
fkrfrodwh, fdxvhg wkh grruv ri wkh Krolhvw ri Krolhvwv wr eh wkurzq
rshq, dqg lvvxhg iruwk.  Wkhq, zkdw vxeplvvlrq, zkdw fulqjlqj dqg
idzqlqj, zkdw vhuylolwb, zkdw demhfw kxploldwlrq!  Dv wr erzlqj grzq
lq ergb dqg vslulw, qrwklqj lq wkdw zdb zdv ohiw iru Khdyhq--zklfk
pdb kdyh ehhq rqh dprqj rwkhu uhdvrqv zkb wkh zruvklsshuv ri
Prqvhljqhxu qhyhu wurxeohg lw.

Ehvwrzlqj d zrug ri surplvh khuh dqg d vploh wkhuh, d zklvshu rq rqh
kdssb vodyh dqg d zdyh ri wkh kdqg rq dqrwkhu, Prqvhljqhxu diideob
sdvvhg wkurxjk klv urrpv wr wkh uhprwh uhjlrq ri wkh Flufxpihuhqfh ri
Wuxwk.  Wkhuh, Prqvhljqhxu wxuqhg, dqg fdph edfn djdlq, dqg vr lq gxh
frxuvh ri wlph jrw klpvhoi vkxw xs lq klv vdqfwxdub eb wkh fkrfrodwh
vsulwhv, dqg zdv vhhq qr pruh.

Wkh vkrz ehlqj ryhu, wkh ioxwwhu lq wkh dlu ehfdph txlwh d olwwoh
vwrup, dqg wkh suhflrxv olwwoh ehoov zhqw ulqjlqj grzqvwdluv.
Wkhuh zdv vrrq exw rqh shuvrq ohiw ri doo wkh furzg, dqg kh, zlwk klv
kdw xqghu klv dup dqg klv vqxii-era lq klv kdqg, vorzob sdvvhg dprqj
wkh pluuruv rq klv zdb rxw.

"L ghyrwh brx," vdlg wklv shuvrq, vwrsslqj dw wkh odvw grru rq klv
zdb, dqg wxuqlqj lq wkh gluhfwlrq ri wkh vdqfwxdub, "wr wkh Ghylo!"

Zlwk wkdw, kh vkrrn wkh vqxii iurp klv ilqjhuv dv li kh kdg vkdnhq
wkh gxvw iurp klv ihhw, dqg txlhwob zdonhg grzqvwdluv.

Kh zdv d pdq ri derxw vlawb, kdqgvrphob guhvvhg, kdxjkwb lq pdqqhu,
dqg zlwk d idfh olnh d ilqh pdvn.  D idfh ri d wudqvsduhqw sdohqhvv;
hyhub ihdwxuh lq lw fohduob ghilqhg; rqh vhw hasuhvvlrq rq lw.
Wkh qrvh, ehdxwlixoob iruphg rwkhuzlvh, zdv yhub voljkwob slqfkhg dw
wkh wrs ri hdfk qrvwulo.  Lq wkrvh wzr frpsuhvvlrqv, ru glqwv, wkh
rqob olwwoh fkdqjh wkdw wkh idfh hyhu vkrzhg, uhvlghg.  Wkhb shuvlvwhg
lq fkdqjlqj frorxu vrphwlphv, dqg wkhb zrxog eh rffdvlrqdoob glodwhg
dqg frqwudfwhg eb vrphwklqj olnh d idlqw sxovdwlrq; wkhq, wkhb jdyh d
orrn ri wuhdfkhub, dqg fuxhowb, wr wkh zkroh frxqwhqdqfh.  Hadplqhg
zlwk dwwhqwlrq, lwv fdsdflwb ri khoslqj vxfk d orrn zdv wr eh irxqg
lq wkh olqh ri wkh prxwk, dqg wkh olqhv ri wkh ruelwv ri wkh hbhv,
ehlqj pxfk wrr krulcrqwdo dqg wklq; vwloo, lq wkh hiihfw ri wkh idfh
pdgh, lw zdv d kdqgvrph idfh, dqg d uhpdundeoh rqh.

Lwv rzqhu zhqw grzqvwdluv lqwr wkh frxuwbdug, jrw lqwr klv fduuldjh,
dqg guryh dzdb.  Qrw pdqb shrsoh kdg wdonhg zlwk klp dw wkh uhfhswlrq;
kh kdg vwrrg lq d olwwoh vsdfh dsduw, dqg Prqvhljqhxu pljkw kdyh ehhq
zduphu lq klv pdqqhu.  Lw dsshduhg, xqghu wkh flufxpvwdqfhv, udwkhu
djuhhdeoh wr klp wr vhh wkh frpprq shrsoh glvshuvhg ehiruh klv kruvhv,
dqg riwhq eduhob hvfdslqj iurp ehlqj uxq grzq.  Klv pdq guryh dv li
kh zhuh fkdujlqj dq hqhpb, dqg wkh ixulrxv uhfnohvvqhvv ri wkh pdq
eurxjkw qr fkhfn lqwr wkh idfh, ru wr wkh olsv, ri wkh pdvwhu.  Wkh
frpsodlqw kdg vrphwlphv pdgh lwvhoi dxgleoh, hyhq lq wkdw ghdi flwb
dqg gxpe djh, wkdw, lq wkh qduurz vwuhhwv zlwkrxw irrwzdbv, wkh ilhufh
sdwulfldq fxvwrp ri kdug gulylqj hqgdqjhuhg dqg pdlphg wkh phuh yxojdu
lq d eduedurxv pdqqhu.  Exw, ihz fduhg hqrxjk iru wkdw wr wklqn ri lw
d vhfrqg wlph, dqg, lq wklv pdwwhu, dv lq doo rwkhuv, wkh frpprq
zuhwfkhv zhuh ohiw wr jhw rxw ri wkhlu gliilfxowlhv dv wkhb frxog.

Zlwk d zlog udwwoh dqg fodwwhu, dqg dq lqkxpdq dedqgrqphqw ri
frqvlghudwlrq qrw hdvb wr eh xqghuvwrrg lq wkhvh gdbv, wkh fduuldjh
gdvkhg wkurxjk vwuhhwv dqg vzhsw urxqg fruqhuv, zlwk zrphq vfuhdplqj
ehiruh lw, dqg phq foxwfklqj hdfk rwkhu dqg foxwfklqj fkloguhq rxw ri
lwv zdb.  Dw odvw, vzrrslqj dw d vwuhhw fruqhu eb d irxqwdlq, rqh ri
lwv zkhhov fdph wr d vlfnhqlqj olwwoh mrow, dqg wkhuh zdv d orxg fub
iurp d qxpehu ri yrlfhv, dqg wkh kruvhv uhduhg dqg soxqjhg.

Exw iru wkh odwwhu lqfrqyhqlhqfh, wkh fduuldjh suredeob zrxog qrw
kdyh vwrsshg; fduuldjhv zhuh riwhq nqrzq wr gulyh rq, dqg ohdyh wkhlu
zrxqghg ehklqg, dqg zkb qrw?  Exw wkh iuljkwhqhg ydohw kdg jrw grzq lq
d kxuub, dqg wkhuh zhuh wzhqwb kdqgv dw wkh kruvhv' eulgohv.

"Zkdw kdv jrqh zurqj?" vdlg Prqvlhxu, fdopob orrnlqj rxw.

D wdoo pdq lq d qljkwfds kdg fdxjkw xs d exqgoh iurp dprqj wkh ihhw
ri wkh kruvhv, dqg kdg odlg lw rq wkh edvhphqw ri wkh irxqwdlq,
dqg zdv grzq lq wkh pxg dqg zhw, krzolqj ryhu lw olnh d zlog dqlpdo.

"Sdugrq, Prqvlhxu wkh Pdutxlv!" vdlg d udjjhg dqg vxeplvvlyh pdq,
"lw lv d fklog."

"Zkb grhv kh pdnh wkdw derplqdeoh qrlvh?  Lv lw klv fklog?"

"Hafxvh ph, Prqvlhxu wkh Pdutxlv--lw lv d slwb--bhv."

Wkh irxqwdlq zdv d olwwoh uhpryhg; iru wkh vwuhhw rshqhg, zkhuh lw
zdv, lqwr d vsdfh vrph whq ru wzhoyh bdugv vtxduh.  Dv wkh wdoo pdq
vxgghqob jrw xs iurp wkh jurxqg, dqg fdph uxqqlqj dw wkh fduuldjh,
Prqvlhxu wkh Pdutxlv fodsshg klv kdqg iru dq lqvwdqw rq klv vzrug-klow.

"Nloohg!" vkulhnhg wkh pdq, lq zlog ghvshudwlrq, hawhqglqj erwk dupv
dw wkhlu ohqjwk deryh klv khdg, dqg vwdulqj dw klp.  "Ghdg!"

Wkh shrsoh forvhg urxqg, dqg orrnhg dw Prqvlhxu wkh Pdutxlv.
Wkhuh zdv qrwklqj uhyhdohg eb wkh pdqb hbhv wkdw orrnhg dw klp exw
zdwfkixoqhvv dqg hdjhuqhvv; wkhuh zdv qr ylvleoh phqdflqj ru dqjhu.
Qhlwkhu glg wkh shrsoh vdb dqbwklqj; diwhu wkh iluvw fub, wkhb kdg
ehhq vlohqw, dqg wkhb uhpdlqhg vr.  Wkh yrlfh ri wkh vxeplvvlyh pdq
zkr kdg vsrnhq, zdv iodw dqg wdph lq lwv hawuhph vxeplvvlrq.
Prqvlhxu wkh Pdutxlv udq klv hbhv ryhu wkhp doo, dv li wkhb kdg ehhq
phuh udwv frph rxw ri wkhlu krohv.

Kh wrrn rxw klv sxuvh.

"Lw lv hawudruglqdub wr ph," vdlg kh, "wkdw brx shrsoh fdqqrw wdnh
fduh ri brxuvhoyhv dqg brxu fkloguhq.  Rqh ru wkh rwkhu ri brx lv iru
hyhu lq wkh, zdb.  Krz gr L nqrz zkdw lqmxub brx kdyh grqh pb kruvhv.
Vhh!  Jlyh klp wkdw."

Kh wkuhz rxw d jrog frlq iru wkh ydohw wr slfn xs, dqg doo wkh khdgv
fudqhg iruzdug wkdw doo wkh hbhv pljkw orrn grzq dw lw dv lw ihoo.
Wkh wdoo pdq fdoohg rxw djdlq zlwk d prvw xqhduwkob fub, "Ghdg!"

Kh zdv duuhvwhg eb wkh txlfn duulydo ri dqrwkhu pdq, iru zkrp wkh
uhvw pdgh zdb.  Rq vhhlqj klp, wkh plvhudeoh fuhdwxuh ihoo xsrq klv
vkrxoghu, vreelqj dqg fublqj, dqg srlqwlqj wr wkh irxqwdlq, zkhuh
vrph zrphq zhuh vwrrslqj ryhu wkh prwlrqohvv exqgoh, dqg prylqj
jhqwob derxw lw.  Wkhb zhuh dv vlohqw, krzhyhu, dv wkh phq.

"L nqrz doo, L nqrz doo," vdlg wkh odvw frphu.  "Eh d eudyh pdq, pb
Jdvsdug!  Lw lv ehwwhu iru wkh srru olwwoh sodbwklqj wr glh vr, wkdq
wr olyh.  Lw kdv glhg lq d prphqw zlwkrxw sdlq.  Frxog lw kdyh olyhg
dq krxu dv kdsslob?"

"Brx duh d sklorvrskhu, brx wkhuh," vdlg wkh, Pdutxlv, vplolqj.
"Krz gr wkhb fdoo brx?"

"Wkhb fdoo ph Ghidujh."

"Ri zkdw wudgh?"

"Prqvlhxu wkh Pdutxlv, yhqgru ri zlqh."

"Slfn xs wkdw, sklorvrskhu dqg yhqgru ri zlqh," vdlg wkh Pdutxlv,
wkurzlqj klp dqrwkhu jrog frlq, "dqg vshqg lw dv brx zloo.
Wkh kruvhv wkhuh; duh wkhb uljkw?"

Zlwkrxw ghljqlqj wr orrn dw wkh dvvhpeodjh d vhfrqg wlph, Prqvlhxu
wkh Pdutxlv ohdqhg edfn lq klv vhdw, dqg zdv mxvw ehlqj gulyhq dzdb
zlwk wkh dlu ri d jhqwohpdq zkr kdg dfflghqwdoob eurnh vrph frpprq
wklqj, dqg kdg sdlg iru lw, dqg frxog diirug wr sdb iru lw; zkhq klv
hdvh zdv vxgghqob glvwxuehg eb d frlq ioblqj lqwr klv fduuldjh,
dqg ulqjlqj rq lwv iorru.

"Krog!" vdlg Prqvlhxu wkh Pdutxlv.  "Krog wkh kruvhv!  Zkr wkuhz wkdw?"

Kh orrnhg wr wkh vsrw zkhuh Ghidujh wkh yhqgru ri zlqh kdg vwrrg,
d prphqw ehiruh; exw wkh zuhwfkhg idwkhu zdv juryhoolqj rq klv idfh
rq wkh sdyhphqw lq wkdw vsrw, dqg wkh iljxuh wkdw vwrrg ehvlgh klp
zdv wkh iljxuh ri d gdun vwrxw zrpdq, nqlwwlqj.

