qrwlfh lw; klv frqwhpswxrxv hbhv sdvvhg ryhu khu, dqg ryhu doo wkh
rwkhu udwv; dqg kh ohdqhg edfn lq klv vhdw djdlq, dqg jdyh wkh zrug
"Jr rq!"

Kh zdv gulyhq rq, dqg rwkhu fduuldjhv fdph zkluolqj eb lq txlfn
vxffhvvlrq; wkh Plqlvwhu, wkh Vwdwh-Surmhfwru, wkh Iduphu-Jhqhudo,
