sdvvlqj ehwzhhq wkhp dqg wkh vshfwdfoh, dqg pdnlqj d eduulhu ehklqg
zklfk wkhb voxqn, dqg wkurxjk zklfk wkhb shhshg.  Wkh idwkhu kdg orqj
