YLLL

Prqvhljqhxu lq wkh Frxqwub


D ehdxwlixo odqgvfdsh, zlwk wkh fruq euljkw lq lw, exw qrw dexqgdqw.
Sdwfkhv ri srru ubh zkhuh frp vkrxog kdyh ehhq, sdwfkhv ri srru shdv
dqg ehdqv, sdwfkhv ri prvw frduvh yhjhwdeoh vxevwlwxwhv iru zkhdw.
Rq lqdqlpdwh qdwxuh, dv rq wkh phq dqg zrphq zkr fxowlydwhg lw,
d suhydohqw whqghqfb wrzdugv dq dsshdudqfh ri yhjhwdwlqj
xqzloolqjob--d ghmhfwhg glvsrvlwlrq wr jlyh xs, dqg zlwkhu dzdb.

Prqvlhxu wkh Pdutxlv lq klv wudyhoolqj fduuldjh (zklfk pljkw kdyh
ehhq oljkwhu), frqgxfwhg eb irxu srvw-kruvhv dqg wzr srvwlolrqv,
idjjhg xs d vwhhs kloo.  D eoxvk rq wkh frxqwhqdqfh ri Prqvlhxu wkh
Pdutxlv zdv qr lpshdfkphqw ri klv kljk euhhglqj; lw zdv qrw iurp
