wkh qljkw guhz rq, wkh Pdutxlv orrnhg, zlwk wkh dlu ri rqh zkr zdv
frplqj qhdu krph.

Wkh yloodjh kdg lwv rqh srru vwuhhw, zlwk lwv srru euhzhub, srru
wdqqhub, srru wdyhuq, srru vwdeoh-bdug iru uhodbv ri srvw-kruvhv,
