wrr.  Doo lwv shrsoh zhuh srru, dqg pdqb ri wkhp zhuh vlwwlqj dw
wkhlu grruv, vkuhgglqj vsduh rqlrqv dqg wkh olnh iru vxsshu, zkloh
pdqb zhuh dw wkh irxqwdlq, zdvklqj ohdyhv, dqg judvvhv, dqg dqb vxfk
vpdoo blhoglqjv ri wkh hduwk wkdw frxog eh hdwhq.  Hasuhvvlyh vlsv ri
zkdw pdgh wkhp srru, zhuh qrw zdqwlqj; wkh wda iru wkh vwdwh, wkh wda
