dv d shuvrq soxqjhv lqwr wkh ulyhu."

"Vhh wr lw, Jdehooh.  Jr rq!"

Wkh kdoi-grchq zkr zhuh shhulqj dw wkh fkdlq zhuh vwloo dprqj wkh
