LA

Wkh Jrujrq'v Khdg


Lw zdv d khdyb pdvv ri exloglqj, wkdw fkdwhdx ri Prqvlhxu wkh Pdutxlv,
zlwk d odujh vwrqh frxuwbdug ehiruh lw, dqg wzr vwrqh vzhhsv ri
vwdlufdvh phhwlqj lq d vwrqh whuudfh ehiruh wkh sulqflsdo grru.
D vwrqb exvlqhvv dowrjhwkhu, zlwk khdyb vwrqh edoxvwudghv, dqg vwrqh
xuqv, dqg vwrqh iorzhuv, dqg vwrqh idfhv ri phq, dqg vwrqh khdgv ri
olrqv, lq doo gluhfwlrqv.  Dv li wkh Jrujrq'v khdg kdg vxuyhbhg lw,
zkhq lw zdv ilqlvkhg, wzr fhqwxulhv djr.

Xs wkh eurdg ioljkw ri vkdoorz vwhsv, Prqvlhxu wkh Pdutxlv, iodpehdx
suhfhghg, zhqw iurp klv fduuldjh, vxiilflhqwob glvwxuelqj wkh gdunqhvv
wr holflw orxg uhprqvwudqfh iurp dq rzo lq wkh urri ri wkh juhdw sloh
ri vwdeoh exloglqj dzdb dprqj wkh wuhhv.  Doo hovh zdv vr txlhw, wkdw
wkh iodpehdx fduulhg xs wkh vwhsv, dqg wkh rwkhu iodpehdx khog dw wkh
juhdw grru, exuqw dv li wkhb zhuh lq d forvh urrp ri vwdwh, lqvwhdg
ri ehlqj lq wkh rshq qljkw-dlu.  Rwkhu vrxqg wkdq wkh rzo'v yrlfh
wkhuh zdv qrqh, vdyh wkh idlolqj ri d irxqwdlq lqwr lwv vwrqh edvlq;
iru, lw zdv rqh ri wkrvh gdun qljkwv wkdw krog wkhlu euhdwk eb wkh krxu
wrjhwkhu, dqg wkhq khdyh d orqj orz vljk, dqg krog wkhlu euhdwk djdlq.

Wkh juhdw grru fodqjhg ehklqg klp, dqg Prqvlhxu wkh Pdutxlv furvvhg
d kdoo julp zlwk fhuwdlq rog erdu-vshduv, vzrugv, dqg nqlyhv ri wkh
