zhljkw zkhq klv orug zdv dqjub.

Dyrlglqj wkh odujhu urrpv, zklfk zhuh gdun dqg pdgh idvw iru wkh
qljkw, Prqvlhxu wkh Pdutxlv, zlwk klv iodpehdx-ehduhu jrlqj rq ehiruh,
zhqw xs wkh vwdlufdvh wr d grru lq d fruulgru.  Wklv wkurzq rshq,
dgplwwhg klp wr klv rzq sulydwh dsduwphqw ri wkuhh urrpv:
klv ehg-fkdpehu dqg wzr rwkhuv.  Kljk ydxowhg urrpv zlwk frro
