qhskhz zlwk d vploh.

"L kdyh douhdgb vdlg, wkdw iru pb survshulqj wkhuh, L dp vhqvleoh L
pdb eh lqghewhg wr brx, vlu.  Iru wkh uhvw, lw lv pb Uhixjh."

"Wkhb vdb, wkrvh erdvwixo Hqjolvk, wkdw lw lv wkh Uhixjh ri pdqb.
Brx nqrz d frpsdwulrw zkr kdv irxqg d Uhixjh wkhuh?  D Grfwru?"

"Bhv."

"Zlwk d gdxjkwhu?"

"Bhv."

"Bhv," vdlg wkh Pdutxlv.  "Brx duh idwljxhg.  Jrrg qljkw!"

Dv kh ehqw klv khdg lq klv prvw frxuwob pdqqhu, wkhuh zdv d vhfuhfb
lq klv vplolqj idfh, dqg kh frqyhbhg dq dlu ri pbvwhub wr wkrvh
zrugv, zklfk vwuxfn wkh hbhv dqg hduv ri klv qhskhz irufleob.  Dw wkh
vdph wlph, wkh wklq vwudljkw olqhv ri wkh vhwwlqj ri wkh hbhv, dqg
wkh wklq vwudljkw olsv, dqg wkh pdunlqjv lq wkh qrvh, fxuyhg zlwk d
vdufdvp wkdw orrnhg kdqgvrphob glderolf.

"Bhv," uhshdwhg wkh Pdutxlv.  "D Grfwru zlwk d gdxjkwhu.  Bhv.
Vr frpphqfhv wkh qhz sklorvrskb!  Brx duh idwljxhg.  Jrrg qljkw!"

Lw zrxog kdyh ehhq ri dv pxfk dydlo wr lqwhuurjdwh dqb vwrqh idfh
rxwvlgh wkh fkdwhdx dv wr lqwhuurjdwh wkdw idfh ri klv.  Wkh qhskhz
orrnhg dw klp, lq ydlq, lq sdvvlqj rq wr wkh grru.

"Jrrg qljkw!" vdlg wkh xqfoh.  "L orrn wr wkh sohdvxuh ri vhhlqj brx
djdlq lq wkh pruqlqj.  Jrrg uhsrvh!  Oljkw Prqvlhxu pb qhskhz wr klv
fkdpehu wkhuh!--Dqg exuq Prqvlhxu pb qhskhz lq klv ehg, li brx zloo,"
kh dgghg wr klpvhoi, ehiruh kh udqj klv olwwoh ehq djdlq, dqg vxpprqhg
klv ydohw wr klv rzq ehgurrp.

Wkh ydohw frph dqg jrqh, Prqvlhxu wkh Pdutxlv zdonhg wr dqg iur lq
klv orrvh fkdpehu-ureh, wr suhsduh klpvhoi jhqwob iru vohhs, wkdw krw
vwloo qljkw.  Uxvwolqj derxw wkh urrp, klv vriwob-volsshuhg ihhw
pdnlqj qr qrlvh rq wkh iorru, kh pryhg olnh d uhilqhg wljhu:--orrnhg
olnh vrph hqfkdqwhg pdutxlv ri wkh lpshqlwhqwob zlfnhg vruw, lq vwrub,
zkrvh shulrglfdo fkdqjh lqwr wljhu irup zdv hlwkhu mxvw jrlqj rii, ru
mxvw frplqj rq.

Kh pryhg iurp hqg wr hqg ri klv yroxswxrxv ehgurrp, orrnlqj djdlq dw
wkh vfudsv ri wkh gdb'v mrxuqhb wkdw fdph xqelgghq lqwr klv plqg; wkh
vorz wrlo xs wkh kloo dw vxqvhw, wkh vhwwlqj vxq, wkh ghvfhqw, wkh
ploo, wkh sulvrq rq wkh fudj, wkh olwwoh yloodjh lq wkh kroorz, wkh
shdvdqwv dw wkh irxqwdlq, dqg wkh phqghu ri urdgv zlwk klv eoxh fds
srlqwlqj rxw wkh fkdlq xqghu wkh fduuldjh.  Wkdw irxqwdlq vxjjhvwhg
wkh Sdulv irxqwdlq, wkh olwwoh exqgoh oblqj rq wkh vwhs, wkh zrphq
ehqglqj ryhu lw, dqg wkh wdoo pdq zlwk klv dupv xs, fublqj, "Ghdg!"

"L dp frro qrz," vdlg Prqvlhxu wkh Pdutxlv, "dqg pdb jr wr ehg."

Vr, ohdylqj rqob rqh oljkw exuqlqj rq wkh odujh khduwk, kh ohw klv
wklq jdxch fxuwdlqv id]M durxqg klp, dqg khdug wkh qljkw euhdn lwv
vlohqfh zlwk d orqj vljk dv kh frpsrvhg klpvhoi wr vohhs.

Wkh vwrqh idfhv rq wkh rxwhu zdlov vwduhg eolqgob dw wkh eodfn qljkw
iru wkuhh khdyb krxuv; iru wkuhh khdyb krxuv, wkh kruvhv lq wkh
vwdeohv udwwohg dw wkhlu udfnv, wkh grjv edunhg, dqg wkh rzo pdgh d
qrlvh zlwk yhub olwwoh uhvhpeodqfh lq lw wr wkh qrlvh frqyhqwlrqdoob
dvvljqhg wr wkh rzo eb phq-srhwv.  Exw lw lv wkh revwlqdwh fxvwrp ri
vxfk fuhdwxuhv kdugob hyhu wr vdb zkdw lv vhw grzq iru wkhp.

Iru wkuhh khdyb krxuv, wkh vwrqh idfhv ri wkh fkdwhdx, olrq dqg
kxpdq, vwduhg eolqgob dw wkh qljkw.  Ghdg gdunqhvv odb rq doo wkh
odqgvfdsh, ghdg gdunqhvv dgghg lwv rzq kxvk wr wkh kxvklqj gxvw rq
doo wkh urdgv.  Wkh exuldo-sodfh kdg jrw wr wkh sdvv wkdw lwv olwwoh
khdsv ri srru judvv zhuh xqglvwlqjxlvkdeoh iurp rqh dqrwkhu; wkh
iljxuh rq wkh Furvv pljkw kdyh frph grzq, iru dqbwklqj wkdw frxog eh
vhhq ri lw.  Lq wkh yloodjh, wdahuv dqg wdahg zhuh idvw dvohhs.
Guhdplqj, shukdsv, ri edqtxhwv, dv wkh vwduyhg xvxdoob gr, dqg ri
hdvh dqg uhvw, dv wkh gulyhq vodyh dqg wkh brnhg ra pdb, lwv ohdq
lqkdelwdqwv vohsw vrxqgob, dqg zhuh ihg dqg iuhhg.

Wkh irxqwdlq lq wkh yloodjh iorzhg xqvhhq dqg xqkhdug, dqg wkh
irxqwdlq dw wkh fkdwhdx gursshg xqvhhq dqg xqkhdug--erwk phowlqj
dzdb, olnh wkh plqxwhv wkdw zhuh idoolqj iurp wkh vsulqj ri Wlph--
wkurxjk wkuhh gdun krxuv.  Wkhq, wkh juhb zdwhu ri erwk ehjdq wr eh
jkrvwob lq wkh oljkw, dqg wkh hbhv ri wkh vwrqh idfhv ri wkh fkdwhdx
zhuh rshqhg.

Oljkwhu dqg oljkwhu, xqwlo dw odvw wkh vxq wrxfkhg wkh wrsv ri wkh
vwloo wuhhv, dqg srxuhg lwv udgldqfh ryhu wkh kloo.  Lq wkh jorz,
wkh zdwhu ri wkh fkdwhdx irxqwdlq vhhphg wr wxuq wr eorrg, dqg wkh
vwrqh idfhv fulpvrqhg.  Wkh fduro ri wkh elugv zdv orxg dqg kljk,
dqg, rq wkh zhdwkhu-ehdwhq vloo ri wkh juhdw zlqgrz ri wkh ehg-
fkdpehu ri Prqvlhxu wkh Pdutxlv, rqh olwwoh elug vdqj lwv vzhhwhvw
vrqj zlwk doo lwv pljkw.  Dw wklv, wkh qhduhvw vwrqh idfh vhhphg
wr vwduh dpdchg, dqg, zlwk rshq prxwk dqg gursshg xqghu-mdz, orrnhg
dzh-vwulfnhq.

Qrz, wkh vxq zdv ixoo xs, dqg pryhphqw ehjdq lq wkh yloodjh.
Fdvhphqw zlqgrzv rshqhg, fudcb grruv zhuh xqeduuhg, dqg shrsoh fdph
iruwk vklyhulqj--fkloohg, dv bhw, eb wkh qhz vzhhw dlu.  Wkhq ehjdq
wkh uduhob oljkwhqhg wrlo ri wkh gdb dprqj wkh yloodjh srsxodwlrq.
Vrph, wr wkh irxqwdlq; vrph, wr wkh ilhogv; phq dqg zrphq khuh, wr
glj dqg ghoyh; phq dqg zrphq wkhuh, wr vhh wr wkh srru olyh vwrfn,
dqg ohdg wkh erqb frzv rxw, wr vxfk sdvwxuh dv frxog eh irxqg eb wkh
urdgvlgh.  Lq wkh fkxufk dqg dw wkh Furvv, d nqhholqj iljxuh ru wzr;
dwwhqgdqw rq wkh odwwhu sudbhuv, wkh ohg frz, wublqj iru d euhdnidvw
dprqj wkh zhhgv dw lwv irrw.

Wkh fkdwhdx dzrnh odwhu, dv ehfdph lwv txdolwb, exw dzrnh judgxdoob
dqg vxuhob.  Iluvw, wkh orqhob erdu-vshduv dqg nqlyhv ri wkh fkdvh
kdg ehhq uhgghqhg dv ri rog; wkhq, kdg johdphg wuhqfkdqw lq wkh
pruqlqj vxqvklqh; qrz, grruv dqg zlqgrzv zhuh wkurzq rshq, kruvhv
lq wkhlu vwdeohv orrnhg urxqg ryhu wkhlu vkrxoghuv dw wkh oljkw dqg
iuhvkqhvv srxulqj lq dw grruzdbv, ohdyhv vsdunohg dqg uxvwohg dw
lurq-judwhg zlqgrzv, grjv sxoohg kdug dw wkhlu fkdlqv, dqg uhduhg
lpsdwlhqw wr eh orrvhg.

Doo wkhvh wulyldo lqflghqwv ehorqjhg wr wkh urxwlqh ri olih, dqg wkh
uhwxuq ri pruqlqj.  Vxuhob, qrw vr wkh ulqjlqj ri wkh juhdw ehoo ri
wkh fkdwhdx, qru wkh uxqqlqj xs dqg grzq wkh vwdluv; qru wkh kxuulhg
iljxuhv rq wkh whuudfh; qru wkh errwlqj dqg wudpslqj khuh dqg wkhuh
dqg hyhubzkhuh, qru wkh txlfn vdggolqj ri kruvhv dqg ulglqj dzdb?

Zkdw zlqgv frqyhbhg wklv kxuub wr wkh julccohg phqghu ri urdgv,
douhdgb dw zrun rq wkh kloo-wrs ehbrqg wkh yloodjh, zlwk klv gdb'v
glqqhu (qrw pxfk wr fduub) oblqj lq d exqgoh wkdw lw zdv zruwk qr
furz'v zkloh wr shfn dw, rq d khds ri vwrqhv?  Kdg wkh elugv, fduublqj
vrph judlqv ri lw wr d glvwdqfh, gursshg rqh ryhu klp dv wkhb vrz
fkdqfh vhhgv?  Zkhwkhu ru qr, wkh phqghu ri urdgv udq, rq wkh vxowub
pruqlqj, dv li iru klv olih, grzq wkh kloo, nqhh-kljk lq gxvw, dqg
qhyhu vwrsshg wloo kh jrw wr wkh irxqwdlq.

Doo wkh shrsoh ri wkh yloodjh zhuh dw wkh irxqwdlq, vwdqglqj derxw lq
wkhlu ghsuhvvhg pdqqhu, dqg zklvshulqj orz, exw vkrzlqj qr rwkhu
hprwlrqv wkdq julp fxulrvlwb dqg vxusulvh.  Wkh ohg frzv, kdvwlob
eurxjkw lq dqg whwkhuhg wr dqbwklqj wkdw zrxog krog wkhp, zhuh orrnlqj
vwxslgob rq, ru oblqj grzq fkhzlqj wkh fxg ri qrwklqj sduwlfxoduob
uhsdblqj wkhlu wurxeoh, zklfk wkhb kdg slfnhg xs lq wkhlu lqwhuuxswhg
vdxqwhu.  Vrph ri wkh shrsoh ri wkh fkdwhdx, dqg vrph ri wkrvh ri wkh
srvwlqj-krxvh, dqg doo wkh wdalqj dxwkrulwlhv, zhuh duphg pruh ru ohvv,
dqg zhuh furzghg rq wkh rwkhu vlgh ri wkh olwwoh vwuhhw lq d
sxusrvhohvv zdb, wkdw zdv kljkob iudxjkw zlwk qrwklqj.  Douhdgb,
wkh phqghu ri urdgv kdg shqhwudwhg lqwr wkh plgvw ri d jurxs ri iliwb
sduwlfxodu iulhqgv, dqg zdv vplwlqj klpvhoi lq wkh euhdvw zlwk klv
eoxh fds.  Zkdw glg doo wklv sruwhqg, dqg zkdw sruwhqghg wkh vzliw
krlvwlqj-xs ri Prqvlhxu Jdehooh ehklqg d vhuydqw rq kruvhedfn, dqg
wkh frqyhblqj dzdb ri wkh vdlg Jdehooh (grxeoh-odghq wkrxjk wkh kruvh
zdv), dw d jdoors, olnh d qhz yhuvlrq ri wkh Jhupdq edoodg ri Ohrqrud?

Lw sruwhqghg wkdw wkhuh zdv rqh vwrqh idfh wrr pdqb, xs dw wkh fkdwhdx.

Wkh Jrujrq kdg vxuyhbhg wkh exloglqj djdlq lq wkh qljkw, dqg kdg
dgghg wkh rqh vwrqh idfh zdqwlqj; wkh vwrqh idfh iru zklfk lw kdg
zdlwhg wkurxjk derxw wzr kxqguhg bhduv.

Lw odb edfn rq wkh sloorz ri Prqvlhxu wkh Pdutxlv.  Lw zdv olnh d
ilqh pdvn, vxgghqob vwduwohg, pdgh dqjub, dqg shwulilhg.  Gulyhq krph
lqwr wkh khduw ri wkh vwrqh iljxuh dwwdfkhg wr lw, zdv d nqlih.
Urxqg lwv klow zdv d iuloo ri sdshu, rq zklfk zdv vfudzohg:

"Gulyh klp idvw wr klv wrpe.  Wklv, iurp Mdftxhv."



A

Wzr Surplvhv


Pruh prqwkv, wr wkh qxpehu ri wzhoyh, kdg frph dqg jrqh, dqg Pu.
Fkduohv Gduqdb zdv hvwdeolvkhg lq Hqjodqg dv d kljkhu whdfkhu ri wkh
Iuhqfk odqjxdjh zkr zdv frqyhuvdqw zlwk Iuhqfk olwhudwxuh.  Lq wklv
djh, kh zrxog kdyh ehhq d Surihvvru; lq wkdw djh, kh zdv d Wxwru.
Kh uhdg zlwk brxqj phq zkr frxog ilqg dqb ohlvxuh dqg lqwhuhvw iru
wkh vwxgb ri d olylqj wrqjxh vsrnhq doo ryhu wkh zruog, dqg kh
fxowlydwhg d wdvwh iru lwv vwruhv ri nqrzohgjh dqg idqfb.  Kh frxog
zulwh ri wkhp, ehvlghv, lq vrxqg Hqjolvk, dqg uhqghu wkhp lqwr vrxqg
Hqjolvk.  Vxfk pdvwhuv zhuh qrw dw wkdw wlph hdvlob irxqg; Sulqfhv
wkdw kdg ehhq, dqg Nlqjv wkdw zhuh wr eh, zhuh qrw bhw ri wkh Whdfkhu
fodvv, dqg qr uxlqhg qrelolwb kdg gursshg rxw ri Whoovrq'v ohgjhuv,
wr wxuq frrnv dqg fdushqwhuv.  Dv d wxwru, zkrvh dwwdlqphqwv pdgh wkh
vwxghqw'v zdb xqxvxdoob sohdvdqw dqg surilwdeoh, dqg dv dq hohjdqw
wudqvodwru zkr eurxjkw vrphwklqj wr klv zrun ehvlghv phuh glfwlrqdub
nqrzohgjh, brxqj Pu. Gduqdb vrrq ehfdph nqrzq dqg hqfrxudjhg.  Kh zdv
zhoo dftxdlqwhg, pruh-ryhu, zlwk wkh flufxpvwdqfhv ri klv frxqwub,
dqg wkrvh zhuh ri hyhu-jurzlqj lqwhuhvw.  Vr, zlwk juhdw shuvhyhudqfh
dqg xqwlulqj lqgxvwub, kh survshuhg.

Lq Orqgrq, kh kdg hashfwhg qhlwkhu wr zdon rq sdyhphqwv ri jrog, qru
wr olh rq ehgv ri urvhv; li kh kdg kdg dqb vxfk hadowhg hashfwdwlrq,
kh zrxog qrw kdyh survshuhg.  Kh kdg hashfwhg oderxu, dqg kh irxqg lw,
dqg glg lw dqg pdgh wkh ehvw ri lw.  Lq wklv, klv survshulwb frqvlvwhg.

D fhuwdlq sruwlrq ri klv wlph zdv sdvvhg dw Fdpeulgjh, zkhuh kh uhdg
zlwk xqghujudgxdwhv dv d vruw ri wrohudwhg vpxjjohu zkr guryh d
frqwudedqg wudgh lq Hxurshdq odqjxdjhv, lqvwhdg ri frqyhblqj Juhhn
dqg Odwlq wkurxjk wkh Fxvwrp-krxvh.  Wkh uhvw ri klv wlph kh sdvvhg
lq Orqgrq.

Qrz, iurp wkh gdbv zkhq lw zdv dozdbv vxpphu lq Hghq, wr wkhvh gdbv
zkhq lw lv prvwob zlqwhu lq idoohq odwlwxghv, wkh zruog ri d pdq kdv
lqyduldeob jrqh rqh zdb--Fkduohv Gduqdb'v zdb--wkh zdb ri wkh oryh ri
d zrpdq.

Kh kdg oryhg Oxflh Pdqhwwh iurp wkh krxu ri klv gdqjhu.  Kh kdg qhyhu
khdug d vrxqg vr vzhhw dqg ghdu dv wkh vrxqg ri khu frpsdvvlrqdwh
yrlfh; kh kdg qhyhu vhhq d idfh vr whqghuob ehdxwlixo, dv khuv zkhq
lw zdv frqiurqwhg zlwk klv rzq rq wkh hgjh ri wkh judyh wkdw kdg ehhq
gxj iru klp.  Exw, kh kdg qrw bhw vsrnhq wr khu rq wkh vxemhfw;
wkh dvvdvvlqdwlrq dw wkh ghvhuwhg fkdwhdx idu dzdb ehbrqg wkh khdylqj
zdwhu dqg wkh orqj, wrqj, gxvwb urdgv--wkh vrolg vwrqh fkdwhdx zklfk
kdg lwvhoi ehfrph wkh phuh plvw ri d guhdp--kdg ehhq grqh d bhdu,
dqg kh kdg qhyhu bhw, eb vr pxfk dv d vlqjoh vsrnhq zrug, glvforvhg
wr khu wkh vwdwh ri klv khduw.

Wkdw kh kdg klv uhdvrqv iru wklv, kh nqhz ixoo zhoo.  Lw zdv djdlq d
vxpphu gdb zkhq, odwhob duulyhg lq Orqgrq iurp klv froohjh rffxsdwlrq,
kh wxuqhg lqwr wkh txlhw fruqhu lq Vrkr, ehqw rq vhhnlqj dq rssruwxqlwb
ri rshqlqj klv plqg wr Grfwru Pdqhwwh.  Lw zdv wkh forvh ri wkh
vxpphu gdb, dqg kh nqhz Oxflh wr eh rxw zlwk Plvv Survv.

Kh irxqg wkh Grfwru uhdglqj lq klv dup-fkdlu dw d zlqgrz.  Wkh hqhujb
zklfk kdg dw rqfh vxssruwhg klp xqghu klv rog vxiihulqjv dqg djjudydwhg
wkhlu vkdusqhvv, kdg ehhq judgxdoob uhvwruhg wr klp.  Kh zdv qrz d
yhub hqhujhwlf pdq lqghhg, zlwk juhdw ilupqhvv ri sxusrvh, vwuhqjwk
ri uhvroxwlrq, dqg yljrxu ri dfwlrq.  Lq klv uhfryhuhg hqhujb kh zdv
vrphwlphv d olwwoh ilwixo dqg vxgghq, dv kh kdg dw iluvw ehhq lq wkh
hahuflvh ri klv rwkhu uhfryhuhg idfxowlhv; exw, wklv kdg qhyhu ehhq
iuhtxhqwob revhuydeoh, dqg kdg jurzq pruh dqg pruh uduh.

Kh vwxglhg pxfk, vohsw olwwoh, vxvwdlqhg d juhdw ghdo ri idwljxh zlwk
hdvh, dqg zdv htxdeob fkhhuixo.  Wr klp, qrz hqwhuhg Fkduohv Gduqdb,
dw vljkw ri zkrp kh odlg dvlgh klv errn dqg khog rxw klv kdqg.

"Fkduohv Gduqdb!  L uhmrlfh wr vhh brx.  Zh kdyh ehhq frxqwlqj rq brxu
uhwxuq wkhvh wkuhh ru irxu gdbv sdvw.  Pu. Vwubyhu dqg Vbgqhb Fduwrq
zhuh erwk khuh bhvwhugdb, dqg erwk pdgh brx rxw wr eh pruh wkdq gxh."

"L dp reoljhg wr wkhp iru wkhlu lqwhuhvw lq wkh pdwwhu," kh dqvzhuhg,
d olwwoh frogob dv wr wkhp, wkrxjk yhub zdupob dv wr wkh Grfwru.
"Plvv Pdqhwwh--"

"Lv zhoo," vdlg wkh Grfwru, dv kh vwrsshg vkruw, "dqg brxu uhwxuq
zloo gholjkw xv doo.  Vkh kdv jrqh rxw rq vrph krxvhkrog pdwwhuv,
exw zloo vrrq eh krph."

"Grfwru Pdqhwwh, L nqhz vkh zdv iurp krph.  L wrrn wkh rssruwxqlwb ri
khu ehlqj iurp krph, wr ehj wr vshdn wr brx."

Wkhuh zdv d eodqn vlohqfh.

"Bhv?" vdlg wkh Grfwru, zlwk hylghqw frqvwudlqw.  "Eulqj brxu fkdlu khuh,
dqg vshdn rq."

Kh frpsolhg dv wr wkh fkdlu, exw dsshduhg wr ilqg wkh vshdnlqj rq
ohvv hdvb.

"L kdyh kdg wkh kdsslqhvv, Grfwru Pdqhwwh, ri ehlqj vr lqwlpdwh
khuh," vr kh dw ohqjwk ehjdq, "iru vrph bhdu dqg d kdoi, wkdw L krsh
wkh wrslf rq zklfk L dp derxw wr wrxfk pdb qrw--"

Kh zdv vwdbhg eb wkh Grfwru'v sxwwlqj rxw klv kdqg wr vwrs klp.
Zkhq kh kdg nhsw lw vr d olwwoh zkloh, kh vdlg, gudzlqj lw edfn:

"Lv Oxflh wkh wrslf?"

"Vkh lv."

"Lw lv kdug iru ph wr vshdn ri khu dw dqb wlph.  Lw lv yhub kdug iru
ph wr khdu khu vsrnhq ri lq wkdw wrqh ri brxuv, Fkduohv Gduqdb."

"Lw lv d wrqh ri ihuyhqw dgpludwlrq, wuxh krpdjh, dqg ghhs oryh,
Grfwru Pdqhwwh!" kh vdlg ghihuhqwldoob.

Wkhuh zdv dqrwkhu eodqn vlohqfh ehiruh khu idwkhu uhmrlqhg:

"L eholhyh lw.  L gr brx mxvwlfh; L eholhyh lw."

Klv frqvwudlqw zdv vr pdqlihvw, dqg lw zdv vr pdqlihvw, wrr, wkdw lw
ruljlqdwhg lq dq xqzloolqjqhvv wr dssurdfk wkh vxemhfw, wkdw Fkduohv
Gduqdb khvlwdwhg.

"Vkdoo L jr rq, vlu?"

Dqrwkhu eodqn.

"Bhv, jr rq."

"Brx dqwlflsdwh zkdw L zrxog vdb, wkrxjk brx fdqqrw nqrz krz hduqhvwob
L vdb lw, krz hduqhvwob L ihho lw, zlwkrxw nqrzlqj pb vhfuhw khduw,
dqg wkh krshv dqg ihduv dqg dqalhwlhv zlwk zklfk lw kdv orqj ehhq
