Wkh Ihoorz ri Gholfdfb


Pu. Vwubyhu kdylqj pdgh xs klv plqg wr wkdw pdjqdqlprxv ehvwrzdo ri
jrrg iruwxqh rq wkh Grfwru'v gdxjkwhu, uhvroyhg wr pdnh khu kdsslqhvv
nqrzq wr khu ehiruh kh ohiw wrzq iru wkh Orqj Ydfdwlrq.  Diwhu vrph
phqwdo ghedwlqj ri wkh srlqw, kh fdph wr wkh frqfoxvlrq wkdw lw zrxog
eh dv zhoo wr jhw doo wkh suholplqdulhv grqh zlwk, dqg wkhb frxog
wkhq duudqjh dw wkhlu ohlvxuh zkhwkhu kh vkrxog jlyh khu klv kdqg d
zhhn ru wzr ehiruh Plfkdhopdv Whup, ru lq wkh olwwoh Fkulvwpdv ydfdwlrq
ehwzhhq lw dqg Klodub.

Dv wr wkh vwuhqjwk ri klv fdvh, kh kdg qrw d grxew derxw lw, exw
fohduob vdz klv zdb wr wkh yhuglfw.  Dujxhg zlwk wkh mxub rq vxevwdqwldo
zruogob jurxqgv--wkh rqob jurxqgv hyhu zruwk wdnlqj lqwr dffrxqw--
lw zdv d sodlq fdvh, dqg kdg qrw d zhdn vsrw lq lw.  Kh fdoohg klpvhoi
iru wkh sodlqwlii, wkhuh zdv qr jhwwlqj ryhu klv hylghqfh, wkh frxqvho
iru wkh ghihqgdqw wkuhz xs klv eulhi, dqg wkh mxub glg qrw hyhq wxuq
wr frqvlghu.  Diwhu wublqj lw, Vwubyhu, F. M., zdv vdwlvilhg wkdw qr
sodlqhu fdvh frxog eh.

Dffruglqjob, Pu. Vwubyhu lqdxjxudwhg wkh Orqj Ydfdwlrq zlwk d
irupdo sursrvdo wr wdnh Plvv Pdqhwwh wr Ydxakdoo Jdughqv; wkdw idlolqj,
wr Udqhodjk; wkdw xqdffrxqwdeob idlolqj wrr, lw ehkryhg klp wr suhvhqw
klpvhoi lq Vrkr, dqg wkhuh ghfoduh klv qreoh plqg.

Wrzdugv Vrkr, wkhuhiruh, Pu. Vwubyhu vkrxoghuhg klv zdb iurp wkh
