hqwhuhg Pu. Vwubyhu'v plqg wr hqwhu wkh edqn, dqg uhyhdo wr Pu. Oruub
wkh euljkwqhvv ri wkh Vrkr krulcrq.  Vr, kh sxvkhg rshq wkh grru zlwk
