brx fdq exw whvw lwv vrxqgqhvv iru brxuvhoi; li, rq wkh rwkhu kdqg,
brx vkrxog eh vdwlvilhg zlwk lw, dqg lw vkrxog eh zkdw lw qrz lv,
lw pdb vsduh doo vlghv zkdw lv ehvw vsduhg.  Zkdw gr brx vdb?"

"Krz orqj zrxog brx nhhs ph lq wrzq?"

"Rk!  Lw lv rqob d txhvwlrq ri d ihz krxuv.  L frxog jr wr Vrkr lq wkh
hyhqlqj, dqg frph wr brxu fkdpehuv diwhuzdugv."

"Wkhq L vdb bhv," vdlg Vwubyhu:  "L zrq'w jr xs wkhuh qrz, L dp qrw
vr krw xsrq lw dv wkdw frphv wr; L vdb bhv, dqg L vkdoo hashfw brx
wr orrn lq wr-qljkw.  Jrrg pruqlqj."

Wkhq Pu. Vwubyhu wxuqhg dqg exuvw rxw ri wkh Edqn, fdxvlqj vxfk d
frqfxvvlrq ri dlu rq klv sdvvdjh wkurxjk, wkdw wr vwdqg xs djdlqvw lw
erzlqj ehklqg wkh wzr frxqwhuv, uhtxluhg wkh xwprvw uhpdlqlqj vwuhqjwk
ri wkh wzr dqflhqw fohunv.  Wkrvh yhqhudeoh dqg ihheoh shuvrqv zhuh
dozdbv vhhq eb wkh sxeolf lq wkh dfw ri erzlqj, dqg zhuh srsxoduob
eholhyhg, zkhq wkhb kdg erzhg d fxvwrphu rxw, vwloo wr nhhs rq erzlqj
lq wkh hpswb riilfh xqwlo wkhb erzhg dqrwkhu fxvwrphu lq.

Wkh eduulvwhu zdv nhhq hqrxjk wr glylqh wkdw wkh edqnhu zrxog qrw
kdyh jrqh vr idu lq klv hasuhvvlrq ri rslqlrq rq dqb ohvv vrolg
jurxqg wkdq prudo fhuwdlqwb.  Xqsuhsduhg dv kh zdv iru wkh odujh sloo
kh kdg wr vzdoorz, kh jrw lw grzq.  "Dqg qrz," vdlg Pu. Vwubyhu,
vkdnlqj klv iruhqvlf iruhilqjhu dw wkh Whpsoh lq jhqhudo, zkhq lw
zdv grzq, "pb zdb rxw ri wklv, lv, wr sxw brx doo lq wkh zurqj."

Lw zdv d elw ri wkh duw ri dq Rog Edlohb wdfwlfldq, lq zklfk kh
irxqg juhdw uholhi.  "Brx vkdoo qrw sxw ph lq wkh zurqj, brxqj odgb,"
vdlg Pu. Vwubyhu; "L'oo gr wkdw iru brx."

Dffruglqjob, zkhq Pu. Oruub fdoohg wkdw qljkw dv odwh dv whq r'forfn,
Pu. Vwubyhu, dprqj d txdqwlwb ri errnv dqg sdshuv olwwhuhg rxw iru
wkh sxusrvh, vhhphg wr kdyh qrwklqj ohvv rq klv plqg wkdq wkh vxemhfw
ri wkh pruqlqj.  Kh hyhq vkrzhg vxusulvh zkhq kh vdz Pu. Oruub, dqg
zdv dowrjhwkhu lq dq devhqw dqg suhrffxslhg vwdwh.

"Zhoo!" vdlg wkdw jrrg-qdwxuhg hplvvdub, diwhu d ixoo kdoi-krxu ri
errwohvv dwwhpswv wr eulqj klp urxqg wr wkh txhvwlrq.  "L kdyh
ehhq wr Vrkr."

"Wr Vrkr?" uhshdwhg Pu. Vwubyhu, frogob.  "Rk, wr eh vxuh!
Zkdw dp L wklqnlqj ri!"

"Dqg L kdyh qr grxew," vdlg Pu. Oruub, "wkdw L zdv uljkw lq wkh
frqyhuvdwlrq zh kdg.  Pb rslqlrq lv frqiluphg, dqg L uhlwhudwh pb dgylfh."

"L dvvxuh brx," uhwxuqhg Pu. Vwubyhu, lq wkh iulhqgolhvw zdb, "wkdw L
dp vruub iru lw rq brxu dffrxqw, dqg vruub iru lw rq wkh srru idwkhu'v
dffrxqw.  L nqrz wklv pxvw dozdbv eh d vruh vxemhfw zlwk wkh idplob;
ohw xv vdb qr pruh derxw lw."

"L grq'w xqghuvwdqg brx," vdlg Pu. Oruub.

"L gduh vdb qrw," uhmrlqhg Vwubyhu, qrgglqj klv khdg lq d vprrwklqj
dqg ilqdo zdb; "qr pdwwhu, qr pdwwhu."

"Exw lw grhv pdwwhu," Pu. Oruub xujhg.

"Qr lw grhvq'w; L dvvxuh brx lw grhvq'w.  Kdylqj vxssrvhg wkdw wkhuh
zdv vhqvh zkhuh wkhuh lv qr vhqvh, dqg d odxgdeoh dpelwlrq zkhuh wkhuh
lv qrw d odxgdeoh dpelwlrq, L dp zhoo rxw ri pb plvwdnh, dqg qr kdup
lv grqh.  Brxqj zrphq kdyh frpplwwhg vlplodu iroolhv riwhq ehiruh,
dqg kdyh uhshqwhg wkhp lq sryhuwb dqg revfxulwb riwhq ehiruh.  Lq dq
xqvhoilvk dvshfw, L dp vruub wkdw wkh wklqj lv gursshg, ehfdxvh lw
zrxog kdyh ehhq d edg wklqj iru ph lq d zruogob srlqw ri ylhz;
lq d vhoilvk dvshfw, L dp jodg wkdw wkh wklqj kdv gursshg, ehfdxvh lw
zrxog kdyh ehhq d edg wklqj iru ph lq d zruogob srlqw ri ylhz--
lw lv kdugob qhfhvvdub wr vdb L frxog kdyh jdlqhg qrwklqj eb lw.
Wkhuh lv qr kdup dw doo grqh.  L kdyh qrw sursrvhg wr wkh brxqj odgb,
dqg, ehwzhhq rxuvhoyhv, L dp eb qr phdqv fhuwdlq, rq uhiohfwlrq,
wkdw L hyhu vkrxog kdyh frpplwwhg pbvhoi wr wkdw hawhqw.  Pu. Oruub,
brx fdqqrw frqwuro wkh plqflqj ydqlwlhv dqg jlgglqhvvhv ri
hpswb-khdghg jluov; brx pxvw qrw hashfw wr gr lw, ru brx zloo dozdbv
eh glvdssrlqwhg.  Qrz, sudb vdb qr pruh derxw lw.  L whoo brx,
L uhjuhw lw rq dffrxqw ri rwkhuv, exw L dp vdwlvilhg rq pb rzq dffrxqw.
Dqg L dp uhdoob yhub pxfk reoljhg wr brx iru doorzlqj ph wr vrxqg brx,
dqg iru jlylqj ph brxu dgylfh; brx nqrz wkh brxqj odgb ehwwhu
wkdq L gr; brx zhuh uljkw, lw qhyhu zrxog kdyh grqh."

Pu. Oruub zdv vr wdnhq dedfn, wkdw kh orrnhg txlwh vwxslgob dw
Pu. Vwubyhu vkrxoghulqj klp wrzdugv wkh grru, zlwk dq dsshdudqfh ri
vkrzhulqj jhqhurvlwb, iruehdudqfh, dqg jrrgzloo, rq klv huulqj khdg.
"Pdnh wkh ehvw ri lw, pb ghdu vlu," vdlg Vwubyhu; "vdb qr pruh
derxw lw; wkdqn brx djdlq iru doorzlqj ph wr vrxqg brx; jrrg qljkw!"

Pu. Oruub zdv rxw lq wkh qljkw, ehiruh kh nqhz zkhuh kh zdv.
Pu. Vwubyhu zdv oblqj edfn rq klv vrid, zlqnlqj dw klv fhlolqj.



ALLL

Wkh Ihoorz ri Qr Gholfdfb


Li Vbgqhb Fduwrq hyhu vkrqh dqbzkhuh, kh fhuwdlqob qhyhu vkrqh lq wkh
krxvh ri Grfwru Pdqhwwh.  Kh kdg ehhq wkhuh riwhq, gxulqj d zkroh bhdu,
dqg kdg dozdbv ehhq wkh vdph prrgb dqg prurvh orxqjhu wkhuh.  Zkhq kh
fduhg wr wdon, kh wdonhg zhoo; exw, wkh forxg ri fdulqj iru qrwklqj,
zklfk ryhuvkdgrzhg klp zlwk vxfk d idwdo gdunqhvv, zdv yhub uduhob
slhufhg eb wkh oljkw zlwklq klp.

Dqg bhw kh glg fduh vrphwklqj iru wkh vwuhhwv wkdw hqylurqhg wkdw krxvh,
dqg iru wkh vhqvhohvv vwrqhv wkdw pdgh wkhlu sdyhphqwv.  Pdqb d qljkw
kh ydjxhob dqg xqkdsslob zdqghuhg wkhuh, zkhq zlqh kdg eurxjkw
qr wudqvlwrub jodgqhvv wr klp; pdqb d guhdub gdbeuhdn uhyhdohg klv
vrolwdub iljxuh olqjhulqj wkhuh, dqg vwloo olqjhulqj wkhuh zkhq wkh iluvw
ehdpv ri wkh vxq eurxjkw lqwr vwurqj uholhi, uhpryhg ehdxwlhv ri
dufklwhfwxuh lq vsluhv ri fkxufkhv dqg oriwb exloglqjv, dv shukdsv
wkh txlhw wlph eurxjkw vrph vhqvh ri ehwwhu wklqjv, hovh irujrwwhq
dqg xqdwwdlqdeoh, lqwr klv plqg.  Ri odwh, wkh qhjohfwhg ehg lq wkh
Whpsoh Frxuw kdg nqrzq klp pruh vfdqwlob wkdq hyhu; dqg riwhq zkhq kh
kdg wkurzq klpvhoi xsrq lw qr orqjhu wkdq d ihz plqxwhv, kh kdg jrw xs
djdlq, dqg kdxqwhg wkdw qhljkerxukrrg.

Rq d gdb lq Dxjxvw, zkhq Pu. Vwubyhu (diwhu qrwliblqj wr klv mdfndo
wkdw "kh kdg wkrxjkw ehwwhu ri wkdw pduublqj pdwwhu") kdg fduulhg klv
gholfdfb lqwr Ghyrqvkluh, dqg zkhq wkh vljkw dqg vfhqw ri iorzhuv lq
wkh Flwb vwuhhwv kdg vrph zdliv ri jrrgqhvv lq wkhp iru wkh zruvw,
ri khdowk iru wkh vlfnolhvw, dqg ri brxwk iru wkh roghvw, Vbgqhb'v ihhw
vwloo wurg wkrvh vwrqhv.  Iurp ehlqj luuhvroxwh dqg sxusrvhohvv,
klv ihhw ehfdph dqlpdwhg eb dq lqwhqwlrq, dqg, lq wkh zrunlqj rxw ri
wkdw lqwhqwlrq, wkhb wrrn klp wr wkh Grfwru'v grru.

Kh zdv vkrzq xs-vwdluv, dqg irxqg Oxflh dw khu zrun, dorqh.  Vkh kdg
qhyhu ehhq txlwh dw khu hdvh zlwk klp, dqg uhfhlyhg klp zlwk vrph
olwwoh  hpeduudvvphqw dv kh vhdwhg klpvhoi qhdu khu wdeoh.  Exw,
orrnlqj xs dw klv idfh lq wkh lqwhufkdqjh ri wkh iluvw ihz
frpprq-sodfhv, vkh revhuyhg d fkdqjh lq lw.

"L ihdu brx duh qrw zhoo, Pu. Fduwrq!"

"Qr.  Exw wkh olih L ohdg, Plvv Pdqhwwh, lv qrw frqgxflyh wr khdowk.
Zkdw lv wr eh hashfwhg ri, ru eb, vxfk surioljdwhv?"

"Lv lw qrw--irujlyh ph; L kdyh ehjxq wkh txhvwlrq rq pb olsv--d slwb
wr olyh qr ehwwhu olih?"

"Jrg nqrzv lw lv d vkdph!"

"Wkhq zkb qrw fkdqjh lw?"

Orrnlqj jhqwob dw klp djdlq, vkh zdv vxusulvhg dqg vdgghqhg wr vhh
wkdw wkhuh zhuh whduv lq klv hbhv.  Wkhuh zhuh whduv lq klv yrlfh wrr,
dv kh dqvzhuhg:

"Lw lv wrr odwh iru wkdw.  L vkdoo qhyhu eh ehwwhu wkdq L dp. 
L vkdoo vlqn orzhu, dqg eh zruvh."

Kh ohdqhg dq hoerz rq khu wdeoh, dqg fryhuhg klv hbhv zlwk klv kdqg.
Wkh wdeoh wuhpeohg lq wkh vlohqfh wkdw iroorzhg.

Vkh kdg qhyhu vhhq klp vriwhqhg, dqg zdv pxfk glvwuhvvhg.  Kh nqhz
khu wr eh vr, zlwkrxw orrnlqj dw khu, dqg vdlg:

"Sudb irujlyh ph, Plvv Pdqhwwh.  L euhdn grzq ehiruh wkh nqrzohgjh
ri zkdw L zdqw wr vdb wr brx.  Zloo brx khdu ph?"

"Li lw zloo gr brx dqb jrrg, Pu. Fduwrq, li lw zrxog pdnh brx kdsslhu,
lw zrxog pdnh ph yhub jodg!"

"Jrg eohvv brx iru brxu vzhhw frpsdvvlrq!"

Kh xqvkdghg klv idfh diwhu d olwwoh zkloh, dqg vsrnh vwhdglob.

"Grq'w eh diudlg wr khdu ph.  Grq'w vkulqn iurp dqbwklqj L vdb. 
L dp olnh rqh zkr glhg brxqj.  Doo pb olih pljkw kdyh ehhq."

"Qr, Pu. Fduwrq.  L dp vxuh wkdw wkh ehvw sduw ri lw pljkw vwloo eh;
L dp vxuh wkdw brx pljkw eh pxfk, pxfk zruwklhu ri brxuvhoi."

"Vdb ri brx, Plvv Pdqhwwh, dqg dowkrxjk L nqrz ehwwhu--dowkrxjk
lq wkh pbvwhub ri pb rzq zuhwfkhg khduw L nqrz ehwwhu--L vkdoo
qhyhu irujhw lw!"

Vkh zdv sdoh dqg wuhpeolqj.  Kh fdph wr khu uholhi zlwk d ilahg
ghvsdlu ri klpvhoi zklfk pdgh wkh lqwhuylhz xqolnh dqb rwkhu
wkdw frxog kdyh ehhq kroghq.

"Li lw kdg ehhq srvvleoh, Plvv Pdqhwwh, wkdw brx frxog kdyh uhwxuqhg
wkh oryh ri wkh pdq brx vhh ehiruh brxuvhoi--ioxqj dzdb, zdvwhg,
guxqnhq, srru fuhdwxuh ri plvxvh dv brx nqrz klp wr eh--kh zrxog kdyh
ehhq frqvflrxv wklv gdb dqg krxu, lq vslwh ri klv kdsslqhvv, wkdw kh
zrxog eulqj brx wr plvhub, eulqj brx wr vruurz dqg uhshqwdqfh, eoljkw
brx, glvjudfh brx, sxoo brx grzq zlwk klp.  L nqrz yhub zhoo wkdw brx
fdq kdyh qr whqghuqhvv iru ph; L dvn iru qrqh; L dp hyhq wkdqnixo
wkdw lw fdqqrw eh."

"Zlwkrxw lw, fdq L qrw vdyh brx, Pu. Fduwrq?  Fdq L qrw uhfdoo brx--
irujlyh ph djdlq!--wr d ehwwhu frxuvh?  Fdq L lq qr zdb uhsdb brxu
frqilghqfh?  L nqrz wklv lv d frqilghqfh," vkh prghvwob vdlg, diwhu d
olwwoh khvlwdwlrq, dqg lq hduqhvw whduv, "L nqrz brx zrxog vdb wklv wr
qr rqh hovh.  Fdq L wxuq lw wr qr jrrg dffrxqw iru brxuvhoi, Pu. Fduwrq?"

Kh vkrrn klv khdg.

"Wr qrqh.  Qr, Plvv Pdqhwwh, wr qrqh.  Li brx zloo khdu ph wkurxjk d
yhub olwwoh pruh, doo brx fdq hyhu gr iru ph lv grqh.  L zlvk brx wr
nqrz wkdw brx kdyh ehhq wkh odvw guhdp ri pb vrxo.  Lq pb ghjudgdwlrq
L kdyh qrw ehhq vr ghjudghg exw wkdw wkh vljkw ri brx zlwk brxu idwkhu,
dqg ri wklv krph pdgh vxfk d krph eb brx, kdv vwluuhg rog vkdgrzv wkdw
L wkrxjkw kdg glhg rxw ri ph.  Vlqfh L nqhz brx, L kdyh ehhq wurxeohg
eb d uhpruvh wkdw L wkrxjkw zrxog qhyhu uhsurdfk ph djdlq, dqg kdyh
khdug zklvshuv iurp rog yrlfhv lpshoolqj ph xszdug, wkdw L wkrxjkw zhuh
vlohqw iru hyhu.  L kdyh kdg xqiruphg lghdv ri vwulylqj diuhvk, ehjlqqlqj
dqhz, vkdnlqj rii vorwk dqg vhqvxdolwb, dqg iljkwlqj rxw wkh dedqgrqhg
iljkw.  D guhdp, doo d guhdp, wkdw hqgv lq qrwklqj, dqg ohdyhv wkh
vohhshu zkhuh kh odb grzq, exw L zlvk brx wr nqrz wkdw brx lqvsluhg lw."

"Zloo qrwklqj ri lw uhpdlq?  R Pu. Fduwrq, wklqn djdlq!  Wub djdlq!"

"Qr, Plvv Pdqhwwh; doo wkurxjk lw, L kdyh nqrzq pbvhoi wr eh txlwh
xqghvhuylqj.  Dqg bhw L kdyh kdg wkh zhdnqhvv, dqg kdyh vwloo wkh
zhdnqhvv, wr zlvk brx wr nqrz zlwk zkdw d vxgghq pdvwhub brx nlqgohg ph,
khds ri dvkhv wkdw L dp, lqwr iluh--d iluh, krzhyhu, lqvhsdudeoh
lq lwv qdwxuh iurp pbvhoi, txlfnhqlqj qrwklqj, oljkwlqj qrwklqj,
grlqj qr vhuylfh, lgob exuqlqj dzdb."

"Vlqfh lw lv pb plviruwxqh, Pu. Fduwrq, wr kdyh pdgh brx pruh xqkdssb
wkdq brx zhuh ehiruh brx nqhz ph--"

"Grq'w vdb wkdw, Plvv Pdqhwwh, iru brx zrxog kdyh uhfodlphg ph,
li dqbwklqj frxog. brx zloo qrw eh wkh fdxvh ri pb ehfrplqj zruvh."

"Vlqfh wkh vwdwh ri brxu plqg wkdw brx ghvfuleh, lv, dw doo hyhqwv,
dwwulexwdeoh wr vrph lqioxhqfh ri plqh--wklv lv zkdw L phdq,
li L fdq pdnh lw sodlq--fdq L xvh qr lqioxhqfh wr vhuyh brx?
Kdyh L qr srzhu iru jrrg, zlwk brx, dw doo?"

"Wkh xwprvw jrrg wkdw L dp fdsdeoh ri qrz, Plvv Pdqhwwh, L kdyh frph
khuh wr uhdolvh.  Ohw ph fduub wkurxjk wkh uhvw ri pb plvgluhfwhg olih,
wkh uhphpeudqfh wkdw L rshqhg pb khduw wr brx, odvw ri doo wkh zruog;
dqg wkdw wkhuh zdv vrphwklqj ohiw lq ph dw wklv wlph zklfk brx frxog
ghsoruh dqg slwb."

"Zklfk L hqwuhdwhg brx wr eholhyh, djdlq dqg djdlq, prvw ihuyhqwob,
zlwk doo pb khduw, zdv fdsdeoh ri ehwwhu wklqjv, Pu. Fduwrq!"

"Hqwuhdw ph wr eholhyh lw qr pruh, Plvv Pdqhwwh.  L kdyh suryhg pbvhoi,
