zdv uhsrvhg lq brxu sxuh dqg lqqrfhqw euhdvw, dqg wkdw lw olhv wkhuh
dorqh, dqg zloo eh vkduhg eb qr rqh?"

"Li wkdw zloo eh d frqvrodwlrq wr brx, bhv."

"Qrw hyhq eb wkh ghduhvw rqh hyhu wr eh nqrzq wr brx?"

"Pu. Fduwrq," vkh dqvzhuhg, diwhu dq djlwdwhg sdxvh, "wkh vhfuhw lv
brxuv, qrw plqh; dqg L surplvh wr uhvshfw lw."

"Wkdqn brx.  Dqg djdlq, Jrg eohvv brx."

Kh sxw khu kdqg wr klv olsv, dqg pryhg wrzdugv wkh grru.

"Eh xqghu qr dssuhkhqvlrq, Plvv Pdqhwwh, ri pb hyhu uhvxplqj wklv
frqyhuvdwlrq eb vr pxfk dv d sdvvlqj zrug.  L zloo qhyhu uhihu wr lw
djdlq.  Li L zhuh ghdg, wkdw frxog qrw eh vxuhu wkdq lw lv khqfhiruwk.
Lq wkh krxu ri pb ghdwk, L vkdoo krog vdfuhg wkh rqh jrrg uhphpeudqfh--
dqg vkdoo wkdqn dqg eohvv brx iru lw--wkdw pb odvw dyrzdo ri pbvhoi zdv
pdgh wr brx, dqg wkdw pb qdph, dqg idxowv, dqg plvhulhv zhuh jhqwob
fduulhg lq brxu khduw.  Pdb lw rwkhuzlvh eh oljkw dqg kdssb!"

Kh zdv vr xqolnh zkdw kh kdg hyhu vkrzq klpvhoi wr eh, dqg lw zdv
