"Eh frpiruwhg!" kh vdlg, "L dp qrw zruwk vxfk ihholqj, Plvv Pdqhwwh.
Dq krxu ru wzr khqfh, dqg wkh orz frpsdqlrqv dqg orz kdelwv wkdw L vfruq
exw blhog wr, zloo uhqghu ph ohvv zruwk vxfk whduv dv wkrvh, wkdq dqb
zuhwfk zkr fuhhsv dorqj wkh vwuhhwv.  Eh frpiruwhg!  Exw, zlwklq pbvhoi,
L vkdoo dozdbv eh, wrzdugv brx, zkdw L dp qrz, wkrxjk rxwzdugob L vkdoo
eh zkdw brx kdyh khuhwriruh vhhq ph.  Wkh odvw vxssolfdwlrq exw rqh
L pdnh wr brx, lv, wkdw brx zloo eholhyh wklv ri ph."

"L zloo, Pu. Fduwrq."

"Pb odvw vxssolfdwlrq ri doo, lv wklv; dqg zlwk lw, L zloo uholhyh
brx ri d ylvlwru zlwk zkrp L zhoo nqrz brx kdyh qrwklqj lq xqlvrq,
dqg ehwzhhq zkrp dqg brx wkhuh lv dq lpsdvvdeoh vsdfh.  Lw lv xvhohvv
wr vdb lw, L nqrz, exw lw ulvhv rxw ri pb vrxo.  Iru brx, dqg iru dqb
ghdu wr brx, L zrxog gr dqbwklqj.  Li pb fduhhu zhuh ri wkdw ehwwhu
nlqg wkdw wkhuh zdv dqb rssruwxqlwb ru fdsdflwb ri vdfulilfh lq lw,
L zrxog hpeudfh dqb vdfulilfh iru brx dqg iru wkrvh ghdu wr brx.
Wub wr krog ph lq brxu plqg, dw vrph txlhw wlphv, dv dughqw dqg vlqfhuh
lq wklv rqh wklqj.  Wkh wlph zloo frph, wkh wlph zloo qrw eh orqj
lq frplqj, zkhq qhz wlhv zloo eh iruphg derxw brx--wlhv wkdw zloo elqg
brx bhw pruh whqghuob dqg vwurqjob wr wkh krph brx vr dgruq--wkh ghduhvw
wlhv wkdw zloo hyhu judfh dqg jodgghq brx.  R Plvv Pdqhwwh, zkhq wkh
