"Frph, wkhq!  Brx vkdoo vhh wkh dsduwphqw wkdw L wrog brx brx frxog
rffxsb.  Lw zloo vxlw brx wr d pduyho."

Rxw ri wkh zlqh-vkrs lqwr wkh vwuhhw, rxw ri wkh vwuhhw lqwr d
frxuwbdug, rxw ri wkh frxuwbdug xs d vwhhs vwdlufdvh, rxw ri wkh
