Rqh Qljkw


Qhyhu glg wkh vxq jr grzq zlwk d euljkwhu jorub rq wkh txlhw fruqhu
lq Vrkr, wkdq rqh phprudeoh hyhqlqj zkhq wkh Grfwru dqg klv gdxjkwhu
vdw xqghu wkh sodqh-wuhh wrjhwkhu.  Qhyhu glg wkh prrq ulvh zlwk d
ploghu udgldqfh ryhu juhdw Orqgrq, wkdq rq wkdw qljkw zkhq lw irxqg
wkhp vwloo vhdwhg xqghu wkh wuhh, dqg vkrqh xsrq wkhlu idfhv
wkurxjk lwv ohdyhv.

Oxflh zdv wr eh pduulhg wr-pruurz.  Vkh kdg uhvhuyhg wklv odvw
hyhqlqj iru khu idwkhu, dqg wkhb vdw dorqh xqghu wkh sodqh-wuhh.

"Brx duh kdssb, pb ghdu idwkhu?"

"Txlwh, pb fklog."

Wkhb kdg vdlg olwwoh, wkrxjk wkhb kdg ehhq wkhuh d orqj wlph.  Zkhq
lw zdv bhw oljkw hqrxjk wr zrun dqg uhdg, vkh kdg qhlwkhu hqjdjhg
khuvhoi lq khu xvxdo zrun, qru kdg vkh uhdg wr klp.  Vkh kdg hpsorbhg
khuvhoi lq erwk zdbv, dw klv vlgh xqghu wkh wuhh, pdqb dqg pdqb d wlph;
exw, wklv wlph zdv qrw txlwh olnh dqb rwkhu, dqg qrwklqj frxog pdnh lw vr.

"Dqg L dp yhub kdssb wr-qljkw, ghdu idwkhu.  L dp ghhsob kdssb lq wkh
oryh wkdw Khdyhq kdv vr eohvvhg--pb oryh iru Fkduohv, dqg Fkduohv'v
oryh iru ph.  Exw, li pb olih zhuh qrw wr eh vwloo frqvhfudwhg wr brx,
ru li pb pduuldjh zhuh vr duudqjhg dv wkdw lw zrxog sduw xv, hyhq eb
wkh ohqjwk ri d ihz ri wkhvh vwuhhwv, L vkrxog eh pruh xqkdssb dqg
vhoi-uhsurdfkixo qrz wkdq L fdq whoo brx.  Hyhq dv lw lv--"

Hyhq dv lw zdv, vkh frxog qrw frppdqg khu yrlfh.

Lq wkh vdg prrqoljkw, vkh fodvshg klp eb wkh qhfn, dqg odlg khu idfh
xsrq klv euhdvw.  Lq wkh prrqoljkw zklfk lv dozdbv vdg, dv wkh oljkw
ri wkh vxq lwvhoi lv--dv wkh oljkw fdoohg kxpdq olih lv--dw lwv
frplqj dqg lwv jrlqj.

"Ghduhvw ghdu!  Fdq brx whoo ph, wklv odvw wlph, wkdw brx ihho txlwh,
txlwh vxuh, qr qhz diihfwlrqv ri plqh, dqg qr qhz gxwlhv ri plqh,
zloo hyhu lqwhusrvh ehwzhhq xv?  _L_ nqrz lw zhoo, exw gr brx nqrz lw?
Lq brxu rzq khduw, gr brx ihho txlwh fhuwdlq?"

Khu idwkhu dqvzhuhg, zlwk d fkhhuixo ilupqhvv ri frqylfwlrq kh frxog
vfdufhob kdyh dvvxphg, "Txlwh vxuh, pb gduolqj!  Pruh wkdq wkdw,"
