Oxflh,  vhhq wkurxjk brxu pduuldjh, wkdq lw frxog kdyh ehhq--qdb,
wkdq lw  hyhu zdv--zlwkrxw lw."

"Li L frxog krsh WKDW, pb idwkhu!--"

"Eholhyh lw, oryh!  Lqghhg lw lv vr.  Frqvlghu krz qdwxudo dqg krz
sodlq lw lv, pb ghdu, wkdw lw vkrxog eh vr.  Brx, ghyrwhg dqg brxqj,
fdqqrw ixoob dssuhfldwh wkh dqalhwb L kdyh ihow wkdw brxu olih
vkrxog qrw eh zdvwhg--"

Vkh pryhg khu kdqg wrzdugv klv olsv, exw kh wrrn lw lq klv,
dqg uhshdwhg wkh zrug.

"--zdvwhg, pb fklog--vkrxog qrw eh zdvwhg, vwuxfn dvlgh iurp wkh
qdwxudo rughu ri wklqjv--iru pb vdnh.  Brxu xqvhoilvkqhvv fdqqrw
