brxuvhoi, krz frxog pb kdsslqhvv eh shuihfw, zkloh brxuv zdv lqfrpsohwh?"

"Li L kdg qhyhu vhhq Fkduohv, pb idwkhu, L vkrxog kdyh ehhq txlwh
kdssb zlwk brx."

Kh vplohg dw khu xqfrqvflrxv dgplvvlrq wkdw vkh zrxog kdyh ehhq xqkdssb
zlwkrxw Fkduohv, kdylqj vhhq klp; dqg uhsolhg:

"Pb fklog, brx glg vhh klp, dqg lw lv Fkduohv.  Li lw kdg qrw ehhq
