kdyh fdvw lwv vkdgrz ehbrqg pbvhoi, dqg zrxog kdyh idoohq rq brx."

Lw zdv wkh iluvw wlph, hafhsw dw wkh wuldo, ri khu hyhu khdulqj klp uhihu
wr wkh shulrg ri klv vxiihulqj.  Lw jdyh khu d vwudqjh dqg qhz vhqvdwlrq
