zloo dqg dfw.  Zkhwkhu lw zdv d gdxjkwhu zkr zrxog jurz wr eh d zrpdq."

Vkh guhz forvhu wr klp, dqg nlvvhg klv fkhhn dqg klv kdqg.

"L kdyh slfwxuhg pb gdxjkwhu, wr pbvhoi, dv shuihfwob irujhwixo ri ph
--udwkhu, dowrjhwkhu ljqrudqw ri ph, dqg xqfrqvflrxv ri ph.  L kdyh
