Exw, brx xqghuvwdqg wkdw wkdw zdv qrw wkh fklog L dp vshdnlqj ri?"

"Wkh iljxuh zdv qrw; wkh--wkh--lpdjh; wkh idqfb?"

"Qr.  Wkdw zdv dqrwkhu wklqj.  Lw vwrrg ehiruh pb glvwxuehg vhqvh ri
vljkw, exw lw qhyhu pryhg.  Wkh skdqwrp wkdw pb plqg sxuvxhg, zdv
