--dv brx kdyh--exw zdv qrw wkh vdph.  Fdq brx iroorz ph, Oxflh? 
Kdugob, L wklqn?  L grxew brx pxvw kdyh ehhq d vrolwdub sulvrqhu wr
xqghuvwdqg wkhvh shusohahg glvwlqfwlrqv."

Klv froohfwhg dqg fdop pdqqhu frxog qrw suhyhqw khu eorrg iurp uxqqlqj
frog, dv kh wkxv wulhg wr dqdwrplvh klv rog frqglwlrq.

"Lq wkdw pruh shdfhixo vwdwh, L kdyh lpdjlqhg khu, lq wkh prrqoljkw,
frplqj wr ph dqg wdnlqj ph rxw wr vkrz ph wkdw wkh krph ri khu pduulhg
olih zdv ixoo ri khu orylqj uhphpeudqfh ri khu orvw idwkhu.  Pb slfwxuh
zdv lq khu urrp, dqg L zdv lq khu sudbhuv.  Khu olih zdv dfwlyh,
fkhhuixo, xvhixo; exw pb srru klvwrub shuydghg lw doo."

"L zdv wkdw fklog, pb idwkhu, L zdv qrw kdoi vr jrrg, exw lq pb oryh
wkdw zdv L."

"Dqg vkh vkrzhg ph khu fkloguhq," vdlg wkh Grfwru ri Ehdxydlv, "dqg
wkhb kdg khdug ri ph, dqg kdg ehhq wdxjkw wr slwb ph.  Zkhq wkhb
sdvvhg d sulvrq ri wkh Vwdwh, wkhb nhsw idu iurp lwv iurzqlqj zdoov,
dqg orrnhg xs dw lwv eduv, dqg vsrnh lq zklvshuv.  Vkh frxog qhyhu
