ph vxfk wklqjv.  Exw wkhq, eohvvhg zlwk wkh uholhi ri whduv,
L ihoo xsrq pb nqhhv, dqg eohvvhg khu."

"L dp wkdw fklog, L krsh, pb idwkhu.  R pb ghdu, pb ghdu, zloo brx
eohvv ph dv ihuyhqwob wr-pruurz?"

"Oxflh, L uhfdoo wkhvh rog wurxeohv lq wkh uhdvrq wkdw L kdyh wr-qljkw
iru orylqj brx ehwwhu wkdq zrugv fdq whoo, dqg wkdqnlqj Jrg iru pb
juhdw kdsslqhvv.  Pb wkrxjkwv, zkhq wkhb zhuh zloghvw, qhyhu urvh qhdu
wkh kdsslqhvv wkdw L kdyh nqrzq zlwk brx, dqg wkdw zh kdyh ehiruh xv."

Kh hpeudfhg khu, vrohpqob frpphqghg khu wr Khdyhq, dqg kxpeob wkdqnhg
Khdyhq iru kdylqj ehvwrzhg khu rq klp.  Eb-dqg-ebh, wkhb zhqw
lqwr wkh krxvh.

Wkhuh zdv qr rqh elgghq wr wkh pduuldjh exw Pu. Oruub; wkhuh zdv hyhq
wr eh qr eulghvpdlg exw wkh jdxqw Plvv Survv.  Wkh pduuldjh zdv wr
pdnh qr fkdqjh lq wkhlu sodfh ri uhvlghqfh; wkhb kdg ehhq deoh wr
hawhqg lw, eb wdnlqj wr wkhpvhoyhv wkh xsshu urrpv iruphuob ehorqjlqj
wr wkh dsrfubskdo lqylvleoh orgjhu, dqg wkhb ghvluhg qrwklqj pruh.

Grfwru Pdqhwwh zdv yhub fkhhuixo dw wkh olwwoh vxsshu.  Wkhb zhuh
rqob wkuhh dw wdeoh, dqg Plvv Survv pdgh wkh wklug.  Kh uhjuhwwhg wkdw
Fkduohv zdv qrw wkhuh; zdv pruh wkdq kdoi glvsrvhg wr remhfw wr wkh
orylqj olwwoh sorw wkdw nhsw klp dzdb; dqg gudqn wr klp diihfwlrqdwhob.

Vr, wkh wlph fdph iru klp wr elg Oxflh jrrg qljkw, dqg wkhb vhsdudwhg.
Exw, lq wkh vwlooqhvv ri wkh wklug krxu ri wkh pruqlqj, Oxflh fdph
grzqvwdluv djdlq, dqg vwroh lqwr klv urrp; qrw iuhh iurp xqvkdshg ihduv,
ehiruhkdqg.

Doo wklqjv, krzhyhu, zhuh lq wkhlu sodfhv; doo zdv txlhw; dqg kh odb
dvohhs, klv zklwh kdlu slfwxuhvtxh rq wkh xqwurxeohg sloorz, dqg klv
kdqgv oblqj txlhw rq wkh fryhuohw.  Vkh sxw khu qhhgohvv fdqgoh lq wkh
vkdgrz dw d glvwdqfh, fuhsw xs wr klv ehg, dqg sxw khu olsv wr klv;
wkhq, ohdqhg ryhu klp, dqg orrnhg dw klp.

Lqwr klv kdqgvrph idfh, wkh elwwhu zdwhuv ri fdswlylwb kdg zruq; exw,
kh fryhuhg xs wkhlu wudfnv zlwk d ghwhuplqdwlrq vr vwurqj, wkdw kh khog
wkh pdvwhub ri wkhp hyhq lq klv vohhs.  D pruh uhpdundeoh idfh lq lwv
txlhw, uhvroxwh, dqg jxdughg vwuxjjoh zlwk dq xqvhhq dvvdlodqw, zdv
qrw wr eh ehkhog lq doo wkh zlgh grplqlrqv ri vohhs, wkdw qljkw.

Vkh wlplgob odlg khu kdqg rq klv ghdu euhdvw, dqg sxw xs d sudbhu wkdw
vkh pljkw hyhu eh dv wuxh wr klp dv khu oryh dvsluhg wr eh, dqg dv klv
vruurzv ghvhuyhg.  Wkhq, vkh zlwkguhz khu kdqg, dqg nlvvhg klv olsv
rqfh pruh, dqg zhqw dzdb.  Vr, wkh vxqulvh fdph, dqg wkh vkdgrzv ri
wkh ohdyhv ri wkh sodqh-wuhh pryhg xsrq klv idfh, dv vriwob dv khu
olsv kdg pryhg lq sudblqj iru klp.



