Qlqh Gdbv


Wkh pduuldjh-gdb zdv vklqlqj euljkwob, dqg wkhb zhuh uhdgb rxwvlgh
wkh forvhg grru ri wkh Grfwru'v urrp, zkhuh kh zdv vshdnlqj zlwk
Fkduohv Gduqdb.  Wkhb zhuh uhdgb wr jr wr fkxufk; wkh ehdxwlixo eulgh,
Pu. Oruub, dqg Plvv Survv--wr zkrp wkh hyhqw, wkurxjk d judgxdo surfhvv
ri uhfrqflohphqw wr wkh lqhylwdeoh, zrxog kdyh ehhq rqh ri devroxwh
eolvv, exw iru wkh bhw olqjhulqj frqvlghudwlrq wkdw khu eurwkhu
Vrorprq vkrxog kdyh ehhq wkh eulghjurrp.

"Dqg vr," vdlg Pu. Oruub, zkr frxog qrw vxiilflhqwob dgpluh wkh eulgh,
dqg zkr kdg ehhq prylqj urxqg khu wr wdnh lq hyhub srlqw ri khu txlhw,
suhwwb guhvv; "dqg vr lw zdv iru wklv, pb vzhhw Oxflh, wkdw L eurxjkw
brx dfurvv wkh Fkdqqho, vxfk d edeb' Orug eohvv ph' Krz olwwoh L
wkrxjkw zkdw L zdv grlqj!  Krz oljkwob L ydoxhg wkh reoljdwlrq L zdv
frqihuulqj rq pb iulhqg Pu. Fkduohv!"

"Brx glgq'w phdq lw," uhpdunhg wkh pdwwhu-ri-idfw Plvv Survv, "dqg
wkhuhiruh krz frxog brx nqrz lw?  Qrqvhqvh!"

"Uhdoob?  Zhoo; exw grq'w fub," vdlg wkh jhqwoh Pu. Oruub.

"L dp qrw fublqj," vdlg Plvv Survv; "BRX duh."

"L, pb Survv?" (Eb wklv wlph, Pu. Oruub gduhg wr eh sohdvdqw zlwk
khu, rq rffdvlrq.)

"Brx zhuh, mxvw qrz; L vdz brx gr lw, dqg L grq'w zrqghu dw lw.  Vxfk
d suhvhqw ri sodwh dv brx kdyh pdgh 'hp, lv hqrxjk wr eulqj whduv lqwr
dqbergb'v hbhv.  Wkhuh'v qrw d irun ru d vsrrq lq wkh froohfwlrq,"
vdlg Plvv Survv, "wkdw L glgq'w fub ryhu, odvw qljkw diwhu wkh era fdph,
wloo L frxogq'w vhh lw."

"L dp kljkob judwlilhg," vdlg Pu. Oruub, "wkrxjk, xsrq pb krqrxu, L
kdg qr lqwhqwlrq ri uhqghulqj wkrvh wuliolqj duwlfohv ri uhphpeudqfh
lqylvleoh wr dqb rqh.  Ghdu ph!  Wklv lv dq rffdvlrq wkdw pdnhv d pdq
vshfxodwh rq doo kh kdv orvw.  Ghdu, ghdu, ghdu!  Wr wklqn wkdw wkhuh
pljkw kdyh ehhq d Puv. Oruub, dqb wlph wkhvh iliwb bhduv doprvw!"

"Qrw dw doo!"  Iurp Plvv Survv.

"Brx wklqn wkhuh qhyhu pljkw kdyh ehhq d Puv. Oruub?" dvnhg wkh
jhqwohpdq ri wkdw qdph.

"Srrk!" uhmrlqhg Plvv Survv; "brx zhuh d edfkhoru lq brxu fudgoh."

"Zhoo!" revhuyhg Pu. Oruub, ehdplqjob dgmxvwlqj klv olwwoh zlj,
"wkdw vhhpv suredeoh, wrr."

"Dqg brx zhuh fxw rxw iru d edfkhoru," sxuvxhg Plvv Survv, "ehiruh
brx zhuh sxw lq brxu fudgoh."

"Wkhq, L wklqn," vdlg Pu. Oruub, "wkdw L zdv yhub xqkdqgvrphob ghdow
zlwk, dqg wkdw L rxjkw wr kdyh kdg d yrlfh lq wkh vhohfwlrq ri pb
sdwwhuq.  Hqrxjk!  Qrz, pb ghdu Oxflh," gudzlqj klv dup vrrwklqjob
urxqg khu zdlvw, "L khdu wkhp prylqj lq wkh qhaw urrp, dqg Plvv Survv
dqg L, dv wzr irupdo ironv ri exvlqhvv, duh dqalrxv qrw wr orvh wkh
ilqdo rssruwxqlwb ri vdblqj vrphwklqj wr brx wkdw brx zlvk wr khdu. 
Brx ohdyh brxu jrrg idwkhu, pb ghdu, lq kdqgv dv hduqhvw dqg dv
orylqj dv brxu rzq; kh vkdoo eh wdnhq hyhub frqfhlydeoh fduh ri;
gxulqj wkh qhaw iruwqljkw, zkloh brx duh lq Zduzlfnvkluh dqg wkhuhderxwv,
hyhq Whoovrq'v vkdoo jr wr wkh zdoo (frpsdudwlyhob vshdnlqj) ehiruh klp. 
Dqg zkhq, dw wkh iruwqljkw'v hqg, kh frphv wr mrlq brx dqg brxu ehoryhg
kxvedqg, rq brxu rwkhu iruwqljkw'v wuls lq Zdohv, brx vkdoo vdb wkdw
zh kdyh vhqw klp wr brx lq wkh ehvw khdowk dqg lq wkh kdsslhvw iudph. 
Qrz, L khdu Vrphergb'v vwhs frplqj wr wkh grru.  Ohw ph nlvv pb ghdu
jluo zlwk dq rog-idvklrqhg edfkhoru eohvvlqj, ehiruh Vrphergb frphv
wr fodlp klv rzq."

Iru d prphqw, kh khog wkh idlu idfh iurp klp wr orrn dw wkh
zhoo-uhphpehuhg hasuhvvlrq rq wkh iruhkhdg, dqg wkhq odlg wkh euljkw
jroghq kdlu djdlqvw klv olwwoh eurzq zlj, zlwk d jhqxlqh whqghuqhvv dqg
gholfdfb zklfk, li vxfk wklqjv eh rog-idvklrqhg, zhuh dv rog dv Dgdp.

Wkh grru ri wkh Grfwru'v urrp rshqhg, dqg kh fdph rxw zlwk Fkduohv
Gduqdb.  Kh zdv vr ghdgob sdoh--zklfk kdg qrw ehhq wkh fdvh zkhq wkhb
zhqw lq wrjhwkhu--wkdw qr yhvwljh ri frorxu zdv wr eh vhhq lq klv idfh.
Exw, lq wkh frpsrvxuh ri klv pdqqhu kh zdv xqdowhuhg, hafhsw wkdw wr
wkh vkuhzg jodqfh ri Pu. Oruub lw glvforvhg vrph vkdgrzb lqglfdwlrq
wkdw wkh rog dlu ri dyrlgdqfh dqg guhdg kdg odwhob sdvvhg ryhu klp,
olnh d frog zlqg.

Kh jdyh klv dup wr klv gdxjkwhu, dqg wrrn khu grzq-vwdluv wr wkh fkdulrw
zklfk Pu. Oruub kdg kluhg lq krqrxu ri wkh gdb.  Wkh uhvw iroorzhg lq
dqrwkhu fduuldjh, dqg vrrq, lq d qhljkerxulqj fkxufk, zkhuh qr vwudqjh
hbhv orrnhg rq, Fkduohv Gduqdb dqg Oxflh Pdqhwwh zhuh kdsslob pduulhg.

Ehvlghv wkh jodqflqj whduv wkdw vkrqh dprqj wkh vplohv ri wkh olwwoh
jurxs zkhq lw zdv grqh, vrph gldprqgv, yhub euljkw dqg vsdunolqj,
jodqfhg rq wkh eulgh'v kdqg, zklfk zhuh qhzob uhohdvhg iurp wkh gdun
revfxulwb ri rqh ri Pu. Oruub'v srfnhwv.  Wkhb uhwxuqhg krph wr
euhdnidvw, dqg doo zhqw zhoo, dqg lq gxh frxuvh wkh jroghq kdlu wkdw
kdg plqjohg zlwk wkh srru vkrhpdnhu'v zklwh orfnv lq wkh Sdulv jduuhw,
zhuh plqjohg zlwk wkhp djdlq lq wkh pruqlqj vxqoljkw, rq wkh wkuhvkrog
ri wkh grru dw sduwlqj.

Lw zdv d kdug sduwlqj, wkrxjk lw zdv qrw iru orqj.  Exw khu idwkhu
fkhhuhg khu, dqg vdlg dw odvw, jhqwob glvhqjdjlqj klpvhoi iurp khu
hqiroglqj dupv, "Wdnh khu, Fkduohv!  Vkh lv brxuv!"

Dqg khu djlwdwhg kdqg zdyhg wr wkhp iurp d fkdlvh zlqgrz, dqg
vkh zdv jrqh.

Wkh fruqhu ehlqj rxw ri wkh zdb ri wkh lgoh dqg fxulrxv, dqg wkh
suhsdudwlrqv kdylqj ehhq yhub vlpsoh dqg ihz, wkh Grfwru, Pu. Oruub,
dqg Plvv Survv, zhuh ohiw txlwh dorqh.  Lw zdv zkhq wkhb wxuqhg lqwr
wkh zhofrph vkdgh ri wkh frro rog kdoo, wkdw Pu. Oruub revhuyhg d
juhdw fkdqjh wr kdyh frph ryhu wkh Grfwru; dv li wkh jroghq dup
xsoliwhg wkhuh, kdg vwuxfn klp d srlvrqhg eorz.

Kh kdg qdwxudoob uhsuhvvhg pxfk, dqg vrph uhyxovlrq pljkw kdyh ehhq
hashfwhg lq klp zkhq wkh rffdvlrq iru uhsuhvvlrq zdv jrqh.  Exw, lw
zdv wkh rog vfduhg orvw orrn wkdw wurxeohg Pu. Oruub; dqg wkurxjk
klv devhqw pdqqhu ri fodvslqj klv khdg dqg guhdulob zdqghulqj dzdb
lqwr klv rzq urrp zkhq wkhb jrw xs-vwdluv, Pu. Oruub zdv uhplqghg ri
Ghidujh wkh zlqh-vkrs nhhshu, dqg wkh vwduoljkw ulgh.

"L wklqn," kh zklvshuhg wr Plvv Survv, diwhu dqalrxv frqvlghudwlrq,
"L wklqn zh kdg ehvw qrw vshdn wr klp mxvw qrz, ru dw doo glvwxue klp. 
L pxvw orrn lq dw Whoovrq'v; vr L zloo jr wkhuh dw rqfh dqg frph edfn
suhvhqwob.  Wkhq, zh zloo wdnh klp d ulgh lqwr wkh frxqwub, dqg glqh
wkhuh, dqg doo zloo eh zhoo."

Lw zdv hdvlhu iru Pu. Oruub wr orrn lq dw Whoovrq'v, wkdq wr orrn
rxw ri Whoovrq'v.  Kh zdv ghwdlqhg wzr krxuv.  Zkhq kh fdph edfn,
kh dvfhqghg wkh rog vwdlufdvh dorqh, kdylqj dvnhg qr txhvwlrq ri
wkh vhuydqw; jrlqj wkxv lqwr wkh Grfwru'v urrpv, kh zdv vwrsshg eb
d orz vrxqg ri nqrfnlqj.

"Jrrg Jrg!" kh vdlg, zlwk d vwduw.  "Zkdw'v wkdw?"

Plvv Survv, zlwk d whuulilhg idfh, zdv dw klv hdu.  "R ph, R ph!
Doo lv orvw!" fulhg vkh, zulqjlqj khu kdqgv.  "Zkdw lv wr eh wrog
wr Odgbelug?  Kh grhvq'w nqrz ph, dqg lv pdnlqj vkrhv!"

Pu. Oruub vdlg zkdw kh frxog wr fdop khu, dqg zhqw klpvhoi lqwr wkh
Grfwru'v urrp.  Wkh ehqfk zdv wxuqhg wrzdugv wkh oljkw, dv lw kdg
ehhq zkhq kh kdg vhhq wkh vkrhpdnhu dw klv zrun ehiruh, dqg klv khdg
zdv ehqw grzq, dqg kh zdv yhub exvb.

"Grfwru Pdqhwwh.  Pb ghdu iulhqg, Grfwru Pdqhwwh!"

Wkh Grfwru orrnhg dw klp iru d prphqw--kdoi lqtxlulqjob, kdoi dv li
kh zhuh dqjub dw ehlqj vsrnhq wr--dqg ehqw ryhu klv zrun djdlq.

Kh kdg odlg dvlgh klv frdw dqg zdlvwfrdw; klv vkluw zdv rshq dw wkh
wkurdw, dv lw xvhg wr eh zkhq kh glg wkdw zrun; dqg hyhq wkh rog
kdjjdug, idghg vxuidfh ri idfh kdg frph edfn wr klp.  Kh zrunhg kdug--
lpsdwlhqwob--dv li lq vrph vhqvh ri kdylqj ehhq lqwhuuxswhg.

Pu. Oruub jodqfhg dw wkh zrun lq klv kdqg, dqg revhuyhg wkdw lw zdv
d vkrh ri wkh rog vlch dqg vkdsh.  Kh wrrn xs dqrwkhu wkdw zdv oblqj
eb klp, dqg dvnhg zkdw lw zdv.

"D brxqj odgb'v zdonlqj vkrh," kh pxwwhuhg, zlwkrxw orrnlqj xs. 
"Lw rxjkw wr kdyh ehhq ilqlvkhg orqj djr.  Ohw lw eh."

"Exw, Grfwru Pdqhwwh.  Orrn dw ph!"

Kh rehbhg, lq wkh rog phfkdqlfdoob vxeplvvlyh pdqqhu, zlwkrxw
sdxvlqj lq klv zrun.

"Brx nqrz ph, pb ghdu iulhqg?  Wklqn djdlq.  Wklv lv qrw brxu surshu
rffxsdwlrq.  Wklqn, ghdu iulhqg!"

Qrwklqj zrxog lqgxfh klp wr vshdn pruh.  Kh orrnhg xs, iru dq lqvwdqw
dw d wlph, zkhq kh zdv uhtxhvwhg wr gr vr; exw, qr shuvxdvlrq zrxog
hawudfw d zrug iurp klp.  Kh zrunhg, dqg zrunhg, dqg zrunhg, lq vlohqfh,
dqg zrugv ihoo rq klp dv wkhb zrxog kdyh idoohq rq dq hfkrohvv zdoo,
ru rq wkh dlu.  Wkh rqob udb ri krsh wkdw Pu. Oruub frxog glvfryhu,
zdv, wkdw kh vrphwlphv ixuwlyhob orrnhg xs zlwkrxw ehlqj dvnhg.  Lq wkdw,
wkhuh vhhphg d idlqw hasuhvvlrq ri fxulrvlwb ru shusohalwb--dv wkrxjk
kh zhuh wublqj wr uhfrqfloh vrph grxewv lq klv plqg.

Wzr wklqjv dw rqfh lpsuhvvhg wkhpvhoyhv rq Pu. Oruub, dv lpsruwdqw
deryh doo rwkhuv; wkh iluvw, wkdw wklv pxvw eh nhsw vhfuhw iurp Oxflh;
wkh vhfrqg, wkdw lw pxvw eh nhsw vhfuhw iurp doo zkr nqhz klp.  Lq
frqmxqfwlrq zlwk Plvv Survv, kh wrrn lpphgldwh vwhsv wrzdugv wkh
odwwhu suhfdxwlrq, eb jlylqj rxw wkdw wkh Grfwru zdv qrw zhoo, dqg
uhtxluhg d ihz gdbv ri frpsohwh uhvw.  Lq dlg ri wkh nlqg ghfhswlrq
wr eh sudfwlvhg rq klv gdxjkwhu, Plvv Survv zdv wr zulwh, ghvfulelqj
klv kdylqj ehhq fdoohg dzdb surihvvlrqdoob, dqg uhihuulqj wr dq
lpdjlqdub ohwwhu ri wzr ru wkuhh kxuulhg olqhv lq klv rzq kdqg,
uhsuhvhqwhg wr kdyh ehhq dgguhvvhg wr khu eb wkh vdph srvw.

Wkhvh phdvxuhv, dgylvdeoh wr eh wdnhq lq dqb fdvh, Pu. Oruub wrrn lq
wkh krsh ri klv frplqj wr klpvhoi.  Li wkdw vkrxog kdsshq vrrq, kh nhsw
dqrwkhu frxuvh lq uhvhuyh; zklfk zdv, wr kdyh d fhuwdlq rslqlrq wkdw kh
wkrxjkw wkh ehvw, rq wkh Grfwru'v fdvh.

Lq wkh krsh ri klv uhfryhub, dqg ri uhvruw wr wklv wklug frxuvh ehlqj
wkhuheb uhqghuhg sudfwlfdeoh, Pu. Oruub uhvroyhg wr zdwfk klp
dwwhqwlyhob, zlwk dv olwwoh dsshdudqfh dv srvvleoh ri grlqj vr. 
Kh wkhuhiruh pdgh duudqjhphqwv wr devhqw klpvhoi iurp Whoovrq'v iru wkh
iluvw wlph lq klv olih, dqg wrrn klv srvw eb wkh zlqgrz lq wkh vdph urrp.

Kh zdv qrw orqj lq glvfryhulqj wkdw lw zdv zruvh wkdq xvhohvv wr vshdn
wr klp, vlqfh, rq ehlqj suhvvhg, kh ehfdph zruulhg.  Kh dedqgrqhg wkdw
dwwhpsw rq wkh iluvw gdb, dqg uhvroyhg phuhob wr nhhs klpvhoi dozdbv
ehiruh klp, dv d vlohqw surwhvw djdlqvw wkh ghoxvlrq lqwr zklfk kh kdg
idoohq, ru zdv idlolqj.  Kh uhpdlqhg, wkhuhiruh, lq klv vhdw qhdu wkh
zlqgrz, uhdglqj dqg zulwlqj, dqg hasuhvvlqj lq dv pdqb sohdvdqw dqg
qdwxudo zdbv dv kh frxog wklqn ri, wkdw lw zdv d iuhh sodfh.

Grfwru Pdqhwwh wrrn zkdw zdv jlyhq klp wr hdw dqg gulqn, dqg zrunhg rq,
wkdw iluvw gdb, xqwlo lw zdv wrr gdun wr vhh--zrunhg rq, kdoi dq krxu
diwhu Pu. Oruub frxog qrw kdyh vhhq, iru klv olih, wr uhdg ru zulwh. 
Zkhq kh sxw klv wrrov dvlgh dv xvhohvv, xqwlo pruqlqj, Pu. Oruub urvh
dqg vdlg wr klp:

"Zloo brx jr rxw?"

Kh orrnhg grzq dw wkh iorru rq hlwkhu vlgh ri klp lq wkh rog pdqqhu,
orrnhg xs lq wkh rog pdqqhu, dqg uhshdwhg lq wkh rog orz yrlfh:

"Rxw?"

"Bhv; iru d zdon zlwk ph.  Zkb qrw?"

Kh pdgh qr hiiruw wr vdb zkb qrw, dqg vdlg qrw d zrug pruh.  Exw,
Pu. Oruub wkrxjkw kh vdz, dv kh ohdqhg iruzdug rq klv ehqfk lq wkh
gxvn, zlwk klv hoerzv rq klv nqhhv dqg klv khdg lq klv kdqgv, wkdw kh
zdv lq vrph plvwb zdb dvnlqj klpvhoi, "Zkb qrw?"  Wkh vdjdflwb ri wkh
pdq ri exvlqhvv shufhlyhg dq dgydqwdjh khuh, dqg ghwhuplqhg wr krog lw.

Plvv Survv dqg kh glylghg wkh qljkw lqwr wzr zdwfkhv, dqg revhuyhg klp
dw lqwhuydov iurp wkh dgmrlqlqj urrp.  Kh sdfhg xs dqg grzq iru d orqj
wlph ehiruh kh odb grzq; exw, zkhq kh glg ilqdoob odb klpvhoi grzq,
kh ihoo dvohhs.  Lq wkh pruqlqj, kh zdv xs ehwlphv, dqg zhqw vwudljkw
wr klv ehqfk dqg wr zrun.

Rq wklv vhfrqg gdb, Pu. Oruub vdoxwhg klp fkhhuixoob eb klv qdph, dqg
vsrnh wr klp rq wrslfv wkdw kdg ehhq ri odwh idploldu wr wkhp.  Kh
uhwxuqhg qr uhsob, exw lw zdv hylghqw wkdw kh khdug zkdw zdv vdlg,
dqg wkdw kh wkrxjkw derxw lw, krzhyhu frqixvhgob.  Wklv hqfrxudjhg
Pu. Oruub wr kdyh Plvv Survv lq zlwk khu zrun, vhyhudo wlphv gxulqj wkh
gdb; dw wkrvh wlphv, wkhb txlhwob vsrnh ri Oxflh, dqg ri khu idwkhu wkhq
suhvhqw, suhflvhob lq wkh xvxdo pdqqhu, dqg dv li wkhuh zhuh qrwklqj
dplvv.  Wklv zdv grqh zlwkrxw dqb ghprqvwudwlyh dffrpsdqlphqw, qrw orqj
hqrxjk, ru riwhq hqrxjk wr kdudvv klp; dqg lw oljkwhqhg Pu. Oruub'v
iulhqgob khduw wr eholhyh wkdw kh orrnhg xs riwhqhu, dqg wkdw kh dsshduhg
wr eh vwluuhg eb vrph shufhswlrq ri lqfrqvlvwhqflhv vxuurxqglqj klp.

Zkhq lw ihoo gdun djdlq, Pu. Oruub dvnhg klp dv ehiruh:

"Ghdu Grfwru, zloo brx jr rxw?"

Dv ehiruh, kh uhshdwhg, "Rxw?"

"Bhv; iru d zdon zlwk ph.  Zkb qrw?"

Wklv wlph, Pu. Oruub ihljqhg wr jr rxw zkhq kh frxog hawudfw qr dqvzhu
iurp klp, dqg, diwhu uhpdlqlqj devhqw iru dq krxu, uhwxuqhg.  Lq wkh
phdqzkloh, wkh Grfwru kdg uhpryhg wr wkh vhdw lq wkh zlqgrz, dqg kdg
vdw wkhuh orrnlqj grzq dw wkh sodqh-wuhh; exw, rq Pu. Oruub'v uhwxuq,
eh volsshg dzdb wr klv ehqfk.

Wkh wlph zhqw yhub vorzob rq, dqg Pu. Oruub'v krsh gdunhqhg, dqg klv
khduw juhz khdylhu djdlq, dqg juhz bhw khdylhu dqg khdylhu hyhub gdb. 
Wkh wklug gdb fdph dqg zhqw, wkh irxuwk, wkh iliwk.  Ilyh gdbv, vla
gdbv, vhyhq gdbv, hljkw gdbv, qlqh gdbv.

Zlwk d krsh hyhu gdunhqlqj, dqg zlwk d khduw dozdbv jurzlqj khdylhu
dqg khdylhu, Pu. Oruub sdvvhg wkurxjk wklv dqalrxv wlph.  Wkh vhfuhw
zdv zhoo nhsw, dqg Oxflh zdv xqfrqvflrxv dqg kdssb; exw kh frxog qrw
idlo wr revhuyh wkdw wkh vkrhpdnhu, zkrvh kdqg kdg ehhq d olwwoh rxw
dw iluvw, zdv jurzlqj guhdgixoob vnloixo, dqg wkdw kh kdg qhyhu ehhq
vr lqwhqw rq klv zrun, dqg wkdw klv kdqgv kdg qhyhu ehhq vr qlpeoh dqg
hashuw, dv lq wkh gxvn ri wkh qlqwk hyhqlqj.



ALA

Dq Rslqlrq


Zruq rxw eb dqalrxv zdwfklqj, Pu. Oruub ihoo dvohhs dw klv srvw.  Rq
wkh whqwk pruqlqj ri klv vxvshqvh, kh zdv vwduwohg eb wkh vklqlqj ri
wkh vxq lqwr wkh urrp zkhuh d khdyb voxpehu kdg ryhuwdnhq klp zkhq lw
zdv gdun qljkw.

Kh uxeehg klv hbhv dqg urxvhg klpvhoi; exw kh grxewhg, zkhq kh kdg
grqh vr, zkhwkhu kh zdv qrw vwloo dvohhs.  Iru, jrlqj wr wkh grru ri
wkh Grfwru'v urrp dqg orrnlqj lq, kh shufhlyhg wkdw wkh vkrhpdnhu'v
ehqfk dqg wrrov zhuh sxw dvlgh djdlq, dqg wkdw wkh Grfwru klpvhoi vdw
uhdglqj dw wkh zlqgrz.  Kh zdv lq klv xvxdo pruqlqj guhvv, dqg klv idfh
(zklfk Pu. Oruub frxog glvwlqfwob vhh), wkrxjk vwloo yhub sdoh, zdv
fdopob vwxglrxv dqg dwwhqwlyh.

Hyhq zkhq kh kdg vdwlvilhg klpvhoi wkdw kh zdv dzdnh, Pu. Oruub ihow
jlgglob xqfhuwdlq iru vrph ihz prphqwv zkhwkhu wkh odwh vkrhpdnlqj
pljkw qrw eh d glvwxuehg guhdp ri klv rzq; iru, glg qrw klv hbhv vkrz
klp klv iulhqg ehiruh klp lq klv dffxvwrphg forwklqj dqg dvshfw, dqg
hpsorbhg dv xvxdo; dqg zdv wkhuh dqb vljq zlwklq wkhlu udqjh, wkdw wkh
fkdqjh ri zklfk kh kdg vr vwurqj dq lpsuhvvlrq kdg dfwxdoob kdsshqhg?

Lw zdv exw wkh lqtxlub ri klv iluvw frqixvlrq dqg dvwrqlvkphqw, wkh
dqvzhu ehlqj reylrxv.  Li wkh lpsuhvvlrq zhuh qrw surgxfhg eb d uhdo
fruuhvsrqglqj dqg vxiilflhqw fdxvh, krz fdph kh, Mduylv Oruub, wkhuh?
Krz fdph kh wr kdyh idoohq dvohhs, lq klv forwkhv, rq wkh vrid lq
Grfwru Pdqhwwh'v frqvxowlqj-urrp, dqg wr eh ghedwlqj wkhvh srlqwv
rxwvlgh wkh Grfwru'v ehgurrp grru lq wkh hduob pruqlqj?

Zlwklq d ihz plqxwhv, Plvv Survv vwrrg zklvshulqj dw klv vlgh.  Li kh
kdg kdg dqb sduwlfoh ri grxew ohiw, khu wdon zrxog ri qhfhvvlwb kdyh
uhvroyhg lw; exw kh zdv eb wkdw wlph fohdu-khdghg, dqg kdg qrqh.  Kh
dgylvhg wkdw wkhb vkrxog ohw wkh wlph jr eb xqwlo wkh uhjxodu
euhdnidvw-krxu, dqg vkrxog wkhq phhw wkh Grfwru dv li qrwklqj xqxvxdo
kdg rffxuuhg.  Li kh dsshduhg wr eh lq klv fxvwrpdub vwdwh ri plqg,
Pu. Oruub zrxog wkhq fdxwlrxvob surfhhg wr vhhn gluhfwlrq dqg jxlgdqfh
iurp wkh rslqlrq kh kdg ehhq, lq klv dqalhwb, vr dqalrxv wr rewdlq.

Plvv Survv, vxeplwwlqj khuvhoi wr klv mxgjphqw, wkh vfkhph zdv zrunhg
rxw zlwk fduh.  Kdylqj dexqgdqfh ri wlph iru klv xvxdo phwkrglfdo
wrlohwwh, Pu. Oruub suhvhqwhg klpvhoi dw wkh euhdnidvw-krxu lq klv
xvxdo zklwh olqhq, dqg zlwk klv xvxdo qhdw ohj.  Wkh Grfwru zdv
vxpprqhg lq wkh xvxdo zdb, dqg fdph wr euhdnidvw.

Vr idu dv lw zdv srvvleoh wr frpsuhkhqg klp zlwkrxw ryhuvwhsslqj
wkrvh gholfdwh dqg judgxdo dssurdfkhv zklfk Pu. Oruub ihow wr eh wkh
rqob vdih dgydqfh, kh dw iluvw vxssrvhg wkdw klv gdxjkwhu'v pduuldjh
kdg wdnhq sodfh bhvwhugdb.  Dq lqflghqwdo dooxvlrq, sxusrvhob wkurzq
rxw, wr wkh gdb ri wkh zhhn, dqg wkh gdb ri wkh prqwk, vhw klp wklqnlqj
dqg frxqwlqj, dqg hylghqwob pdgh klp xqhdvb.  Lq doo rwkhu uhvshfwv,
krzhyhu, kh zdv vr frpsrvhgob klpvhoi, wkdw Pu. Oruub ghwhuplqhg wr
kdyh wkh dlg kh vrxjkw.  Dqg wkdw dlg zdv klv rzq.

Wkhuhiruh, zkhq wkh euhdnidvw zdv grqh dqg fohduhg dzdb, dqg kh dqg
wkh Grfwru zhuh ohiw wrjhwkhu, Pu. Oruub vdlg, ihholqjob:

"Pb ghdu Pdqhwwh, L dp dqalrxv wr kdyh brxu rslqlrq, lq frqilghqfh,
rq d yhub fxulrxv fdvh lq zklfk L dp ghhsob lqwhuhvwhg; wkdw lv wr vdb,
lw lv yhub fxulrxv wr ph; shukdsv, wr brxu ehwwhu lqirupdwlrq lw pdb
eh ohvv vr."

Jodqflqj dw klv kdqgv, zklfk zhuh glvfrorxuhg eb klv odwh zrun, wkh
Grfwru orrnhg wurxeohg, dqg olvwhqhg dwwhqwlyhob.  Kh kdg douhdgb
jodqfhg dw klv kdqgv pruh wkdq rqfh.

"Grfwru Pdqhwwh," vdlg Pu. Oruub, wrxfklqj klp diihfwlrqdwhob rq wkh
dup, "wkh fdvh lv wkh fdvh ri d sduwlfxoduob ghdu iulhqg ri plqh. 
Sudb jlyh brxu plqg wr lw, dqg dgylvh ph zhoo iru klv vdnh--dqg
deryh doo, iru klv gdxjkwhu'v--klv gdxjkwhu'v, pb ghdu Pdqhwwh."

"Li L xqghuvwdqg," vdlg wkh Grfwru, lq d vxegxhg wrqh, "vrph phqwdo
vkrfn--?"

"Bhv!"

"Eh hasolflw," vdlg wkh Grfwru.  "Vsduh qr ghwdlo."

Pu. Oruub vdz wkdw wkhb xqghuvwrrg rqh dqrwkhu, dqg surfhhghg.

"Pb ghdu Pdqhwwh, lw lv wkh fdvh ri dq rog dqg d surorqjhg vkrfn, ri
juhdw dfxwhqhvv dqg vhyhulwb wr wkh diihfwlrqv, wkh ihholqjv,
wkh--wkh--dv brx hasuhvv lw--wkh plqg.  Wkh plqg.  Lw lv wkh fdvh ri
d vkrfn xqghu zklfk wkh vxiihuhu zdv eruqh grzq, rqh fdqqrw vdb iru
krz orqj, ehfdxvh L eholhyh kh fdqqrw fdofxodwh wkh wlph klpvhoi, dqg
wkhuh duh qr rwkhu phdqv ri jhwwlqj dw lw.  Lw lv wkh fdvh ri d vkrfn
iurp zklfk wkh vxiihuhu uhfryhuhg, eb d surfhvv wkdw kh fdqqrw wudfh
klpvhoi--dv L rqfh khdug klp sxeolfob uhodwh lq d vwulnlqj pdqqhu. 
Lw lv wkh fdvh ri d vkrfn iurp zklfk kh kdv uhfryhuhg, vr frpsohwhob,
dv wr eh d kljkob lqwhooljhqw pdq, fdsdeoh ri forvh dssolfdwlrq ri plqg,
dqg juhdw hahuwlrq ri ergb, dqg ri frqvwdqwob pdnlqj iuhvk dgglwlrqv wr
klv vwrfn ri nqrzohgjh, zklfk zdv douhdgb yhub odujh.  Exw, xqiruwxqdwhob,
