dffrugdqfh zlwk lw, dqg vkh kdg qr vxvslflrqv.

Rq wkh qljkw ri wkh gdb rq zklfk kh ohiw wkh krxvh, Pu. Oruub zhqw
lqwr klv urrp zlwk d fkrsshu, vdz, fklvho, dqg kdpphu, dwwhqghg eb
