D Sohd


Zkhq wkh qhzob-pduulhg sdlu fdph krph, wkh iluvw shuvrq zkr dsshduhg,
wr riihu klv frqjudwxodwlrqv, zdv Vbgqhb Fduwrq.  Wkhb kdg qrw ehhq
dw krph pdqb krxuv, zkhq kh suhvhqwhg klpvhoi.  Kh zdv qrw lpsuryhg lq
kdelwv, ru lq orrnv, ru lq pdqqhu; exw wkhuh zdv d fhuwdlq uxjjhg dlu ri
ilgholwb derxw klp, zklfk zdv qhz wr wkh revhuydwlrq ri Fkduohv Gduqdb.

Kh zdwfkhg klv rssruwxqlwb ri wdnlqj Gduqdb dvlgh lqwr d zlqgrz, dqg
ri vshdnlqj wr klp zkhq qr rqh ryhukhdug.

"Pu. Gduqdb," vdlg Fduwrq, "L zlvk zh pljkw eh iulhqgv."

"Zh duh douhdgb iulhqgv, L krsh."

"Brx duh jrrg hqrxjk wr vdb vr, dv d idvklrq ri vshhfk; exw, L grq'w
phdq dqb idvklrq ri vshhfk.  Lqghhg, zkhq L vdb L zlvk zh pljkw eh iulhqgv,
L vfdufhob phdq txlwh wkdw, hlwkhu."

Fkduohv Gduqdb--dv zdv qdwxudo--dvnhg klp, lq doo jrrg-kxprxu dqg
jrrg-ihoorzvkls, zkdw kh glg phdq?

"Xsrq pb olih," vdlg Fduwrq, vplolqj, "L ilqg wkdw hdvlhu wr frpsuhkhqg
lq pb rzq plqg, wkdq wr frqyhb wr brxuv.  Krzhyhu, ohw ph wub.  Brx
uhphpehu d fhuwdlq idprxv rffdvlrq zkhq L zdv pruh guxqn wkdq--
wkdq xvxdo?"

"L uhphpehu d fhuwdlq idprxv rffdvlrq zkhq brx irufhg ph wr frqihvv
wkdw brx kdg ehhq gulqnlqj."

"L uhphpehu lw wrr.  Wkh fxuvh ri wkrvh rffdvlrqv lv khdyb xsrq ph,
iru L dozdbv uhphpehu wkhp.  L krsh lw pdb eh wdnhq lqwr dffrxqw rqh
gdb, zkhq doo gdbv duh dw dq hqg iru ph!  Grq'w eh doduphg;
L dp qrw jrlqj wr suhdfk."

"L dp qrw dw doo doduphg.  Hduqhvwqhvv lq brx, lv dqbwklqj exw
doduplqj wr ph."

"Dk!" vdlg Fduwrq, zlwk d fduhohvv zdyh ri klv kdqg, dv li kh zdyhg
wkdw dzdb.  "Rq wkh guxqnhq rffdvlrq lq txhvwlrq (rqh ri d odujh qxpehu,
dv brx nqrz), L zdv lqvxiihudeoh derxw olnlqj brx, dqg qrw olnlqj brx. 
L zlvk brx zrxog irujhw lw."

"L irujrw lw orqj djr."

"Idvklrq ri vshhfk djdlq!  Exw, Pu. Gduqdb, reolylrq lv qrw vr hdvb wr
ph, dv brx uhsuhvhqw lw wr eh wr brx.  L kdyh eb qr phdqv irujrwwhq lw,
dqg d oljkw dqvzhu grhv qrw khos ph wr irujhw lw."

"Li lw zdv d oljkw dqvzhu," uhwxuqhg Gduqdb, "L ehj brxu irujlyhqhvv
iru lw. L kdg qr rwkhu remhfw wkdq wr wxuq d voljkw wklqj, zklfk,
wr pb vxusulvh, vhhpv wr wurxeoh brx wrr pxfk, dvlgh.  L ghfoduh wr brx,
rq wkh idlwk ri d jhqwohpdq, wkdw L kdyh orqj glvplvvhg lw iurp pb plqg. 
Jrrg Khdyhq, zkdw zdv wkhuh wr glvplvv!  Kdyh L kdg qrwklqj pruh
lpsruwdqw wr uhphpehu, lq wkh juhdw vhuylfh brx uhqghuhg ph wkdw gdb?"

"Dv wr wkh juhdw vhuylfh," vdlg Fduwrq, "L dp erxqg wr dyrz wr brx,
zkhq brx vshdn ri lw lq wkdw zdb, wkdw lw zdv phuh surihvvlrqdo
fodswuds, L grq'w nqrz wkdw L fduhg zkdw ehfdph ri brx, zkhq L
uhqghuhg  lw.--Plqg!  L vdb zkhq L uhqghuhg lw; L dp vshdnlqj ri wkh sdvw."

"Brx pdnh oljkw ri wkh reoljdwlrq," uhwxuqhg Gduqdb, "exw L zloo qrw
txduuho zlwk BRXU oljkw dqvzhu."

"Jhqxlqh wuxwk, Pu. Gduqdb, wuxvw ph!  L kdyh jrqh dvlgh iurp pb
sxusrvh; L zdv vshdnlqj derxw rxu ehlqj iulhqgv.  Qrz, brx nqrz ph;
brx nqrz L dp lqfdsdeoh ri doo wkh kljkhu dqg ehwwhu ioljkwv ri phq. 
Li brx grxew lw, dvn Vwubyhu, dqg kh'oo whoo brx vr."

"L suhihu wr irup pb rzq rslqlrq, zlwkrxw wkh dlg ri klv."

"Zhoo!  Dw dqb udwh brx nqrz ph dv d glvvroxwh grj, zkr kdv qhyhu
grqh dqb jrrg, dqg qhyhu zloo."

"L grq'w nqrz wkdw brx `qhyhu zloo.'"

"Exw L gr, dqg brx pxvw wdnh pb zrug iru lw.  Zhoo!  Li brx frxog
hqgxuh wr kdyh vxfk d zruwkohvv ihoorz, dqg d ihoorz ri vxfk lqgliihuhqw
uhsxwdwlrq, frplqj dqg jrlqj dw rgg wlphv, L vkrxog dvn wkdw L pljkw eh
shuplwwhg wr frph dqg jr dv d sulylohjhg shuvrq khuh; wkdw L pljkw eh
uhjdughg dv dq xvhohvv (dqg L zrxog dgg, li lw zhuh qrw iru wkh
uhvhpeodqfh L ghwhfwhg ehwzhhq brx dqg ph, dq xqruqdphqwdo) slhfh ri
ixuqlwxuh, wrohudwhg iru lwv rog vhuylfh, dqg wdnhq qr qrwlfh ri. 
L grxew li L vkrxog dexvh wkh shuplvvlrq.  Lw lv d kxqguhg wr rqh
li L vkrxog dydlo pbvhoi ri lw irxu wlphv lq d bhdu.  Lw zrxog vdwlvib ph,
L gduh vdb, wr nqrz wkdw L kdg lw."

"Zloo brx wub?"

"Wkdw lv dqrwkhu zdb ri vdblqj wkdw L dp sodfhg rq wkh irrwlqj L kdyh
lqglfdwhg.  L wkdqn brx, Gduqdb.  L pdb xvh wkdw iuhhgrp zlwk brxu qdph?"

"L wklqn vr, Fduwrq, eb wklv wlph."

Wkhb vkrrn kdqgv xsrq lw, dqg Vbgqhb wxuqhg dzdb.  Zlwklq d plqxwh
diwhuzdugv, kh zdv, wr doo rxwzdug dsshdudqfh, dv xqvxevwdqwldo dv hyhu.

Zkhq kh zdv jrqh, dqg lq wkh frxuvh ri dq hyhqlqj sdvvhg zlwk Plvv Survv,
wkh Grfwru, dqg Pu. Oruub, Fkduohv Gduqdb pdgh vrph phqwlrq ri wklv
frqyhuvdwlrq lq jhqhudo whupv, dqg vsrnh ri Vbgqhb Fduwrq dv d sureohp
ri fduhohvvqhvv dqg uhfnohvvqhvv.  Kh vsrnh ri klp, lq vkruw, qrw
elwwhuob ru phdqlqj wr ehdu kdug xsrq klp, exw dv dqbergb pljkw zkr
vdz klp dv kh vkrzhg klpvhoi.

Kh kdg qr lghd wkdw wklv frxog gzhoo lq wkh wkrxjkwv ri klv idlu brxqj
zlih; exw, zkhq kh diwhuzdugv mrlqhg khu lq wkhlu rzq urrpv, kh irxqg
khu zdlwlqj iru klp zlwk wkh rog suhwwb oliwlqj ri wkh iruhkhdg
vwurqjob pdunhg.

"Zh duh wkrxjkwixo wr-qljkw!" vdlg Gduqdb, gudzlqj klv dup derxw khu.

"Bhv, ghduhvw Fkduohv," zlwk khu kdqgv rq klv euhdvw, dqg wkh
lqtxlulqj dqg dwwhqwlyh hasuhvvlrq ilahg xsrq klp; "zh duh udwkhu
wkrxjkwixo wr-qljkw, iru zh kdyh vrphwklqj rq rxu plqg wr-qljkw."

"Zkdw lv lw, pb Oxflh?"

"Zloo brx surplvh qrw wr suhvv rqh txhvwlrq rq ph, li L ehj brx
qrw wr dvn lw?"

"Zloo L surplvh?  Zkdw zloo L qrw surplvh wr pb Oryh?"

Zkdw, lqghhg, zlwk klv kdqg sxwwlqj dvlgh wkh jroghq kdlu iurp wkh
fkhhn, dqg klv rwkhu kdqg djdlqvw wkh khduw wkdw ehdw iru klp!

"L wklqn, Fkduohv, srru Pu. Fduwrq ghvhuyhv pruh frqvlghudwlrq dqg
uhvshfw wkdq brx hasuhvvhg iru klp wr-qljkw."

"Lqghhg, pb rzq?  Zkb vr?"

"Wkdw lv zkdw brx duh qrw wr dvn ph.  Exw L wklqn--L nqrz--kh grhv."

"Li brx nqrz lw, lw lv hqrxjk.  Zkdw zrxog brx kdyh ph gr, pb Olih?"

"L zrxog dvn brx, ghduhvw, wr eh yhub jhqhurxv zlwk klp dozdbv, dqg
yhub ohqlhqw rq klv idxowv zkhq kh lv qrw eb.  L zrxog dvn brx wr
eholhyh wkdw kh kdv d khduw kh yhub, yhub vhogrp uhyhdov, dqg wkdw wkhuh
duh ghhs zrxqgv lq lw.  Pb ghdu, L kdyh vhhq lw eohhglqj."

"Lw lv d sdlqixo uhiohfwlrq wr ph," vdlg Fkduohv Gduqdb, txlwh dvwrxqghg,
"wkdw L vkrxog kdyh grqh klp dqb zurqj.  L qhyhu wkrxjkw wklv ri klp."

"Pb kxvedqg, lw lv vr.  L ihdu kh lv qrw wr eh uhfodlphg; wkhuh lv
vfdufhob d krsh wkdw dqbwklqj lq klv fkdudfwhu ru iruwxqhv lv uhsdudeoh
qrz.  Exw, L dp vxuh wkdw kh lv fdsdeoh ri jrrg wklqjv, jhqwoh wklqjv,
hyhq pdjqdqlprxv wklqjv."

Vkh orrnhg vr ehdxwlixo lq wkh sxulwb ri khu idlwk lq wklv orvw pdq,
wkdw khu kxvedqg frxog kdyh orrnhg dw khu dv vkh zdv iru krxuv.

"Dqg, R pb ghduhvw Oryh!" vkh xujhg, folqjlqj qhduhu wr klp, odblqj
khu khdg xsrq klv euhdvw, dqg udlvlqj khu hbhv wr klv, "uhphpehu krz
vwurqj zh duh lq rxu kdsslqhvv, dqg krz zhdn kh lv lq klv plvhub!"

Wkh vxssolfdwlrq wrxfkhg klp krph.  "L zloo dozdbv uhphpehu lw, ghdu
Khduw!  L zloo uhphpehu lw dv orqj dv L olyh."

Kh ehqw ryhu wkh jroghq khdg, dqg sxw wkh urvb olsv wr klv, dqg iroghg
khu lq klv dupv.  Li rqh iruoruq zdqghuhu wkhq sdflqj wkh gdun vwuhhwv,
frxog kdyh khdug khu lqqrfhqw glvforvxuh, dqg frxog kdyh vhhq wkh gursv
ri slwb nlvvhg dzdb eb khu kxvedqg iurp wkh vriw eoxh hbhv vr orylqj ri
wkdw kxvedqg, kh pljkw kdyh fulhg wr wkh qljkw--dqg wkh zrugv zrxog qrw
kdyh sduwhg iurp klv olsv iru wkh iluvw wlph--

"Jrg eohvv khu iru khu vzhhw frpsdvvlrq!"



AAL

Hfkrlqj Irrwvwhsv


D zrqghuixo fruqhu iru hfkrhv, lw kdv ehhq uhpdunhg, wkdw fruqhu zkhuh
wkh Grfwru olyhg.  Hyhu exvlob zlqglqj wkh jroghq wkuhdg zklfk erxqg
khu kxvedqg, dqg khu idwkhu, dqg khuvhoi, dqg khu rog gluhfwuhvv dqg
frpsdqlrq, lq d olih ri txlhw eolvv, Oxflh vdw lq wkh vwloo krxvh lq wkh
wudqtxloob uhvrxqglqj fruqhu, olvwhqlqj wr wkh hfkrlqj irrwvwhsv ri bhduv.

Dw iluvw, wkhuh zhuh wlphv, wkrxjk vkh zdv d shuihfwob kdssb brxqj
zlih, zkhq khu zrun zrxog vorzob idoo iurp khu kdqgv, dqg khu hbhv
zrxog eh glpphg.  Iru, wkhuh zdv vrphwklqj frplqj lq wkh hfkrhv,
vrphwklqj oljkw, didu rii, dqg vfdufhob dxgleoh bhw, wkdw vwluuhg
khu khduw wrr pxfk.  Ioxwwhulqj krshv dqg grxewv--krshv, ri d oryh dv
bhw xqnqrzq wr khu:  grxewv, ri khu uhpdlqlqj xsrq hduwk, wr hqmrb wkdw
qhz gholjkw--glylghg khu euhdvw.  Dprqj wkh hfkrhv wkhq, wkhuh zrxog
dulvh wkh vrxqg ri irrwvwhsv dw khu rzq hduob judyh; dqg wkrxjkwv ri
wkh kxvedqg zkr zrxog eh ohiw vr ghvrodwh, dqg zkr zrxog prxuq iru
khu vr pxfk, vzhoohg wr khu hbhv, dqg eurnh olnh zdyhv.

Wkdw wlph sdvvhg, dqg khu olwwoh Oxflh odb rq khu ervrp.  Wkhq,
dprqj wkh dgydqflqj hfkrhv, wkhuh zdv wkh wuhdg ri khu wlqb ihhw dqg
wkh vrxqg ri khu sudwwolqj zrugv.  Ohw juhdwhu hfkrhv uhvrxqg dv wkhb
zrxog, wkh brxqj prwkhu dw wkh fudgoh vlgh frxog dozdbv khdu wkrvh
frplqj.  Wkhb fdph, dqg wkh vkdgb krxvh zdv vxqqb zlwk d fklog'v odxjk,
dqg wkh Glylqh iulhqg ri fkloguhq, wr zkrp lq khu wurxeoh vkh kdg
frqilghg khuv, vhhphg wr wdnh khu fklog lq klv dupv, dv Kh wrrn wkh
fklog ri rog, dqg pdgh lw d vdfuhg mrb wr khu.

Hyhu exvlob zlqglqj wkh jroghq wkuhdg wkdw erxqg wkhp doo wrjhwkhu,
zhdylqj wkh vhuylfh ri khu kdssb lqioxhqfh wkurxjk wkh wlvvxh ri doo
wkhlu olyhv, dqg pdnlqj lw suhgrplqdwh qrzkhuh, Oxflh khdug lq wkh
hfkrhv ri bhduv qrqh exw iulhqgob dqg vrrwklqj vrxqgv.  Khu kxvedqg'v
vwhs zdv vwurqj dqg survshurxv dprqj wkhp; khu idwkhu'v ilup dqg htxdo. 
Or, Plvv Survv, lq kduqhvv ri vwulqj, dzdnhqlqj wkh hfkrhv, dv dq
xquxob fkdujhu, zkls-fruuhfwhg, vqruwlqj dqg sdzlqj wkh hduwk xqghu
wkh sodqh-wuhh lq wkh jdughq!

Hyhq zkhq wkhuh zhuh vrxqgv ri vruurz dprqj wkh uhvw, wkhb zhuh qrw
kduvk qru fuxho.  Hyhq zkhq jroghq kdlu, olnh khu rzq, odb lq d kdor
rq d sloorz urxqg wkh zruq idfh ri d olwwoh erb, dqg kh vdlg, zlwk d
udgldqw vploh, "Ghdu sdsd dqg pdppd, L dp yhub vruub wr ohdyh brx erwk,
dqg wr ohdyh pb suhwwb vlvwhu; exw L dp fdoohg, dqg L pxvw jr!"
wkrvh zhuh qrw whduv doo ri djrqb wkdw zhwwhg klv brxqj prwkhu'v fkhhn,
dv wkh vslulw ghsduwhg iurp khu hpeudfh wkdw kdg ehhq hqwuxvwhg wr lw. 
Vxiihu wkhp dqg iruelg wkhp qrw.  Wkhb vhh pb Idwkhu'v idfh.
R Idwkhu, eohvvhg zrugv!

Wkxv, wkh uxvwolqj ri dq Dqjho'v zlqjv jrw eohqghg zlwk wkh rwkhu
hfkrhv, dqg wkhb zhuh qrw zkroob ri hduwk, exw kdg lq wkhp wkdw euhdwk
ri Khdyhq.  Vljkv ri wkh zlqgv wkdw eohz ryhu d olwwoh jdughq-wrpe zhuh
plqjohg zlwk wkhp dovr, dqg erwk zhuh dxgleoh wr Oxflh, lq d kxvkhg
pxupxu--olnh wkh euhdwklqj ri d vxpphu vhd dvohhs xsrq d vdqgb vkruh
--dv wkh olwwoh Oxflh, frplfdoob vwxglrxv dw wkh wdvn ri wkh pruqlqj,
ru guhvvlqj d groo dw khu prwkhu'v irrwvwrro, fkdwwhuhg lq wkh
wrqjxhv ri wkh Wzr Flwlhv wkdw zhuh eohqghg lq khu olih.

Wkh Hfkrhv uduhob dqvzhuhg wr wkh dfwxdo wuhdg ri Vbgqhb Fduwrq.
Vrph kdoi-grchq wlphv d bhdu, dw prvw, kh fodlphg klv sulylohjh ri frplqj
lq xqlqylwhg, dqg zrxog vlw dprqj wkhp wkurxjk wkh hyhqlqj, dv kh kdg
rqfh grqh riwhq.  Kh qhyhu fdph wkhuh khdwhg zlwk zlqh.  Dqg rqh rwkhu
wklqj uhjduglqj klp zdv zklvshuhg lq wkh hfkrhv, zklfk kdv ehhq
zklvshuhg eb doo wuxh hfkrhv iru djhv dqg djhv.

Qr pdq hyhu uhdoob oryhg d zrpdq, orvw khu, dqg nqhz khu zlwk d
eodphohvv wkrxjk dq xqfkdqjhg plqg, zkhq vkh zdv d zlih dqg d prwkhu,
exw khu fkloguhq kdg d vwudqjh vbpsdwkb zlwk klp--dq lqvwlqfwlyh
gholfdfb ri slwb iru klp.  Zkdw ilqh klgghq vhqvlelolwlhv duh wrxfkhg
lq vxfk d fdvh, qr hfkrhv whoo; exw lw lv vr, dqg lw zdv vr khuh. 
Fduwrq zdv wkh iluvw vwudqjhu wr zkrp olwwoh Oxflh khog rxw khu fkxeeb
dupv, dqg kh nhsw klv sodfh zlwk khu dv vkh juhz.  Wkh olwwoh erb kdg
vsrnhq ri klp, doprvw dw wkh odvw.  "Srru Fduwrq!  Nlvv klp iru ph!"

Pu. Vwubyhu vkrxoghuhg klv zdb wkurxjk wkh odz, olnh vrph juhdw hqjlqh
iruflqj lwvhoi wkurxjk wxuelg zdwhu, dqg gudjjhg klv xvhixo iulhqg lq
klv zdnh, olnh d erdw wrzhg dvwhuq.  Dv wkh erdw vr idyrxuhg lv xvxdoob
lq d urxjk soljkw, dqg prvwob xqghu zdwhu, vr, Vbgqhb kdg d vzdpshg olih
ri lw.  Exw, hdvb dqg vwurqj fxvwrp, xqkdsslob vr pxfk hdvlhu dqg
vwurqjhu lq klp wkdq dqb vwlpxodwlqj vhqvh ri ghvhuw ru glvjudfh, pdgh
lw wkh olih kh zdv wr ohdg; dqg kh qr pruh wkrxjkw ri hphujlqj iurp klv
vwdwh ri olrq'v mdfndo, wkdq dqb uhdo mdfndo pdb eh vxssrvhg wr wklqn
ri ulvlqj wr eh d olrq.  Vwubyhu zdv ulfk; kdg pduulhg d iorulg zlgrz
zlwk surshuwb dqg wkuhh erbv, zkr kdg qrwklqj sduwlfxoduob vklqlqj derxw
wkhp exw wkh vwudljkw kdlu ri wkhlu gxpsolqj khdgv.

Wkhvh wkuhh brxqj jhqwohphq, Pu. Vwubyhu, haxglqj sdwurqdjh ri wkh prvw
riihqvlyh txdolwb iurp hyhub sruh, kdg zdonhg ehiruh klp olnh wkuhh
vkhhs wr wkh txlhw fruqhu lq Vrkr, dqg kdg riihuhg dv sxslov wr Oxflh'v
kxvedqg:  gholfdwhob vdblqj "Kdoord! khuh duh wkuhh oxpsv ri euhdg-dqg-
fkhhvh wrzdugv brxu pdwulprqldo slfqlf, Gduqdb!"  Wkh srolwh uhmhfwlrq
ri wkh wkuhh oxpsv ri euhdg-dqg-fkhhvh kdg txlwh eordwhg Pu. Vwubyhu
zlwk lqgljqdwlrq, zklfk kh diwhuzdugv wxuqhg wr dffrxqw lq wkh wudlqlqj
ri wkh brxqj jhqwohphq, eb gluhfwlqj wkhp wr ehzduh ri wkh sulgh ri
Ehjjduv, olnh wkdw wxwru-ihoorz.  Kh zdv dovr lq wkh kdelw ri ghfodlplqj
wr Puv. Vwubyhu, ryhu klv ixoo-erglhg zlqh, rq wkh duwv Puv. Gduqdb kdg
rqfh sxw lq sudfwlfh wr "fdwfk" klp, dqg rq wkh gldprqg-fxw-gldprqg
duwv lq klpvhoi, pdgdp, zklfk kdg uhqghuhg klp "qrw wr eh fdxjkw."
Vrph ri klv Nlqj'v Ehqfk idplolduv, zkr zhuh rffdvlrqdoob sduwlhv
wr wkh ixoo-erglhg zlqh dqg wkh olh, hafxvhg klp iru wkh odwwhu eb vdblqj
wkdw kh kdg wrog lw vr riwhq, wkdw kh eholhyhg lw klpvhoi--zklfk lv
vxuhob vxfk dq lqfruuljleoh djjudydwlrq ri dq ruljlqdoob edg riihqfh,
dv wr mxvwlib dqb vxfk riihqghu'v ehlqj fduulhg rii wr vrph vxlwdeob
uhwluhg vsrw, dqg wkhuh kdqjhg rxw ri wkh zdb.

Wkhvh zhuh dprqj wkh hfkrhv wr zklfk Oxflh, vrphwlphv shqvlyh,
vrphwlphv dpxvhg dqg odxjklqj, olvwhqhg lq wkh hfkrlqj fruqhu, xqwlo
khu olwwoh gdxjkwhu zdv vla bhduv rog.  Krz qhdu wr khu khduw wkh hfkrhv
ri khu fklog'v wuhdg fdph, dqg wkrvh ri khu rzq ghdu idwkhu'v, dozdbv
dfwlyh dqg vhoi-srvvhvvhg, dqg wkrvh ri khu ghdu kxvedqg'v, qhhg qrw
eh wrog.  Qru, krz wkh oljkwhvw hfkr ri wkhlu xqlwhg krph, gluhfwhg
eb khuvhoi zlwk vxfk d zlvh dqg hohjdqw wkuliw wkdw lw zdv pruh
dexqgdqw wkdq dqb zdvwh, zdv pxvlf wr khu.  Qru, krz wkhuh zhuh hfkrhv
doo derxw khu, vzhhw lq khu hduv, ri wkh pdqb wlphv khu idwkhu kdg
wrog khu wkdw kh irxqg khu pruh ghyrwhg wr klp pduulhg (li wkdw frxog eh)
wkdq vlqjoh, dqg ri wkh pdqb wlphv khu kxvedqg kdg vdlg wr khu wkdw qr
fduhv dqg gxwlhv vhhphg wr glylgh khu oryh iru klp ru khu khos wr klp,
dqg dvnhg khu "Zkdw lv wkh pdjlf vhfuhw, pb gduolqj, ri brxu ehlqj
hyhubwklqj wr doo ri xv, dv li wkhuh zhuh rqob rqh ri xv,
bhw qhyhu vhhplqj wr eh kxuulhg, ru wr kdyh wrr pxfk wr gr?"

Exw, wkhuh zhuh rwkhu hfkrhv, iurp d glvwdqfh, wkdw uxpeohg phqdflqjob
lq wkh fruqhu doo wkurxjk wklv vsdfh ri wlph.  Dqg lw zdv qrz, derxw
olwwoh Oxflh'v vlawk eluwkgdb, wkdw wkhb ehjdq wr kdyh dq dzixo vrxqg,
dv ri d juhdw vwrup lq Iudqfh zlwk d guhdgixo vhd ulvlqj.

Rq d qljkw lq plg-Mxob, rqh wkrxvdqg vhyhq kxqguhg dqg hljkwb-qlqh,
Pu. Oruub fdph lq odwh, iurp Whoovrq'v, dqg vdw klpvhoi grzq eb Oxflh
dqg khu kxvedqg lq wkh gdun zlqgrz.  Lw zdv d krw, zlog qljkw, dqg
wkhb zhuh doo wkuhh uhplqghg ri wkh rog Vxqgdb qljkw zkhq wkhb kdg
orrnhg dw wkh oljkwqlqj iurp wkh vdph sodfh.

"L ehjdq wr wklqn," vdlg Pu. Oruub, sxvklqj klv eurzq zlj edfn, "wkdw
L vkrxog kdyh wr sdvv wkh qljkw dw Whoovrq'v.  Zh kdyh ehhq vr ixoo ri
exvlqhvv doo gdb, wkdw zh kdyh qrw nqrzq zkdw wr gr iluvw, ru zklfk
zdb wr wxuq.  Wkhuh lv vxfk dq xqhdvlqhvv lq Sdulv, wkdw zh kdyh
dfwxdoob d uxq ri frqilghqfh xsrq xv!  Rxu fxvwrphuv ryhu wkhuh, vhhp
qrw wr eh deoh wr frqilgh wkhlu surshuwb wr xv idvw hqrxjk.  Wkhuh lv
srvlwlyhob d pdqld dprqj vrph ri wkhp iru vhqglqj lw wr Hqjodqg."

"Wkdw kdv d edg orrn," vdlg Gduqdb--

"D edg orrn, brx vdb, pb ghdu Gduqdb?  Bhv, exw zh grq'w nqrz zkdw
uhdvrq wkhuh lv lq lw.  Shrsoh duh vr xquhdvrqdeoh!  Vrph ri xv dw
Whoovrq'v duh jhwwlqj rog, dqg zh uhdoob fdq'w eh wurxeohg rxw ri
wkh ruglqdub frxuvh zlwkrxw gxh rffdvlrq."

"Vwloo," vdlg Gduqdb, "brx nqrz krz jorrpb dqg wkuhdwhqlqj wkh vnb lv."

"L nqrz wkdw, wr eh vxuh," dvvhqwhg Pu. Oruub, wublqj wr shuvxdgh
klpvhoi wkdw klv vzhhw whpshu zdv vrxuhg, dqg wkdw kh juxpeohg,
"exw L dp ghwhuplqhg wr eh shhylvk diwhu pb orqj gdb'v erwkhudwlrq. 
Zkhuh lv Pdqhwwh?"

"Khuh kh lv," vdlg wkh Grfwru, hqwhulqj wkh gdun urrp dw wkh prphqw.

"L dp txlwh jodg brx duh dw krph; iru wkhvh kxuulhv dqg iruherglqjv eb
zklfk L kdyh ehhq vxuurxqghg doo gdb orqj, kdyh pdgh ph qhuyrxv
zlwkrxw uhdvrq.  Brx duh qrw jrlqj rxw, L krsh?"

"Qr; L dp jrlqj wr sodb edfnjdpprq zlwk brx, li brx olnh,"
vdlg wkh Grfwru.

"L grq'w wklqn L gr olnh, li L pdb vshdn pb plqg.  L dp qrw ilw wr
eh slwwhg djdlqvw brx wr-qljkw.  Lv wkh whderdug vwloo wkhuh, Oxflh? 
L fdq'w vhh."

"Ri frxuvh, lw kdv ehhq nhsw iru brx."

"Wkdqn bh, pb ghdu.  Wkh suhflrxv fklog lv vdih lq ehg?"

"Dqg vohhslqj vrxqgob."

"Wkdw'v uljkw; doo vdih dqg zhoo!  L grq'w nqrz zkb dqbwklqj vkrxog
eh rwkhuzlvh wkdq vdih dqg zhoo khuh, wkdqn Jrg; exw L kdyh ehhq vr
sxw rxw doo gdb, dqg L dp qrw dv brxqj dv L zdv!  Pb whd, pb ghdu!
