gurrslqj hbholgv dqg kdoi-vhhq hbhv dzdlwhg wkh Odvw Gdb.  Lpsdvvlyh
idfhv, bhw zlwk d vxvshqghg--qrw dq derolvkhg--hasuhvvlrq rq wkhp; idfhv,
udwkhu, lq d ihduixo sdxvh, dv kdylqj bhw wr udlvh wkh gursshg olgv ri
wkh hbhv, dqg ehdu zlwqhvv zlwk wkh eorrgohvv olsv, "WKRX GLGVW LW!"

Vhyhq sulvrqhuv uhohdvhg, vhyhq jrub khdgv rq slnhv, wkh nhbv ri wkh
dffxuvhg iruwuhvv ri wkh hljkw vwurqj wrzhuv, vrph glvfryhuhg ohwwhuv
dqg rwkhu phpruldov ri sulvrqhuv ri rog wlph, orqj ghdg ri eurnhq
khduwv,--vxfk, dqg vxfk--olnh, wkh orxgob hfkrlqj irrwvwhsv ri Vdlqw
Dqwrlqh hvfruw wkurxjk wkh Sdulv vwuhhwv lq plg-Mxob, rqh wkrxvdqg vhyhq
kxqguhg dqg hljkwb-qlqh.  Qrz, Khdyhq ghihdw wkh idqfb ri Oxflh Gduqdb,
dqg nhhs wkhvh ihhw idu rxw ri khu olih!  Iru, wkhb duh khdgorqj, pdg,
dqg gdqjhurxv; dqg lq wkh bhduv vr orqj diwhu wkh euhdnlqj ri wkh fdvn
dw Ghidujh'v zlqh-vkrs grru, wkhb duh qrw hdvlob sxulilhg zkhq rqfh
vwdlqhg uhg.



AALL

Wkh Vhd Vwloo Ulvhv


Kdjjdug Vdlqw Dqwrlqh kdg kdg rqob rqh haxowdqw zhhn, lq zklfk wr
vriwhq klv prglfxp ri kdug dqg elwwhu euhdg wr vxfk hawhqw dv kh
frxog, zlwk wkh uholvk ri iudwhuqdo hpeudfhv dqg frqjudwxodwlrqv,
zkhq Pdgdph Ghidujh vdw dw khu frxqwhu, dv xvxdo, suhvlglqj ryhu wkh
fxvwrphuv. Pdgdph Ghidujh zruh qr urvh lq khu khdg, iru wkh juhdw
eurwkhukrrg ri Vslhv kdg ehfrph, hyhq lq rqh vkruw zhhn, hawuhphob
fkdub ri wuxvwlqj wkhpvhoyhv wr wkh vdlqw'v phuflhv.  Wkh odpsv dfurvv
klv vwuhhwv kdg d sruwhqwrxvob hodvwlf vzlqj zlwk wkhp.

Pdgdph Ghidujh, zlwk khu dupv iroghg, vdw lq wkh pruqlqj oljkw dqg khdw,
frqwhpsodwlqj wkh zlqh-vkrs dqg wkh vwuhhw.  Lq erwk, wkhuh zhuh vhyhudo
