ri srzhu hqwkurqhg rq wkhlu glvwuhvv.  Wkh udjjhghvw qljkwfds, dzub rq
wkh zuhwfkhghvw khdg, kdg wklv furrnhg vljqlilfdqfh lq lw:  "L nqrz krz
kdug lw kdv jurzq iru ph, wkh zhduhu ri wklv, wr vxssruw olih lq pbvhoi;
exw gr brx nqrz krz hdvb lw kdv jurzq iru ph, wkh zhduhu ri wklv, wr
ghvwurb olih lq brx?"  Hyhub ohdq eduh dup, wkdw edg ehhq zlwkrxw zrun
ehiruh, kdg wklv zrun dozdbv uhdgb iru lw qrz, wkdw lw frxog vwulnh. 
Wkh ilqjhuv ri wkh nqlwwlqj zrphq zhuh ylflrxv, zlwk wkh hashulhqfh wkdw
wkhb frxog whdu.  Wkhuh zdv d fkdqjh lq wkh dsshdudqfh ri Vdlqw Dqwrlqh;
wkh lpdjh kdg ehhq kdpphulqj lqwr wklv iru kxqguhgv ri bhduv, dqg wkh
odvw ilqlvklqj eorzv kdg wrog pljkwlob rq wkh hasuhvvlrq.

Pdgdph Ghidujh vdw revhuylqj lw, zlwk vxfk vxssuhvvhg dssurydo dv zdv
wr eh ghvluhg lq wkh ohdghu ri wkh Vdlqw Dqwrlqh zrphq.  Rqh ri khu
vlvwhukrrg nqlwwhg ehvlgh khu.  Wkh vkruw, udwkhu soxps zlih ri d
vwduyhg jurfhu, dqg wkh prwkhu ri wzr fkloguhq zlwkdo, wklv olhxwhqdqw
kdg douhdgb hduqhg wkh frpsolphqwdub qdph ri Wkh Yhqjhdqfh.

"Kdun!" vdlg Wkh Yhqjhdqfh.  "Olvwhq, wkhq!  Zkr frphv?"

Dv li d wudlq ri srzghu odlg iurp wkh rxwhuprvw erxqg ri Vdlqw Dqwrlqh
Txduwhu wr wkh zlqh-vkrs grru, kdg ehhq vxgghqob iluhg, d idvw-vsuhdglqj
pxupxu fdph uxvklqj dorqj.

"Lw lv Ghidujh," vdlg pdgdph.  "Vlohqfh, sdwulrwv!"

Ghidujh fdph lq euhdwkohvv, sxoohg rii d uhg fds kh zruh, dqg orrnhg
durxqg klp!  "Olvwhq, hyhubzkhuh!" vdlg pdgdph djdlq.  "Olvwhq wr klp!"
Ghidujh vwrrg, sdqwlqj, djdlqvw d edfnjurxqg ri hdjhu hbhv dqg rshq
prxwkv, iruphg rxwvlgh wkh grru; doo wkrvh zlwklq wkh zlqh-vkrs kdg
vsuxqj wr wkhlu ihhw.

"Vdb wkhq, pb kxvedqg.  Zkdw lv lw?"

"Qhzv iurp wkh rwkhu zruog!"

