"Qrw ghdg!  Kh ihduhg xv vr pxfk--dqg zlwk uhdvrq--wkdw kh fdxvhg
klpvhoi wr eh uhsuhvhqwhg dv ghdg, dqg kdg d judqg prfn-ixqhudo.  Exw
wkhb kdyh irxqg klp dolyh, klglqj lq wkh frxqwub, dqg kdyh eurxjkw klp
