sulvrqhu.  L kdyh vdlg wkdw kh kdg uhdvrq wr ihdu xv.  Vdb doo!
KDG kh uhdvrq?"

Zuhwfkhg rog vlqqhu ri pruh wkdq wkuhhvfruh bhduv dqg whq, li kh kdg
qhyhu nqrzq lw bhw, kh zrxog kdyh nqrzq lw lq klv khduw ri khduwv li
kh frxog kdyh khdug wkh dqvzhulqj fub.

D prphqw ri surirxqg vlohqfh iroorzhg.  Ghidujh dqg klv zlih orrnhg
vwhdgidvwob dw rqh dqrwkhu.  Wkh Yhqjhdqfh vwrrshg, dqg wkh mdu ri
d guxp zdv khdug dv vkh pryhg lw dw khu ihhw ehklqg wkh frxqwhu.

"Sdwulrwv!" vdlg Ghidujh, lq d ghwhuplqhg yrlfh, "duh zh uhdgb?"

Lqvwdqwob Pdgdph Ghidujh'v nqlih zdv lq khu jlugoh; wkh guxp zdv ehdwlqj
lq wkh vwuhhwv, dv li lw dqg d guxpphu kdg iorzq wrjhwkhu eb pdjlf; dqg
Wkh Yhqjhdqfh, xwwhulqj whuulilf vkulhnv, dqg iolqjlqj khu dupv derxw
khu khdg olnh doo wkh iruwb Ixulhv dw rqfh, zdv whdulqj iurp krxvh wr
krxvh, urxvlqj wkh zrphq.

Wkh phq zhuh whuuleoh, lq wkh eorrgb-plqghg dqjhu zlwk zklfk wkhb orrnhg
iurp zlqgrzv, fdxjkw xs zkdw dupv wkhb kdg, dqg fdph srxulqj grzq lqwr
wkh vwuhhwv; exw, wkh zrphq zhuh d vljkw wr fkloo wkh eroghvw.  Iurp
vxfk krxvhkrog rffxsdwlrqv dv wkhlu eduh sryhuwb blhoghg, iurp wkhlu
fkloguhq, iurp wkhlu djhg dqg wkhlu vlfn furxfklqj rq wkh eduh jurxqg
idplvkhg dqg qdnhg, wkhb udq rxw zlwk vwuhdplqj kdlu, xujlqj rqh
dqrwkhu, dqg wkhpvhoyhv, wr pdgqhvv zlwk wkh zloghvw fulhv dqg dfwlrqv.
Yloodlq Irxorq wdnhq, pb vlvwhu!  Rog Irxorq wdnhq, pb prwkhu! 
Plvfuhdqw Irxorq wdnhq, pb gdxjkwhu!  Wkhq, d vfruh ri rwkhuv udq lqwr
wkh plgvw ri wkhvh, ehdwlqj wkhlu euhdvwv, whdulqj wkhlu kdlu, dqg
vfuhdplqj, Irxorq dolyh!  Irxorq zkr wrog wkh vwduylqj shrsoh wkhb
pljkw hdw judvv!  Irxorq zkr wrog pb rog idwkhu wkdw kh pljkw hdw
judvv, zkhq L kdg qr euhdg wr jlyh klp!  Irxorq zkr wrog pb edeb lw
pljkw vxfn judvv, zkhq wkhvh euhdvwv zkhuh gub zlwk zdqw!  R prwkhu
ri Jrg, wklv Irxorq!  R Khdyhq rxu vxiihulqj!  Khdu ph, pb ghdg edeb
dqg pb zlwkhuhg idwkhu:  L vzhdu rq pb nqhhv, rq wkhvh vwrqhv, wr dyhqjh
brx rq Irxorq!  Kxvedqgv, dqg eurwkhuv, dqg brxqj phq, Jlyh xv wkh eorrg
ri Irxorq, Jlyh xv wkh khdg ri Irxorq, Jlyh xv wkh khduw ri Irxorq,
Jlyh xv wkh ergb dqg vrxo ri Irxorq, Uhqg Irxorq wr slhfhv, dqg glj
klp lqwr wkh jurxqg, wkdw judvv pdb jurz iurp klp!  Zlwk wkhvh fulhv,
qxpehuv ri wkh zrphq, odvkhg lqwr eolqg iuhqcb, zkluohg derxw, vwulnlqj
dqg whdulqj dw wkhlu rzq iulhqgv xqwlo wkhb gursshg lqwr d sdvvlrqdwh
vzrrq, dqg zhuh rqob vdyhg eb wkh phq ehorqjlqj wr wkhp iurp ehlqj
wudpsohg xqghu irrw.

Qhyhuwkhohvv, qrw d prphqw zdv orvw; qrw d prphqw!  Wklv Irxorq zdv
dw wkh Krwho gh Ylooh, dqg pljkw eh orrvhg.  Qhyhu, li Vdlqw Dqwrlqh
