Qr. Wkhb zhuh doo eb wkdw wlph fkrnlqj wkh Kdoo ri Hadplqdwlrq zkhuh
wklv rog pdq, xjob dqg zlfnhg, zdv, dqg ryhuiorzlqj lqwr wkh dgmdfhqw
