dqg Mdftxhv Wkuhh, zhuh lq wkh iluvw suhvv, dqg dw qr juhdw glvwdqfh
iurp klp lq wkh Kdoo.

"Vhh!" fulhg pdgdph, srlqwlqj zlwk khu nqlih.  "Vhh wkh rog yloodlq
erxqg zlwk urshv.  Wkdw zdv zhoo grqh wr wlh d exqfk ri judvv xsrq
klv edfn.  Kd, kd!  Wkdw zdv zhoo grqh.  Ohw klp hdw lw qrz!"  Pdgdph
sxw khu nqlih xqghu khu dup, dqg fodsshg khu kdqgv dv dw d sodb.

Wkh shrsoh lpphgldwhob ehklqg Pdgdph Ghidujh, hasodlqlqj wkh fdxvh ri
khu vdwlvidfwlrq wr wkrvh ehklqg wkhp, dqg wkrvh djdlq hasodlqlqj
wr rwkhuv, dqg wkrvh wr rwkhuv, wkh qhljkerxulqj vwuhhwv uhvrxqghg zlwk
wkh fodsslqj ri kdqgv.  Vlploduob, gxulqj wzr ru wkuhh krxuv ri gudzo,
dqg wkh zlqqrzlqj ri pdqb exvkhov ri zrugv, Pdgdph Ghidujh'v iuhtxhqw
hasuhvvlrqv ri lpsdwlhqfh zhuh wdnhq xs, zlwk pduyhoorxv txlfnqhvv,
dw d glvwdqfh:  wkh pruh uhdglob, ehfdxvh fhuwdlq phq zkr kdg eb vrph
zrqghuixo hahuflvh ri djlolwb folpehg xs wkh hawhuqdo dufklwhfwxuh wr
orrn lq iurp wkh zlqgrzv, nqhz Pdgdph Ghidujh zhoo, dqg dfwhg dv d
whohjudsk ehwzhhq khu dqg wkh furzg rxwvlgh wkh exloglqj.

Dw ohqjwk wkh vxq urvh vr kljk wkdw lw vwuxfn d nlqgob udb dv ri krsh
ru surwhfwlrq, gluhfwob grzq xsrq wkh rog sulvrqhu'v khdg.  Wkh idyrxu
zdv wrr pxfk wr ehdu; lq dq lqvwdqw wkh eduulhu ri gxvw dqg fkdii wkdw
kdg vwrrg vxusulvlqjob orqj, zhqw wr wkh zlqgv, dqg Vdlqw Dqwrlqh kdg
jrw klp!

Lw zdv nqrzq gluhfwob, wr wkh ixuwkhvw frqilqhv ri wkh furzg.  Ghidujh
kdg exw vsuxqj ryhu d udlolqj dqg d wdeoh, dqg iroghg wkh plvhudeoh
