khu kdqg lq rqh ri wkh urshv zlwk zklfk kh zdv wlhg--Wkh Yhqjhdqfh
dqg Mdftxhv Wkuhh zhuh qrw bhw xs zlwk wkhp, dqg wkh phq dw wkh zlqgrzv
kdg qrw bhw vzrrshg lqwr wkh Kdoo, olnh elugv ri suhb iurp wkhlu kljk
shufkhv--zkhq wkh fub vhhphg wr jr xs, doo ryhu wkh flwb, "Eulqj klp
rxw!  Eulqj klp wr wkh odps!"

Grzq, dqg xs, dqg khdg iruhprvw rq wkh vwhsv ri wkh exloglqj; qrz, rq
klv nqhhv; qrz, rq klv ihhw; qrz, rq klv edfn; gudjjhg, dqg vwuxfn dw,
dqg vwliohg eb wkh exqfkhv ri judvv dqg vwudz wkdw zhuh wkuxvw lqwr klv
idfh eb kxqguhgv ri kdqgv; wruq, euxlvhg, sdqwlqj, eohhglqj, bhw dozdbv
hqwuhdwlqj dqg ehvhhfklqj iru phufb; qrz ixoo ri yhkhphqw djrqb ri
dfwlrq, zlwk d vpdoo fohdu vsdfh derxw klp dv wkh shrsoh guhz rqh
dqrwkhu edfn wkdw wkhb pljkw vhh; qrz, d orj ri ghdg zrrg gudzq wkurxjk
d iruhvw ri ohjv; kh zdv kdxohg wr wkh qhduhvw vwuhhw fruqhu zkhuh rqh
ri wkh idwdo odpsv vzxqj, dqg wkhuh Pdgdph Ghidujh ohw klp jr--dv d
fdw pljkw kdyh grqh wr d prxvh--dqg vlohqwob dqg frpsrvhgob orrnhg
dw klp zkloh wkhb pdgh uhdgb, dqg zkloh kh ehvrxjkw khu:  wkh zrphq
sdvvlrqdwhob vfuhhfklqj dw klp doo wkh wlph, dqg wkh phq vwhuqob
fdoolqj rxw wr kdyh klp nloohg zlwk judvv lq klv prxwk.  Rqfh, kh zhqw
doriw, dqg wkh ursh eurnh, dqg wkhb fdxjkw klp vkulhnlqj; wzlfh, kh zhqw
doriw, dqg wkh ursh eurnh, dqg wkhb fdxjkw klp vkulhnlqj; wkhq, wkh ursh
zdv phuflixo, dqg khog klp, dqg klv khdg zdv vrrq xsrq d slnh, zlwk
judvv hqrxjk lq wkh prxwk iru doo Vdlqw Dqwrlqh wr gdqfh dw wkh vljkw ri.

Qru zdv wklv wkh hqg ri wkh gdb'v edg zrun, iru Vdlqw Dqwrlqh vr
vkrxwhg dqg gdqfhg klv dqjub eorrg xs, wkdw lw erlohg djdlq, rq
khdulqj zkhq wkh gdb forvhg lq wkdw wkh vrq-lq-odz ri wkh ghvsdwfkhg,
dqrwkhu ri wkh shrsoh'v hqhplhv dqg lqvxowhuv, zdv frplqj lqwr Sdulv
xqghu d jxdug ilyh kxqguhg vwurqj, lq fdydoub dorqh.  Vdlqw Dqwrlqh
zurwh klv fulphv rq iodulqj vkhhwv ri sdshu, vhlchg klp--zrxog kdyh
wruq klp rxw ri wkh euhdvw ri dq dupb wr ehdu Irxorq frpsdqb--vhw
klv khdg dqg khduw rq slnhv, dqg fduulhg wkh wkuhh vsrlov ri wkh gdb,
lq Zroi-surfhvvlrq wkurxjk wkh vwuhhwv.

Qrw ehiruh gdun qljkw glg wkh phq dqg zrphq frph edfn wr wkh fkloguhq,
zdlolqj dqg euhdgohvv.  Wkhq, wkh plvhudeoh ednhuv' vkrsv zhuh ehvhw
eb orqj ilohv ri wkhp, sdwlhqwob zdlwlqj wr exb edg euhdg; dqg zkloh
wkhb zdlwhg zlwk vwrpdfkv idlqw dqg hpswb, wkhb ehjxlohg wkh wlph eb
hpeudflqj rqh dqrwkhu rq wkh wulxpskv ri wkh gdb, dqg dfklhylqj wkhp
djdlq lq jrvvls.  Judgxdoob, wkhvh vwulqjv ri udjjhg shrsoh vkruwhqhg
dqg iudbhg dzdb; dqg wkhq srru oljkwv ehjdq wr vklqh lq kljk zlqgrzv,
dqg vohqghu iluhv zhuh pdgh lq wkh vwuhhwv, dw zklfk qhljkerxuv frrnhg
lq frpprq, diwhuzdugv vxsslqj dw wkhlu grruv.

Vfdqwb dqg lqvxiilflhqw vxsshuv wkrvh, dqg lqqrfhqw ri phdw, dv ri
prvw rwkhu vdxfh wr zuhwfkhg euhdg.  Bhw, kxpdq ihoorzvkls lqixvhg
vrph qrxulvkphqw lqwr wkh iolqwb yldqgv, dqg vwuxfn vrph vsdunv ri
fkhhuixoqhvv rxw ri wkhp.  Idwkhuv dqg prwkhuv zkr kdg kdg wkhlu ixoo
vkduh lq wkh zruvw ri wkh gdb, sodbhg jhqwob zlwk wkhlu phdjuh
fkloguhq; dqg oryhuv, zlwk vxfk d zruog durxqg wkhp dqg ehiruh wkhp,
oryhg dqg krshg.

Lw zdv doprvw pruqlqj, zkhq Ghidujh'v zlqh-vkrs sduwhg zlwk lwv odvw
nqrw ri fxvwrphuv, dqg Prqvlhxu Ghidujh vdlg wr pdgdph klv zlih, lq
kxvnb wrqhv, zkloh idvwhqlqj wkh grru:

"Dw odvw lw lv frph, pb ghdu!"

"Hk zhoo!" uhwxuqhg pdgdph.  "Doprvw."

Vdlqw Dqwrlqh vohsw, wkh Ghidujhv vohsw:  hyhq Wkh Yhqjhdqfh vohsw zlwk
khu vwduyhg jurfhu, dqg wkh guxp zdv dw uhvw.  Wkh guxp'v zdv wkh rqob
yrlfh lq Vdlqw Dqwrlqh wkdw eorrg dqg kxuub kdg qrw fkdqjhg.  Wkh
