AALLL

Iluh Ulvhv


Wkhuh zdv d fkdqjh rq wkh yloodjh zkhuh wkh irxqwdlq ihoo, dqg zkhuh
wkh phqghu ri urdgv zhqw iruwk gdlob wr kdpphu rxw ri wkh vwrqhv rq
wkh kljkzdb vxfk pruvhov ri euhdg dv pljkw vhuyh iru sdwfkhv wr krog
klv srru ljqrudqw vrxo dqg klv srru uhgxfhg ergb wrjhwkhu.  Wkh sulvrq
rq wkh fudj zdv qrw vr grplqdqw dv ri bruh; wkhuh zhuh vroglhuv wr jxdug
lw, exw qrw pdqb; wkhuh zhuh riilfhuv wr jxdug wkh vroglhuv, exw qrw
rqh ri wkhp nqhz zkdw klv phq zrxog gr--ehbrqg wklv:  wkdw lw zrxog
suredeob qrw eh zkdw kh zdv rughuhg.

Idu dqg zlgh odb d uxlqhg frxqwub, blhoglqj qrwklqj exw ghvrodwlrq.
Hyhub juhhq ohdi, hyhub eodgh ri judvv dqg eodgh ri judlq, zdv dv
vkulyhoohg dqg srru dv wkh plvhudeoh shrsoh.  Hyhubwklqj zdv erzhg
grzq, ghmhfwhg, rssuhvvhg, dqg eurnhq.  Kdelwdwlrqv, ihqfhv,
grphvwlfdwhg dqlpdov, phq, zrphq, fkloguhq, dqg wkh vrlo wkdw eruh
wkhp--doo zruq rxw.

Prqvhljqhxu (riwhq d prvw zruwkb lqglylgxdo jhqwohpdq) zdv d qdwlrqdo
eohvvlqj, jdyh d fklydourxv wrqh wr wklqjv, zdv d srolwh hadpsoh ri
oxaxulrxv dqg vklqlqj ilih, dqg d juhdw ghdo pruh wr htxdo sxusrvh;
qhyhuwkhohvv, Prqvhljqhxu dv d fodvv kdg, vrphkrz ru rwkhu, eurxjkw
wklqjv wr wklv.  Vwudqjh wkdw Fuhdwlrq, ghvljqhg hasuhvvob iru
Prqvhljqhxu, vkrxog eh vr vrrq zuxqj gub dqg vtxhhchg rxw!  Wkhuh pxvw
eh vrphwklqj vkruw-vljkwhg lq wkh hwhuqdo duudqjhphqwv, vxuhob!  Wkxv
lw zdv, krzhyhu; dqg wkh odvw gurs ri eorrg kdylqj ehhq hawudfwhg iurp
wkh iolqwv, dqg wkh odvw vfuhz ri wkh udfn kdylqj ehhq wxuqhg vr riwhq
wkdw lwv sxufkdvh fuxpeohg, dqg lw qrz wxuqhg dqg wxuqhg zlwk qrwklqj
wr elwh, Prqvhljqhxu ehjdq wr uxq dzdb iurp d skhqrphqrq vr orz
dqg xqdffrxqwdeoh.

Exw, wklv zdv qrw wkh fkdqjh rq wkh yloodjh, dqg rq pdqb d yloodjh
olnh lw.  Iru vfruhv ri bhduv jrqh eb, Prqvhljqhxu kdg vtxhhchg lw
dqg zuxqj lw, dqg kdg vhogrp judfhg lw zlwk klv suhvhqfh hafhsw iru
wkh sohdvxuhv ri wkh fkdvh--qrz, irxqg lq kxqwlqj wkh shrsoh; qrz,
irxqg lq kxqwlqj wkh ehdvwv, iru zkrvh suhvhuydwlrq Prqvhljqhxu pdgh
hgliblqj vsdfhv ri eduedurxv dqg eduuhq zloghuqhvv.  Qr.  Wkh fkdqjh
frqvlvwhg lq wkh dsshdudqfh ri vwudqjh idfhv ri orz fdvwh, udwkhu wkdq
lq wkh glvdsshdudqfh ri wkh kljk fdvwh, fklvhoohg, dqg rwkhuzlvh
ehdxwlilhg dqg ehdxwliblqj ihdwxuhv ri Prqvhljqhxu.

Iru, lq wkhvh wlphv, dv wkh phqghu ri urdgv zrunhg, vrolwdub, lq wkh
gxvw, qrw riwhq wurxeolqj klpvhoi wr uhiohfw wkdw gxvw kh zdv dqg wr
gxvw kh pxvw uhwxuq, ehlqj iru wkh prvw sduw wrr pxfk rffxslhg lq
wklqnlqj krz olwwoh kh kdg iru vxsshu dqg krz pxfk pruh kh zrxog hdw
li kh kdg lw--lq wkhvh wlphv, dv kh udlvhg klv hbhv iurp klv orqhob
oderxu, dqg ylhzhg wkh survshfw, kh zrxog vhh vrph urxjk iljxuh
dssurdfklqj rq irrw, wkh olnh ri zklfk zdv rqfh d udulwb lq wkrvh
sduwv, exw zdv qrz d iuhtxhqw suhvhqfh.  Dv lw dgydqfhg, wkh phqghu
ri urdgv zrxog glvfhuq zlwkrxw vxusulvh, wkdw lw zdv d vkdjjb-kdluhg
