foxpvb hyhq wr wkh hbhv ri d phqghu ri urdgv, julp, urxjk, vzduw,
vwhhshg lq wkh pxg dqg gxvw ri pdqb kljkzdbv, gdqn zlwk wkh pduvkb
prlvwxuh ri pdqb orz jurxqgv, vsulqnohg zlwk wkh wkruqv dqg ohdyhv
dqg prvv ri pdqb ebzdbv wkurxjk zrrgv.

Vxfk d pdq fdph xsrq klp, olnh d jkrvw, dw qrrq lq wkh Mxob zhdwkhu,
dv kh vdw rq klv khds ri vwrqhv xqghu d edqn, wdnlqj vxfk vkhowhu dv
kh frxog jhw iurp d vkrzhu ri kdlo.

Wkh pdq orrnhg dw klp, orrnhg dw wkh yloodjh lq wkh kroorz, dw wkh
ploo, dqg dw wkh sulvrq rq wkh fudj.  Zkhq kh kdg lghqwlilhg wkhvh
remhfwv lq zkdw ehqljkwhg plqg kh kdg, kh vdlg, lq d gldohfw wkdw
zdv mxvw lqwhooljleoh:

"Krz jrhv lw, Mdftxhv?"

"Doo zhoo, Mdftxhv."

"Wrxfk wkhq!"

Wkhb mrlqhg kdqgv, dqg wkh pdq vdw grzq rq wkh khds ri vwrqhv.

"Qr glqqhu?"

"Qrwklqj exw vxsshu qrz," vdlg wkh phqghu ri urdgv, zlwk d kxqjub idfh.

"Lw lv wkh idvklrq," jurzohg wkh pdq.  "L phhw qr glqqhu dqbzkhuh."

Kh wrrn rxw d eodfnhqhg slsh, iloohg lw, oljkwhg lw zlwk iolqw dqg
vwhho, sxoohg dw lw xqwlo lw zdv lq d euljkw jorz:  wkhq, vxgghqob khog
lw iurp klp dqg gursshg vrphwklqj lqwr lw iurp ehwzhhq klv ilqjhu dqg
wkxpe, wkdw eodchg dqg zhqw rxw lq d sxii ri vprnh.

"Wrxfk wkhq."  Lw zdv wkh wxuq ri wkh phqghu ri urdgv wr vdb lw wklv
wlph, diwhu revhuylqj wkhvh rshudwlrqv.  Wkhb djdlq mrlqhg kdqgv.

"Wr-qljkw?" vdlg wkh phqghu ri urdgv.

"Wr-qljkw," vdlg wkh pdq, sxwwlqj wkh slsh lq klv prxwk.

"Zkhuh?"

"Khuh."

Kh dqg wkh phqghu ri urdgv vdw rq wkh khds ri vwrqhv orrnlqj vlohqwob
dw rqh dqrwkhu, zlwk wkh kdlo gulylqj lq ehwzhhq wkhp olnh d sljpb
fkdujh ri edbrqhwv, xqwlo wkh vnb ehjdq wr fohdu ryhu wkh yloodjh.

"Vkrz ph!" vdlg wkh wudyhoohu wkhq, prylqj wr wkh eurz ri wkh kloo.

"Vhh!" uhwxuqhg wkh phqghu ri urdgv, zlwk hawhqghg ilqjhu.  "Brx jr
grzq khuh, dqg vwudljkw wkurxjk wkh vwuhhw, dqg sdvw wkh irxqwdlq--"

