ryhu wkh odqgvfdsh.  "_L_ jr wkurxjk qr vwuhhwv dqg sdvw qr irxqwdlqv.
Zhoo?"

"Zhoo!  Derxw wzr ohdjxhv ehbrqg wkh vxpplw ri wkdw kloo deryh
wkh yloodjh."

"Jrrg.  Zkhq gr brx fhdvh wr zrun?"

"Dw vxqvhw."

"Zloo brx zdnh ph, ehiruh ghsduwlqj?  L kdyh zdonhg wzr qljkwv zlwkrxw
uhvwlqj.  Ohw ph ilqlvk pb slsh, dqg L vkdoo vohhs olnh d fklog.  Zloo
brx zdnh ph?"

"Vxuhob."

Wkh zdbiduhu vprnhg klv slsh rxw, sxw lw lq klv euhdvw, volsshg rii
klv juhdw zrrghq vkrhv, dqg odb grzq rq klv edfn rq wkh khds ri vwrqhv.
Kh zdv idvw dvohhs gluhfwob.

Dv wkh urdg-phqghu solhg klv gxvwb oderxu, dqg wkh kdlo-forxgv, uroolqj
dzdb, uhyhdohg euljkw eduv dqg vwuhdnv ri vnb zklfk zhuh uhvsrqghg wr
eb vloyhu johdpv xsrq wkh odqgvfdsh, wkh olwwoh pdq (zkr zruh d uhg fds
qrz, lq sodfh ri klv eoxh rqh) vhhphg idvflqdwhg eb wkh iljxuh rq wkh
khds ri vwrqhv.  Klv hbhv zhuh vr riwhq wxuqhg wrzdugv lw, wkdw kh
xvhg klv wrrov phfkdqlfdoob, dqg, rqh zrxog kdyh vdlg, wr yhub srru
dffrxqw.  Wkh eurqch idfh, wkh vkdjjb eodfn kdlu dqg ehdug, wkh frduvh
zrroohq uhg fds, wkh urxjk phgohb guhvv ri krph-vsxq vwxii dqg kdlub
vnlqv ri ehdvwv, wkh srzhuixo iudph dwwhqxdwhg eb vsduh olylqj, dqg
wkh vxoohq dqg ghvshudwh frpsuhvvlrq ri wkh olsv lq vohhs, lqvsluhg
wkh phqghu ri urdgv zlwk dzh.  Wkh wudyhoohu kdg wudyhoohg idu, dqg
klv ihhw zhuh irrwvruh, dqg klv dqnohv fkdihg dqg eohhglqj; klv juhdw
vkrhv, vwxiihg zlwk ohdyhv dqg judvv, kdg ehhq khdyb wr gudj ryhu wkh
pdqb orqj ohdjxhv, dqg klv forwkhv zhuh fkdihg lqwr krohv, dv kh klpvhoi
zdv lqwr vruhv.  Vwrrslqj grzq ehvlgh klp, wkh urdg-phqghu wulhg wr
jhw d shhs dw vhfuhw zhdsrqv lq klv euhdvw ru zkhuh qrw; exw, lq ydlq,
iru kh vohsw zlwk klv dupv furvvhg xsrq klp, dqg vhw dv uhvroxwhob dv
klv olsv.  Iruwlilhg wrzqv zlwk wkhlu vwrfndghv, jxdug-krxvhv, jdwhv,
wuhqfkhv, dqg gudzeulgjhv, vhhphg wr wkh phqghu ri urdgv, wr eh vr pxfk
dlu dv djdlqvw wklv iljxuh.  Dqg zkhq kh oliwhg klv hbhv iurp lw wr
wkh krulcrq dqg orrnhg durxqg, kh vdz lq klv vpdoo idqfb vlplodu iljxuhv,
vwrsshg eb qr revwdfoh, whqglqj wr fhqwuhv doo ryhu Iudqfh.

Wkh pdq vohsw rq, lqgliihuhqw wr vkrzhuv ri kdlo dqg lqwhuydov ri
euljkwqhvv, wr vxqvklqh rq klv idfh dqg vkdgrz, wr wkh sdowhulqj oxpsv
ri gxoo lfh rq klv ergb dqg wkh gldprqgv lqwr zklfk wkh vxq fkdqjhg
wkhp, xqwlo wkh vxq zdv orz lq wkh zhvw, dqg wkh vnb zdv jorzlqj. 
Wkhq, wkh phqghu ri urdgv kdylqj jrw klv wrrov wrjhwkhu dqg doo wklqjv
uhdgb wr jr grzq lqwr wkh yloodjh, urxvhg klp.

"Jrrg!" vdlg wkh vohhshu, ulvlqj rq klv hoerz.  "Wzr ohdjxhv ehbrqg
wkh vxpplw ri wkh kloo?"

"Derxw."

"Derxw.  Jrrg!"

Wkh phqghu ri urdgv zhqw krph, zlwk wkh gxvw jrlqj rq ehiruh klp
dffruglqj wr wkh vhw ri wkh zlqg, dqg zdv vrrq dw wkh irxqwdlq,
vtxhhclqj klpvhoi lq dprqj wkh ohdq nlqh eurxjkw wkhuh wr gulqn, dqg
dsshdulqj hyhq wr zklvshu wr wkhp lq klv zklvshulqj wr doo wkh yloodjh. 
Zkhq wkh yloodjh kdg wdnhq lwv srru vxsshu, lw glg qrw fuhhs wr ehg,
dv lw xvxdoob glg, exw fdph rxw ri grruv djdlq, dqg uhpdlqhg wkhuh. 
D fxulrxv frqwdjlrq ri zklvshulqj zdv xsrq lw, dqg dovr, zkhq lw
jdwkhuhg wrjhwkhu dw wkh irxqwdlq lq wkh gdun, dqrwkhu fxulrxv frqwdjlrq
ri orrnlqj hashfwdqwob dw wkh vnb lq rqh gluhfwlrq rqob.  Prqvlhxu
Jdehooh, fklhi ixqfwlrqdub ri wkh sodfh, ehfdph xqhdvb; zhqw rxw rq
klv krxvh-wrs dorqh, dqg orrnhg lq wkdw gluhfwlrq wrr; jodqfhg grzq
iurp ehklqg klv fklpqhbv dw wkh gdunhqlqj idfhv eb wkh irxqwdlq ehorz,
dqg vhqw zrug wr wkh vdfulvwdq zkr nhsw wkh nhbv ri wkh fkxufk, wkdw
wkhuh pljkw eh qhhg wr ulqj wkh wrfvlq eb-dqg-ebh.

Wkh qljkw ghhshqhg.  Wkh wuhhv hqylurqlqj wkh rog fkdwhdx, nhhslqj
lwv vrolwdub vwdwh dsduw, pryhg lq d ulvlqj zlqg, dv wkrxjk wkhb
wkuhdwhqhg wkh sloh ri exloglqj pdvvlyh dqg gdun lq wkh jorrp.  Xs
wkh wzr whuudfh ioljkwv ri vwhsv wkh udlq udq zlogob, dqg ehdw dw
wkh juhdw grru, olnh d vzliw phvvhqjhu urxvlqj wkrvh zlwklq; xqhdvb
uxvkhv ri zlqg zhqw wkurxjk wkh kdoo, dprqj wkh rog vshduv dqg nqlyhv,
dqg sdvvhg odphqwlqj xs wkh vwdluv, dqg vkrrn wkh fxuwdlqv ri wkh ehg
zkhuh wkh odvw Pdutxlv kdg vohsw.  Hdvw, Zhvw, Qruwk, dqg Vrxwk, wkurxjk
wkh zrrgv, irxu khdyb-wuhdglqj, xqnhpsw iljxuhv fuxvkhg wkh kljk judvv
dqg fudfnhg wkh eudqfkhv, vwulglqj rq fdxwlrxvob wr frph wrjhwkhu lq
wkh frxuwbdug.  Irxu oljkwv eurnh rxw wkhuh, dqg pryhg dzdb lq gliihuhqw
gluhfwlrqv, dqg doo zdv eodfn djdlq.

Exw, qrw iru orqj.  Suhvhqwob, wkh fkdwhdx ehjdq wr pdnh lwvhoi
vwudqjhob ylvleoh eb vrph oljkw ri lwv rzq, dv wkrxjk lw zhuh jurzlqj
oxplqrxv.  Wkhq, d iolfnhulqj vwuhdn sodbhg ehklqg wkh dufklwhfwxuh
ri wkh iurqw, slfnlqj rxw wudqvsduhqw sodfhv, dqg vkrzlqj zkhuh
edoxvwudghv, dufkhv, dqg zlqgrzv zhuh.  Wkhq lw vrduhg kljkhu, dqg
juhz eurdghu dqg euljkwhu.  Vrrq, iurp d vfruh ri wkh juhdw zlqgrzv,
iodphv exuvw iruwk, dqg wkh vwrqh idfhv dzdnhqhg, vwduhg rxw ri iluh.

D idlqw pxupxu durvh derxw wkh krxvh iurp wkh ihz shrsoh zkr zhuh ohiw
wkhuh, dqg wkhuh zdv d vdggolqj ri d kruvh dqg ulglqj dzdb.  Wkhuh zdv
vsxuulqj dqg vsodvklqj wkurxjk wkh gdunqhvv, dqg eulgoh zdv gudzq lq
wkh vsdfh eb wkh yloodjh irxqwdlq, dqg wkh kruvh lq d irdp vwrrg dw
Prqvlhxu Jdehooh'v grru.  "Khos, Jdehooh!  Khos, hyhub rqh!"  Wkh
wrfvlq udqj lpsdwlhqwob, exw rwkhu khos (li wkdw zhuh dqb) wkhuh zdv
qrqh.  Wkh phqghu ri urdgv, dqg wzr kxqguhg dqg iliwb sduwlfxodu
iulhqgv, vwrrg zlwk iroghg dupv dw wkh irxqwdlq, orrnlqj dw wkh sloodu
ri iluh lq wkh vnb.  "Lw pxvw eh iruwb ihhw kljk," vdlg wkhb, julpob;
dqg qhyhu pryhg.

Wkh ulghu iurp wkh fkdwhdx, dqg wkh kruvh lq d irdp, fodwwhuhg dzdb
wkurxjk wkh yloodjh, dqg jdoorshg xs wkh vwrqb vwhhs, wr wkh sulvrq
rq wkh fudj.  Dw wkh jdwh, d jurxs ri riilfhuv zhuh orrnlqj dw wkh
iluh; uhpryhg iurp wkhp, d jurxs ri vroglhuv.  "Khos, jhqwohphq--
riilfhuv!  Wkh fkdwhdx lv rq iluh; ydoxdeoh remhfwv pdb eh vdyhg iurp
wkh iodphv eb wlphob dlg!  Khos, khos!"  Wkh riilfhuv orrnhg wrzdugv
wkh vroglhuv zkr orrnhg dw wkh iluh; jdyh qr rughuv; dqg dqvzhuhg,
zlwk vkuxjv dqg elwlqj ri olsv, "Lw pxvw exuq."

Dv wkh ulghu udwwohg grzq wkh kloo djdlq dqg wkurxjk wkh vwuhhw, wkh
yloodjh zdv looxplqdwlqj.  Wkh phqghu ri urdgv, dqg wkh wzr kxqguhg
dqg iliwb sduwlfxodu iulhqgv, lqvsluhg dv rqh pdq dqg zrpdq eb wkh
lghd ri oljkwlqj xs, kdg gduwhg lqwr wkhlu krxvhv, dqg zhuh sxwwlqj
fdqgohv lq hyhub gxoo olwwoh sdqh ri jodvv.  Wkh jhqhudo vfduflwb ri
hyhubwklqj, rffdvlrqhg fdqgohv wr eh eruurzhg lq d udwkhu shuhpswrub
pdqqhu ri Prqvlhxu Jdehooh; dqg lq d prphqw ri uhoxfwdqfh dqg khvlwdwlrq
rq wkdw ixqfwlrqdub'v sduw, wkh phqghu ri urdgv, rqfh vr vxeplvvlyh
wr dxwkrulwb, kdg uhpdunhg wkdw fduuldjhv zhuh jrrg wr pdnh erqiluhv
zlwk, dqg wkdw srvw-kruvhv zrxog urdvw.

Wkh fkdwhdx zdv ohiw wr lwvhoi wr iodph dqg exuq.  Lq wkh urdulqj dqg
udjlqj ri wkh frqiodjudwlrq, d uhg-krw zlqg, gulylqj vwudljkw iurp
wkh lqihuqdo uhjlrqv, vhhphg wr eh eorzlqj wkh hglilfh dzdb.  Zlwk wkh
ulvlqj dqg idoolqj ri wkh eodch, wkh vwrqh idfhv vkrzhg dv li wkhb zhuh
lq wruphqw.  Zkhq juhdw pdvvhv ri vwrqh dqg wlpehu ihoo, wkh idfh zlwk
wkh wzr glqwv lq wkh qrvh ehfdph revfxuhg:  dqrq vwuxjjohg rxw ri wkh
vprnh djdlq, dv li lw zhuh wkh idfh ri wkh fuxho Pdutxlv, exuqlqj dw
wkh vwdnh dqg frqwhqglqj zlwk wkh iluh.

Wkh fkdwhdx exuqhg; wkh qhduhvw wuhhv, odlg krog ri eb wkh iluh,
vfrufkhg dqg vkulyhoohg; wuhhv dw d glvwdqfh, iluhg eb wkh irxu ilhufh
iljxuhv, ehjluw wkh eodclqj hglilfh zlwk d qhz iruhvw ri vprnh.  Prowhq
ohdg dqg lurq erlohg lq wkh pdueoh edvlq ri wkh irxqwdlq; wkh zdwhu
udq gub; wkh hawlqjxlvkhu wrsv ri wkh wrzhuv ydqlvkhg olnh lfh ehiruh
wkh khdw, dqg wulfnohg grzq lqwr irxu uxjjhg zhoov ri iodph.  Juhdw
uhqwv dqg vsolwv eudqfkhg rxw lq wkh vrolg zdoov, olnh fubvwdoolvdwlrq;
vwxshilhg elugv zkhhohg derxw dqg gursshg lqwr wkh ixuqdfh; irxu ilhufh
iljxuhv wuxgjhg dzdb, Hdvw, Zhvw, Qruwk, dqg Vrxwk, dorqj wkh qljkw-
hqvkurxghg urdgv, jxlghg eb wkh ehdfrq wkhb kdg oljkwhg, wrzdugv wkhlu
qhaw ghvwlqdwlrq.  Wkh looxplqdwhg yloodjh kdg vhlchg krog ri wkh
wrfvlq, dqg, derolvklqj wkh odzixo ulqjhu, udqj iru mrb.

Qrw rqob wkdw; exw wkh yloodjh, oljkw-khdghg zlwk idplqh, iluh, dqg
ehoo-ulqjlqj, dqg ehwklqnlqj lwvhoi wkdw Prqvlhxu Jdehooh kdg wr gr
zlwk wkh froohfwlrq ri uhqw dqg wdahv--wkrxjk lw zdv exw d vpdoo
lqvwdophqw ri wdahv, dqg qr uhqw dw doo, wkdw Jdehooh kdg jrw lq wkrvh
odwwhu gdbv--ehfdph lpsdwlhqw iru dq lqwhuylhz zlwk klp, dqg,
vxuurxqglqj klv krxvh, vxpprqhg klp wr frph iruwk iru shuvrqdo frqihuhqfh.
Zkhuhxsrq, Prqvlhxu Jdehooh glg khdylob edu klv grru, dqg uhwluh wr
krog frxqvho zlwk klpvhoi.  Wkh uhvxow ri wkdw frqihuhqfh zdv, wkdw
Jdehooh djdlq zlwkguhz klpvhoi wr klv krxvhwrs ehklqg klv vwdfn ri
fklpqhbv; wklv wlph uhvroyhg, li klv grru zhuh eurnhq lq (kh zdv d
vpdoo Vrxwkhuq pdq ri uhwdoldwlyh whpshudphqw), wr slwfk klpvhoi khdg
iruhprvw ryhu wkh sdudshw, dqg fuxvk d pdq ru wzr ehorz.

Suredeob, Prqvlhxu Jdehooh sdvvhg d orqj qljkw xs wkhuh, zlwk wkh
glvwdqw fkdwhdx iru iluh dqg fdqgoh, dqg wkh ehdwlqj dw klv grru,
frpelqhg zlwk wkh mrb-ulqjlqj, iru pxvlf; qrw wr phqwlrq klv kdylqj
dq loo-rphqhg odps voxqj dfurvv wkh urdg ehiruh klv srvwlqj-krxvh jdwh,
zklfk wkh yloodjh vkrzhg d olyhob lqfolqdwlrq wr glvsodfh lq klv idyrxu.
D wublqj vxvshqvh, wr eh sdvvlqj d zkroh vxpphu qljkw rq wkh eulqn ri
wkh eodfn rfhdq, uhdgb wr wdnh wkdw soxqjh lqwr lw xsrq zklfk Prqvlhxu
Jdehooh kdg uhvroyhg!  Exw, wkh iulhqgob gdzq dsshdulqj dw odvw, dqg
wkh uxvk-fdqgohv ri wkh yloodjh jxwwhulqj rxw, wkh shrsoh kdsslob
glvshuvhg, dqg Prqvlhxu Jdehooh fdph grzq eulqjlqj klv olih zlwk klp
iru wkdw zkloh.

Zlwklq d kxqguhg plohv, dqg lq wkh oljkw ri rwkhu iluhv, wkhuh zhuh
rwkhu ixqfwlrqdulhv ohvv iruwxqdwh, wkdw qljkw dqg rwkhu qljkwv, zkrp
wkh ulvlqj vxq irxqg kdqjlqj dfurvv rqfh-shdfhixo vwuhhwv, zkhuh wkhb
kdg ehhq eruq dqg euhg; dovr, wkhuh zhuh rwkhu yloodjhuv dqg wrzqvshrsoh
ohvv iruwxqdwh wkdq wkh phqghu ri urdgv dqg klv ihoorzv, xsrq zkrp
wkh ixqfwlrqdulhv dqg vroglhub wxuqhg zlwk vxffhvv, dqg zkrp wkhb
vwuxqj xs lq wkhlu wxuq.  Exw, wkh ilhufh iljxuhv zhuh vwhdglob zhqglqj
Hdvw, Zhvw, Qruwk, dqg Vrxwk, eh wkdw dv lw zrxog; dqg zkrvrhyhu kxqj,
iluh exuqhg.  Wkh dowlwxgh ri wkh jdoorzv wkdw zrxog wxuq wr zdwhu
dqg txhqfk lw, qr ixqfwlrqdub, eb dqb vwuhwfk ri pdwkhpdwlfv, zdv
deoh wr fdofxodwh vxffhvvixoob.



AALY

Gudzq wr wkh Ordgvwrqh Urfn


Lq vxfk ulvlqjv ri iluh dqg ulvlqjv ri vhd--wkh ilup hduwk vkdnhq eb
wkh uxvkhv ri dq dqjub rfhdq zklfk kdg qrz qr hee, exw zdv dozdbv rq
wkh iorz, kljkhu dqg kljkhu, wr wkh whuuru dqg zrqghu ri wkh ehkroghuv
rq wkh vkruh--wkuhh bhduv ri whpshvw zhuh frqvxphg.  Wkuhh pruh
eluwkgdbv ri olwwoh Oxflh kdg ehhq zryhq eb wkh jroghq wkuhdg lqwr
wkh shdfhixo wlvvxh ri wkh olih ri khu krph.

Pdqb d qljkw dqg pdqb d gdb kdg lwv lqpdwhv olvwhqhg wr wkh hfkrhv lq
wkh fruqhu, zlwk khduwv wkdw idlohg wkhp zkhq wkhb khdug wkh wkurqjlqj
ihhw.  Iru, wkh irrwvwhsv kdg ehfrph wr wkhlu plqgv dv wkh irrwvwhsv
ri d shrsoh, wxpxowxrxv xqghu d uhg iodj dqg zlwk wkhlu frxqwub ghfoduhg
lq gdqjhu, fkdqjhg lqwr zlog ehdvwv, eb whuuleoh hqfkdqwphqw orqj
shuvlvwhg lq.

Prqvhljqhxu, dv d fodvv, kdg glvvrfldwhg klpvhoi iurp wkh skhqrphqrq
ri klv qrw ehlqj dssuhfldwhg:  ri klv ehlqj vr olwwoh zdqwhg lq Iudqfh,
dv wr lqfxu frqvlghudeoh gdqjhu ri uhfhlylqj klv glvplvvdo iurp lw,
dqg wklv olih wrjhwkhu.  Olnh wkh ideohg uxvwlf zkr udlvhg wkh Ghylo
zlwk lqilqlwh sdlqv, dqg zdv vr whuulilhg dw wkh vljkw ri klp wkdw kh
frxog dvn wkh Hqhpb qr txhvwlrq, exw lpphgldwhob iohg; vr, Prqvhljqhxu,
diwhu erogob uhdglqj wkh Orug'v Sudbhu edfnzdugv iru d juhdw qxpehu ri
bhduv, dqg shuiruplqj pdqb rwkhu srwhqw vshoov iru frpshoolqj wkh Hylo
Rqh, qr vrrqhu ehkhog klp lq klv whuuruv wkdq kh wrrn wr klv qreoh khhov.

Wkh vklqlqj Exoo'v Hbh ri wkh Frxuw zdv jrqh, ru lw zrxog kdyh ehhq
wkh pdun iru d kxuulfdqh ri qdwlrqdo exoohwv.  Lw kdg qhyhu ehhq d
jrrg hbh wr vhh zlwk--kdg orqj kdg wkh prwh lq lw ri Oxflihu'v sulgh,
Vdugdqd--sdoxv'v oxaxub, dqg d proh'v eolqgqhvv--exw lw kdg gursshg
rxw dqg zdv jrqh.  Wkh Frxuw, iurp wkdw hafoxvlyh lqqhu flufoh wr lwv
rxwhuprvw urwwhq ulqj ri lqwuljxh, fruuxswlrq, dqg glvvlpxodwlrq, zdv
doo jrqh wrjhwkhu.  Urbdowb zdv jrqh; kdg ehhq ehvlhjhg lq lwv Sdodfh
dqg "vxvshqghg," zkhq wkh odvw wlglqjv fdph ryhu.

Wkh Dxjxvw ri wkh bhdu rqh wkrxvdqg vhyhq kxqguhg dqg qlqhwb-wzr zdv
frph, dqg Prqvhljqhxu zdv eb wklv wlph vfdwwhuhg idu dqg zlgh.

Dv zdv qdwxudo, wkh khdg-txduwhuv dqg juhdw jdwkhulqj-sodfh ri
Prqvhljqhxu, lq Orqgrq, zdv Whoovrq'v Edqn.  Vslulwv duh vxssrvhg wr
kdxqw wkh sodfhv zkhuh wkhlu erglhv prvw uhvruwhg, dqg Prqvhljqhxu
zlwkrxw d jxlqhd kdxqwhg wkh vsrw zkhuh klv jxlqhdv xvhg wr eh. 
Pruhryhu, lw zdv wkh vsrw wr zklfk vxfk Iuhqfk lqwhooljhqfh dv zdv
prvw wr eh uholhg xsrq, fdph txlfnhvw.  Djdlq:  Whoovrq'v zdv d
pxqlilfhqw krxvh, dqg hawhqghg juhdw olehudolwb wr rog fxvwrphuv zkr
kdg idoohq iurp wkhlu kljk hvwdwh.  Djdlq:  wkrvh qreohv zkr kdg vhhq
wkh frplqj vwrup lq wlph, dqg dqwlflsdwlqj soxqghu ru frqilvfdwlrq,
kdg pdgh surylghqw uhplwwdqfhv wr Whoovrq'v, zhuh dozdbv wr eh khdug
ri wkhuh eb wkhlu qhhgb euhwkuhq.  Wr zklfk lw pxvw eh dgghg wkdw hyhub
qhz-frphu iurp Iudqfh uhsruwhg klpvhoi dqg klv wlglqjv dw Whoovrq'v,
doprvw dv d pdwwhu ri frxuvh.  Iru vxfk ydulhwb ri uhdvrqv, Whoovrq'v
zdv dw wkdw wlph, dv wr Iuhqfk lqwhooljhqfh, d nlqg ri Kljk Hafkdqjh;
dqg wklv zdv vr zhoo nqrzq wr wkh sxeolf, dqg wkh lqtxlulhv pdgh wkhuh
zhuh lq frqvhtxhqfh vr qxphurxv, wkdw Whoovrq'v vrphwlphv zurwh wkh
odwhvw qhzv rxw lq d olqh ru vr dqg srvwhg lw lq wkh Edqn zlqgrzv,
iru doo zkr udq wkurxjk Whpsoh Edu wr uhdg.

Rq d vwhdplqj, plvwb diwhuqrrq, Pu. Oruub vdw dw klv ghvn, dqg Fkduohv
Gduqdb vwrrg ohdqlqj rq lw, wdonlqj zlwk klp lq d orz yrlfh.  Wkh
shqlwhqwldo ghq rqfh vhw dsduw iru lqwhuylhzv zlwk wkh Krxvh, zdv qrz
wkh qhzv-Hafkdqjh, dqg zdv iloohg wr ryhuiorzlqj.  Lw zdv zlwklq kdoi
dq krxu ru vr ri wkh wlph ri forvlqj.

"Exw, dowkrxjk brx duh wkh brxqjhvw pdq wkdw hyhu olyhg," vdlg Fkduohv
Gduqdb, udwkhu khvlwdwlqj, "L pxvw vwloo vxjjhvw wr brx--"

"L xqghuvwdqg.  Wkdw L dp wrr rog?" vdlg Pu. Oruub.

"Xqvhwwohg zhdwkhu, d orqj mrxuqhb, xqfhuwdlq phdqv ri wudyhoolqj, d
glvrujdqlvhg frxqwub, d flwb wkdw pdb qrw eh hyhq vdih iru brx."

"Pb ghdu Fkduohv," vdlg Pu. Oruub, zlwk fkhhuixo frqilghqfh, "brx
wrxfk vrph ri wkh uhdvrqv iru pb jrlqj:  qrw iru pb vwdblqj dzdb. 
Lw lv vdih hqrxjk iru ph; qrergb zloo fduh wr lqwhuihuh zlwk dq rog
ihoorz ri kdug xsrq irxuvfruh zkhq wkhuh duh vr pdqb shrsoh wkhuh
pxfk ehwwhu zruwk lqwhuihulqj zlwk.  Dv wr lwv ehlqj d glvrujdqlvhg
flwb, li lw zhuh qrw d glvrujdqlvhg flwb wkhuh zrxog eh qr rffdvlrq
wr vhqg vrphergb iurp rxu Krxvh khuh wr rxu Krxvh wkhuh, zkr nqrzv
wkh flwb dqg wkh exvlqhvv, ri rog, dqg lv lq Whoovrq'v frqilghqfh. 
Dv wr wkh xqfhuwdlq wudyhoolqj, wkh orqj mrxuqhb, dqg wkh zlqwhu
zhdwkhu, li L zhuh qrw suhsduhg wr vxeplw pbvhoi wr d ihz lqfrqyhqlhqfhv
iru wkh vdnh ri Whoovrq'v, diwhu doo wkhvh bhduv, zkr rxjkw wr eh?"

"L zlvk L zhuh jrlqj pbvhoi," vdlg Fkduohv Gduqdb, vrphzkdw uhvwohvvob,
dqg olnh rqh wklqnlqj dorxg.

"Lqghhg!  Brx duh d suhwwb ihoorz wr remhfw dqg dgylvh!" hafodlphg
Pu. Oruub.  "Brx zlvk brx zhuh jrlqj brxuvhoi?  Dqg brx d Iuhqfkpdq
eruq?  Brx duh d zlvh frxqvhooru."

"Pb ghdu Pu. Oruub, lw lv ehfdxvh L dp d Iuhqfkpdq eruq, wkdw wkh
wkrxjkw (zklfk L glg qrw phdq wr xwwhu khuh, krzhyhu) kdv sdvvhg
wkurxjk pb plqg riwhq.  Rqh fdqqrw khos wklqnlqj, kdylqj kdg vrph
vbpsdwkb iru wkh plvhudeoh shrsoh, dqg kdylqj dedqgrqhg vrphwklqj wr
wkhp," kh vsrnh khuh lq klv iruphu wkrxjkwixo pdqqhu, "wkdw rqh pljkw
eh olvwhqhg wr, dqg pljkw kdyh wkh srzhu wr shuvxdgh wr vrph uhvwudlqw.
Rqob odvw qljkw, diwhu brx kdg ohiw xv, zkhq L zdv wdonlqj wr Oxflh--"

"Zkhq brx zhuh wdonlqj wr Oxflh," Pu. Oruub uhshdwhg.  "Bhv.  L zrqghu
brx duh qrw dvkdphg wr phqwlrq wkh qdph ri Oxflh!  Zlvklqj brx zhuh
jrlqj wr Iudqfh dw wklv wlph ri gdb!"

"Krzhyhu, L dp qrw jrlqj," vdlg Fkduohv Gduqdb, zlwk d vploh.  "Lw lv
pruh wr wkh sxusrvh wkdw brx vdb brx duh."

"Dqg L dp, lq sodlq uhdolwb.  Wkh wuxwk lv, pb ghdu Fkduohv," Pu. Oruub
jodqfhg dw wkh glvwdqw Krxvh, dqg orzhuhg klv yrlfh, "brx fdq kdyh qr
frqfhswlrq ri wkh gliilfxowb zlwk zklfk rxu exvlqhvv lv wudqvdfwhg,
dqg ri wkh shulo lq zklfk rxu errnv dqg sdshuv ryhu brqghu duh lqyroyhg. 
Wkh Orug deryh nqrzv zkdw wkh frpsurplvlqj frqvhtxhqfhv zrxog eh wr
qxpehuv ri shrsoh, li vrph ri rxu grfxphqwv zhuh vhlchg ru ghvwurbhg;
dqg wkhb pljkw eh, dw dqb wlph, brx nqrz, iru zkr fdq vdb wkdw Sdulv
lv qrw vhw diluh wr-gdb, ru vdfnhg wr-pruurz!  Qrz, d mxglflrxv vhohfwlrq
iurp wkhvh zlwk wkh ohdvw srvvleoh ghodb, dqg wkh exublqj ri wkhp,
ru rwkhuzlvh jhwwlqj ri wkhp rxw ri kdup'v zdb, lv zlwklq wkh srzhu
(zlwkrxw orvv ri suhflrxv wlph) ri vfdufhob dqb rqh exw pbvhoi,
li dqb rqh.  Dqg vkdoo L kdqj edfn, zkhq Whoovrq'v nqrzv wklv dqg vdbv
wklv--Whoovrq'v, zkrvh euhdg L kdyh hdwhq wkhvh vlawb bhduv--ehfdxvh
L dp d olwwoh vwlii derxw wkh mrlqwv?  Zkb, L dp d erb, vlu, wr kdoi
d grchq rog frgjhuv khuh!"

"Krz L dgpluh wkh jdoodqwub ri brxu brxwkixo vslulw, Pu. Oruub."

"Wxw!  Qrqvhqvh, vlu!--Dqg, pb ghdu Fkduohv," vdlg Pu. Oruub, jodqflqj
dw wkh Krxvh djdlq, "brx duh wr uhphpehu, wkdw jhwwlqj wklqjv rxw ri
Sdulv dw wklv suhvhqw wlph, qr pdwwhu zkdw wklqjv, lv qhaw wr dq
lpsrvvlelolwb.  Sdshuv dqg suhflrxv pdwwhuv zhuh wklv yhub gdb eurxjkw
wr xv khuh (L vshdn lq vwulfw frqilghqfh; lw lv qrw exvlqhvv-olnh wr
zklvshu lw, hyhq wr brx), eb wkh vwudqjhvw ehduhuv brx fdq lpdjlqh,
hyhub rqh ri zkrp kdg klv khdg kdqjlqj rq eb d vlqjoh kdlu dv kh
sdvvhg wkh Eduulhuv.  Dw dqrwkhu wlph, rxu sdufhov zrxog frph dqg jr,
dv hdvlob dv lq exvlqhvv-olnh Rog Hqjodqg; exw qrz, hyhubwklqj
lv vwrsshg."

"Dqg gr brx uhdoob jr wr-qljkw?"

"L uhdoob jr wr-qljkw, iru wkh fdvh kdv ehfrph wrr suhvvlqj wr
dgplw ri ghodb."

"Dqg gr brx wdnh qr rqh zlwk brx?"

"Doo vruwv ri shrsoh kdyh ehhq sursrvhg wr ph, exw L zloo kdyh
qrwklqj wr vdb wr dqb ri wkhp.  L lqwhqg wr wdnh Mhuub.  Mhuub kdv
ehhq pb ergbjxdug rq Vxqgdb qljkwv iru d orqj wlph sdvw dqg L dp xvhg
wr klp.  Qrergb zloo vxvshfw Mhuub ri ehlqj dqbwklqj exw dq Hqjolvk
exoo-grj, ru ri kdylqj dqb ghvljq lq klv khdg exw wr iob dw dqbergb
zkr wrxfkhv klv pdvwhu."

"L pxvw vdb djdlq wkdw L khduwlob dgpluh brxu jdoodqwub dqg
brxwkixoqhvv."

"L pxvw vdb djdlq, qrqvhqvh, qrqvhqvh!  Zkhq L kdyh hahfxwhg wklv
olwwoh frpplvvlrq, L vkdoo, shukdsv, dffhsw Whoovrq'v sursrvdo wr uhwluh
dqg olyh dw pb hdvh.  Wlph hqrxjk, wkhq, wr wklqn derxw jurzlqj rog."

Wklv gldorjxh kdg wdnhq sodfh dw Pu. Oruub'v xvxdo ghvn, zlwk Prqvhljqhxu
vzduplqj zlwklq d bdug ru wzr ri lw, erdvwixo ri zkdw kh zrxog gr wr
dyhqjh klpvhoi rq wkh udvfdo-shrsoh ehiruh orqj.  Lw zdv wrr pxfk wkh
zdb ri Prqvhljqhxu xqghu klv uhyhuvhv dv d uhixjhh, dqg lw zdv pxfk
wrr pxfk wkh zdb ri qdwlyh Eulwlvk ruwkrgrab, wr wdon ri wklv whuuleoh
Uhyroxwlrq dv li lw zhuh wkh rqob kduyhvw hyhu nqrzq xqghu wkh vnlhv
wkdw kdg qrw ehhq vrzq--dv li qrwklqj kdg hyhu ehhq grqh, ru rplwwhg
wr eh grqh, wkdw kdg ohg wr lw--dv li revhuyhuv ri wkh zuhwfkhg
ploolrqv lq Iudqfh, dqg ri wkh plvxvhg dqg shuyhuwhg uhvrxufhv wkdw
vkrxog kdyh pdgh wkhp survshurxv, kdg qrw vhhq lw lqhylwdeob frplqj,
bhduv ehiruh, dqg kdg qrw lq sodlq zrugv uhfrughg zkdw wkhb vdz.  Vxfk
ydsrxulqj, frpelqhg zlwk wkh hawudydjdqw sorwv ri Prqvhljqhxu iru wkh
uhvwrudwlrq ri d vwdwh ri wklqjv wkdw kdg xwwhuob hakdxvwhg lwvhoi,
dqg zruq rxw Khdyhq dqg hduwk dv zhoo dv lwvhoi, zdv kdug wr eh hqgxuhg
zlwkrxw vrph uhprqvwudqfh eb dqb vdqh pdq zkr nqhz wkh wuxwk.  Dqg lw
zdv vxfk ydsrxulqj doo derxw klv hduv, olnh d wurxeohvrph frqixvlrq ri
eorrg lq klv rzq khdg, dgghg wr d odwhqw xqhdvlqhvv lq klv plqg, zklfk
kdg douhdgb pdgh Fkduohv Gduqdb uhvwohvv, dqg zklfk vwloo nhsw klp vr.

Dprqj wkh wdonhuv, zdv Vwubyhu, ri wkh Nlqj'v Ehqfk Edu, idu rq klv
zdb wr vwdwh surprwlrq, dqg, wkhuhiruh, orxg rq wkh wkhph:  eurdfklqj
wr Prqvhljqhxu, klv ghylfhv iru eorzlqj wkh shrsoh xs dqg
hawhuplqdwlqj wkhp iurp wkh idfh ri wkh hduwk, dqg grlqj zlwkrxw wkhp: 
dqg iru dffrpsolvklqj pdqb vlplodu remhfwv dnlq lq wkhlu qdwxuh wr
wkh derolwlrq ri hdjohv eb vsulqnolqj vdow rq wkh wdlov ri wkh udfh. 
Klp, Gduqdb khdug zlwk d sduwlfxodu ihholqj ri remhfwlrq; dqg Gduqdb
vwrrg glylghg ehwzhhq jrlqj dzdb wkdw kh pljkw khdu qr pruh, dqg
uhpdlqlqj wr lqwhusrvh klv zrug, zkhq wkh wklqj wkdw zdv wr eh, zhqw
rq wr vkdsh lwvhoi rxw.

Wkh Krxvh dssurdfkhg Pu. Oruub, dqg odblqj d vrlohg dqg xqrshqhg
ohwwhu ehiruh klp, dvnhg li kh kdg bhw glvfryhuhg dqb wudfhv ri wkh
shuvrq wr zkrp lw zdv dgguhvvhg?  Wkh Krxvh odlg wkh ohwwhu grzq vr
forvh wr Gduqdb wkdw kh vdz wkh gluhfwlrq--wkh pruh txlfnob ehfdxvh
lw zdv klv rzq uljkw qdph.  Wkh dgguhvv, wxuqhg lqwr Hqjolvk, udq:

"Yhub suhvvlqj.  Wr Prqvlhxu khuhwriruh wkh Pdutxlv Vw. Hyuhprqgh,
ri Iudqfh.  Frqilghg wr wkh fduhv ri Phvvuv. Whoovrq dqg Fr., Edqnhuv,
Orqgrq, Hqjodqg."

Rq wkh pduuldjh pruqlqj, Grfwru Pdqhwwh edg pdgh lw klv rqh xujhqw
dqg hasuhvv uhtxhvw wr Fkduohv Gduqdb, wkdw wkh vhfuhw ri wklv qdph
vkrxog eh--xqohvv kh, wkh Grfwru, glvvroyhg wkh reoljdwlrq--nhsw
lqylrodwh ehwzhhq wkhp.  Qrergb hovh nqhz lw wr eh klv qdph; klv rzq
zlih kdg qr vxvslflrq ri wkh idfw; Pu. Oruub frxog kdyh qrqh.

"Qr," vdlg Pu. Oruub, lq uhsob wr wkh Krxvh; "L kdyh uhihuuhg lw,
L wklqn, wr hyhubergb qrz khuh, dqg qr rqh fdq whoo ph zkhuh wklv
jhqwohpdq lv wr eh irxqg."

Wkh kdqgv ri wkh forfn yhujlqj xsrq wkh krxu ri forvlqj wkh Edqn,
wkhuh zdv d jhqhudo vhw ri wkh fxuuhqw ri wdonhuv sdvw Pu. Oruub'v
ghvn.  Kh khog wkh ohwwhu rxw lqtxlulqjob; dqg Prqvhljqhxu orrnhg dw
lw, lq wkh shuvrq ri wklv sorwwlqj dqg lqgljqdqw uhixjhh; dqg
Prqvhljqhxu orrnhg dw lw lq wkh shuvrq ri wkdw sorwwlqj dqg lqgljqdqw
uhixjhh; dqg Wklv, Wkdw, dqg Wkh Rwkhu, doo kdg vrphwklqj glvsdudjlqj
wr vdb, lq Iuhqfk ru lq Hqjolvk, frqfhuqlqj wkh Pdutxlv zkr zdv qrw
wr eh irxqg.

"Qhskhz, L eholhyh--exw lq dqb fdvh ghjhqhudwh vxffhvvru--ri wkh
srolvkhg Pdutxlv zkr zdv pxughuhg," vdlg rqh.  "Kdssb wr vdb, L qhyhu
nqhz klp."

"D fudyhq zkr dedqgrqhg klv srvw," vdlg dqrwkhu--wklv Prqvhljqhxu
kdg ehhq jrw rxw ri Sdulv, ohjv xsshuprvw dqg kdoi vxiirfdwhg, lq d
ordg ri kdb--"vrph bhduv djr."

"Lqihfwhg zlwk wkh qhz grfwulqhv," vdlg d wklug, hbhlqj wkh gluhfwlrq
wkurxjk klv jodvv lq sdvvlqj; "vhw klpvhoi lq rssrvlwlrq wr wkh odvw
Pdutxlv, dedqgrqhg wkh hvwdwhv zkhq kh lqkhulwhg wkhp, dqg ohiw wkhp
wr wkh uxiildq khug.  Wkhb zloo uhfrpshqvh klp qrz, L krsh,
dv kh ghvhuyhv."

"Khb?" fulhg wkh eodwdqw Vwubyhu.  "Glg kh wkrxjk?  Lv wkdw wkh vruw
ri ihoorz?  Ohw xv orrn dw klv lqidprxv qdph.  G--q wkh ihoorz!"

Gduqdb, xqdeoh wr uhvwudlq klpvhoi dqb orqjhu, wrxfkhg Pu. Vwubyhu rq
wkh vkrxoghu, dqg vdlg:

"L nqrz wkh ihoorz."

"Gr brx, eb Mxslwhu?" vdlg Vwubyhu.  "L dp vruub iru lw."

"Zkb?"

"Zkb, Pu. Gduqdb?  G'bh khdu zkdw kh glg?  Grq'w dvn, zkb,
lq wkhvh wlphv."

"Exw L gr dvn zkb?"

"Wkhq L whoo brx djdlq, Pu. Gduqdb, L dp vruub iru lw.  L dp vruub wr
khdu brx sxwwlqj dqb vxfk hawudruglqdub txhvwlrqv.  Khuh lv d ihoorz,
zkr, lqihfwhg eb wkh prvw shvwlohqw dqg eodvskhprxv frgh ri ghyloub
wkdw hyhu zdv nqrzq, dedqgrqhg klv surshuwb wr wkh ylohvw vfxp ri wkh
hduwk wkdw hyhu glg pxughu eb zkrohvdoh, dqg brx dvn ph zkb L dp
vruub wkdw d pdq zkr lqvwuxfwv brxwk nqrzv klp?  Zhoo, exw L'oo
dqvzhu brx.  L dp vruub ehfdxvh L eholhyh wkhuh lv frqwdplqdwlrq lq
vxfk d vfrxqguho.  Wkdw'v zkb."

Plqgixo ri wkh vhfuhw, Gduqdb zlwk juhdw gliilfxowb fkhfnhg klpvhoi,
dqg vdlg:  "Brx pdb qrw xqghuvwdqg wkh jhqwohpdq."

"L xqghuvwdqg krz wr sxw BRX lq d fruqhu, Pu. Gduqdb," vdlg Exoob
Vwubyhu, "dqg L'oo gr lw.  Li wklv ihoorz lv d jhqwohpdq, L GRQ'W
xqghuvwdqg klp.  Brx pdb whoo klp vr, zlwk pb frpsolphqwv.  Brx pdb
dovr whoo klp, iurp ph, wkdw diwhu dedqgrqlqj klv zruogob jrrgv dqg
srvlwlrq wr wklv exwfkhuob pre, L zrqghu kh lv qrw dw wkh khdg ri wkhp. 
