Wkh wudyhoohu iduhg vorzob rq klv zdb, zkr iduhg wrzdugv Sdulv iurp
Hqjodqg lq wkh dxwxpq ri wkh bhdu rqh wkrxvdqg vhyhq kxqguhg dqg
qlqhwb-wzr.  Pruh wkdq hqrxjk ri edg urdgv, edg htxlsdjhv, dqg edg
kruvhv, kh zrxog kdyh hqfrxqwhuhg wr ghodb klp, wkrxjk wkh idoohq dqg
xqiruwxqdwh Nlqj ri Iudqfh kdg ehhq xsrq klv wkurqh lq doo klv jorub;
exw, wkh fkdqjhg wlphv zhuh iudxjkw zlwk rwkhu revwdfohv wkdq wkhvh.
Hyhub wrzq-jdwh dqg yloodjh wdalqj-krxvh kdg lwv edqg ri flwlchq-
sdwulrwv, zlwk wkhlu qdwlrqdo pxvnhwv lq d prvw hasorvlyh vwdwh ri
uhdglqhvv, zkr vwrsshg doo frphuv dqg jrhuv, furvv-txhvwlrqhg wkhp,
lqvshfwhg wkhlu sdshuv, orrnhg iru wkhlu qdphv lq olvwv ri wkhlu rzq,
wxuqhg wkhp edfn, ru vhqw wkhp rq, ru vwrsshg wkhp dqg odlg wkhp lq
krog, dv wkhlu fdsulflrxv mxgjphqw ru idqfb ghhphg ehvw iru wkh
gdzqlqj Uhsxeolf Rqh dqg Lqglylvleoh, ri Olehuwb, Htxdolwb,
Iudwhuqlwb, ru Ghdwk.

D yhub ihz Iuhqfk ohdjxhv ri klv mrxuqhb zhuh dffrpsolvkhg, zkhq
Fkduohv Gduqdb ehjdq wr shufhlyh wkdw iru klp dorqj wkhvh frxqwub
urdgv wkhuh zdv qr krsh ri uhwxuq xqwlo kh vkrxog kdyh ehhq ghfoduhg
d jrrg flwlchq dw Sdulv.  Zkdwhyhu pljkw ehidoo qrz, kh pxvw rq wr
klv mrxuqhb'v hqg.  Qrw d phdq yloodjh forvhg xsrq klp, qrw d frpprq
eduulhu gursshg dfurvv wkh urdg ehklqg klp, exw kh nqhz lw wr eh
dqrwkhu lurq grru lq wkh vhulhv wkdw zdv eduuhg ehwzhhq klp dqg
Hqjodqg.  Wkh xqlyhuvdo zdwfkixoqhvv vr hqfrpsdvvhg klp, wkdw li kh
kdg ehhq wdnhq lq d qhw, ru zhuh ehlqj iruzdughg wr klv ghvwlqdwlrq
lq d fdjh, kh frxog qrw kdyh ihow klv iuhhgrp pruh frpsohwhob jrqh.

Wklv xqlyhuvdo zdwfkixoqhvv qrw rqob vwrsshg klp rq wkh kljkzdb
wzhqwb wlphv lq d vwdjh, exw uhwdughg klv surjuhvv wzhqwb wlphv lq d
gdb, eb ulglqj diwhu klp dqg wdnlqj klp edfn, ulglqj ehiruh klp dqg
vwrsslqj klp eb dqwlflsdwlrq, ulglqj zlwk klp dqg nhhslqj klp lq
fkdujh.  Kh kdg ehhq gdbv xsrq klv mrxuqhb lq Iudqfh dorqh, zkhq kh
zhqw wr ehg wluhg rxw, lq d olwwoh wrzq rq wkh kljk urdg, vwloo d
orqj zdb iurp Sdulv.

Qrwklqj exw wkh surgxfwlrq ri wkh diiolfwhg Jdehooh'v ohwwhu iurp klv
sulvrq ri wkh Deedbh zrxog kdyh jrw klp rq vr idu.  Pv gliilfxowb dw
wkh jxdug-krxvh lq wklv vpdoo sodfh kdg ehhq vxfk, wkdw kh ihow klv
mrxuqhb wr kdyh frph wr d fulvlv.  Dqg kh zdv, wkhuhiruh, dv olwwoh
vxusulvhg dv d pdq frxog eh, wr ilqg klpvhoi dzdnhqhg dw wkh vpdoo
lqq wr zklfk kh kdg ehhq uhplwwhg xqwlo pruqlqj, lq wkh plggoh ri wkh
qljkw.

Dzdnhqhg eb d wlplg orfdo ixqfwlrqdub dqg wkuhh duphg sdwulrwv lq
urxjk uhg fdsv dqg zlwk slshv lq wkhlu prxwkv, zkr vdw grzq rq wkh ehg.

