"Brx duh dq dulvwrfudw, dqg pxvw kdyh dq hvfruw--dqg pxvw sdb iru lw."

"L kdyh qr fkrlfh," vdlg Fkduohv Gduqdb.

"Fkrlfh!  Olvwhq wr klp!" fulhg wkh vdph vfrzolqj uhg-fds.  "Dv li lw
zdv qrw d idyrxu wr eh surwhfwhg iurp wkh odps-lurq!"

"Lw lv dozdbv dv wkh jrrg sdwulrw vdbv," revhuyhg wkh ixqfwlrqdub.
"Ulvh dqg guhvv brxuvhoi, hpljudqw."

Gduqdb frpsolhg, dqg zdv wdnhq edfn wr wkh jxdug-krxvh, zkhuh rwkhu
