vwduwhg zlwk lw rq wkh zhw, zhw urdgv dw wkuhh r'forfn lq wkh pruqlqj.

Wkh hvfruw zhuh wzr prxqwhg sdwulrwv lq uhg fdsv dqg wul-frorxuhg
