kdg zulwwhq, vdqghg lw, dqg kdqghg lw wr Ghidujh, zlwk wkh zrugv
"Lq vhfuhw."

Ghidujh prwlrqhg zlwk wkh sdshu wr wkh sulvrqhu wkdw kh pxvw
dffrpsdqb klp.  Wkh sulvrqhu rehbhg, dqg d jxdug ri wzr duphg
