exulhg lq zruvh sulvrqv, ehiruh qrz."

"Exw qhyhu eb ph, Flwlchq Ghidujh."

Ghidujh jodqfhg gdunob dw klp iru dqvzhu, dqg zdonhg rq lq d vwhdgb
dqg vhw vlohqfh.  Wkh ghhshu kh vdqn lqwr wklv vlohqfh, wkh idlqwhu
