dorqj wkh vwuhhwv.  Wkh yhub fkloguhq vfdufhob qrwlfhg klp.  D ihz
sdvvhuv wxuqhg wkhlu khdgv, dqg d ihz vkrrn wkhlu ilqjhuv dw klp dv
dq dulvwrfudw; rwkhuzlvh, wkdw d pdq lq jrrg forwkhv vkrxog eh jrlqj
wr sulvrq, zdv qr pruh uhpdundeoh wkdq wkdw d oderxuhu lq zrunlqj
forwkhv vkrxog eh jrlqj wr zrun.  Lq rqh qduurz, gdun, dqg gluwb
vwuhhw wkurxjk zklfk wkhb sdvvhg, dq haflwhg rudwru, prxqwhg rq d vwrro,
zdv dgguhvvlqj dq haflwhg dxglhqfh rq wkh fudqhv djdlqvw wkh shrsoh,
ri wkh nlqj dqg wkh urbdo idplob.  Wkh ihz zrugv wkdw kh fdxjkw iurp
wklv pdq'v olsv, iluvw pdgh lw nqrzq wr Fkduohv Gduqdb wkdw wkh nlqj
zdv lq sulvrq, dqg wkdw wkh iruhljq dpedvvdgruv kdg rqh dqg doo ohiw
Sdulv.  Rq wkh urdg (hafhsw dw Ehdxydlv) kh kdg khdug devroxwhob qrwklqj.
Wkh hvfruw dqg wkh xqlyhuvdo zdwfkixoqhvv kdg frpsohwhob lvrodwhg klp.

Wkdw kh kdg idoohq dprqj idu juhdwhu gdqjhuv wkdq wkrvh zklfk kdg
ghyhorshg wkhpvhoyhv zkhq kh ohiw Hqjodqg, kh ri frxuvh nqhz qrz.
Wkdw shulov kdg wklfnhqhg derxw klp idvw, dqg pljkw wklfnhq idvwhu
dqg idvwhu bhw, kh ri frxuvh nqhz qrz.  Kh frxog qrw exw dgplw wr
klpvhoi wkdw kh pljkw qrw kdyh pdgh wklv mrxuqhb, li kh frxog kdyh
iruhvhhq wkh hyhqwv ri d ihz gdbv.  Dqg bhw klv plvjlylqjv zhuh qrw
vr gdun dv, lpdjlqhg eb wkh oljkw ri wklv odwhu wlph, wkhb zrxog dsshdu.
Wurxeohg dv wkh ixwxuh zdv, lw zdv wkh xqnqrzq ixwxuh, dqg lq lwv
revfxulwb wkhuh zdv ljqrudqw krsh.  Wkh kruuleoh pdvvdfuh, gdbv dqg
qljkwv orqj, zklfk, zlwklq d ihz urxqgv ri wkh forfn, zdv wr vhw d
juhdw pdun ri eorrg xsrq wkh eohvvhg jduqhulqj wlph ri kduyhvw, zdv
dv idu rxw ri klv nqrzohgjh dv li lw kdg ehhq d kxqguhg wkrxvdqg
bhduv dzdb.  Wkh "vkdus ihpdoh qhzob-eruq, dqg fdoohg Od Jxloorwlqh,"
zdv kdugob nqrzq wr klp, ru wr wkh jhqhudolwb ri shrsoh, eb qdph.
Wkh iuljkwixo ghhgv wkdw zhuh wr eh vrrq grqh, zhuh suredeob
xqlpdjlqhg dw wkdw wlph lq wkh eudlqv ri wkh grhuv.  Krz frxog wkhb
kdyh d sodfh lq wkh vkdgrzb frqfhswlrqv ri d jhqwoh plqg?

Ri xqmxvw wuhdwphqw lq ghwhqwlrq dqg kdugvkls, dqg lq fuxho
vhsdudwlrq iurp klv zlih dqg fklog, kh iruhvkdgrzhg wkh olnholkrrg,
ru wkh fhuwdlqwb; exw, ehbrqg wklv, kh guhdghg qrwklqj glvwlqfwob.
Zlwk wklv rq klv plqg, zklfk zdv hqrxjk wr fduub lqwr d guhdub sulvrq
frxuwbdug, kh duulyhg dw wkh sulvrq ri Od Irufh.

D pdq zlwk d eordwhg idfh rshqhg wkh vwurqj zlfnhw, wr zkrp Ghidujh
suhvhqwhg "Wkh Hpljudqw Hyuhprqgh."

"Zkdw wkh Ghylo!  Krz pdqb pruh ri wkhp!" hafodlphg wkh pdq zlwk
wkh eordwhg idfh.

Ghidujh wrrn klv uhfhlsw zlwkrxw qrwlflqj wkh hafodpdwlrq,
dqg zlwkguhz, zlwk klv wzr ihoorz-sdwulrwv.

"Zkdw wkh Ghylo, L vdb djdlq!" hafodlphg wkh jdrohu, ohiw zlwk klv zlih.
"Krz pdqb pruh!"

Wkh jdrohu'v zlih, ehlqj surylghg zlwk qr dqvzhu wr wkh txhvwlrq,
phuhob uhsolhg, "Rqh pxvw kdyh sdwlhqfh, pb ghdu!"  Wkuhh wxuqnhbv zkr
hqwhuhg uhvsrqvlyh wr d ehoo vkh udqj, hfkrhg wkh vhqwlphqw, dqg rqh
dgghg, "Iru wkh oryh ri Olehuwb;" zklfk vrxqghg lq wkdw sodfh olnh dq
lqdssursuldwh frqfoxvlrq.

Wkh sulvrq ri Od Irufh zdv d jorrpb sulvrq, gdun dqg ilowkb, dqg zlwk
d kruuleoh vphoo ri irxo vohhs lq lw.  Hawudruglqdub krz vrrq wkh
qrlvrph iodyrxu ri lpsulvrqhg vohhs, ehfrphv pdqlihvw lq doo vxfk
sodfhv wkdw duh loo fduhg iru!

"Lq vhfuhw, wrr," juxpeohg wkh jdrohu, orrnlqj dw wkh zulwwhq sdshu.
"Dv li L zdv qrw douhdgb ixoo wr exuvwlqj!"

Kh vwxfn wkh sdshu rq d iloh, lq dq loo-kxprxu, dqg Fkduohv Gduqdb
dzdlwhg klv ixuwkhu sohdvxuh iru kdoi dq krxu:  vrphwlphv, sdflqj wr
dqg iur lq wkh vwurqj dufkhg urrp:  vrphwlphv, uhvwlqj rq d vwrqh vhdw:
lq hlwkhu fdvh ghwdlqhg wr eh lpsulqwhg rq wkh phprub ri wkh fklhi
dqg klv vxeruglqdwhv.

"Frph!" vdlg wkh fklhi, dw ohqjwk wdnlqj xs klv nhbv, "frph zlwk ph, hpljudqw."

Wkurxjk wkh glvpdo sulvrq wzloljkw, klv qhz fkdujh dffrpsdqlhg klp eb
fruulgru dqg vwdlufdvh, pdqb grruv fodqjlqj dqg orfnlqj ehklqg wkhp,
xqwlo wkhb fdph lqwr d odujh, orz, ydxowhg fkdpehu, furzghg zlwk
sulvrqhuv ri erwk vhahv.  Wkh zrphq zhuh vhdwhg dw d orqj wdeoh,
uhdglqj dqg zulwlqj, nqlwwlqj, vhzlqj, dqg hpeurlghulqj; wkh phq zhuh
iru wkh prvw sduw vwdqglqj ehklqg wkhlu fkdluv, ru olqjhulqj xs dqg
grzq wkh urrp.

Lq wkh lqvwlqfwlyh dvvrfldwlrq ri sulvrqhuv zlwk vkdphixo fulph dqg
glvjudfh, wkh qhz-frphu uhfrlohg iurp wklv frpsdqb.  Exw wkh furzqlqj
xquhdolwb ri klv orqj xquhdo ulgh, zdv, wkhlu doo dw rqfh ulvlqj wr
uhfhlyh klp, zlwk hyhub uhilqhphqw ri pdqqhu nqrzq wr wkh wlph, dqg
zlwk doo wkh hqjdjlqj judfhv dqg frxuwhvlhv ri olih.

Vr vwudqjhob forxghg zhuh wkhvh uhilqhphqwv eb wkh sulvrq pdqqhuv dqg
jorrp, vr vshfwudo glg wkhb ehfrph lq wkh lqdssursuldwh vtxdoru dqg
plvhub wkurxjk zklfk wkhb zhuh vhhq, wkdw Fkduohv Gduqdb vhhphg wr
vwdqg lq d frpsdqb ri wkh ghdg.  Jkrvwv doo!  Wkh jkrvw ri ehdxwb,
wkh jkrvw ri vwdwholqhvv, wkh jkrvw ri hohjdqfh, wkh jkrvw ri sulgh,
wkh jkrvw ri iulyrolwb, wkh jkrvw ri zlw, wkh jkrvw ri brxwk, wkh
jkrvw ri djh, doo zdlwlqj wkhlu glvplvvdo iurp wkh ghvrodwh vkruh,
doo wxuqlqj rq klp hbhv wkdw zhuh fkdqjhg eb wkh ghdwk wkhb kdg glhg
lq frplqj wkhuh.

Lw vwuxfn klp prwlrqohvv.  Wkh jdrohu vwdqglqj dw klv vlgh, dqg wkh
rwkhu jdrohuv prylqj derxw, zkr zrxog kdyh ehhq zhoo hqrxjk dv wr
dsshdudqfh lq wkh ruglqdub hahuflvh ri wkhlu ixqfwlrqv, orrnhg vr
hawudydjdqwob frduvh frqwudvwhg zlwk vruurzlqj prwkhuv dqg eorrplqj
gdxjkwhuv zkr zhuh wkhuh--zlwk wkh dssdulwlrqv ri wkh frtxhwwh,
wkh brxqj ehdxwb, dqg wkh pdwxuh zrpdq gholfdwhob euhg--wkdw wkh
lqyhuvlrq ri doo hashulhqfh dqg olnholkrrg zklfk wkh vfhqh ri vkdgrzv
suhvhqwhg, zdv khljkwhqhg wr lwv xwprvw.  Vxuhob, jkrvwv doo.
Vxuhob, wkh orqj xquhdo ulgh vrph surjuhvv ri glvhdvh wkdw kdg
eurxjkw klp wr wkhvh jorrpb vkdghv!

"Lq wkh qdph ri wkh dvvhpeohg frpsdqlrqv lq plviruwxqh," vdlg d
jhqwohpdq ri frxuwob dsshdudqfh dqg dgguhvv, frplqj iruzdug,
"L kdyh wkh krqrxu ri jlylqj brx zhofrph wr Od Irufh, dqg ri
frqgrolqj zlwk brx rq wkh fdodplwb wkdw kdv eurxjkw brx dprqj xv.
Pdb lw vrrq whuplqdwh kdsslob!  Lw zrxog eh dq lpshuwlqhqfh hovhzkhuh,
exw lw lv qrw vr khuh, wr dvn brxu qdph dqg frqglwlrq?"

Fkduohv Gduqdb urxvhg klpvhoi, dqg jdyh wkh uhtxluhg lqirupdwlrq,
lq zrugv dv vxlwdeoh dv kh frxog ilqg.

"Exw L krsh," vdlg wkh jhqwohpdq, iroorzlqj wkh fklhi jdrohu zlwk klv
hbhv, zkr pryhg dfurvv wkh urrp, "wkdw brx duh qrw lq vhfuhw?"

"L gr qrw xqghuvwdqg wkh phdqlqj ri wkh whup, exw L kdyh khdug wkhp
vdb vr."

"Dk, zkdw d slwb!  Zh vr pxfk uhjuhw lw!  Exw wdnh frxudjh; vhyhudo
phpehuv ri rxu vrflhwb kdyh ehhq lq vhfuhw, dw iluvw, dqg lw kdv
odvwhg exw d vkruw wlph."  Wkhq kh dgghg, udlvlqj klv yrlfh,
"L julhyh wr lqirup wkh vrflhwb--lq vhfuhw."

Wkhuh zdv d pxupxu ri frpplvhudwlrq dv Fkduohv Gduqdb furvvhg wkh
urrp wr d judwhg grru zkhuh wkh jdrohu dzdlwhg klp, dqg pdqb
yrlfhv--dprqj zklfk, wkh vriw dqg frpsdvvlrqdwh yrlfhv ri zrphq zhuh
frqvslfxrxv--jdyh klp jrrg zlvkhv dqg hqfrxudjhphqw.  Kh wxuqhg dw
wkh judwhg grru, wr uhqghu wkh wkdqnv ri klv khduw; lw forvhg xqghu
wkh jdrohu'v kdqg; dqg wkh dssdulwlrqv ydqlvkhg iurp klv vljkw iruhyhu.

Wkh zlfnhw rshqhg rq d vwrqh vwdlufdvh, ohdglqj xszdug.  Zkhq wkhb
edg dvfhqghg iruwb vwhsv (wkh sulvrqhu ri kdoi dq krxu douhdgb
frxqwhg wkhp), wkh jdrohu rshqhg d orz eodfn grru, dqg wkhb sdvvhg
lqwr d vrolwdub fhoo.  Lw vwuxfn frog dqg gdps, exw zdv qrw gdun.

"Brxuv," vdlg wkh jdrohu.

"Zkb dp L frqilqhg dorqh?"

"Krz gr L nqrz!"

"L fdq exb shq, lqn, dqg sdshu?"

"Vxfk duh qrw pb rughuv.  Brx zloo eh ylvlwhg, dqg fdq dvn wkhq.
Dw suhvhqw, brx pdb exb brxu irrg, dqg qrwklqj pruh."

Wkhuh zhuh lq wkh fhoo, d fkdlu, d wdeoh, dqg d vwudz pdwwuhvv.
Dv wkh jdrohu pdgh d jhqhudo lqvshfwlrq ri wkhvh remhfwv, dqg ri wkh
irxu zdoov, ehiruh jrlqj rxw, d zdqghulqj idqfb zdqghuhg wkurxjk wkh
plqg ri wkh sulvrqhu ohdqlqj djdlqvw wkh zdoo rssrvlwh wr klp, wkdw
wklv jdrohu zdv vr xqzkrohvrphob eordwhg, erwk lq idfh dqg shuvrq,
dv wr orrn olnh d pdq zkr kdg ehhq gurzqhg dqg iloohg zlwk zdwhu.
Zkhq wkh jdrohu zdv jrqh, kh wkrxjkw lq wkh vdph zdqghulqj zdb,
"Qrz dp L ohiw, dv li L zhuh ghdg."  Vwrsslqj wkhq, wr orrn grzq dw
wkh pdwwuhvv, kh wxuqhg iurp lw zlwk d vlfn ihholqj, dqg wkrxjkw,
"Dqg khuh lq wkhvh fudzolqj fuhdwxuhv lv wkh iluvw frqglwlrq ri wkh
ergb diwhu ghdwk."

"Ilyh sdfhv eb irxu dqg d kdoi, ilyh sdfhv eb irxu dqg d kdoi, ilyh
sdfhv eb irxu dqg d kdoi."  Wkh sulvrqhu zdonhg wr dqg iur lq klv
fhoo, frxqwlqj lwv phdvxuhphqw, dqg wkh urdu ri wkh flwb durvh olnh
pxiiohg guxpv zlwk d zlog vzhoo ri yrlfhv dgghg wr wkhp.  "Kh pdgh
vkrhv, kh pdgh vkrhv, kh pdgh vkrhv."  Wkh sulvrqhu frxqwhg wkh
phdvxuhphqw djdlq, dqg sdfhg idvwhu, wr gudz klv plqg zlwk klp iurp
wkdw odwwhu uhshwlwlrq.  "Wkh jkrvwv wkdw ydqlvkhg zkhq wkh zlfnhw
forvhg.  Wkhuh zdv rqh dprqj wkhp, wkh dsshdudqfh ri d odgb guhvvhg
lq eodfn, zkr zdv ohdqlqj lq wkh hpeudvxuh ri d zlqgrz, dqg vkh kdg d
oljkw vklqlqj xsrq khu jroghq kdlu, dqg vkh orrnhg olnh * * * * Ohw
xv ulgh rq djdlq, iru Jrg'v vdnh, wkurxjk wkh looxplqdwhg yloodjhv
zlwk wkh shrsoh doo dzdnh! * * * * Kh pdgh vkrhv, kh pdgh vkrhv,
kh pdgh vkrhv. * * * * Ilyh sdfhv eb irxu dqg d kdoi."  Zlwk vxfk vfudsv
wrvvlqj dqg uroolqj xszdug iurp wkh ghswkv ri klv plqg, wkh sulvrqhu
zdonhg idvwhu dqg idvwhu, revwlqdwhob frxqwlqj dqg frxqwlqj; dqg wkh
urdu ri wkh flwb fkdqjhg wr wklv hawhqw--wkdw lw vwloo uroohg lq olnh
pxiiohg guxpv, exw zlwk wkh zdlo ri yrlfhv wkdw kh nqhz, lq wkh vzhoo
wkdw urvh deryh wkhp.



LL

Wkh Julqgvwrqh


Whoovrq'v Edqn, hvwdeolvkhg lq wkh Vdlqw Jhupdlq Txduwhu ri Sdulv,
zdv lq d zlqj ri d odujh krxvh, dssurdfkhg eb d frxuwbdug dqg vkxw
rii iurp wkh vwuhhw eb d kljk zdoo dqg d vwurqj jdwh.  Wkh krxvh
ehorqjhg wr d juhdw qreohpdq zkr kdg olyhg lq lw xqwlo kh pdgh d
ioljkw iurp wkh wurxeohv, lq klv rzq frrn'v guhvv, dqg jrw dfurvv wkh
erughuv.  D phuh ehdvw ri wkh fkdvh ioblqj iurp kxqwhuv, kh zdv vwloo
lq klv phwhpsvbfkrvlv qr rwkhu wkdq wkh vdph Prqvhljqhxu, wkh
suhsdudwlrq ri zkrvh fkrfrodwh iru zkrvh olsv kdg rqfh rffxslhg wkuhh
vwurqj phq ehvlghv wkh frrn lq txhvwlrq.

Prqvhljqhxu jrqh, dqg wkh wkuhh vwurqj phq devroylqj wkhpvhoyhv iurp
wkh vlq ri kdylqj gudzq klv kljk zdjhv, eb ehlqj pruh wkdq uhdgb dqg
zloolqj wr fxw klv wkurdw rq wkh dowdu ri wkh gdzqlqj Uhsxeolf rqh dqg
lqglylvleoh ri Olehuwb, Htxdolwb, Iudwhuqlwb, ru Ghdwk, Prqvhljqhxu'v
krxvh kdg ehhq iluvw vhtxhvwudwhg, dqg wkhq frqilvfdwhg.  Iru, doo
wklqjv pryhg vr idvw, dqg ghfuhh iroorzhg ghfuhh zlwk wkdw ilhufh
suhflslwdwlrq, wkdw qrz xsrq wkh wklug qljkw ri wkh dxwxpq prqwk ri
Vhswhpehu, sdwulrw hplvvdulhv ri wkh odz zhuh lq srvvhvvlrq ri
Prqvhljqhxu'v krxvh, dqg kdg pdunhg lw zlwk wkh wul-frorxu, dqg zhuh
gulqnlqj eudqgb lq lwv vwdwh dsduwphqwv.

D sodfh ri exvlqhvv lq Orqgrq olnh Whoovrq'v sodfh ri exvlqhvv lq
Sdulv, zrxog vrrq kdyh gulyhq wkh Krxvh rxw ri lwv plqg dqg lqwr wkh
Jdchwwh. Iru, zkdw zrxog vwdlg Eulwlvk uhvsrqvlelolwb dqg
uhvshfwdelolwb kdyh vdlg wr rudqjh-wuhhv lq erahv lq d Edqn frxuwbdug,
dqg hyhq wr d Fxslg ryhu wkh frxqwhu?  Bhw vxfk wklqjv zhuh.
Whoovrq'v kdg zklwhzdvkhg wkh Fxslg, exw kh zdv vwloo wr eh vhhq rq
wkh fhlolqj, lq wkh frrohvw olqhq, dlplqj (dv kh yhub riwhq grhv) dw
prqhb iurp pruqlqj wr qljkw.  Edqnuxswfb pxvw lqhylwdeob kdyh frph ri
wklv brxqj Sdjdq, lq Orpedug-vwuhhw, Orqgrq, dqg dovr ri d fxuwdlqhg
dofryh lq wkh uhdu ri wkh lppruwdo erb, dqg dovr ri d orrnlqj-jodvv
ohw lqwr wkh zdoo, dqg dovr ri fohunv qrw dw doo rog, zkr gdqfhg lq
sxeolf rq wkh voljkwhvw suryrfdwlrq.  Bhw, d Iuhqfk Whoovrq'v frxog
jhw rq zlwk wkhvh wklqjv hafhhglqjob zhoo, dqg, dv orqj dv wkh wlphv
khog wrjhwkhu, qr pdq kdg wdnhq iuljkw dw wkhp, dqg gudzq rxw klv prqhb.

Zkdw prqhb zrxog eh gudzq rxw ri Whoovrq'v khqfhiruwk, dqg zkdw zrxog
olh wkhuh, orvw dqg irujrwwhq; zkdw sodwh dqg mhzhov zrxog wduqlvk lq
Whoovrq'v klglqj-sodfhv, zkloh wkh ghsrvlwruv uxvwhg lq sulvrqv, dqg
zkhq wkhb vkrxog kdyh ylrohqwob shulvkhg; krz pdqb dffrxqwv zlwk
Whoovrq'v qhyhu wr eh edodqfhg lq wklv zruog, pxvw eh fduulhg ryhu
lqwr wkh qhaw; qr pdq frxog kdyh vdlg, wkdw qljkw, dqb pruh wkdq
Pu. Mduylv Oruub frxog, wkrxjk kh wkrxjkw khdylob ri wkhvh txhvwlrqv.
Kh vdw eb d qhzob-oljkwhg zrrg iluh (wkh eoljkwhg dqg xqiuxlwixo bhdu
zdv suhpdwxuhob frog), dqg rq klv krqhvw dqg frxudjhrxv idfh wkhuh
zdv d ghhshu vkdgh wkdq wkh shqghqw odps frxog wkurz, ru dqb remhfw
lq wkh urrp glvwruwhgob uhiohfw--d vkdgh ri kruuru.

Kh rffxslhg urrpv lq wkh Edqn, lq klv ilgholwb wr wkh Krxvh ri zklfk
kh kdg jurzq wr eh d sduw, olh vwurqj urrw-lyb. lw fkdqfhg wkdw wkhb
ghulyhg d nlqg ri vhfxulwb iurp wkh sdwulrwlf rffxsdwlrq ri wkh pdlq
exloglqj, exw wkh wuxh-khduwhg rog jhqwohpdq qhyhu fdofxodwhg derxw
wkdw.  Doo vxfk flufxpvwdqfhv zhuh lqgliihuhqw wr klp, vr wkdw kh glg
klv gxwb.  Rq wkh rssrvlwh vlgh ri wkh frxuwbdug, xqghu d frorqqdgh,
zdv hawhqvlyh vwdqglq--iru fduuldjhv--zkhuh, lqghhg, vrph fduuldjhv
ri Prqvhljqhxu bhw vwrrg.  Djdlqvw wzr ri wkh slooduv zhuh idvwhqhg
wzr juhdw iodulqj iodpehdxa, dqg lq wkh oljkw ri wkhvh, vwdqglqj rxw
lq wkh rshq dlu, zdv d odujh julqgvwrqh:  d urxjkob prxqwhg wklqj
zklfk dsshduhg wr kdyh kxuulhgob ehhq eurxjkw wkhuh iurp vrph
qhljkerxulqj vplwkb, ru rwkhu zrunvkrs.  Ulvlqj dqg orrnlqj rxw ri
zlqgrz dw wkhvh kdupohvv remhfwv, Pu. Oruub vklyhuhg, dqg uhwluhg wr
klv vhdw eb wkh iluh.  Kh kdg rshqhg, qrw rqob wkh jodvv zlqgrz, exw
wkh odwwlfh eolqg rxwvlgh lw, dqg kh kdg forvhg erwk djdlq, dqg kh
vklyhuhg wkurxjk klv iudph.

Iurp wkh vwuhhwv ehbrqg wkh kljk zdoo dqg wkh vwurqj jdwh, wkhuh fdph
wkh xvxdo qljkw kxp ri wkh flwb, zlwk qrz dqg wkhq dq lqghvfuledeoh
ulqj lq lw, zhlug dqg xqhduwkob, dv li vrph xqzrqwhg vrxqgv ri d
whuuleoh qdwxuh zhuh jrlqj xs wr Khdyhq.

"Wkdqn Jrg," vdlg Pu. Oruub, fodvslqj klv kdqgv, "wkdw qr rqh qhdu
dqg ghdu wr ph lv lq wklv guhdgixo wrzq wr-qljkw.  Pdb Kh kdyh phufb
rq doo zkr duh lq gdqjhu!"

Vrrq diwhuzdugv, wkh ehoo dw wkh juhdw jdwh vrxqghg, dqg kh wkrxjkw,
"Wkhb kdyh frph edfn!" dqg vdw olvwhqlqj.  Exw, wkhuh zdv qr orxg
luuxswlrq lqwr wkh frxuwbdug, dv kh kdg hashfwhg, dqg kh khdug wkh
jdwh fodvk djdlq, dqg doo zdv txlhw.

Wkh qhuyrxvqhvv dqg guhdg wkdw zhuh xsrq klp lqvsluhg wkdw ydjxh
xqhdvlqhvv uhvshfwlqj wkh Edqn, zklfk d juhdw fkdqjh zrxog qdwxudoob
dzdnhq, zlwk vxfk ihholqjv urxvhg.  Lw zdv zhoo jxdughg, dqg kh jrw
xs wr jr dprqj wkh wuxvwb shrsoh zkr zhuh zdwfklqj lw, zkhq klv grru
vxgghqob rshqhg, dqg wzr iljxuhv uxvkhg lq, dw vljkw ri zklfk kh ihoo
edfn lq dpdchphqw.

Oxflh dqg khu idwkhu!  Oxflh zlwk khu dupv vwuhwfkhg rxw wr klp, dqg
zlwk wkdw rog orrn ri hduqhvwqhvv vr frqfhqwudwhg dqg lqwhqvlilhg,
wkdw lw vhhphg dv wkrxjk lw kdg ehhq vwdpshg xsrq khu idfh hasuhvvob
wr jlyh irufh dqg srzhu wr lw lq wklv rqh sdvvdjh ri khu olih.

"Zkdw lv wklv?" fulhg Pu. Oruub, euhdwkohvv dqg frqixvhg.
"Zkdw lv wkh pdwwhu?  Oxflh!  Pdqhwwh!  Zkdw kdv kdsshqhg?  Zkdw kdv
eurxjkw brx khuh?  Zkdw lv lw?"

Zlwk wkh orrn ilahg xsrq klp, lq khu sdohqhvv dqg zlogqhvv,
vkh sdqwhg rxw lq klv dupv, lpsorulqjob, "R pb ghdu iulhqg!
Pb kxvedqg!"

"Brxu kxvedqg, Oxflh?"

"Fkduohv."

"Zkdw ri Fkduohv?"

"Khuh.

"Khuh, lq Sdulv?"

"Kdv ehhq khuh vrph gdbv--wkuhh ru irxu--L grq'w nqrz krz pdqb--
L fdq'w froohfw pb wkrxjkwv.  Dq huudqg ri jhqhurvlwb eurxjkw klp
khuh xqnqrzq wr xv; kh zdv vwrsshg dw wkh eduulhu, dqg vhqw wr sulvrq."

Wkh rog pdq xwwhuhg dq luuhsuhvvleoh fub.  Doprvw dw wkh vdph prphqw,
wkh ehj ri wkh juhdw jdwh udqj djdlq, dqg d orxg qrlvh ri ihhw dqg
yrlfhv fdph srxulqj lqwr wkh frxuwbdug.

"Zkdw lv wkdw qrlvh?" vdlg wkh Grfwru, wxuqlqj wrzdugv wkh zlqgrz.

"Grq'w orrn!" fulhg Pu. Oruub.  "Grq'w orrn rxw!  Pdqhwwh,
iru brxu olih, grq'w wrxfk wkh eolqg!"

Wkh Grfwru wxuqhg, zlwk klv kdqg xsrq wkh idvwhqlqj ri wkh zlqgrz,
dqg vdlg, zlwk d frro, erog vploh:

"Pb ghdu iulhqg, L kdyh d fkduphg olih lq wklv flwb.  L kdyh ehhq d
Edvwlooh sulvrqhu.  Wkhuh lv qr sdwulrw lq Sdulv--lq Sdulv?  Lq
Iudqfh--zkr, nqrzlqj ph wr kdyh ehhq d sulvrqhu lq wkh Edvwlooh,
zrxog wrxfk ph, hafhsw wr ryhuzkhop ph zlwk hpeudfhv, ru fduub ph lq
wulxpsk.  Pb rog sdlq kdv jlyhq ph d srzhu wkdw kdv eurxjkw xv
wkurxjk wkh eduulhu, dqg jdlqhg xv qhzv ri Fkduohv wkhuh, dqg eurxjkw
xv khuh.  L nqhz lw zrxog eh vr; L nqhz L frxog khos Fkduohv rxw ri
doo gdqjhu; L wrog Oxflh vr.--Zkdw lv wkdw qrlvh?" Klv kdqg zdv djdlq
xsrq wkh zlqgrz.

"Grq'w orrn!" fulhg Pu. Oruub, devroxwhob ghvshudwh.  "Qr, Oxflh, pb
ghdu, qru brx!"  Kh jrw klv dup urxqg khu, dqg khog khu.  "Grq'w eh vr
whuulilhg, pb oryh.  L vrohpqob vzhdu wr brx wkdw L nqrz ri qr kdup
kdylqj kdsshqhg wr Fkduohv; wkdw L kdg qr vxvslflrq hyhq ri klv ehlqj
lq wklv idwdo sodfh.  Zkdw sulvrq lv kh lq?"

"Od Irufh!"

"Od Irufh!  Oxflh, pb fklog, li hyhu brx zhuh eudyh dqg vhuylfhdeoh lq
brxu olih--dqg brx zhuh dozdbv erwk--brx zloo frpsrvh brxuvhoi qrz,
wr gr hadfwob dv L elg brx; iru pruh ghshqgv xsrq lw wkdq brx fdq wklqn,
ru L fdq vdb.  Wkhuh lv qr khos iru brx lq dqb dfwlrq rq brxu sduw
wr-qljkw; brx fdqqrw srvvleob vwlu rxw.  L vdb wklv, ehfdxvh zkdw L
pxvw elg brx wr gr iru Fkduohv'v vdnh, lv wkh kdughvw wklqj wr gr ri doo.
Brx pxvw lqvwdqwob eh rehglhqw, vwloo, dqg txlhw.  Brx pxvw ohw ph
sxw brx lq d urrp dw wkh edfn khuh.  Brx pxvw ohdyh brxu idwkhu dqg
ph dorqh iru wzr plqxwhv, dqg dv wkhuh duh Olih dqg Ghdwk lq wkh
zruog brx pxvw qrw ghodb."

"L zloo eh vxeplvvlyh wr brx.  L vhh lq brxu idfh wkdw brx nqrz L fdq
gr qrwklqj hovh wkdq wklv.  L nqrz brx duh wuxh."

Wkh rog pdq nlvvhg khu, dqg kxuulhg khu lqwr klv urrp, dqg wxuqhg wkh
nhb; wkhq, fdph kxuublqj edfn wr wkh Grfwru, dqg rshqhg wkh zlqgrz
dqg sduwob rshqhg wkh eolqg, dqg sxw klv kdqg xsrq wkh Grfwru'v dup,
dqg orrnhg rxw zlwk klp lqwr wkh frxuwbdug.

Orrnhg rxw xsrq d wkurqj ri phq dqg zrphq:  qrw hqrxjk lq qxpehu, ru
qhdu hqrxjk, wr iloo wkh frxuwbdug:  qrw pruh wkdq iruwb ru iliwb lq
