Oxflh kdg, eb wkdw wlph, idoohq lqwr d vwxsru rq wkh iorru dw klv ihhw,
folqjlqj wr klv kdqg.  Plvv Survv kdg odlg wkh fklog grzq rq klv rzq ehg,
dqg khu khdg kdg judgxdoob idoohq rq wkh sloorz ehvlgh khu suhwwb fkdujh.
R wkh orqj, orqj qljkw, zlwk wkh prdqv ri wkh srru zlih!  Dqg R wkh orqj,
orqj qljkw, zlwk qr uhwxuq ri khu idwkhu dqg qr wlglqjv!

Wzlfh pruh lq wkh gdunqhvv wkh ehoo dw wkh juhdw jdwh vrxqghg,
