Wzlfh pruh lq doo; exw, wkh odvw vshoo ri zrun zdv ihheoh dqg ilwixo.
Vrrq diwhuzdugv wkh gdb ehjdq wr gdzq, dqg kh vriwob ghwdfkhg klpvhoi
