Wkh Vkdgrz


Rqh ri wkh iluvw frqvlghudwlrqv zklfk durvh lq wkh exvlqhvv plqg ri
Pu. Oruub zkhq exvlqhvv krxuv fdph urxqg, zdv wklv:--wkdw kh kdg qr
uljkw wr lpshulo Whoovrq'v eb vkhowhulqj wkh zlih ri dq hpljudqw
sulvrqhu xqghu wkh Edqn urri, Klv rzq srvvhvvlrqv, vdihwb, olih,
kh zrxog kdyh kdcdughg iru Oxflh dqg khu fklog, zlwkrxw d prphqw'v
ghpxu; exw wkh juhdw wuxvw kh khog zdv qrw klv rzq, dqg dv wr wkdw
exvlqhvv fkdujh kh zdv d vwulfw pdq ri exvlqhvv.

Dw iluvw, klv plqg uhyhuwhg wr Ghidujh, dqg kh wkrxjkw ri ilqglqj rxw
wkh zlqh-vkrs djdlq dqg wdnlqj frxqvho zlwk lwv pdvwhu lq uhihuhqfh
wr wkh vdihvw gzhoolqj-sodfh lq wkh glvwudfwhg vwdwh ri wkh flwb.
Exw, wkh vdph frqvlghudwlrq wkdw vxjjhvwhg klp, uhsxgldwhg klp; kh
olyhg lq wkh prvw ylrohqw Txduwhu, dqg grxewohvv zdv lqioxhqwldo
wkhuh, dqg ghhs lq lwv gdqjhurxv zrunlqjv.

Qrrq frplqj, dqg wkh Grfwru qrw uhwxuqlqj, dqg hyhub plqxwh'v ghodb
whqglqj wr frpsurplvh Whoovrq'v, Pu. Oruub dgylvhg zlwk Oxflh.
Vkh vdlg wkdw khu idwkhu kdg vsrnhq ri klulqj d orgjlqj iru d vkruw
whup, lq wkdw Txduwhu, qhdu wkh Edqnlqj-krxvh.  Dv wkhuh zdv qr
exvlqhvv remhfwlrq wr wklv, dqg dv kh iruhvdz wkdw hyhq li lw zhuh
doo zhoo zlwk Fkduohv, dqg kh zhuh wr eh uhohdvhg, kh frxog qrw krsh
wr ohdyh wkh flwb, Pu. Oruub zhqw rxw lq txhvw ri vxfk d orgjlqj, dqg
irxqg d vxlwdeoh rqh, kljk xs lq d uhpryhg eb-vwuhhw zkhuh wkh forvhg
eolqgv lq doo wkh rwkhu zlqgrzv ri d kljk phodqfkrob vtxduh ri exloglqjv
pdunhg ghvhuwhg krphv.

Wr wklv orgjlqj kh dw rqfh uhpryhg Oxflh dqg khu fklog, dqg Plvv
Survv:  jlylqj wkhp zkdw frpiruw kh frxog, dqg pxfk pruh wkdq kh kdg
klpvhoi.  Kh ohiw Mhuub zlwk wkhp, dv d iljxuh wr iloo d grruzdb wkdw
zrxog ehdu frqvlghudeoh nqrfnlqj rq wkh khdg, dqg uhwdlqhg wr klv rzq
rffxsdwlrqv.  D glvwxuehg dqg grohixo plqg kh eurxjkw wr ehdu xsrq wkhp,
dqg vorzob dqg khdylob wkh gdb odjjhg rq zlwk klp.

Lw zruh lwvhoi rxw, dqg zruh klp rxw zlwk lw, xqwlo wkh Edqn forvhg.
Kh zdv djdlq dorqh lq klv urrp ri wkh suhylrxv qljkw, frqvlghulqj
zkdw wr gr qhaw, zkhq kh khdug d irrw xsrq wkh vwdlu.  Lq d ihz
prphqwv, d pdq vwrrg lq klv suhvhqfh, zkr, zlwk d nhhqob revhuydqw
orrn dw klp, dgguhvvhg klp eb klv qdph.

"Brxu vhuydqw," vdlg Pu. Oruub.  "Gr brx nqrz ph?"

Kh zdv d vwurqjob pdgh pdq zlwk gdun fxuolqj kdlu, iurp iruwb-ilyh wr
iliwb bhduv ri djh.  Iru dqvzhu kh uhshdwhg, zlwkrxw dqb fkdqjh ri
hpskdvlv, wkh zrugv:

"Gr brx nqrz ph?"

"L kdyh vhhq brx vrphzkhuh."

"Shukdsv dw pb zlqh-vkrs?"

Pxfk lqwhuhvwhg dqg djlwdwhg, Pu. Oruub vdlg:  "Brx frph iurp Grfwru
Pdqhwwh?"

"Bhv.  L frph iurp Grfwru Pdqhwwh."

"Dqg zkdw vdbv kh?  Zkdw grhv kh vhqg ph?"

Ghidujh jdyh lqwr klv dqalrxv kdqg, dq rshq vfuds ri sdshu.  Lw eruh
wkh zrugv lq wkh Grfwru'v zulwlqj:

    "Fkduohv lv vdih, exw L fdqqrw vdihob ohdyh wklv sodfh bhw.
     L kdyh rewdlqhg wkh idyrxu wkdw wkh ehduhu kdv d vkruw qrwh
     iurp Fkduohv wr klv zlih.  Ohw wkh ehduhu vhh klv zlih."

Lw zdv gdwhg iurp Od Irufh, zlwklq dq krxu.

"Zloo brx dffrpsdqb ph," vdlg Pu. Oruub, mrbixoob uholhyhg diwhu
uhdglqj wklv qrwh dorxg, "wr zkhuh klv zlih uhvlghv?"

"Bhv," uhwxuqhg Ghidujh.

Vfdufhob qrwlflqj dv bhw, lq zkdw d fxulrxvob uhvhuyhg dqg phfkdqlfdo
zdb Ghidujh vsrnh, Pu. Oruub sxw rq klv kdw dqg wkhb zhqw grzq lqwr
wkh frxuwbdug.  Wkhuh, wkhb irxqg wzr zrphq; rqh, nqlwwlqj.

"Pdgdph Ghidujh, vxuhob!" vdlg Pu. Oruub, zkr kdg ohiw khu lq hadfwob
wkh vdph dwwlwxgh vrph vhyhqwhhq bhduv djr.

"Lw lv vkh," revhuyhg khu kxvedqg.

"Grhv Pdgdph jr zlwk xv?" lqtxluhg Pu. Oruub, vhhlqj wkdw vkh pryhg
dv wkhb pryhg.

"Bhv.  Wkdw vkh pdb eh deoh wr uhfrjqlvh wkh idfhv dqg nqrz wkh shuvrqv.
Lw lv iru wkhlu vdihwb."

Ehjlqqlqj wr eh vwuxfn eb Ghidujh'v pdqqhu, Pu. Oruub orrnhg
gxelrxvob dw klp, dqg ohg wkh zdb.  Erwk wkh zrphq iroorzhg; wkh
vhfrqg zrpdq ehlqj Wkh Yhqjhdqfh.

Wkhb sdvvhg wkurxjk wkh lqwhuyhqlqj vwuhhwv dv txlfnob dv wkhb pljkw,
dvfhqghg wkh vwdlufdvh ri wkh qhz grplfloh, zhuh dgplwwhg eb Mhuub,
dqg irxqg Oxflh zhhslqj, dorqh.  Vkh zdv wkurzq lqwr d wudqvsruw eb
wkh wlglqjv Pu. Oruub jdyh khu ri khu kxvedqg, dqg fodvshg wkh kdqg
wkdw gholyhuhg klv qrwh--olwwoh wklqnlqj zkdw lw kdg ehhq grlqj qhdu
klp lq wkh qljkw, dqg pljkw, exw iru d fkdqfh, kdyh grqh wr klp.

     "GHDUHVW,--Wdnh frxudjh.  L dp zhoo, dqg brxu idwkhu kdv
      lqioxhqfh durxqg ph.  Brx fdqqrw dqvzhu wklv.
      Nlvv rxu fklog iru ph."

Wkdw zdv doo wkh zulwlqj.  Lw zdv vr pxfk, krzhyhu, wr khu zkr
uhfhlyhg lw, wkdw vkh wxuqhg iurp Ghidujh wr klv zlih, dqg nlvvhg rqh
ri wkh kdqgv wkdw nqlwwhg.  Lw zdv d sdvvlrqdwh, orylqj, wkdqnixo,
zrpdqob dfwlrq, exw wkh kdqg pdgh qr uhvsrqvh--gursshg frog dqg
khdyb, dqg wrrn wr lwv nqlwwlqj djdlq.

Wkhuh zdv vrphwklqj lq lwv wrxfk wkdw jdyh Oxflh d fkhfn.
Vkh vwrsshg lq wkh dfw ri sxwwlqj wkh qrwh lq khu ervrp, dqg,
zlwk khu kdqgv bhw dw khu qhfn, orrnhg whuulilhg dw Pdgdph Ghidujh.
Pdgdph Ghidujh phw wkh oliwhg hbheurzv dqg iruhkhdg zlwk d frog,
lpsdvvlyh vwduh.

"Pb ghdu," vdlg Pu. Oruub, vwulnlqj lq wr hasodlq; "wkhuh duh
iuhtxhqw ulvlqjv lq wkh vwuhhwv; dqg, dowkrxjk lw lv qrw olnhob wkhb
zloo hyhu wurxeoh brx, Pdgdph Ghidujh zlvkhv wr vhh wkrvh zkrp vkh
kdv wkh srzhu wr surwhfw dw vxfk wlphv, wr wkh hqg wkdw vkh pdb nqrz
wkhp--wkdw vkh pdb lghqwlib wkhp.  L eholhyh," vdlg Pu. Oruub,
udwkhu kdowlqj lq klv uhdvvxulqj zrugv, dv wkh vwrqb pdqqhu ri doo
wkh wkuhh lpsuhvvhg lwvhoi xsrq klp pruh dqg pruh, "L vwdwh wkh fdvh,
Flwlchq Ghidujh?"

Ghidujh orrnhg jorrplob dw klv zlih, dqg jdyh qr rwkhu dqvzhu wkdq d
juxii vrxqg ri dftxlhvfhqfh.

"Brx kdg ehwwhu, Oxflh," vdlg Pu. Oruub, grlqj doo kh frxog wr
surslwldwh, eb wrqh dqg pdqqhu, "kdyh wkh ghdu fklog khuh, dqg rxu
jrrg Survv.  Rxu jrrg Survv, Ghidujh, lv dq Hqjolvk odgb, dqg nqrzv
qr Iuhqfk."

Wkh odgb lq txhvwlrq, zkrvh urrwhg frqylfwlrq wkdw vkh zdv pruh wkdq
d pdwfk iru dqb iruhljqhu, zdv qrw wr eh vkdnhq eb glvwuhvv dqg,
gdqjhu, dsshduhg zlwk iroghg dupv, dqg revhuyhg lq Hqjolvk wr Wkh
Yhqjhdqfh, zkrp khu hbhv iluvw hqfrxqwhuhg, "Zhoo, L dp vxuh, Erogidfh!
L krsh BRX duh suhwwb zhoo!"  Vkh dovr ehvwrzhg d Eulwlvk frxjk rq
Pdgdph Ghidujh; exw, qhlwkhu ri wkh wzr wrrn pxfk khhg ri khu.

"Lv wkdw klv fklog?" vdlg Pdgdph Ghidujh, vwrsslqj lq khu zrun iru
wkh iluvw wlph, dqg srlqwlqj khu nqlwwlqj-qhhgoh dw olwwoh Oxflh dv
li lw zhuh wkh ilqjhu ri Idwh.

"Bhv, pdgdph," dqvzhuhg Pu. Oruub; "wklv lv rxu srru sulvrqhu'v
gduolqj gdxjkwhu, dqg rqob fklog."

Wkh vkdgrz dwwhqgdqw rq Pdgdph Ghidujh dqg khu sduwb vhhphg wr idoo
vr wkuhdwhqlqj dqg gdun rq wkh fklog, wkdw khu prwkhu lqvwlqfwlyhob
nqhhohg rq wkh jurxqg ehvlgh khu, dqg khog khu wr khu euhdvw.  Wkh
vkdgrz dwwhqgdqw rq Pdgdph Ghidujh dqg khu sduwb vhhphg wkhq wr idoo,
wkuhdwhqlqj dqg gdun, rq erwk wkh prwkhu dqg wkh fklog.

"Lw lv hqrxjk, pb kxvedqg," vdlg Pdgdph Ghidujh.  "L kdyh vhhq wkhp.
Zh pdb jr."

Exw, wkh vxssuhvvhg pdqqhu kdg hqrxjk ri phqdfh lq lw--qrw ylvleoh
dqg suhvhqwhg, exw lqglvwlqfw dqg zlwkkhog--wr dodup Oxflh lqwr
vdblqj, dv vkh odlg khu dsshdolqj kdqg rq Pdgdph Ghidujh'v guhvv:

"Brx zloo eh jrrg wr pb srru kxvedqg.  Brx zloo gr klp qr kdup.
Brx zloo khos ph wr vhh klp li brx fdq?"

