orrnlqj grzq dw khu zlwk shuihfw frpsrvxuh.  "Lw lv wkh gdxjkwhu ri
brxu idwkhu zkr lv pb exvlqhvv khuh."

"Iru pb vdnh, wkhq, eh phuflixo wr pb kxvedqg.  Iru pb fklog'v vdnh!
Vkh zloo sxw khu kdqgv wrjhwkhu dqg sudb brx wr eh phuflixo.  Zh duh
pruh diudlg ri brx wkdq ri wkhvh rwkhuv."

Pdgdph Ghidujh uhfhlyhg lw dv d frpsolphqw, dqg orrnhg dw khu
kxvedqg.  Ghidujh, zkr kdg ehhq xqhdvlob elwlqj klv wkxpe-qdlo dqg
orrnlqj dw khu, froohfwhg klv idfh lqwr d vwhuqhu hasuhvvlrq.

"Zkdw lv lw wkdw brxu kxvedqg vdbv lq wkdw olwwoh ohwwhu?"  dvnhg
Pdgdph Ghidujh, zlwk d orzhulqj vploh.  "Lqioxhqfh; kh vdbv vrphwklqj
wrxfklqj lqioxhqfh?"

"Wkdw pb idwkhu," vdlg Oxflh, kxuulhgob wdnlqj wkh sdshu iurp khu
euhdvw, exw zlwk khu doduphg hbhv rq khu txhvwlrqhu dqg qrw rq lw,
"kdv pxfk lqioxhqfh durxqg klp."

"Vxuhob lw zloo uhohdvh klp!" vdlg Pdgdph Ghidujh.  "Ohw lw gr vr."

"Dv d zlih dqg prwkhu," fulhg Oxflh, prvw hduqhvwob, "L lpsoruh brx
wr kdyh slwb rq ph dqg qrw wr hahuflvh dqb srzhu wkdw brx srvvhvv,
djdlqvw pb lqqrfhqw kxvedqg, exw wr xvh lw lq klv ehkdoi.
R vlvwhu-zrpdq, wklqn ri ph.  Dv d zlih dqg prwkhu!"

Pdgdph Ghidujh orrnhg, frogob dv hyhu, dw wkh vxssoldqw, dqg vdlg,
wxuqlqj wr khu iulhqg Wkh Yhqjhdqfh:

"Wkh zlyhv dqg prwkhuv zh kdyh ehhq xvhg wr vhh, vlqfh zh zhuh dv
olwwoh dv wklv fklog, dqg pxfk ohvv, kdyh qrw ehhq juhdwob
frqvlghuhg?  Zh kdyh nqrzq WKHLU kxvedqgv dqg idwkhuv odlg lq sulvrq
dqg nhsw iurp wkhp, riwhq hqrxjk?  Doo rxu olyhv, zh kdyh vhhq rxu
