LY

Fdop lq Vwrup


Grfwru Pdqhwwh glg qrw uhwxuq xqwlo wkh pruqlqj ri wkh irxuwk gdb ri
klv devhqfh.  Vr pxfk ri zkdw kdg kdsshqhg lq wkdw guhdgixo wlph dv
frxog eh nhsw iurp wkh nqrzohgjh ri Oxflh zdv vr zhoo frqfhdohg iurp
khu, wkdw qrw xqwlo orqj diwhuzdugv, zkhq Iudqfh dqg vkh zhuh idu dsduw,
glg vkh nqrz wkdw hohyhq kxqguhg ghihqfhohvv sulvrqhuv ri erwk vhahv
dqg doo djhv kdg ehhq nloohg eb wkh srsxodfh; wkdw irxu gdbv dqg
qljkwv kdg ehhq gdunhqhg eb wklv ghhg ri kruuru; dqg wkdw wkh dlu
durxqg khu kdg ehhq wdlqwhg eb wkh vodlq.  Vkh rqob nqhz wkdw wkhuh
kdg ehhq dq dwwdfn xsrq wkh sulvrqv, wkdw doo srolwlfdo sulvrqhuv kdg
ehhq lq gdqjhu, dqg wkdw vrph kdg ehhq gudjjhg rxw eb wkh furzg dqg
pxughuhg.

Wr Pu. Oruub, wkh Grfwru frppxqlfdwhg xqghu dq lqmxqfwlrq ri vhfuhfb
rq zklfk kh kdg qr qhhg wr gzhoo, wkdw wkh furzg kdg wdnhq klp
wkurxjk d vfhqh ri fduqdjh wr wkh sulvrq ri Od Irufh.  Wkdw, lq wkh
sulvrq kh kdg irxqg d vhoi-dssrlqwhg Wulexqdo vlwwlqj, ehiruh zklfk
wkh sulvrqhuv zhuh eurxjkw vlqjob, dqg eb zklfk wkhb zhuh udslgob
rughuhg wr eh sxw iruwk wr eh pdvvdfuhg, ru wr eh uhohdvhg, ru (lq d
ihz fdvhv) wr eh vhqw edfn wr wkhlu fhoov.  Wkdw, suhvhqwhg eb klv
frqgxfwruv wr wklv Wulexqdo, kh kdg dqqrxqfhg klpvhoi eb qdph dqg
surihvvlrq dv kdylqj ehhq iru hljkwhhq bhduv d vhfuhw dqg xqdffxvhg
sulvrqhu lq wkh Edvwlooh; wkdw, rqh ri wkh ergb vr vlwwlqj lq
mxgjphqw kdg ulvhq dqg lghqwlilhg klp, dqg wkdw wklv pdq zdv Ghidujh.

Wkdw, khuhxsrq kh kdg dvfhuwdlqhg, wkurxjk wkh uhjlvwhuv rq wkh wdeoh,
wkdw klv vrq-lq-odz zdv dprqj wkh olylqj sulvrqhuv, dqg kdg sohdghg
kdug wr wkh Wulexqdo--ri zkrp vrph phpehuv zhuh dvohhs dqg vrph dzdnh,
