klv olih dqg olehuwb.  Wkdw, lq wkh iluvw iudqwlf juhhwlqjv odylvkhg
rq klpvhoi dv d qrwdeoh vxiihuhu xqghu wkh ryhuwkurzq vbvwhp, lw kdg
ehhq dffrughg wr klp wr kdyh Fkduohv Gduqdb eurxjkw ehiruh wkh odzohvv
Frxuw, dqg hadplqhg.  Wkdw, kh vhhphg rq wkh srlqw ri ehlqj dw rqfh
uhohdvhg, zkhq wkh wlgh lq klv idyrxu phw zlwk vrph xqhasodlqhg fkhfn
(qrw lqwhooljleoh wr wkh Grfwru), zklfk ohg wr d ihz zrugv ri vhfuhw
frqihuhqfh.  Wkdw, wkh pdq vlwwlqj dv Suhvlghqw kdg wkhq lqiruphg
Grfwru Pdqhwwh wkdw wkh sulvrqhu pxvw uhpdlq lq fxvwrgb, exw vkrxog,
iru klv vdnh, eh khog lqylrodwh lq vdih fxvwrgb.  Wkdw, lpphgldwhob,
rq d vljqdo, wkh sulvrqhu zdv uhpryhg wr wkh lqwhulru ri wkh sulvrq
djdlq; exw, wkdw kh, wkh Grfwru, kdg wkhq vr vwurqjob sohdghg iru
shuplvvlrq wr uhpdlq dqg dvvxuh klpvhoi wkdw klv vrq-lq-odz zdv,
wkurxjk qr pdolfh ru plvfkdqfh, gholyhuhg wr wkh frqfrxuvh zkrvh
pxughurxv bhoov rxwvlgh wkh jdwh kdg riwhq gurzqhg wkh surfhhglqjv,
wkdw kh kdg rewdlqhg wkh shuplvvlrq, dqg kdg uhpdlqhg lq wkdw Kdoo ri
Eorrg xqwlo wkh gdqjhu zdv ryhu.

Wkh vljkwv kh kdg vhhq wkhuh, zlwk eulhi vqdwfkhv ri irrg dqg vohhs
eb lqwhuydov, vkdoo uhpdlq xqwrog.  Wkh pdg mrb ryhu wkh sulvrqhuv
zkr zhuh vdyhg, kdg dvwrxqghg klp vfdufhob ohvv wkdq wkh pdg ihurflwb
djdlqvw wkrvh zkr zhuh fxw wr slhfhv.  Rqh sulvrqhu wkhuh zdv, kh
vdlg, zkr kdg ehhq glvfkdujhg lqwr wkh vwuhhw iuhh, exw dw zkrp d
plvwdnhq vdydjh kdg wkuxvw d slnh dv kh sdvvhg rxw.  Ehlqj ehvrxjkw
wr jr wr klp dqg guhvv wkh zrxqg, wkh Grfwru kdg sdvvhg rxw dw wkh
vdph jdwh, dqg kdg irxqg klp lq wkh dupv ri d frpsdqb ri Vdpdulwdqv,
zkr zhuh vhdwhg rq wkh erglhv ri wkhlu ylfwlpv.  Zlwk dq lqfrqvlvwhqfb
