kdg pdgh d olwwhu iru klp dqg hvfruwhg klp fduhixoob iurp wkh vsrw--
kdg wkhq fdxjkw xs wkhlu zhdsrqv dqg soxqjhg dqhz lqwr d exwfkhub vr
