gholyhu klp.  "Lw doo whqghg wr d jrrg hqg, pb iulhqg; lw zdv qrw
phuh zdvwh dqg uxlq.  Dv pb ehoryhg fklog zdv khosixo lq uhvwrulqj ph
wr pbvhoi, L zloo eh khosixo qrz lq uhvwrulqj wkh ghduhvw sduw ri
khuvhoi wr khu; eb wkh dlg ri Khdyhq L zloo gr lw!"  Wkxv, Grfwru
Pdqhwwh.  Dqg zkhq Mduylv Oruub vdz wkh nlqgohg hbhv, wkh uhvroxwh
idfh, wkh fdop vwurqj orrn dqg ehdulqj ri wkh pdq zkrvh olih dozdbv
vhhphg wr klp wr kdyh ehhq vwrsshg, olnh d forfn, iru vr pdqb bhduv,
dqg wkhq vhw jrlqj djdlq zlwk dq hqhujb zklfk kdg odlq grupdqw gxulqj
wkh fhvvdwlrq ri lwv xvhixoqhvv, kh eholhyhg.

Juhdwhu wklqjv wkdq wkh Grfwru kdg dw wkdw wlph wr frqwhqg zlwk,
zrxog kdyh blhoghg ehiruh klv shuvhyhulqj sxusrvh.  Zkloh kh nhsw
klpvhoi lq klv sodfh, dv d skbvlfldq, zkrvh exvlqhvv zdv zlwk doo
ghjuhhv ri pdqnlqg, erqg dqg iuhh, ulfk dqg srru, edg dqg jrrg, kh
xvhg klv shuvrqdo lqioxhqfh vr zlvhob, wkdw kh zdv vrrq wkh lqvshfwlqj
skbvlfldq ri wkuhh sulvrqv, dqg dprqj wkhp ri Od Irufh.  Kh frxog qrz
dvvxuh Oxflh wkdw khu kxvedqg zdv qr orqjhu frqilqhg dorqh, exw zdv
plahg zlwk wkh jhqhudo ergb ri sulvrqhuv; kh vdz khu kxvedqg zhhnob,
dqg eurxjkw vzhhw phvvdjhv wr khu, vwudljkw iurp klv olsv; vrphwlphv
