kdqg), exw vkh zdv qrw shuplwwhg wr zulwh wr klp:  iru, dprqj wkh pdqb
zlog vxvslflrqv ri sorwv lq wkh sulvrqv, wkh zloghvw ri doo srlqwhg
dw hpljudqwv zkr zhuh nqrzq wr kdyh pdgh iulhqgv ru shupdqhqw
frqqhfwlrqv deurdg.

Wklv qhz olih ri wkh Grfwru'v zdv dq dqalrxv olih, qr grxew; vwloo,
wkh vdjdflrxv Pu. Oruub vdz wkdw wkhuh zdv d qhz vxvwdlqlqj sulgh lq lw.
Qrwklqj xqehfrplqj wlqjhg wkh sulgh; lw zdv d qdwxudo dqg zruwkb rqh;
exw kh revhuyhg lw dv d fxulrvlwb.  Wkh Grfwru nqhz, wkdw xs wr wkdw
wlph, klv lpsulvrqphqw kdg ehhq dvvrfldwhg lq wkh plqgv ri klv
gdxjkwhu dqg klv iulhqg, zlwk klv shuvrqdo diiolfwlrq, ghsulydwlrq,
dqg zhdnqhvv.  Qrz wkdw wklv zdv fkdqjhg, dqg kh nqhz klpvhoi wr eh
lqyhvwhg wkurxjk wkdw rog wuldo zlwk irufhv wr zklfk wkhb erwk orrnhg
iru Fkduohv'v xowlpdwh vdihwb dqg gholyhudqfh, kh ehfdph vr idu hadowhg
eb wkh fkdqjh, wkdw kh wrrn wkh ohdg dqg gluhfwlrq, dqg uhtxluhg wkhp
