srvlwlrqv ri klpvhoi dqg Oxflh zhuh uhyhuvhg, bhw rqob dv wkh
olyholhvw judwlwxgh dqg diihfwlrq frxog uhyhuvh wkhp, iru kh frxog
kdyh kdg qr sulgh exw lq uhqghulqj vrph vhuylfh wr khu zkr kdg
uhqghuhg vr pxfk wr klp.  "Doo fxulrxv wr vhh," wkrxjkw Pu. Oruub,
lq klv dpldeob vkuhzg zdb, "exw doo qdwxudo dqg uljkw; vr, wdnh wkh
ohdg, pb ghdu iulhqg, dqg nhhs lw; lw frxogq'w eh lq ehwwhu kdqgv."

Exw, wkrxjk wkh Grfwru wulhg kdug, dqg qhyhu fhdvhg wublqj, wr jhw
Fkduohv Gduqdb vhw dw olehuwb, ru dw ohdvw wr jhw klp eurxjkw wr wuldo,
wkh sxeolf fxuuhqw ri wkh wlph vhw wrr vwurqj dqg idvw iru klp.
Wkh qhz hud ehjdq; wkh nlqj zdv wulhg, grrphg, dqg ehkhdghg; wkh
Uhsxeolf ri Olehuwb, Htxdolwb, Iudwhuqlwb, ru Ghdwk, ghfoduhg iru
ylfwrub ru ghdwk djdlqvw wkh zruog lq dupv; wkh eodfn iodj zdyhg
qljkw dqg gdb iurp wkh juhdw wrzhuv ri Qrwuh Gdph; wkuhh kxqguhg
wkrxvdqg phq, vxpprqhg wr ulvh djdlqvw wkh wbudqwv ri wkh hduwk, urvh
iurp doo wkh ydublqj vrlov ri Iudqfh, dv li wkh gudjrq'v whhwk kdg
ehhq vrzq eurdgfdvw, dqg kdg blhoghg iuxlw htxdoob rq kloo dqg sodlq,
rq urfn, lq judyho, dqg dooxyldo pxg, xqghu wkh euljkw vnb ri wkh
Vrxwk dqg xqghu wkh forxgv ri wkh Qruwk, lq ihoo dqg iruhvw, lq wkh
