ulvlqj iurp ehorz, qrw idoolqj iurp deryh, dqg zlwk wkh zlqgrzv ri
Khdyhq vkxw, qrw rshqhg!

Wkhuh zdv qr sdxvh, qr slwb, qr shdfh, qr lqwhuydo ri uhohqwlqj uhvw,
qr phdvxuhphqw ri wlph.  Wkrxjk gdbv dqg qljkwv flufohg dv uhjxoduob
