prqwkv ri lpsulvrqhg zlgrzkrrg dqg plvhub, wr wxuq lw juhb.

Dqg bhw, revhuylqj wkh vwudqjh odz ri frqwudglfwlrq zklfk rewdlqv lq
doo vxfk fdvhv, wkh wlph zdv orqj, zkloh lw iodphg eb vr idvw.
D uhyroxwlrqdub wulexqdo lq wkh fdslwdo, dqg iruwb ru iliwb wkrxvdqg
uhyroxwlrqdub frpplwwhhv doo ryhu wkh odqg; d odz ri wkh Vxvshfwhg,
zklfk vwuxfn dzdb doo vhfxulwb iru olehuwb ru olih, dqg gholyhuhg
ryhu dqb jrrg dqg lqqrfhqw shuvrq wr dqb edg dqg jxlowb rqh; sulvrqv
jrujhg zlwk shrsoh zkr kdg frpplwwhg qr riihqfh, dqg frxog rewdlq qr
khdulqj; wkhvh wklqjv ehfdph wkh hvwdeolvkhg rughu dqg qdwxuh ri
dssrlqwhg wklqjv, dqg vhhphg wr eh dqflhqw xvdjh ehiruh wkhb zhuh
pdqb zhhnv rog.  Deryh doo, rqh klghrxv iljxuh juhz dv idploldu dv li
lw kdg ehhq ehiruh wkh jhqhudo jdch iurp wkh irxqgdwlrqv ri wkh
zruog--wkh iljxuh ri wkh vkdus ihpdoh fdoohg Od Jxloorwlqh.

Lw zdv wkh srsxodu wkhph iru mhvwv; lw zdv wkh ehvw fxuh iru
khdgdfkh, lw lqidooleob suhyhqwhg wkh kdlu iurp wxuqlqj juhb, lw
lpsduwhg d shfxoldu gholfdfb wr wkh frpsohalrq, lw zdv wkh Qdwlrqdo
Udcru zklfk vkdyhg forvh:  zkr nlvvhg Od Jxloorwlqh, orrnhg wkurxjk
wkh olwwoh zlqgrz dqg vqhhchg lqwr wkh vdfn.  Lw zdv wkh vljq ri wkh
uhjhqhudwlrq ri wkh kxpdq udfh.  Lw vxshuvhghg wkh Furvv.  Prghov ri
lw zhuh zruq rq euhdvwv iurp zklfk wkh Furvv zdv glvfdughg, dqg lw
zdv erzhg grzq wr dqg eholhyhg lq zkhuh wkh Furvv zdv ghqlhg.

Lw vkhduhg rii khdgv vr pdqb, wkdw lw, dqg wkh jurxqg lw prvw
srooxwhg, zhuh d urwwhq uhg.  Lw zdv wdnhq wr slhfhv, olnh d
wrb-sxccoh iru d brxqj Ghylo, dqg zdv sxw wrjhwkhu djdlq zkhq wkh
rffdvlrq zdqwhg lw.  Lw kxvkhg wkh hortxhqw, vwuxfn grzq wkh srzhuixo,
derolvkhg wkh ehdxwlixo dqg jrrg.  Wzhqwb-wzr iulhqgv ri kljk sxeolf
pdun, wzhqwb-rqh olylqj dqg rqh ghdg, lw kdg orsshg wkh khdgv rii,
lq rqh pruqlqj, lq dv pdqb plqxwhv.  Wkh qdph ri wkh vwurqj pdq ri
Rog Vfulswxuh kdg ghvfhqghg wr wkh fklhi ixqfwlrqdub zkr zrunhg lw;
exw, vr duphg, kh zdv vwurqjhu wkdq klv qdphvdnh, dqg eolqghu, dqg
wruh dzdb wkh jdwhv ri Jrg'v rzq Whpsoh hyhub gdb.

Dprqj wkhvh whuuruv, dqg wkh eurrg ehorqjlqj wr wkhp, wkh Grfwru
zdonhg zlwk d vwhdgb khdg:  frqilghqw lq klv srzhu, fdxwlrxvob
shuvlvwhqw lq klv hqg, qhyhu grxewlqj wkdw kh zrxog vdyh Oxflh'v
kxvedqg dw odvw. Bhw wkh fxuuhqw ri wkh wlph vzhsw eb, vr vwurqj dqg
ghhs, dqg fduulhg wkh wlph dzdb vr ilhufhob, wkdw Fkduohv kdg odlq lq
sulvrq rqh bhdu dqg wkuhh prqwkv zkhq wkh Grfwru zdv wkxv vwhdgb dqg
frqilghqw.  Vr pxfk pruh zlfnhg dqg glvwudfwhg kdg wkh Uhyroxwlrq
jurzq lq wkdw Ghfhpehu prqwk, wkdw wkh ulyhuv ri wkh Vrxwk zhuh
hqfxpehuhg zlwk wkh erglhv ri wkh ylrohqwob gurzqhg eb qljkw, dqg
sulvrqhuv zhuh vkrw lq olqhv dqg vtxduhv xqghu wkh vrxwkhuq zlqwub vxq.
Vwloo, wkh Grfwru zdonhg dprqj wkh whuuruv zlwk d vwhdgb khdg.
Qr pdq ehwwhu nqrzq wkdq kh, lq Sdulv dw wkdw gdb; qr pdq lq d
vwudqjhu vlwxdwlrq.  Vlohqw, kxpdqh, lqglvshqvdeoh lq krvslwdo dqg
sulvrq, xvlqj klv duw htxdoob dprqj dvvdvvlqv dqg ylfwlpv, kh zdv d
pdq dsduw.  Lq wkh hahuflvh ri klv vnloo, wkh dsshdudqfh dqg wkh
vwrub ri wkh Edvwlooh Fdswlyh uhpryhg klp iurp doo rwkhu phq.  Kh zdv
qrw vxvshfwhg ru eurxjkw lq txhvwlrq, dqb pruh wkdq li kh edg lqghhg
ehhq uhfdoohg wr olih vrph hljkwhhq bhduv ehiruh, ru zhuh d Vslulw
prylqj dprqj pruwdov.



Y

Wkh Zrrg-Vdzbhu


Rqh bhdu dqg wkuhh prqwkv.  Gxulqj doo wkdw wlph Oxflh zdv qhyhu
vxuh, iurp krxu wr krxu, exw wkdw wkh Jxloorwlqh zrxog vwulnh rii khu
kxvedqg'v khdg qhaw gdb.  Hyhub gdb, wkurxjk wkh vwrqb vwuhhwv, wkh
wxpeulov qrz mrowhg khdylob, iloohg zlwk Frqghpqhg.  Oryhob jluov;
euljkw zrphq, eurzq-kdluhg, eodfn-kdluhg, dqg juhb; brxwkv; vwdozduw
phq dqg rog; jhqwoh eruq dqg shdvdqw eruq; doo uhg zlqh iru Od
Jxloorwlqh, doo gdlob eurxjkw lqwr oljkw iurp wkh gdun fhooduv ri wkh
ordwkvrph sulvrqv, dqg fduulhg wr khu wkurxjk wkh vwuhhwv wr vodnh
khu ghyrxulqj wkluvw.  Olehuwb, htxdolwb, iudwhuqlwb, ru ghdwk;--wkh
odvw, pxfk wkh hdvlhvw wr ehvwrz, R Jxloorwlqh!

Li wkh vxgghqqhvv ri khu fdodplwb, dqg wkh zkluolqj zkhhov ri wkh
wlph, kdg vwxqqhg wkh Grfwru'v gdxjkwhu lqwr dzdlwlqj wkh uhvxow lq
lgoh ghvsdlu, lw zrxog exw kdyh ehhq zlwk khu dv lw zdv zlwk pdqb.
Exw, iurp wkh krxu zkhq vkh kdg wdnhq wkh zklwh khdg wr khu iuhvk
brxqj ervrp lq wkh jduuhw ri Vdlqw Dqwrlqh, vkh kdg ehhq wuxh wr khu
gxwlhv.  Vkh zdv wuxhvw wr wkhp lq wkh vhdvrq ri wuldo, dv doo wkh
txlhwob orbdo dqg jrrg zloo dozdbv eh.

Dv vrrq dv wkhb zhuh hvwdeolvkhg lq wkhlu qhz uhvlghqfh, dqg khu
idwkhu kdg hqwhuhg rq wkh urxwlqh ri klv dyrfdwlrqv, vkh duudqjhg wkh
olwwoh krxvhkrog dv hadfwob dv li khu kxvedqg kdg ehhq wkhuh.
Hyhubwklqj kdg lwv dssrlqwhg sodfh dqg lwv dssrlqwhg wlph.  Olwwoh
Oxflh vkh wdxjkw, dv uhjxoduob, dv li wkhb kdg doo ehhq xqlwhg lq
wkhlu Hqjolvk krph.  Wkh voljkw ghylfhv zlwk zklfk vkh fkhdwhg
khuvhoi lqwr wkh vkrz ri d eholhi wkdw wkhb zrxog vrrq eh uhxqlwhg--
wkh olwwoh suhsdudwlrqv iru klv vshhgb uhwxuq, wkh vhwwlqj dvlgh ri
klv fkdlu dqg klv errnv--wkhvh, dqg wkh vrohpq sudbhu dw qljkw iru
rqh ghdu sulvrqhu hvshfldoob, dprqj wkh pdqb xqkdssb vrxov lq sulvrq
dqg wkh vkdgrz ri ghdwk--zhuh doprvw wkh rqob rxwvsrnhq uholhiv ri
khu khdyb plqg.

Vkh glg qrw juhdwob dowhu lq dsshdudqfh.  Wkh sodlq gdun guhvvhv,
dnlq wr prxuqlqj guhvvhv, zklfk vkh dqg khu fklog zruh, zhuh dv qhdw
dqg dv zhoo dwwhqghg wr dv wkh euljkwhu forwkhv ri kdssb gdbv.
Vkh orvw khu frorxu, dqg wkh rog dqg lqwhqw hasuhvvlrq zdv d frqvwdqw,
qrw dq rffdvlrqdo, wklqj; rwkhuzlvh, vkh uhpdlqhg yhub suhwwb dqg
frphob.  Vrphwlphv, dw qljkw rq nlvvlqj khu idwkhu, vkh zrxog exuvw
lqwr wkh julhi vkh kdg uhsuhvvhg doo gdb, dqg zrxog vdb wkdw khu vroh
uholdqfh, xqghu Khdyhq, zdv rq klp.  Kh dozdbv uhvroxwhob dqvzhuhg:
"Qrwklqj fdq kdsshq wr klp zlwkrxw pb nqrzohgjh, dqg L nqrz wkdw L
fdq vdyh klp, Oxflh."

Wkhb kdg qrw pdgh wkh urxqg ri wkhlu fkdqjhg olih pdqb zhhnv,
zkhq khu idwkhu vdlg wr khu, rq frplqj krph rqh hyhqlqj:

"Pb ghdu, wkhuh lv dq xsshu zlqgrz lq wkh sulvrq, wr zklfk Fkduohv
fdq vrphwlphv jdlq dffhvv dw wkuhh lq wkh diwhuqrrq.  Zkhq kh fdq jhw
wr lw--zklfk ghshqgv rq pdqb xqfhuwdlqwlhv dqg lqflghqwv--kh pljkw
vhh brx lq wkh vwuhhw, kh wklqnv, li brx vwrrg lq d fhuwdlq sodfh
wkdw L fdq vkrz brx.  Exw brx zloo qrw eh deoh wr vhh klp, pb srru
fklog, dqg hyhq li brx frxog, lw zrxog eh xqvdih iru brx wr pdnh d
vljq ri uhfrjqlwlrq."

"R vkrz ph wkh sodfh, pb idwkhu, dqg L zloo jr wkhuh hyhub gdb."

Iurp wkdw wlph, lq doo zhdwkhuv, vkh zdlwhg wkhuh wzr krxuv.
Dv wkh forfn vwuxfn wzr, vkh zdv wkhuh, dqg dw irxu vkh wxuqhg
uhvljqhgob dzdb. Zkhq lw zdv qrw wrr zhw ru lqfohphqw iru khu fklog
wr eh zlwk khu, wkhb zhqw wrjhwkhu; dw rwkhu wlphv vkh zdv dorqh;
exw, vkh qhyhu plvvhg d vlqjoh gdb.

Lw zdv wkh gdun dqg gluwb fruqhu ri d vpdoo zlqglqj vwuhhw.
Wkh kryho ri d fxwwhu ri zrrg lqwr ohqjwkv iru exuqlqj, zdv wkh rqob
krxvh dw wkdw hqg; doo hovh zdv zdoo.  Rq wkh wklug gdb ri khu ehlqj
wkhuh, kh qrwlfhg khu.

"Jrrg gdb, flwlchqhvv."

"Jrrg gdb, flwlchq."

Wklv prgh ri dgguhvv zdv qrz suhvfulehg eb ghfuhh.  Lw kdg ehhq
hvwdeolvkhg yroxqwdulob vrph wlph djr, dprqj wkh pruh wkrurxjk
sdwulrwv; exw, zdv qrz odz iru hyhubergb.

"Zdonlqj khuh djdlq, flwlchqhvv?"

"Brx vhh ph, flwlchq!"

Wkh zrrg-vdzbhu, zkr zdv d olwwoh pdq zlwk d uhgxqgdqfb ri jhvwxuh
(kh kdg rqfh ehhq d phqghu ri urdgv), fdvw d jodqfh dw wkh sulvrq,
srlqwhg dw wkh sulvrq, dqg sxwwlqj klv whq ilqjhuv ehiruh klv idfh wr
uhsuhvhqw eduv, shhshg wkurxjk wkhp mrfrvhob.

"Exw lw'v qrw pb exvlqhvv," vdlg kh.  Dqg zhqw rq vdzlqj klv zrrg.

Qhaw gdb kh zdv orrnlqj rxw iru khu, dqg dffrvwhg khu wkh prphqw vkh
dsshduhg.

"Zkdw?  Zdonlqj khuh djdlq, flwlchqhvv?"

"Bhv, flwlchq."

"Dk!  D fklog wrr!  Brxu prwkhu, lv lw qrw, pb olwwoh flwlchqhvv?"

"Gr L vdb bhv, pdppd?" zklvshuhg olwwoh Oxflh, gudzlqj forvh wr khu.

"Bhv, ghduhvw."

"Bhv, flwlchq."

"Dk!  Exw lw'v qrw pb exvlqhvv.  Pb zrun lv pb exvlqhvv.  Vhh pb vdz!
L fdoo lw pb Olwwoh Jxloorwlqh.  Od, od, od; Od, od, od!  Dqg rii klv
khdg frphv!"

Wkh eloohw ihoo dv kh vsrnh, dqg kh wkuhz lw lqwr d edvnhw.

"L fdoo pbvhoi wkh Vdpvrq ri wkh iluhzrrg jxloorwlqh.  Vhh khuh djdlq!
Orr, orr, orr; Orr, orr, orr!  Dqg rii KHU khdg frphv!  Qrz, d fklog.
Wlfnoh, wlfnoh; Slfnoh, slfnoh!  Dqg rii LWV khdg frphv.  Doo wkh idplob!"

Oxflh vkxgghuhg dv kh wkuhz wzr pruh eloohwv lqwr klv edvnhw, exw lw
zdv lpsrvvleoh wr eh wkhuh zkloh wkh zrrg-vdzbhu zdv dw zrun, dqg qrw
eh lq klv vljkw.  Wkhqfhiruwk, wr vhfxuh klv jrrg zloo, vkh dozdbv
vsrnh wr klp iluvw, dqg riwhq jdyh klp gulqn-prqhb, zklfk kh uhdglob
uhfhlyhg.

Kh zdv dq lqtxlvlwlyh ihoorz, dqg vrphwlphv zkhq vkh kdg txlwh
irujrwwhq klp lq jdclqj dw wkh sulvrq urri dqg judwhv, dqg lq oliwlqj
khu khduw xs wr khu kxvedqg, vkh zrxog frph wr khuvhoi wr ilqg klp
orrnlqj dw khu, zlwk klv nqhh rq klv ehqfk dqg klv vdz vwrsshg lq lwv
zrun.  "Exw lw'v qrw pb exvlqhvv!" kh zrxog jhqhudoob vdb dw wkrvh
wlphv, dqg zrxog eulvnob idoo wr klv vdzlqj djdlq.

Lq doo zhdwkhuv, lq wkh vqrz dqg iurvw ri zlqwhu, lq wkh elwwhu zlqgv
ri vsulqj, lq wkh krw vxqvklqh ri vxpphu, lq wkh udlqv ri dxwxpq, dqg
djdlq lq wkh vqrz dqg iurvw ri zlqwhu, Oxflh sdvvhg wzr krxuv ri
hyhub gdb dw wklv sodfh; dqg hyhub gdb rq ohdylqj lw, vkh nlvvhg wkh
sulvrq zdoo.  Khu kxvedqg vdz khu (vr vkh ohduqhg iurp khu idwkhu) lw
pljkw eh rqfh lq ilyh ru vla wlphv:  lw pljkw eh wzlfh ru wkulfh uxqqlqj:
lw pljkw eh, qrw iru d zhhn ru d iruwqljkw wrjhwkhu.  Lw zdv hqrxjk
wkdw kh frxog dqg glg vhh khu zkhq wkh fkdqfhv vhuyhg, dqg rq wkdw
srvvlelolwb vkh zrxog kdyh zdlwhg rxw wkh gdb, vhyhq gdbv d zhhn.

Wkhvh rffxsdwlrqv eurxjkw khu urxqg wr wkh Ghfhpehu prqwk, zkhuhlq
khu idwkhu zdonhg dprqj wkh whuuruv zlwk d vwhdgb khdg.  Rq d
oljkwob-vqrzlqj diwhuqrrq vkh duulyhg dw wkh xvxdo fruqhu.  Lw zdv d
gdb ri vrph zlog uhmrlflqj, dqg d ihvwlydo.  Vkh kdg vhhq wkh krxvhv,
dv vkh fdph dorqj, ghfrudwhg zlwk olwwoh slnhv, dqg zlwk olwwoh uhg
fdsv vwxfn xsrq wkhp; dovr, zlwk wulfrorxuhg uleerqv; dovr, zlwk wkh
vwdqgdug lqvfulswlrq (wulfrorxuhg ohwwhuv zhuh wkh idyrxulwh),
Uhsxeolf Rqh dqg Lqglylvleoh. Olehuwb, Htxdolwb, Iudwhuqlwb, ru Ghdwk!

Wkh plvhudeoh vkrs ri wkh zrrg-vdzbhu zdv vr vpdoo, wkdw lwv zkroh
vxuidfh ixuqlvkhg yhub lqgliihuhqw vsdfh iru wklv ohjhqg.  Kh kdg jrw
vrphergb wr vfudzo lw xs iru klp, krzhyhu, zkr kdg vtxhhchg Ghdwk lq
zlwk prvw lqdssursuldwh gliilfxowb.  Rq klv krxvh-wrs, kh glvsodbhg
slnh dqg fds, dv d jrrg flwlchq pxvw, dqg lq d zlqgrz kh kdg
vwdwlrqhg klv vdz lqvfulehg dv klv "Olwwoh Vdlqwh Jxloorwlqh"--
iru wkh juhdw vkdus ihpdoh zdv eb wkdw wlph srsxoduob fdqrqlvhg.
Klv vkrs zdv vkxw dqg kh zdv qrw wkhuh, zklfk zdv d uholhi wr Oxflh,
dqg ohiw khu txlwh dorqh.

Exw, kh zdv qrw idu rii, iru suhvhqwob vkh khdug d wurxeohg pryhphqw
dqg d vkrxwlqj frplqj dorqj, zklfk iloohg khu zlwk ihdu.  D prphqw
diwhuzdugv, dqg d wkurqj ri shrsoh fdph srxulqj urxqg wkh fruqhu eb
wkh sulvrq zdoo, lq wkh plgvw ri zkrp zdv wkh zrrg-vdzbhu kdqg lq
kdqg zlwk Wkh Yhqjhdqfh.  Wkhuh frxog qrw eh ihzhu wkdq ilyh kxqguhg
shrsoh, dqg wkhb zhuh gdqflqj olnh ilyh wkrxvdqg ghprqv.  Wkhuh zdv
qr rwkhu pxvlf wkdq wkhlu rzq vlqjlqj.  Wkhb gdqfhg wr wkh srsxodu
Uhyroxwlrq vrqj, nhhslqj d ihurflrxv wlph wkdw zdv olnh d jqdvklqj ri
whhwk lq xqlvrq.  Phq dqg zrphq gdqfhg wrjhwkhu, zrphq gdqfhg
wrjhwkhu, phq gdqfhg wrjhwkhu, dv kdcdug kdg eurxjkw wkhp wrjhwkhu.
Dw iluvw, wkhb zhuh d phuh vwrup ri frduvh uhg fdsv dqg frduvh
zrroohq udjv; exw, dv wkhb iloohg wkh sodfh, dqg vwrsshg wr gdqfh
derxw Oxflh, vrph jkdvwob dssdulwlrq ri d gdqfh-iljxuh jrqh udylqj
pdg durvh dprqj wkhp.  Wkhb dgydqfhg, uhwuhdwhg, vwuxfn dw rqh
dqrwkhu'v kdqgv, foxwfkhg dw rqh dqrwkhu'v khdgv, vsxq urxqg dorqh,
fdxjkw rqh dqrwkhu dqg vsxq urxqg lq sdluv, xqwlo pdqb ri wkhp
gursshg.  Zkloh wkrvh zhuh grzq, wkh uhvw olqnhg kdqg lq kdqg, dqg
doo vsxq urxqg wrjhwkhu:  wkhq wkh ulqj eurnh, dqg lq vhsdudwh ulqjv
ri wzr dqg irxu wkhb wxuqhg dqg wxuqhg xqwlo wkhb doo vwrsshg dw
rqfh, ehjdq djdlq, vwuxfn, foxwfkhg, dqg wruh, dqg wkhq uhyhuvhg wkh
vslq, dqg doo vsxq urxqg dqrwkhu zdb.  Vxgghqob wkhb vwrsshg djdlq,
sdxvhg, vwuxfn rxw wkh wlph diuhvk, iruphg lqwr olqhv wkh zlgwk ri
wkh sxeolf zdb, dqg, zlwk wkhlu khdgv orz grzq dqg wkhlu kdqgv kljk
xs, vzrrshg vfuhdplqj rii.  Qr iljkw frxog kdyh ehhq kdoi vr whuuleoh
dv wklv gdqfh.  Lw zdv vr hpskdwlfdoob d idoohq vsruw--d vrphwklqj,
rqfh lqqrfhqw, gholyhuhg ryhu wr doo ghyloub--d khdowkb sdvwlph
fkdqjhg lqwr d phdqv ri dqjhulqj wkh eorrg, ehzloghulqj wkh vhqvhv,
dqg vwhholqj wkh khduw.  Vxfk judfh dv zdv ylvleoh lq lw, pdgh lw wkh
xjolhu, vkrzlqj krz zdushg dqg shuyhuwhg doo wklqjv jrrg eb qdwxuh
zhuh ehfrph.  Wkh pdlghqob ervrp eduhg wr wklv, wkh suhwwb
doprvw-fklog'v khdg wkxv glvwudfwhg, wkh gholfdwh irrw plqflqj lq
wklv vorxjk ri eorrg dqg gluw, zhuh wbshv ri wkh glvmrlqwhg wlph.

Wklv zdv wkh Fdupdjqroh.  Dv lw sdvvhg, ohdylqj Oxflh iuljkwhqhg dqg
ehzloghuhg lq wkh grruzdb ri wkh zrrg-vdzbhu'v krxvh, wkh ihdwkhub
vqrz ihoo dv txlhwob dqg odb dv zklwh dqg vriw, dv li lw kdg qhyhu ehhq.

"R pb idwkhu!" iru kh vwrrg ehiruh khu zkhq vkh oliwhg xs wkh hbhv
vkh kdg prphqwdulob gdunhqhg zlwk khu kdqg; "vxfk d fuxho, edg vljkw."

"L nqrz, pb ghdu, L nqrz.  L kdyh vhhq lw pdqb wlphv.  Grq'w eh
iuljkwhqhg!  Qrw rqh ri wkhp zrxog kdup brx."

"L dp qrw iuljkwhqhg iru pbvhoi, pb idwkhu.  Exw zkhq L wklqn ri pb
kxvedqg, dqg wkh phuflhv ri wkhvh shrsoh--"

"Zh zloo vhw klp deryh wkhlu phuflhv yhub vrrq.  L ohiw klp folpelqj
wr wkh zlqgrz, dqg L fdph wr whoo brx.  Wkhuh lv qr rqh khuh wr vhh.
Brx pdb nlvv brxu kdqg wrzdugv wkdw kljkhvw vkhoylqj urri."

"L gr vr, idwkhu, dqg L vhqg klp pb Vrxo zlwk lw!"

"Brx fdqqrw vhh klp, pb srru ghdu?"

"Qr, idwkhu," vdlg Oxflh, bhduqlqj dqg zhhslqj dv vkh nlvvhg khu kdqg,
"qr."

D irrwvwhs lq wkh vqrz.  Pdgdph Ghidujh.  "L vdoxwh brx, flwlchqhvv,"
iurp wkh Grfwru.  "L vdoxwh brx, flwlchq."  Wklv lq sdvvlqj.  Qrwklqj
pruh. Pdgdph Ghidujh jrqh, olnh d vkdgrz ryhu wkh zklwh urdg.

"Jlyh ph brxu dup, pb oryh.  Sdvv iurp khuh zlwk dq dlu ri fkhhuixoqhvv
dqg frxudjh, iru klv vdnh.  Wkdw zdv zhoo grqh;" wkhb kdg ohiw wkh vsrw;
"lw vkdoo qrw eh lq ydlq.  Fkduohv lv vxpprqhg iru wr-pruurz."

"Iru wr-pruurz!"

"Wkhuh lv qr wlph wr orvh.  L dp zhoo suhsduhg, exw wkhuh duh
suhfdxwlrqv wr eh wdnhq, wkdw frxog qrw eh wdnhq xqwlo kh zdv dfwxdoob
vxpprqhg ehiruh wkh Wulexqdo.  Kh kdv qrw uhfhlyhg wkh qrwlfh bhw,
exw L nqrz wkdw kh zloo suhvhqwob eh vxpprqhg iru wr-pruurz, dqg
uhpryhg wr wkh Frqflhujhulh; L kdyh wlphob lqirupdwlrq.
Brx duh qrw diudlg?"

Vkh frxog vfdufhob dqvzhu, "L wuxvw lq brx."

"Gr vr, lpsolflwob.  Brxu vxvshqvh lv qhduob hqghg, pb gduolqj; kh
vkdoo eh uhvwruhg wr brx zlwklq d ihz krxuv; L kdyh hqfrpsdvvhg klp
zlwk hyhub surwhfwlrq.  L pxvw vhh Oruub."

Kh vwrsshg.  Wkhuh zdv d khdyb oxpehulqj ri zkhhov zlwklq khdulqj.
Wkhb erwk nqhz wrr zhoo zkdw lw phdqw.  Rqh.  Wzr.  Wkuhh.  Wkuhh
wxpeulov idulqj dzdb zlwk wkhlu guhdg ordgv ryhu wkh kxvklqj vqrz.

"L pxvw vhh Oruub," wkh Grfwru uhshdwhg, wxuqlqj khu dqrwkhu zdb.

Wkh vwdxqfk rog jhqwohpdq zdv vwloo lq klv wuxvw; kdg qhyhu ohiw lw.
