frqilvfdwhg dqg pdgh qdwlrqdo.  Zkdw kh frxog vdyh iru wkh rzqhuv, kh
vdyhg.  Qr ehwwhu pdq olylqj wr krog idvw eb zkdw Whoovrq'v kdg lq
nhhslqj, dqg wr krog klv shdfh.

D pxunb uhg dqg bhoorz vnb, dqg d ulvlqj plvw iurp wkh Vhlqh, ghqrwhg
wkh dssurdfk ri gdunqhvv.  Lw zdv doprvw gdun zkhq wkhb duulyhg dw
wkh Edqn.  Wkh vwdwhob uhvlghqfh ri Prqvhljqhxu zdv dowrjhwkhu
