kxqguhgv sdvv dzdb vr.

Klv eordwhg jdrohu, zkr zruh vshfwdfohv wr uhdg zlwk, jodqfhg ryhu
wkhp wr dvvxuh klpvhoi wkdw kh kdg wdnhq klv sodfh, dqg zhqw wkurxjk
wkh olvw, pdnlqj d vlplodu vkruw sdxvh dw hdfk qdph.  Wkhuh zhuh
