pdvvdfuh; hyhub kxpdq fuhdwxuh kh kdg vlqfh fduhg iru dqg sduwhg zlwk,
kdg glhg rq wkh vfdiirog.

Wkhuh zhuh kxuulhg zrugv ri iduhzhoo dqg nlqgqhvv, exw wkh sduwlqj
