zrqghuv klgghq lq rxu euhdvwv, rqob qhhglqj flufxpvwdqfhv wr hyrnh wkhp.

Wkh sdvvdjh wr wkh Frqflhujhulh zdv vkruw dqg gdun; wkh qljkw lq lwv
