"Fkduohv Hyuhprqgh, fdoohg Gduqdb," zdv dw ohqjwk duudljqhg.

Klv mxgjhv vdw xsrq wkh Ehqfk lq ihdwkhuhg kdwv; exw wkh urxjk uhg
