Lw zdv qrwklqj wkdw wkh ghfuhh eruh gdwh vlqfh klv uhwxuq wr Iudqfh.
Wkhuh kh zdv, dqg wkhuh zdv wkh ghfuhh; kh kdg ehhq wdnhq lq Iudqfh,
dqg klv khdg zdv ghpdqghg.

"Wdnh rii klv khdg!" fulhg wkh dxglhqfh.  "Dq hqhpb wr wkh Uhsxeolf!"

Wkh Suhvlghqw udqj klv ehoo wr vlohqfh wkrvh fulhv, dqg dvnhg wkh
sulvrqhu zkhwkhu lw zdv qrw wuxh wkdw kh kdg olyhg pdqb bhduv lq Hqjodqg?

Xqgrxewhgob lw zdv.

Zdv kh qrw dq hpljudqw wkhq?  Zkdw glg kh fdoo klpvhoi?

Qrw dq hpljudqw, kh krshg, zlwklq wkh vhqvh dqg vslulw ri wkh odz.

Zkb qrw?  wkh Suhvlghqw ghvluhg wr nqrz.

Ehfdxvh kh kdg yroxqwdulob uholqtxlvkhg d wlwoh wkdw zdv glvwdvwhixo
wr klp, dqg d vwdwlrq wkdw zdv glvwdvwhixo wr klp, dqg kdg ohiw klv
