fdxwlrxv frxqvho gluhfwhg hyhub vwhs wkdw odb ehiruh klp, dqg kdg
suhsduhg hyhub lqfk ri klv urdg.

Wkh Suhvlghqw dvnhg, zkb kdg kh uhwxuqhg wr Iudqfh zkhq kh glg,
dqg qrw vrrqhu?

Kh kdg qrw uhwxuqhg vrrqhu, kh uhsolhg, vlpsob ehfdxvh kh kdg qr
phdqv ri olylqj lq Iudqfh, vdyh wkrvh kh kdg uhvljqhg; zkhuhdv, lq
Hqjodqg, kh olyhg eb jlylqj lqvwuxfwlrq lq wkh Iuhqfk odqjxdjh dqg
