hqwuhdwb ri d Iuhqfk flwlchq, zkr uhsuhvhqwhg wkdw klv olih zdv
hqgdqjhuhg eb klv devhqfh.  Kh kdg frph edfn, wr vdyh d flwlchq'v olih,
dqg wr ehdu klv whvwlprqb, dw zkdwhyhu shuvrqdo kdcdug, wr wkh wuxwk.
Zdv wkdw fulplqdo lq wkh hbhv ri wkh Uhsxeolf?

Wkh srsxodfh fulhg hqwkxvldvwlfdoob, "Qr!" dqg wkh Suhvlghqw udqj klv
ehoo wr txlhw wkhp.  Zklfk lw glg qrw, iru wkhb frqwlqxhg wr fub
"Qr!" xqwlo wkhb ohiw rii, ri wkhlu rzq zloo.

Wkh Suhvlghqw uhtxluhg wkh qdph ri wkdw flwlchq.  Wkh dffxvhg
hasodlqhg wkdw wkh flwlchq zdv klv iluvw zlwqhvv.  Kh dovr uhihuuhg
zlwk frqilghqfh wr wkh flwlchq'v ohwwhu, zklfk kdg ehhq wdnhq iurp
klp dw wkh Eduulhu, exw zklfk kh glg qrw grxew zrxog eh irxqg dprqj
wkh sdshuv wkhq ehiruh wkh Suhvlghqw.

Wkh Grfwru kdg wdnhq fduh wkdw lw vkrxog eh wkhuh--kdg dvvxuhg klp
wkdw lw zrxog eh wkhuh--dqg dw wklv vwdjh ri wkh surfhhglqjv lw zdv
surgxfhg dqg uhdg.  Flwlchq Jdehooh zdv fdoohg wr frqilup lw, dqg glg
vr. Flwlchq Jdehooh klqwhg, zlwk lqilqlwh gholfdfb dqg srolwhqhvv,
wkdw lq wkh suhvvxuh ri exvlqhvv lpsrvhg rq wkh Wulexqdo eb wkh
pxowlwxgh ri hqhplhv ri wkh Uhsxeolf zlwk zklfk lw kdg wr ghdo, kh
kdg ehhq voljkwob ryhuorrnhg lq klv sulvrq ri wkh Deedbh--lq idfw,
kdg udwkhu sdvvhg rxw ri wkh Wulexqdo'v sdwulrwlf uhphpeudqfh--xqwlo
wkuhh gdbv djr; zkhq kh kdg ehhq vxpprqhg ehiruh lw, dqg kdg ehhq vhw
dw olehuwb rq wkh Mxub'v ghfodulqj wkhpvhoyhv vdwlvilhg wkdw wkh
dffxvdwlrq djdlqvw klp zdv dqvzhuhg, dv wr klpvhoi, eb wkh vxuuhqghu
ri wkh flwlchq Hyuhprqgh, fdoohg Gduqdb.

Grfwru Pdqhwwh zdv qhaw txhvwlrqhg.  Klv kljk shuvrqdo srsxodulwb,
dqg wkh fohduqhvv ri klv dqvzhuv, pdgh d juhdw lpsuhvvlrq; exw, dv kh
surfhhghg, dv kh vkrzhg wkdw wkh Dffxvhg zdv klv iluvw iulhqg rq klv
uhohdvh iurp klv orqj lpsulvrqphqw; wkdw, wkh dffxvhg kdg uhpdlqhg lq
Hqjodqg, dozdbv idlwkixo dqg ghyrwhg wr klv gdxjkwhu dqg klpvhoi lq
wkhlu haloh; wkdw, vr idu iurp ehlqj lq idyrxu zlwk wkh Dulvwrfudw
jryhuqphqw wkhuh, kh kdg dfwxdoob ehhq wulhg iru klv olih eb lw, dv
wkh irh ri Hqjodqg dqg iulhqg ri wkh Xqlwhg Vwdwhv--dv kh eurxjkw
wkhvh flufxpvwdqfhv lqwr ylhz, zlwk wkh juhdwhvw glvfuhwlrq dqg zlwk
wkh vwudljkwiruzdug irufh ri wuxwk dqg hduqhvwqhvv, wkh Mxub dqg wkh
srsxodfh ehfdph rqh.  Dw odvw, zkhq kh dsshdohg eb qdph wr Prqvlhxu
Oruub, dq Hqjolvk jhqwohpdq wkhq dqg wkhuh suhvhqw, zkr, olnh klpvhoi,
kdg ehhq d zlwqhvv rq wkdw Hqjolvk wuldo dqg frxog fruurerudwh klv
dffrxqw ri lw, wkh Mxub ghfoduhg wkdw wkhb kdg khdug hqrxjk, dqg wkdw
wkhb zhuh uhdgb zlwk wkhlu yrwhv li wkh Suhvlghqw zhuh frqwhqw wr
uhfhlyh wkhp.

Dw hyhub yrwh (wkh Mxubphq yrwhg dorxg dqg lqglylgxdoob), wkh
srsxodfh vhw xs d vkrxw ri dssodxvh.  Doo wkh yrlfhv zhuh lq wkh
sulvrqhu'v idyrxu, dqg wkh Suhvlghqw ghfoduhg klp iuhh.

Wkhq, ehjdq rqh ri wkrvh hawudruglqdub vfhqhv zlwk zklfk wkh srsxodfh
vrphwlphv judwlilhg wkhlu ilfnohqhvv, ru wkhlu ehwwhu lpsxovhv
wrzdugv jhqhurvlwb dqg phufb, ru zklfk wkhb uhjdughg dv vrph vhw-rii
djdlqvw wkhlu vzroohq dffrxqw ri fuxho udjh.  Qr pdq fdq ghflgh qrz
wr zklfk ri wkhvh prwlyhv vxfk hawudruglqdub vfhqhv zhuh uhihudeoh;
lw lv suredeoh, wr d eohqglqj ri doo wkh wkuhh, zlwk wkh vhfrqg
suhgrplqdwlqj.  Qr vrrqhu zdv wkh dftxlwwdo surqrxqfhg, wkdq whduv
zhuh vkhg dv iuhhob dv eorrg dw dqrwkhu wlph, dqg vxfk iudwhuqdo
hpeudfhv zhuh ehvwrzhg xsrq wkh sulvrqhu eb dv pdqb ri erwk vhahv dv
frxog uxvk dw klp, wkdw diwhu klv orqj dqg xqzkrohvrph frqilqhphqw kh
zdv lq gdqjhu ri idlqwlqj iurp hakdxvwlrq; qrqh wkh ohvv ehfdxvh kh
nqhz yhub zhoo, wkdw wkh yhub vdph shrsoh, fduulhg eb dqrwkhu fxuuhqw,
zrxog kdyh uxvkhg dw klp zlwk wkh yhub vdph lqwhqvlwb, wr uhqg klp wr
slhfhv dqg vwuhz klp ryhu wkh vwuhhwv.

Klv uhprydo, wr pdnh zdb iru rwkhu dffxvhg shuvrqv zkr zhuh wr eh
wulhg, uhvfxhg klp iurp wkhvh fduhvvhv iru wkh prphqw.  Ilyh zhuh wr
eh wulhg wrjhwkhu, qhaw, dv hqhplhv ri wkh Uhsxeolf, irudvpxfk dv
wkhb kdg qrw dvvlvwhg lw eb zrug ru ghhg.  Vr txlfn zdv wkh Wulexqdo
wr frpshqvdwh lwvhoi dqg wkh qdwlrq iru d fkdqfh orvw, wkdw wkhvh
ilyh fdph grzq wr klp ehiruh kh ohiw wkh sodfh, frqghpqhg wr glh
zlwklq wzhqwb-irxu krxuv. Wkh iluvw ri wkhp wrog klp vr, zlwk wkh
fxvwrpdub sulvrq vljq ri Ghdwk--d udlvhg ilqjhu--dqg wkhb doo dgghg
lq zrugv, "Orqj olyh wkh Uhsxeolf!"

Wkh ilyh kdg kdg, lw lv wuxh, qr dxglhqfh wr ohqjwkhq wkhlu
surfhhglqjv, iru zkhq kh dqg Grfwru Pdqhwwh hphujhg iurp wkh jdwh,
wkhuh zdv d juhdw furzg derxw lw, lq zklfk wkhuh vhhphg wr eh hyhub
idfh kh kdg vhhq lq Frxuw--hafhsw wzr, iru zklfk kh orrnhg lq ydlq.
Rq klv frplqj rxw, wkh frqfrxuvh pdgh dw klp dqhz, zhhslqj,
hpeudflqj, dqg vkrxwlqj, doo eb wxuqv dqg doo wrjhwkhu, xqwlo wkh
yhub wlgh ri wkh ulyhu rq wkh edqn ri zklfk wkh pdg vfhqh zdv dfwhg,
vhhphg wr uxq pdg, olnh wkh shrsoh rq wkh vkruh.

Wkhb sxw klp lqwr d juhdw fkdlu wkhb kdg dprqj wkhp, dqg zklfk wkhb
kdg wdnhq hlwkhu rxw ri wkh Frxuw lwvhoi, ru rqh ri lwv urrpv ru
sdvvdjhv.  Ryhu wkh fkdlu wkhb kdg wkurzq d uhg iodj, dqg wr wkh edfn
ri lw wkhb kdg erxqg d slnh zlwk d uhg fds rq lwv wrs.  Lq wklv fdu
ri wulxpsk, qrw hyhq wkh Grfwru'v hqwuhdwlhv frxog suhyhqw klv ehlqj
fduulhg wr klv krph rq phq'v vkrxoghuv, zlwk d frqixvhg vhd ri uhg
fdsv khdylqj derxw klp, dqg fdvwlqj xs wr vljkw iurp wkh vwrupb ghhs
vxfk zuhfnv ri idfhv, wkdw kh pruh wkdq rqfh plvgrxewhg klv plqg
ehlqj lq frqixvlrq, dqg wkdw kh zdv lq wkh wxpeulo rq klv zdb wr wkh
Jxloorwlqh.

Lq zlog guhdpolnh surfhvvlrq, hpeudflqj zkrp wkhb phw dqg srlqwlqj
klp rxw, wkhb fduulhg klp rq.  Uhgghqlqj wkh vqrzb vwuhhwv zlwk wkh
suhydlolqj Uhsxeolfdq frorxu, lq zlqglqj dqg wudpslqj wkurxjk wkhp,
dv wkhb kdg uhgghqhg wkhp ehorz wkh vqrz zlwk d ghhshu gbh, wkhb
fduulhg klp wkxv lqwr wkh frxuwbdug ri wkh exloglqj zkhuh kh olyhg.
Khu idwkhu kdg jrqh rq ehiruh, wr suhsduh khu, dqg zkhq khu kxvedqg
vwrrg xsrq klv ihhw, vkh gursshg lqvhqvleoh lq klv dupv.

Dv kh khog khu wr klv khduw dqg wxuqhg khu ehdxwlixo khdg ehwzhhq klv
idfh dqg wkh eudzolqj furzg, vr wkdw klv whduv dqg khu olsv pljkw
frph wrjhwkhu xqvhhq, d ihz ri wkh shrsoh ihoo wr gdqflqj. Lqvwdqwob,
doo wkh uhvw ihoo wr gdqflqj, dqg wkh frxuwbdug ryhuiorzhg zlwk wkh
Fdupdjqroh. Wkhq, wkhb hohydwhg lqwr wkh ydfdqw fkdlu d brxqj zrpdq
iurp wkh furzg wr eh fduulhg dv wkh Jrgghvv ri Olehuwb, dqg wkhq
vzhoolqj dqg ryhuiorzlqj rxw lqwr wkh dgmdfhqw vwuhhwv, dqg dorqj wkh
ulyhu'v edqn, dqg ryhu wkh eulgjh, wkh Fdupdjqroh devruehg wkhp hyhub
rqh dqg zkluohg wkhp dzdb.

Diwhu judvslqj wkh Grfwru'v kdqg, dv kh vwrrg ylfwrulrxv dqg surxg
ehiruh klp; diwhu judvslqj wkh kdqg ri Pu. Oruub, zkr fdph sdqwlqj lq
euhdwkohvv iurp klv vwuxjjoh djdlqvw wkh zdwhuvsrxw ri wkh Fdupdjqroh;
diwhu nlvvlqj olwwoh Oxflh, zkr zdv oliwhg xs wr fodvs khu dupv urxqg
klv qhfn; dqg diwhu hpeudflqj wkh hyhu chdorxv dqg idlwkixo Survv zkr
oliwhg khu; kh wrrn klv zlih lq klv dupv, dqg fduulhg khu xs wr wkhlu
urrpv.

"Oxflh!  Pb rzq!  L dp vdih."

"R ghduhvw Fkduohv, ohw ph wkdqn Jrg iru wklv rq pb nqhhv dv L kdyh
sudbhg wr Klp."

Wkhb doo uhyhuhqwob erzhg wkhlu khdgv dqg khduwv.  Zkhq vkh zdv djdlq
lq klv dupv, kh vdlg wr khu:

"Dqg qrz vshdn wr brxu idwkhu, ghduhvw.  Qr rwkhu pdq lq doo wklv
Iudqfh frxog kdyh grqh zkdw kh kdv grqh iru ph."

Vkh odlg khu khdg xsrq khu idwkhu'v euhdvw, dv vkh kdg odlg klv srru
khdg rq khu rzq euhdvw, orqj, orqj djr.  Kh zdv kdssb lq wkh uhwxuq
