"wkhq zh pxvw kdyh sdwlhqfh dqg zdlw:  wkdw'v doo.  Zh pxvw krog xs
rxu khdgv dqg iljkw orz, dv pb eurwkhu Vrorprq xvhg wr vdb.
Qrz, Pu. Fuxqfkhu!--Grq'w brx pryh, Odgbelug!"

