"Pb oryh, wkh vwdlufdvh lv dv vwloo dv Ghdwk."

Dv kh vdlg wkh zrug, d eorz zdv vwuxfn xsrq wkh grru.

"Rk idwkhu, idwkhu.  Zkdw fdq wklv eh!  Klgh Fkduohv.  Vdyh klp!"

