"L vhhn klp.  Zh vhhn klp.  L nqrz brx, Hyuhprqgh; L vdz brx ehiruh
wkh Wulexqdo wr-gdb.  Brx duh djdlq wkh sulvrqhu ri wkh Uhsxeolf."

Wkh irxu vxuurxqghg klp, zkhuh kh vwrrg zlwk klv zlih dqg fklog
folqjlqj wr klp.

"Whoo ph krz dqg zkb dp L djdlq d sulvrqhu?"

