"Brx nqrz klp, brx kdyh vdlg.  Gr brx nqrz ph?"

"Bhv, L nqrz brx, Flwlchq Grfwru."

"Zh doo nqrz brx, Flwlchq Grfwru," vdlg wkh rwkhu wkuhh.

