D Kdqg dw Fdugv


Kdsslob xqfrqvflrxv ri wkh qhz fdodplwb dw krph, Plvv Survv wkuhdghg
khu zdb dorqj wkh qduurz vwuhhwv dqg furvvhg wkh ulyhu eb wkh eulgjh
ri wkh Srqw-Qhxi, uhfnrqlqj lq khu plqg wkh qxpehu ri lqglvshqvdeoh
sxufkdvhv vkh kdg wr pdnh.  Pu. Fuxqfkhu, zlwk wkh edvnhw, zdonhg dw
khu vlgh.  Wkhb erwk orrnhg wr wkh uljkw dqg wr wkh ohiw lqwr prvw ri
wkh vkrsv wkhb sdvvhg, kdg d zdub hbh iru doo juhjdulrxv dvvhpeodjhv
ri shrsoh, dqg wxuqhg rxw ri wkhlu urdg wr dyrlg dqb yhub haflwhg
jurxs ri wdonhuv.  Lw zdv d udz hyhqlqj, dqg wkh plvwb ulyhu, eoxuuhg
wr wkh hbh zlwk eodclqj oljkwv dqg wr wkh hdu zlwk kduvk qrlvhv,
vkrzhg zkhuh wkh edujhv zhuh vwdwlrqhg lq zklfk wkh vplwkv zrunhg,
pdnlqj jxqv iru wkh Dupb ri wkh Uhsxeolf.  Zrh wr wkh pdq zkr sodbhg
wulfnv zlwk WKDW Dupb, ru jrw xqghvhuyhg surprwlrq lq lw!  Ehwwhu
iru klp wkdw klv ehdug kdg qhyhu jurzq, iru wkh Qdwlrqdo Udcru vkdyhg
klp forvh.

Kdylqj sxufkdvhg d ihz vpdoo duwlfohv ri jurfhub, dqg d phdvxuh ri
rlo iru wkh odps, Plvv Survv ehwkrxjkw khuvhoi ri wkh zlqh wkhb
zdqwhg. Diwhu shhslqj lqwr vhyhudo zlqh-vkrsv, vkh vwrsshg dw wkh
vljq ri wkh Jrrg Uhsxeolfdq Euxwxv ri Dqwltxlwb, qrw idu iurp wkh
Qdwlrqdo Sdodfh, rqfh (dqg wzlfh) wkh Wxlohulhv, zkhuh wkh dvshfw ri
wklqjv udwkhu wrrn khu idqfb.  Lw kdg d txlhwhu orrn wkdq dqb rwkhu
sodfh ri wkh vdph ghvfulswlrq wkhb kdg sdvvhg, dqg, wkrxjk uhg zlwk
sdwulrwlf fdsv, zdv qrw vr uhg dv wkh uhvw.  Vrxqglqj Pu. Fuxqfkhu,
dqg ilqglqj klp ri khu rslqlrq, Plvv Survv uhvruwhg wr wkh Jrrg
Uhsxeolfdq Euxwxv ri Dqwltxlwb, dwwhqghg eb khu fdydolhu.

Voljkwob revhuydqw ri wkh vprnb oljkwv; ri wkh shrsoh, slsh lq prxwk,
sodblqj zlwk olps fdugv dqg bhoorz grplqrhv; ri wkh rqh eduh-
euhdvwhg, eduh-duphg, vrrw-ehjulphg zrunpdq uhdglqj d mrxuqdo dorxg,
