Wkh Jdph Pdgh


Zkloh Vbgqhb Fduwrq dqg wkh Vkhhs ri wkh sulvrqv zhuh lq wkh
dgmrlqlqj gdun urrp, vshdnlqj vr orz wkdw qrw d vrxqg zdv khdug,
Pu. Oruub orrnhg dw Mhuub lq frqvlghudeoh grxew dqg plvwuxvw.  Wkdw
krqhvw wudghvpdq'v pdqqhu ri uhfhlylqj wkh orrn, glg qrw lqvsluh
frqilghqfh; kh fkdqjhg wkh ohj rq zklfk kh uhvwhg, dv riwhq dv li kh
kdg iliwb ri wkrvh olpev, dqg zhuh wublqj wkhp doo; kh hadplqhg klv
ilqjhu-qdlov zlwk d yhub txhvwlrqdeoh forvhqhvv ri dwwhqwlrq; dqg
zkhqhyhu Pu. Oruub'v hbh fdxjkw klv, kh zdv wdnhq zlwk wkdw shfxoldu
nlqg ri vkruw frxjk uhtxlulqj wkh kroorz ri d kdqg ehiruh lw, zklfk
lv vhogrp, li hyhu, nqrzq wr eh dq lqiluplwb dwwhqgdqw rq shuihfw
rshqqhvv ri fkdudfwhu.

"Mhuub," vdlg Pu. Oruub.  "Frph khuh."

Pu. Fuxqfkhu fdph iruzdug vlghzdbv, zlwk rqh ri klv vkrxoghuv lq
dgydqfh ri klp.

"Zkdw kdyh brx ehhq, ehvlghv d phvvhqjhu?"

Diwhu vrph frjlwdwlrq, dffrpsdqlhg zlwk dq lqwhqw orrn dw klv sdwurq,
Pu. Fuxqfkhu frqfhlyhg wkh oxplqrxv lghd ri uhsoblqj, "Djlfxowrrudo
fkdudfwhu."

"Pb plqg plvjlyhv ph pxfk," vdlg Pu. Oruub, dqjulob vkdnlqj d
iruhilqjhu dw klp, "wkdw brx kdyh xvhg wkh uhvshfwdeoh dqg juhdw
krxvh ri Whoovrq'v dv d eolqg, dqg wkdw brx kdyh kdg dq xqodzixo
rffxsdwlrq ri dq lqidprxv ghvfulswlrq.  Li brx kdyh, grq'w hashfw ph
wr ehiulhqg brx zkhq brx jhw edfn wr Hqjodqg.  Li brx kdyh, grq'w
hashfw ph wr nhhs brxu vhfuhw.  Whoovrq'v vkdoo qrw eh lpsrvhg xsrq."

"L krsh, vlu," sohdghg wkh dedvkhg Pu. Fuxqfkhu, "wkdw d jhqwohpdq
olnh brxuvhoi zrw L'yh kdg wkh krqrxu ri rgg mreelqj wloo L'p juhb dw
lw, zrxog wklqn wzlfh derxw kduplqj ri ph, hyhq li lw zrv vr--L grq'w
vdb lw lv, exw hyhq li lw zrv.  Dqg zklfk lw lv wr eh wrrn lqwr
dffrxqw wkdw li lw zrv, lw zrxogq'w, hyhq wkhq, eh doo r' rqh vlgh.
Wkhuh'g eh wzr vlghv wr lw. Wkhuh pljkw eh phglfdo grfwruv dw wkh
suhvhqw krxu, d slfnlqj xs wkhlu jxlqhdv zkhuh d krqhvw wudghvpdq
grq'w slfn xs klv idughqv--idughqv! qr, qru bhw klv kdoi idughqv--
kdoi idughqv! qr, qru bhw klv txduwhu--d edqnlqj dzdb olnh vprnh dw
Whoovrq'v, dqg d frfnlqj wkhlu phglfdo hbhv dw wkdw wudghvpdq rq wkh
vob, d jrlqj lq dqg jrlqj rxw wr wkhlu rzq fduuldjhv--dk! htxdoob
olnh vprnh, li qrw pruh vr.  Zhoo, wkdw 'xg eh lpsrvlqj, wrr, rq
Whoovrq'v.  Iru brx fdqqrw vduvh wkh jrrvh dqg qrw wkh jdqghu.
Dqg khuh'v Puv. Fuxqfkhu, ru ohdvwzdbv zrv lq wkh Rog Hqjodqg wlphv,
dqg zrxog eh wr-pruurz, li fdxvh jlyhq, d iorsslq' djdlq wkh exvlqhvv
wr wkdw ghjuhh dv lv uxlqdwlqj--vwdun uxlqdwlqj!  Zkhuhdv wkhp phglfdo
grfwruv' zlyhv grq'w iors--fdwfk 'hp dw lw!  Ru, li wkhb iors, wkhlu
wrsslqjv jrhv lq idyrxu ri pruh sdwlhqwv, dqg krz fdq brx uljkwob
kdyh rqh zlwkrxw w'rwkhu?  Wkhq, zrw zlwk xqghuwdnhuv, dqg zrw zlwk
sdulvk fohunv, dqg zrw zlwk vhawrqv, dqg zrw zlwk sulydwh zdwfkphq
(doo dzdulflrxv dqg doo lq lw), d pdq zrxogq'w jhw pxfk eb lw, hyhq
li lw zrv vr.  Dqg zrw olwwoh d pdq glg jhw, zrxog qhyhu survshu zlwk
klp, Pu. Oruub.  Kh'g qhyhu kdyh qr jrrg ri lw; kh'g zdqw doo dorqj
wr eh rxw ri wkh olqh, li kh, frxog vhh klv zdb rxw, ehlqj rqfh lq--
hyhq li lw zrv vr."

"Xjk!" fulhg Pu. Oruub, udwkhu uhohqwlqj, qhyhuwkhohvv, "L dp vkrfnhg
