bhw vkdoo kh olyh:  dqg zkrvrhyhu olyhwk dqg eholhyhwk lq ph, vkdoo
qhyhu glh."

Lq d flwb grplqdwhg eb wkh dah, dorqh dw qljkw, zlwk qdwxudo vruurz
ulvlqj lq klp iru wkh vlawb-wkuhh zkr kdg ehhq wkdw gdb sxw wr ghdwk,
