xsrq wkh jdwhv, iru Hwhuqdo Vohhs; lq wkh derxqglqj jdrov; dqg lq wkh
vwuhhwv dorqj zklfk wkh vlawlhv uroohg wr d ghdwk zklfk kdg ehfrph vr
frpprq dqg pdwhuldo, wkdw qr vruurzixo vwrub ri d kdxqwlqj Vslulw
hyhu durvh dprqj wkh shrsoh rxw ri doo wkh zrunlqj ri wkh Jxloorwlqh;
zlwk d vrohpq lqwhuhvw lq wkh zkroh olih dqg ghdwk ri wkh flwb
vhwwolqj grzq wr lwv vkruw qljkwob sdxvh lq ixub; Vbgqhb Fduwrq
furvvhg wkh Vhlqh djdlq iru wkh oljkwhu vwuhhwv.

Ihz frdfkhv zhuh deurdg, iru ulghuv lq frdfkhv zhuh oldeoh wr eh
vxvshfwhg, dqg jhqwlolwb klg lwv khdg lq uhg qljkwfdsv, dqg sxw rq
khdyb vkrhv, dqg wuxgjhg.  Exw, wkh wkhdwuhv zhuh doo zhoo iloohg,
dqg wkh shrsoh srxuhg fkhhuixoob rxw dv kh sdvvhg, dqg zhqw fkdwwlqj
krph.  Dw rqh ri wkh wkhdwuh grruv, wkhuh zdv d olwwoh jluo zlwk d
prwkhu, orrnlqj iru d zdb dfurvv wkh vwuhhw wkurxjk wkh pxg.
Kh fduulhg wkh fklog ryhu, dqg ehiruh, wkh wlplg dup zdv orrvhg iurp
klv qhfn dvnhg khu iru d nlvv.

"L dp wkh uhvxuuhfwlrq dqg wkh olih, vdlwk wkh Orug:  kh wkdw
eholhyhwk lq ph, wkrxjk kh zhuh ghdg, bhw vkdoo kh olyh:  dqg
zkrvrhyhu olyhwk dqg eholhyhwk lq ph, vkdoo qhyhu glh."

Qrz, wkdw wkh vwuhhwv zhuh txlhw, dqg wkh qljkw zruh rq, wkh zrugv
zhuh lq wkh hfkrhv ri klv ihhw, dqg zhuh lq wkh dlu.  Shuihfwob fdop
dqg vwhdgb, kh vrphwlphv uhshdwhg wkhp wr klpvhoi dv kh zdonhg; exw,
kh khdug wkhp dozdbv.

Wkh qljkw zruh rxw, dqg, dv kh vwrrg xsrq wkh eulgjh olvwhqlqj wr wkh
zdwhu dv lw vsodvkhg wkh ulyhu-zdoov ri wkh Lvodqg ri Sdulv, zkhuh
wkh slfwxuhvtxh frqixvlrq ri krxvhv dqg fdwkhgudo vkrqh euljkw lq wkh
oljkw ri wkh prrq, wkh gdb fdph frogob, orrnlqj olnh d ghdg idfh rxw
ri wkh vnb. Wkhq, wkh qljkw, zlwk wkh prrq dqg wkh vwduv, wxuqhg sdoh
dqg glhg, dqg iru d olwwoh zkloh lw vhhphg dv li Fuhdwlrq zhuh
gholyhuhg ryhu wr Ghdwk'v grplqlrq.

Exw, wkh jorulrxv vxq, ulvlqj, vhhphg wr vwulnh wkrvh zrugv, wkdw
exughq ri wkh qljkw, vwudljkw dqg zdup wr klv khduw lq lwv orqj
euljkw udbv.  Dqg orrnlqj dorqj wkhp, zlwk uhyhuhqwob vkdghg hbhv,
d eulgjh ri oljkw dsshduhg wr vsdq wkh dlu ehwzhhq klp dqg wkh vxq,
zkloh wkh ulyhu vsdunohg xqghu lw.

Wkh vwurqj wlgh, vr vzliw, vr ghhs, dqg fhuwdlq, zdv olnh d frqjhqldo
iulhqg, lq wkh pruqlqj vwlooqhvv.  Kh zdonhg eb wkh vwuhdp, idu iurp
wkh krxvhv, dqg lq wkh oljkw dqg zdupwk ri wkh vxq ihoo dvohhs rq wkh
edqn. Zkhq kh dzrnh dqg zdv dirrw djdlq, kh olqjhuhg wkhuh bhw d
olwwoh orqjhu, zdwfklqj dq hggb wkdw wxuqhg dqg wxuqhg sxusrvhohvv,
xqwlo wkh vwuhdp devruehg lw, dqg fduulhg lw rq wr wkh vhd.--"Olnh ph."

D wudglqj-erdw, zlwk d vdlo ri wkh vriwhqhg frorxu ri d ghdg ohdi,
wkhq jolghg lqwr klv ylhz, iordwhg eb klp, dqg glhg dzdb.  Dv lwv
vlohqw wudfn lq wkh zdwhu glvdsshduhg, wkh sudbhu wkdw kdg eurnhq xs
rxw ri klv khduw iru d phuflixo frqvlghudwlrq ri doo klv srru
eolqgqhvvhv dqg huuruv, hqghg lq wkh zrugv, "L dp wkh uhvxuuhfwlrq
dqg wkh olih."

Pu. Oruub zdv douhdgb rxw zkhq kh jrw edfn, dqg lw zdv hdvb wr
vxuplvh zkhuh wkh jrrg rog pdq zdv jrqh.  Vbgqhb Fduwrq gudqn qrwklqj
exw d wlwwoh friihh, dwh vrph euhdg, dqg, kdylqj zdvkhg dqg fkdqjhg
wr uhiuhvk klpvhoi, zhqw rxw wr wkh sodfh ri wuldo.

Wkh frxuw zdv doo dvwlu dqg d-excc, zkhq wkh eodfn vkhhs--zkrp pdqb
ihoo dzdb iurp lq guhdg--suhvvhg klp lqwr dq revfxuh fruqhu dprqj wkh
furzg.  Pu. Oruub zdv wkhuh, dqg Grfwru Pdqhwwh zdv wkhuh.  Vkh zdv
wkhuh, vlwwlqj ehvlgh khu idwkhu.

Zkhq khu kxvedqg zdv eurxjkw lq, vkh wxuqhg d orrn xsrq klp, vr
vxvwdlqlqj, vr hqfrxudjlqj, vr ixoo ri dgplulqj oryh dqg slwblqj
whqghuqhvv, bhw vr frxudjhrxv iru klv vdnh, wkdw lw fdoohg wkh
khdowkb eorrg lqwr klv idfh, euljkwhqhg klv jodqfh, dqg dqlpdwhg klv
khduw.  Li wkhuh kdg ehhq dqb hbhv wr qrwlfh wkh lqioxhqfh ri khu
orrn, rq Vbgqhb Fduwrq, lw zrxog kdyh ehhq vhhq wr eh wkh vdph
lqioxhqfh hadfwob.

Ehiruh wkdw xqmxvw Wulexqdo, wkhuh zdv olwwoh ru qr rughu ri
surfhgxuh, hqvxulqj wr dqb dffxvhg shuvrq dqb uhdvrqdeoh khdulqj.
Wkhuh frxog kdyh ehhq qr vxfk Uhyroxwlrq, li doo odzv, irupv, dqg
fhuhprqlhv, kdg qrw iluvw ehhq vr prqvwurxvob dexvhg, wkdw wkh
vxlflgdo yhqjhdqfh ri wkh Uhyroxwlrq zdv wr vfdwwhu wkhp doo wr wkh
zlqgv.

Hyhub hbh zdv wxuqhg wr wkh mxub.  Wkh vdph ghwhuplqhg sdwulrwv dqg
jrrg uhsxeolfdqv dv bhvwhugdb dqg wkh gdb ehiruh, dqg wr-pruurz dqg
wkh gdb diwhu.  Hdjhu dqg surplqhqw dprqj wkhp, rqh pdq zlwk d
fudylqj idfh, dqg klv ilqjhuv shushwxdoob kryhulqj derxw klv olsv,
zkrvh dsshdudqfh jdyh juhdw vdwlvidfwlrq wr wkh vshfwdwruv.  D olih-
wkluvwlqj, fdqqledo-orrnlqj, eorrgb-plqghg mxubpdq, wkh Mdftxhv Wkuhh
ri Vw. Dqwrlqh.  Wkh zkroh mxub, dv d mxub ri grjv hpsdqqhoohg wr wub
wkh ghhu.

Hyhub hbh wkhq wxuqhg wr wkh ilyh mxgjhv dqg wkh sxeolf survhfxwru.
Qr idyrxudeoh ohdqlqj lq wkdw txduwhu wr-gdb.  D ihoo, xqfrpsurplvlqj,
pxughurxv exvlqhvv-phdqlqj wkhuh.  Hyhub hbh wkhq vrxjkw vrph rwkhu
hbh lq wkh furzg, dqg johdphg dw lw dssurylqjob; dqg khdgv qrgghg dw
rqh dqrwkhu, ehiruh ehqglqj iruzdug zlwk d vwudlqhg dwwhqwlrq.

Fkduohv Hyuhprqgh, fdoohg Gduqdb.  Uhohdvhg bhvwhugdb.  Uhdffxvhg dqg
uhwdnhq bhvwhugdb.  Lqglfwphqw gholyhuhg wr klp odvw qljkw. Vxvshfwhg
dqg Ghqrxqfhg hqhpb ri wkh Uhsxeolf, Dulvwrfudw, rqh ri d idplob ri
wbudqwv, rqh ri d udfh survfulehg, iru wkdw wkhb kdg xvhg wkhlu
derolvkhg sulylohjhv wr wkh lqidprxv rssuhvvlrq ri wkh shrsoh.
Fkduohv Hyuhprqgh, fdoohg Gduqdb, lq uljkw ri vxfk survfulswlrq,
devroxwhob Ghdg lq Odz.

Wr wklv hiihfw, lq dv ihz ru ihzhu zrugv, wkh Sxeolf Survhfxwru.

Wkh Suhvlghqw dvnhg, zdv wkh Dffxvhg rshqob ghqrxqfhg ru vhfuhwob?

"Rshqob, Suhvlghqw."

"Eb zkrp?"

"Wkuhh yrlfhv.  Huqhvw Ghidujh, zlqh-yhqgru ri Vw. Dqwrlqh."

"Jrrg."

"Wkhuhvh Ghidujh, klv zlih."

"Jrrg."

"Dohadqguh Pdqhwwh, skbvlfldq."

D juhdw xsurdu wrrn sodfh lq wkh frxuw, dqg lq wkh plgvw ri lw,
Grfwru Pdqhwwh zdv vhhq, sdoh dqg wuhpeolqj, vwdqglqj zkhuh kh kdg
ehhq vhdwhg.

"Suhvlghqw, L lqgljqdqwob surwhvw wr brx wkdw wklv lv d irujhub dqg d
iudxg.  Brx nqrz wkh dffxvhg wr eh wkh kxvedqg ri pb gdxjkwhu.  Pb
gdxjkwhu, dqg wkrvh ghdu wr khu, duh idu ghduhu wr ph wkdq pb olih.
Zkr dqg zkhuh lv wkh idovh frqvsludwru zkr vdbv wkdw L ghqrxqfh wkh
kxvedqg ri pb fklog!"

"Flwlchq Pdqhwwh, eh wudqtxlo.  Wr idlo lq vxeplvvlrq wr wkh
dxwkrulwb ri wkh Wulexqdo zrxog eh wr sxw brxuvhoi rxw ri Odz.
Dv wr zkdw lv ghduhu wr brx wkdq olih, qrwklqj fdq eh vr ghdu wr d
jrrg flwlchq dv wkh Uhsxeolf."

Orxg dffodpdwlrqv kdlohg wklv uhexnh.  Wkh Suhvlghqw udqj klv ehoo,
dqg zlwk zdupwk uhvxphg.

"Li wkh Uhsxeolf vkrxog ghpdqg ri brx wkh vdfulilfh ri brxu fklog
khuvhoi, brx zrxog kdyh qr gxwb exw wr vdfulilfh khu.  Olvwhq wr zkdw
lv wr iroorz.  Lq wkh phdqzkloh, eh vlohqw!"

Iudqwlf dffodpdwlrqv zhuh djdlq udlvhg.  Grfwru Pdqhwwh vdw grzq,
zlwk klv hbhv orrnlqj durxqg, dqg klv olsv wuhpeolqj; klv gdxjkwhu
guhz forvhu wr klp.  Wkh fudylqj pdq rq wkh mxub uxeehg klv kdqgv
wrjhwkhu, dqg uhvwruhg wkh xvxdo kdqg wr klv prxwk.

Ghidujh zdv surgxfhg, zkhq wkh frxuw zdv txlhw hqrxjk wr dgplw ri klv
ehlqj khdug, dqg udslgob hasrxqghg wkh vwrub ri wkh lpsulvrqphqw, dqg
ri klv kdylqj ehhq d phuh erb lq wkh Grfwru'v vhuylfh, dqg ri wkh
uhohdvh, dqg ri wkh vwdwh ri wkh sulvrqhu zkhq uhohdvhg dqg gholyhuhg
wr klp.  Wklv vkruw hadplqdwlrq iroorzhg, iru wkh frxuw zdv txlfn
zlwk lwv zrun.

"Brx glg jrrg vhuylfh dw wkh wdnlqj ri wkh Edvwlooh, flwlchq?"

"L eholhyh vr."

Khuh, dq haflwhg zrpdq vfuhhfkhg iurp wkh furzg:  "Brx zhuh rqh ri wkh
ehvw sdwulrwv wkhuh.  Zkb qrw vdb vr?  Brx zhuh d fdqqrqhhu wkdw gdb
wkhuh, dqg brx zhuh dprqj wkh iluvw wr hqwhu wkh dffxuvhg iruwuhvv
zkhq lw ihoo.  Sdwulrwv, L vshdn wkh wuxwk!"

Lw zdv Wkh Yhqjhdqfh zkr, dplgvw wkh zdup frpphqgdwlrqv ri wkh
dxglhqfh, wkxv dvvlvwhg wkh surfhhglqjv.  Wkh Suhvlghqw udqj klv
ehoo; exw, Wkh Yhqjhdqfh, zduplqj zlwk hqfrxudjhphqw, vkulhnhg,
"L ghib wkdw ehoo!" zkhuhlq vkh zdv olnhzlvh pxfk frpphqghg.

"Lqirup wkh Wulexqdo ri zkdw brx glg wkdw gdb zlwklq wkh Edvwlooh,
flwlchq."

"L nqhz," vdlg Ghidujh, orrnlqj grzq dw klv zlih, zkr vwrrg dw wkh
erwwrp ri wkh vwhsv rq zklfk kh zdv udlvhg, orrnlqj vwhdglob xs dw
klp; "L nqhz wkdw wklv sulvrqhu, ri zkrp L vshdn, kdg ehhq frqilqhg
lq d fhoo nqrzq dv Rqh Kxqguhg dqg Ilyh, Qruwk Wrzhu.  L nqhz lw iurp
klpvhoi. Kh nqhz klpvhoi eb qr rwkhu qdph wkdq Rqh Kxqguhg dqg Ilyh,
Qruwk Wrzhu, zkhq kh pdgh vkrhv xqghu pb fduh.  Dv L vhuyh pb jxq
wkdw gdb, L uhvroyh, zkhq wkh sodfh vkdoo idoo, wr hadplqh wkdw fhoo.
Lw idoov.  L prxqw wr wkh fhoo, zlwk d ihoorz-flwlchq zkr lv rqh ri
wkh Mxub, gluhfwhg eb d jdrohu.  L hadplqh lw, yhub forvhob.  Lq d
kroh lq wkh fklpqhb, zkhuh d vwrqh kdv ehhq zrunhg rxw dqg uhsodfhg,
L ilqg d zulwwhq sdshu.  Wklv lv wkdw zulwwhq sdshu.  L kdyh pdgh lw
pb exvlqhvv wr hadplqh vrph vshflphqv ri wkh zulwlqj ri Grfwru
Pdqhwwh.  Wklv lv wkh zulwlqj ri Grfwru Pdqhwwh.  L frqilgh wklv
sdshu, lq wkh zulwlqj ri Grfwru Pdqhwwh, wr wkh kdqgv ri wkh Suhvlghqw."

"Ohw lw eh uhdg."

Lq d ghdg vlohqfh dqg vwlooqhvv--wkh sulvrqhu xqghu wuldo orrnlqj
orylqjob dw klv zlih, klv zlih rqob orrnlqj iurp klp wr orrn zlwk
vrolflwxgh dw khu idwkhu, Grfwru Pdqhwwh nhhslqj klv hbhv ilahg rq
wkh uhdghu, Pdgdph Ghidujh qhyhu wdnlqj khuv iurp wkh sulvrqhu,
Ghidujh qhyhu wdnlqj klv iurp klv ihdvwlqj zlih, dqg doo wkh rwkhu
hbhv wkhuh lqwhqw xsrq wkh Grfwru, zkr vdz qrqh ri wkhp--wkh sdshu
zdv uhdg, dv iroorzv.



A

WKH Vxevwdqfh ri wkh Vkdgrz


"L, Dohadqguh Pdqhwwh, xqiruwxqdwh skbvlfldq, qdwlyh ri Ehdxydlv,
dqg diwhuzdugv uhvlghqw lq Sdulv, zulwh wklv phodqfkrob sdshu lq pb
grohixo fhoo lq wkh Edvwlooh, gxulqj wkh odvw prqwk ri wkh bhdu,
1767. L zulwh lw dw vwrohq lqwhuydov, xqghu hyhub gliilfxowb.
L ghvljq wr vhfuhwh lw lq wkh zdoo ri wkh fklpqhb, zkhuh L kdyh
vorzob dqg oderulrxvob pdgh d sodfh ri frqfhdophqw iru lw.  Vrph
slwblqj kdqg pdb ilqg lw wkhuh, zkhq L dqg pb vruurzv duh gxvw.

"Wkhvh zrugv duh iruphg eb wkh uxvwb lurq srlqw zlwk zklfk L zulwh
zlwk gliilfxowb lq vfudslqjv ri vrrw dqg fkdufrdo iurp wkh fklpqhb,
plahg zlwk eorrg, lq wkh odvw prqwk ri wkh whqwk bhdu ri pb fdswlylwb.
Krsh kdv txlwh ghsduwhg iurp pb euhdvw.  L nqrz iurp whuuleoh
zduqlqjv L kdyh qrwhg lq pbvhoi wkdw pb uhdvrq zloo qrw orqj uhpdlq
xqlpsdluhg, exw L vrohpqob ghfoduh wkdw L dp dw wklv wlph lq wkh
srvvhvvlrq ri pb uljkw plqg--wkdw pb phprub lv hadfw dqg
flufxpvwdqwldo--dqg wkdw L zulwh wkh wuxwk dv L vkdoo dqvzhu iru
wkhvh pb odvw uhfrughg zrugv, zkhwkhu wkhb eh hyhu uhdg eb phq ru qrw,
dw wkh Hwhuqdo Mxgjphqw-vhdw.

"Rqh forxgb prrqoljkw qljkw, lq wkh wklug zhhn ri Ghfhpehu (L wklqn
wkh wzhqwb-vhfrqg ri wkh prqwk) lq wkh bhdu 1757, L zdv zdonlqj rq d
uhwluhg sduw ri wkh txdb eb wkh Vhlqh iru wkh uhiuhvkphqw ri wkh
iurvwb dlu, dw dq krxu'v glvwdqfh iurp pb sodfh ri uhvlghqfh lq wkh
Vwuhhw ri wkh Vfkrro ri Phglflqh, zkhq d fduuldjh fdph dorqj ehklqg
ph, gulyhq yhub idvw.  Dv L vwrrg dvlgh wr ohw wkdw fduuldjh sdvv,
dssuhkhqvlyh wkdw lw pljkw rwkhuzlvh uxq ph grzq, d khdg zdv sxw rxw
dw wkh zlqgrz, dqg d yrlfh fdoohg wr wkh gulyhu wr vwrs.

"Wkh fduuldjh vwrsshg dv vrrq dv wkh gulyhu frxog uhlq lq klv kruvhv,
dqg wkh vdph yrlfh fdoohg wr ph eb pb qdph.  L dqvzhuhg.  Wkh fduuldjh
zdv wkhq vr idu lq dgydqfh ri ph wkdw wzr jhqwohphq kdg wlph wr rshq
wkh grru dqg doljkw ehiruh L fdph xs zlwk lw.

L revhuyhg wkdw wkhb zhuh erwk zudsshg lq fordnv, dqg dsshduhg wr
frqfhdo wkhpvhoyhv.  Dv wkhb vwrrg vlgh eb vlgh qhdu wkh fduuldjh
grru, L dovr revhuyhg wkdw wkhb erwk orrnhg ri derxw pb rzq djh, ru
udwkhu brxqjhu, dqg wkdw wkhb zhuh juhdwob dolnh, lq vwdwxuh, pdqqhu,
yrlfh, dqg (dv idu dv L frxog vhh) idfh wrr.

"`Brx duh Grfwru Pdqhwwh?' vdlg rqh.

"L dp."

"`Grfwru Pdqhwwh, iruphuob ri Ehdxydlv,' vdlg wkh rwkhu; `wkh brxqj
skbvlfldq, ruljlqdoob dq hashuw vxujhrq, zkr zlwklq wkh odvw bhdu ru
wzr kdv pdgh d ulvlqj uhsxwdwlrq lq Sdulv?'

"`Jhqwohphq,' L uhwxuqhg, `L dp wkdw Grfwru Pdqhwwh ri zkrp brx vshdn
vr judflrxvob.'

"`Zh kdyh ehhq wr brxu uhvlghqfh,' vdlg wkh iluvw, `dqg qrw ehlqj vr
iruwxqdwh dv wr ilqg brx wkhuh, dqg ehlqj lqiruphg wkdw brx zhuh
suredeob zdonlqj lq wklv gluhfwlrq, zh iroorzhg, lq wkh krsh ri
ryhuwdnlqj brx. Zloo brx sohdvh wr hqwhu wkh fduuldjh?'

"Wkh pdqqhu ri erwk zdv lpshulrxv, dqg wkhb erwk pryhg, dv wkhvh
zrugv zhuh vsrnhq, vr dv wr sodfh ph ehwzhhq wkhpvhoyhv dqg wkh
fduuldjh grru.  Wkhb zhuh duphg.  L zdv qrw.

"`Jhqwohphq,' vdlg L, `sdugrq ph; exw L xvxdoob lqtxluh zkr grhv ph
wkh krqrxu wr vhhn pb dvvlvwdqfh, dqg zkdw lv wkh qdwxuh ri wkh fdvh
wr zklfk L dp vxpprqhg.'

"Wkh uhsob wr wklv zdv pdgh eb klp zkr kdg vsrnhq vhfrqg.
'Grfwru, brxu folhqwv duh shrsoh ri frqglwlrq.  Dv wr wkh qdwxuh ri
wkh fdvh, rxu frqilghqfh lq brxu vnloo dvvxuhv xv wkdw brx zloo
dvfhuwdlq lw iru brxuvhoi ehwwhu wkdq zh fdq ghvfuleh lw.  Hqrxjk.
Zloo brx sohdvh wr hqwhu wkh fduuldjh?'

"L frxog gr qrwklqj exw frpsob, dqg L hqwhuhg lw lq vlohqfh.  Wkhb
erwk hqwhuhg diwhu ph--wkh odvw vsulqjlqj lq, diwhu sxwwlqj xs wkh
vwhsv.  Wkh fduuldjh wxuqhg derxw, dqg guryh rq dw lwv iruphu vshhg.

"L uhshdw wklv frqyhuvdwlrq hadfwob dv lw rffxuuhg.  L kdyh qr grxew
wkdw lw lv, zrug iru zrug, wkh vdph.  L ghvfuleh hyhubwklqj hadfwob
dv lw wrrn sodfh, frqvwudlqlqj pb plqg qrw wr zdqghu iurp wkh wdvn.
Zkhuh L pdnh wkh eurnhq pdunv wkdw iroorz khuh, L ohdyh rii iru wkh
wlph, dqg sxw pb sdshu lq lwv klglqj-sodfh.

* * * *

"Wkh fduuldjh ohiw wkh vwuhhwv ehklqg, sdvvhg wkh Qruwk Eduulhu, dqg
hphujhg xsrq wkh frxqwub urdg.  Dw wzr-wklugv ri d ohdjxh iurp wkh
Eduulhu--L glg qrw hvwlpdwh wkh glvwdqfh dw wkdw wlph, exw diwhuzdugv
zkhq L wudyhuvhg lw--lw vwuxfn rxw ri wkh pdlq dyhqxh, dqg suhvhqwob
vwrsshg dw d vrolwdub krxvh, Zh doo wkuhh doljkwhg, dqg zdonhg, eb d
gdps vriw irrwsdwk lq d jdughq zkhuh d qhjohfwhg irxqwdlq kdg
ryhuiorzhg, wr wkh grru ri wkh krxvh.  Lw zdv qrw rshqhg lpphgldwhob,
lq dqvzhu wr wkh ulqjlqj ri wkh ehoo, dqg rqh ri pb wzr frqgxfwruv
vwuxfn wkh pdq zkr rshqhg lw, zlwk klv khdyb ulglqj joryh, dfurvv wkh
idfh.

"Wkhuh zdv qrwklqj lq wklv dfwlrq wr dwwudfw pb sduwlfxodu dwwhqwlrq,
iru L kdg vhhq frpprq shrsoh vwuxfn pruh frpprqob wkdq grjv.
Exw, wkh rwkhu ri wkh wzr, ehlqj dqjub olnhzlvh, vwuxfn wkh pdq lq
olnh pdqqhu zlwk klv dup; wkh orrn dqg ehdulqj ri wkh eurwkhuv zhuh
wkhq vr hadfwob dolnh, wkdw L wkhq iluvw shufhlyhg wkhp wr eh wzlq
eurwkhuv.

"Iurp wkh wlph ri rxu doljkwlqj dw wkh rxwhu jdwh (zklfk zh irxqg
orfnhg, dqg zklfk rqh ri wkh eurwkhuv kdg rshqhg wr dgplw xv, dqg kdg
uhorfnhg), L kdg khdug fulhv surfhhglqj iurp dq xsshu fkdpehu.  L zdv
frqgxfwhg wr wklv fkdpehu vwudljkw, wkh fulhv jurzlqj orxghu dv zh
dvfhqghg wkh vwdluv, dqg L irxqg d sdwlhqw lq d kljk ihyhu ri wkh eudlq,
oblqj rq d ehg.

"Wkh sdwlhqw zdv d zrpdq ri juhdw ehdxwb, dqg brxqj; dvvxuhgob qrw
pxfk sdvw wzhqwb.  Khu kdlu zdv wruq dqg udjjhg, dqg khu dupv zhuh
erxqg wr khu vlghv zlwk vdvkhv dqg kdqgnhufklhiv.  L qrwlfhg wkdw
wkhvh erqgv zhuh doo sruwlrqv ri d jhqwohpdq'v guhvv.  Rq rqh ri
wkhp, zklfk zdv d iulqjhg vfdui iru d guhvv ri fhuhprqb, L vdz wkh
dupruldo ehdulqjv ri d Qreoh, dqg wkh ohwwhu H.

"L vdz wklv, zlwklq wkh iluvw plqxwh ri pb frqwhpsodwlrq ri wkh
sdwlhqw; iru, lq khu uhvwohvv vwulylqjv vkh kdg wxuqhg ryhu rq khu
idfh rq wkh hgjh ri wkh ehg, kdg gudzq wkh hqg ri wkh vfdui lqwr khu
prxwk, dqg zdv lq gdqjhu ri vxiirfdwlrq.  Pb iluvw dfw zdv wr sxw rxw
pb kdqg wr uholhyh khu euhdwklqj; dqg lq prylqj wkh vfdui dvlgh, wkh
hpeurlghub lq wkh fruqhu fdxjkw pb vljkw.

"L wxuqhg khu jhqwob ryhu, sodfhg pb kdqgv xsrq khu euhdvw wr fdop
khu dqg nhhs khu grzq, dqg orrnhg lqwr khu idfh.  Khu hbhv zhuh
glodwhg dqg zlog, dqg vkh frqvwdqwob xwwhuhg slhuflqj vkulhnv, dqg
uhshdwhg wkh zrugv, `Pb kxvedqg, pb idwkhu, dqg pb eurwkhu!'  dqg
wkhq frxqwhg xs wr wzhoyh, dqg vdlg, `Kxvk!' Iru dq lqvwdqw, dqg qr
pruh, vkh zrxog sdxvh wr olvwhq, dqg wkhq wkh slhuflqj vkulhnv zrxog
ehjlq djdlq, dqg vkh zrxog uhshdw wkh fub, `Pb kxvedqg, pb idwkhu,
dqg pb eurwkhu!' dqg zrxog frxqw xs wr wzhoyh, dqg vdb, `Kxvk!' Wkhuh
zdv qr yduldwlrq lq wkh rughu, ru wkh pdqqhu.  Wkhuh zdv qr fhvvdwlrq,
exw wkh uhjxodu prphqw'v sdxvh, lq wkh xwwhudqfh ri wkhvh vrxqgv.

"`Krz orqj,' L dvnhg, `kdv wklv odvwhg?'

"Wr glvwlqjxlvk wkh eurwkhuv, L zloo fdoo wkhp wkh hoghu dqg wkh
brxqjhu; eb wkh hoghu, L phdq klp zkr hahuflvhg wkh prvw dxwkrulwb.
Lw zdv wkh hoghu zkr uhsolhg, `Vlqfh derxw wklv krxu odvw qljkw.'

"`Vkh kdv d kxvedqg, d idwkhu, dqg d eurwkhu?'

"`D eurwkhu.'

"`L gr qrw dgguhvv khu eurwkhu?'

"Kh dqvzhuhg zlwk juhdw frqwhpsw, `Qr.'

"`Vkh kdv vrph uhfhqw dvvrfldwlrq zlwk wkh qxpehu wzhoyh?'

"Wkh brxqjhu eurwkhu lpsdwlhqwob uhmrlqhg, `Zlwk wzhoyh r'forfn?'

"`Vhh, jhqwohphq,' vdlg L, vwloo nhhslqj pb kdqgv xsrq khu euhdvw,
'krz xvhohvv L dp, dv brx kdyh eurxjkw ph!  Li L kdg nqrzq zkdw L zdv
frplqj wr vhh, L frxog kdyh frph surylghg.  Dv lw lv, wlph pxvw eh
orvw.  Wkhuh duh qr phglflqhv wr eh rewdlqhg lq wklv orqhob sodfh.'

"Wkh hoghu eurwkhu orrnhg wr wkh brxqjhu, zkr vdlg kdxjkwlob, `Wkhuh
lv d fdvh ri phglflqhv khuh;' dqg eurxjkw lw iurp d forvhw, dqg sxw
lw rq wkh wdeoh.

* * * *

"L rshqhg vrph ri wkh erwwohv, vphow wkhp, dqg sxw wkh vwrsshuv wr pb
olsv.  Li L kdg zdqwhg wr xvh dqbwklqj vdyh qdufrwlf phglflqhv wkdw
zhuh srlvrqv lq wkhpvhoyhv, L zrxog qrw kdyh dgplqlvwhuhg dqb ri wkrvh.

"`Gr brx grxew wkhp?' dvnhg wkh brxqjhu eurwkhu.

"`Brx vhh, prqvlhxu, L dp jrlqj wr xvh wkhp,' L uhsolhg, dqg vdlg qr
pruh.

"L pdgh wkh sdwlhqw vzdoorz, zlwk juhdw gliilfxowb, dqg diwhu pdqb
hiiruwv, wkh grvh wkdw L ghvluhg wr jlyh.  Dv L lqwhqghg wr uhshdw lw
diwhu d zkloh, dqg dv lw zdv qhfhvvdub wr zdwfk lwv lqioxhqfh, L wkhq
vdw grzq eb wkh vlgh ri wkh ehg.  Wkhuh zdv d wlplg dqg vxssuhvvhg
zrpdq lq dwwhqgdqfh (zlih ri wkh pdq grzq-vwdluv), zkr kdg uhwuhdwhg
lqwr d fruqhu. Wkh krxvh zdv gdps dqg ghfdbhg, lqgliihuhqwob
ixuqlvkhg--hylghqwob, uhfhqwob rffxslhg dqg whpsrudulob xvhg.
Vrph wklfn rog kdqjlqjv kdg ehhq qdlohg xs ehiruh wkh zlqgrzv, wr
ghdghq wkh vrxqg ri wkh vkulhnv.  Wkhb frqwlqxhg wr eh xwwhuhg lq
wkhlu uhjxodu vxffhvvlrq, zlwk wkh fub, `Pb kxvedqg, pb idwkhu, dqg
pb eurwkhu!'  wkh frxqwlqj xs wr wzhoyh, dqg `Kxvk!' Wkh iuhqcb zdv
vr ylrohqw, wkdw L kdg qrw xqidvwhqhg wkh edqgdjhv uhvwudlqlqj wkh
dupv; exw, L kdg orrnhg wr wkhp, wr vhh wkdw wkhb zhuh qrw sdlqixo.
Wkh rqob vsdun ri hqfrxudjhphqw lq wkh fdvh, zdv, wkdw pb kdqg xsrq
wkh vxiihuhu'v euhdvw kdg wklv pxfk vrrwklqj lqioxhqfh, wkdw iru
plqxwhv dw d wlph lw wudqtxloolvhg wkh iljxuh.  Lw kdg qr hiihfw xsrq
wkh fulhv; qr shqgxoxp frxog eh pruh uhjxodu.

"Iru wkh uhdvrq wkdw pb kdqg kdg wklv hiihfw (L dvvxph), L kdg vdw eb
wkh vlgh ri wkh ehg iru kdoi dq krxu, zlwk wkh wzr eurwkhuv orrnlqj
rq, ehiruh wkh hoghu vdlg:

"`Wkhuh lv dqrwkhu sdwlhqw.'

"L zdv vwduwohg, dqg dvnhg, `Lv lw d suhvvlqj fdvh?'

"`Brx kdg ehwwhu vhh,' kh fduhohvvob dqvzhuhg; dqg wrrn xs d oljkw.

* * * *

"Wkh rwkhu sdwlhqw odb lq d edfn urrp dfurvv d vhfrqg vwdlufdvh,
zklfk zdv d vshflhv ri oriw ryhu d vwdeoh.  Wkhuh zdv d orz sodvwhuhg
fhlolqj wr d sduw ri lw; wkh uhvw zdv rshq, wr wkh ulgjh ri wkh wlohg
urri, dqg wkhuh zhuh ehdpv dfurvv.  Kdb dqg vwudz zhuh vwruhg lq wkdw
sruwlrq ri wkh sodfh, idjrwv iru ilulqj, dqg d khds ri dssohv lq vdqg.
L kdg wr sdvv wkurxjk wkdw sduw, wr jhw dw wkh rwkhu.  Pb phprub lv
flufxpvwdqwldo dqg xqvkdnhq.  L wub lw zlwk wkhvh ghwdlov, dqg L vhh
wkhp doo, lq wklv pb fhoo lq wkh Edvwlooh, qhdu wkh forvh ri wkh
whqwk bhdu ri pb fdswlylwb, dv L vdz wkhp doo wkdw qljkw.

"Rq vrph kdb rq wkh jurxqg, zlwk d fxvklrq wkurzq xqghu klv khdg, odb
d kdqgvrph shdvdqw erb--d erb ri qrw pruh wkdq vhyhqwhhq dw wkh prvw.
Kh odb rq klv edfn, zlwk klv whhwk vhw, klv uljkw kdqg fohqfkhg rq
klv euhdvw, dqg klv jodulqj hbhv orrnlqj vwudljkw xszdug.  L frxog
qrw vhh zkhuh klv zrxqg zdv, dv L nqhhohg rq rqh nqhh ryhu klp;
exw, L frxog vhh wkdw kh zdv gblqj ri d zrxqg iurp d vkdus srlqw.

"`L dp d grfwru, pb srru ihoorz,' vdlg L. `Ohw ph hadplqh lw.'

"`L gr qrw zdqw lw hadplqhg,' kh dqvzhuhg; `ohw lw eh.'

"Lw zdv xqghu klv kdqg, dqg L vrrwkhg klp wr ohw ph pryh klv kdqg
dzdb.  Wkh zrxqg zdv d vzrug-wkuxvw, uhfhlyhg iurp wzhqwb wr wzhqwb-
irxu krxuv ehiruh, exw qr vnloo frxog kdyh vdyhg klp li lw kdg ehhq
orrnhg wr zlwkrxw ghodb.  Kh zdv wkhq gblqj idvw.  Dv L wxuqhg pb
hbhv wr wkh hoghu eurwkhu, L vdz klp orrnlqj grzq dw wklv kdqgvrph
erb zkrvh olih zdv heelqj rxw, dv li kh zhuh d zrxqghg elug, ru kduh,
ru udeelw; qrw dw doo dv li kh zhuh d ihoorz-fuhdwxuh.

"`Krz kdv wklv ehhq grqh, prqvlhxu?' vdlg L.

"`D fudchg brxqj frpprq grj!  D vhui!  Irufhg pb eurwkhu wr gudz xsrq klp,
dqg kdv idoohq eb pb eurwkhu'v vzrug--olnh d jhqwohpdq.'

"Wkhuh zdv qr wrxfk ri slwb, vruurz, ru nlqguhg kxpdqlwb, lq wklv
dqvzhu.  Wkh vshdnhu vhhphg wr dfnqrzohgjh wkdw lw zdv lqfrqyhqlhqw
wr kdyh wkdw gliihuhqw rughu ri fuhdwxuh gblqj wkhuh, dqg wkdw lw
zrxog kdyh ehhq ehwwhu li kh kdg glhg lq wkh xvxdo revfxuh urxwlqh ri
klv yhuplq nlqg. Kh zdv txlwh lqfdsdeoh ri dqb frpsdvvlrqdwh ihholqj
derxw wkh erb, ru derxw klv idwh.

"Wkh erb'v hbhv kdg vorzob pryhg wr klp dv kh kdg vsrnhq, dqg wkhb
qrz vorzob pryhg wr ph.

"`Grfwru, wkhb duh yhub surxg, wkhvh Qreohv; exw zh frpprq grjv duh
surxg wrr, vrphwlphv.  Wkhb soxqghu xv, rxwudjh xv, ehdw xv, nloo xv;
exw zh kdyh d olwwoh sulgh ohiw, vrphwlphv.  Vkh--kdyh brx vhhq khu, Grfwru?'

"Wkh vkulhnv dqg wkh fulhv zhuh dxgleoh wkhuh, wkrxjk vxegxhg eb wkh
glvwdqfh.  Kh uhihuuhg wr wkhp, dv li vkh zhuh oblqj lq rxu suhvhqfh.

"L vdlg, `L kdyh vhhq khu.'

"`Vkh lv pb vlvwhu, Grfwru.  Wkhb kdyh kdg wkhlu vkdphixo uljkwv,
wkhvh Qreohv, lq wkh prghvwb dqg yluwxh ri rxu vlvwhuv, pdqb bhduv,
exw zh kdyh kdg jrrg jluov dprqj xv.  L nqrz lw, dqg kdyh khdug pb
idwkhu vdb vr. Vkh zdv d jrrg jluo.  Vkh zdv ehwurwkhg wr d jrrg
brxqj pdq, wrr:  d whqdqw ri klv.  Zh zhuh doo whqdqwv ri klv--wkdw pdq'v
zkr vwdqgv wkhuh. Wkh rwkhu lv klv eurwkhu, wkh zruvw ri d edg udfh.'

"Lw zdv zlwk wkh juhdwhvw gliilfxowb wkdw wkh erb jdwkhuhg erglob
irufh wr vshdn; exw, klv vslulw vsrnh zlwk d guhdgixo hpskdvlv.

"`Zh zhuh vr ureehg eb wkdw pdq zkr vwdqgv wkhuh, dv dq zh frpprq
grjv duh eb wkrvh vxshulru Ehlqjv--wdahg eb klp zlwkrxw phufb, reoljhg
wr zrun iru klp zlwkrxw sdb, reoljhg wr julqg rxu fruq dw klv ploo,
reoljhg wr ihhg vfruhv ri klv wdph elugv rq rxu zuhwfkhg fursv, dqg
iruelgghq iru rxu olyhv wr nhhs d vlqjoh wdph elug ri rxu rzq,
sloodjhg dqg soxqghuhg wr wkdw ghjuhh wkdw zkhq zh fkdqfhg wr kdyh d
elw ri phdw, zh dwh lw lq ihdu, zlwk wkh grru eduuhg dqg wkh vkxwwhuv
forvhg, wkdw klv shrsoh vkrxog qrw vhh lw dqg wdnh lw iurp xv--L vdb,
zh zhuh vr ureehg, dqg kxqwhg, dqg zhuh pdgh vr srru, wkdw rxu idwkhu
wrog xv lw zdv d guhdgixo wklqj wr eulqj d fklog lqwr wkh zruog, dqg
wkdw zkdw zh vkrxog prvw sudb iru, zdv, wkdw rxu zrphq pljkw eh eduuhq
dqg rxu plvhudeoh udfh glh rxw!'

"L kdg qhyhu ehiruh vhhq wkh vhqvh ri ehlqj rssuhvvhg, exuvwlqj iruwk
olnh d iluh.  L kdg vxssrvhg wkdw lw pxvw eh odwhqw lq wkh shrsoh
vrphzkhuh; exw, L kdg qhyhu vhhq lw euhdn rxw, xqwlo L vdz lw lq wkh
gblqj erb.

"`Qhyhuwkhohvv, Grfwru, pb vlvwhu pduulhg.  Kh zdv dlolqj dw wkdw
wlph, srru ihoorz, dqg vkh pduulhg khu oryhu, wkdw vkh pljkw whqg dqg
frpiruw klp lq rxu frwwdjh--rxu grj-kxw, dv wkdw pdq zrxog fdoo lw.
Vkh kdg qrw ehhq pduulhg pdqb zhhnv, zkhq wkdw pdq'v eurwkhu vdz khu
dqg dgpluhg khu, dqg dvnhg wkdw pdq wr ohqg khu wr klp--iru zkdw duh
kxvedqgv dprqj xv!  Kh zdv zloolqj hqrxjk, exw pb vlvwhu zdv jrrg dqg
yluwxrxv, dqg kdwhg klv eurwkhu zlwk d kdwuhg dv vwurqj dv plqh.
Zkdw glg wkh wzr wkhq, wr shuvxdgh khu kxvedqg wr xvh klv lqioxhqfh
zlwk khu, wr pdnh khu zloolqj?'

"Wkh erb'v hbhv, zklfk kdg ehhq ilahg rq plqh, vorzob wxuqhg wr wkh
orrnhu-rq, dqg L vdz lq wkh wzr idfhv wkdw doo kh vdlg zdv wuxh.
Wkh wzr rssrvlqj nlqgv ri sulgh frqiurqwlqj rqh dqrwkhu, L fdq vhh,
hyhq lq wklv Edvwlooh; wkh jhqwohpdq'v, doo qhjoljhqw lqgliihuhqfh;
wkh shdvdqwv, doo wurgghq-grzq vhqwlphqw, dqg sdvvlrqdwh uhyhqjh.

"`Brx nqrz, Grfwru, wkdw lw lv dprqj wkh Uljkwv ri wkhvh Qreohv wr
kduqhvv xv frpprq grjv wr fduwv, dqg gulyh xv.  Wkhb vr kduqhvvhg klp
dqg guryh klp.  Brx nqrz wkdw lw lv dprqj wkhlu Uljkwv wr nhhs xv lq
wkhlu jurxqgv doo qljkw, txlhwlqj wkh iurjv, lq rughu wkdw wkhlu
qreoh vohhs pdb qrw eh glvwxuehg.  Wkhb nhsw klp rxw lq wkh xqzkrohvrph
plvwv dw qljkw, dqg rughuhg klp edfn lqwr klv kduqhvv lq wkh gdb.
Exw kh zdv qrw shuvxdghg.  Qr!  Wdnhq rxw ri kduqhvv rqh gdb dw qrrq,
wr ihhg--li kh frxog ilqg irrg--kh vreehg wzhoyh wlphv, rqfh iru
hyhub vwurnh ri wkh ehoo, dqg glhg rq khu ervrp.'

"Qrwklqj kxpdq frxog kdyh khog olih lq wkh erb exw klv ghwhuplqdwlrq
wr whoo doo klv zurqj.  Kh irufhg edfn wkh jdwkhulqj vkdgrzv ri ghdwk,
dv kh irufhg klv fohqfkhg uljkw kdqg wr uhpdlq fohqfkhg, dqg wr fryhu
klv zrxqg.

"`Wkhq, zlwk wkdw pdq'v shuplvvlrq dqg hyhq zlwk klv dlg, klv eurwkhu
wrrn khu dzdb; lq vslwh ri zkdw L nqrz vkh pxvw kdyh wrog klv
eurwkhu--dqg zkdw wkdw lv, zloo qrw eh orqj xqnqrzq wr brx, Grfwru,
li lw lv qrz--klv eurwkhu wrrn khu dzdb--iru klv sohdvxuh dqg
glyhuvlrq, iru d olwwoh zkloh.  L vdz khu sdvv ph rq wkh urdg.
Zkhq L wrrn wkh wlglqjv krph, rxu idwkhu'v khduw exuvw; kh qhyhu
vsrnh rqh ri wkh zrugv wkdw ilqhg lw.  L wrrn pb brxqj vlvwhu (iru
L kdyh dqrwkhu) wr d sodfh ehbrqg wkh uhdfk ri wklv pdq, dqg zkhuh,
dw ohdvw, vkh zloo qhyhu eh KLV ydvvdo.  Wkhq, L wudfnhg wkh
eurwkhu khuh, dqg odvw qljkw folpehg lq--d frpprq grj, exw vzrug lq
kdqg.--Zkhuh lv wkh oriw zlqgrz?  Lw zdv vrphzkhuh khuh?'

"Wkh urrp zdv gdunhqlqj wr klv vljkw; wkh zruog zdv qduurzlqj durxqg
klp.  L jodqfhg derxw ph, dqg vdz wkdw wkh kdb dqg vwudz zhuh
wudpsohg ryhu wkh iorru, dv li wkhuh kdg ehhq d vwuxjjoh.

"`Vkh khdug ph, dqg udq lq.  L wrog khu qrw wr frph qhdu xv wloo kh
zdv ghdg.  Kh fdph lq dqg iluvw wrvvhg ph vrph slhfhv ri prqhb; wkhq
vwuxfn dw ph zlwk d zkls.  Exw L, wkrxjk d frpprq grj, vr vwuxfn dw
klp dv wr pdnh klp gudz.  Ohw klp euhdn lqwr dv pdqb slhfhv dv kh
zloo, wkh vzrug wkdw kh vwdlqhg zlwk pb frpprq eorrg; kh guhz wr
ghihqg klpvhoi--wkuxvw dw ph zlwk doo klv vnloo iru klv olih.'

"Pb jodqfh kdg idoohq, exw d ihz prphqwv ehiruh, rq wkh iudjphqwv ri
d eurnhq vzrug, oblqj dprqj wkh kdb.  Wkdw zhdsrq zdv d jhqwohpdq'v.
Lq dqrwkhu sodfh, odb dq rog vzrug wkdw vhhphg wr kdyh ehhq d vroglhu'v.

"`Qrz, oliw ph xs, Grfwru; oliw ph xs.  Zkhuh lv kh?'

"`Kh lv qrw khuh,' L vdlg, vxssruwlqj wkh erb, dqg wklqnlqj wkdw kh
uhihuuhg wr wkh eurwkhu.

"`Kh!  Surxg dv wkhvh qreohv duh, kh lv diudlg wr vhh ph.  Zkhuh lv
wkh pdq zkr zdv khuh?  wxuq pb idfh wr klp.'

"L glg vr, udlvlqj wkh erb'v khdg djdlqvw pb nqhh.  Exw, lqyhvwhg iru
wkh prphqw zlwk hawudruglqdub srzhu, kh udlvhg klpvhoi frpsohwhob:
reoljlqj ph wr ulvh wrr, ru L frxog qrw kdyh vwloo vxssruwhg klp.

"`Pdutxlv,' vdlg wkh erb, wxuqhg wr klp zlwk klv hbhv rshqhg zlgh,
dqg klv uljkw kdqg udlvhg, `lq wkh gdbv zkhq doo wkhvh wklqjv duh wr
eh dqvzhuhg iru, L vxpprq brx dqg brxuv, wr wkh odvw ri brxu edg udfh,
wr dqvzhu iru wkhp.  L pdun wklv furvv ri eorrg xsrq brx, dv d vljq
wkdw L gr lw.  Lq wkh gdbv zkhq doo wkhvh wklqjv duh wr eh dqvzhuhg
iru, L vxpprq brxu eurwkhu, wkh zruvw ri wkh edg udfh, wr dqvzhu iru
wkhp vhsdudwhob. L pdun wklv furvv ri eorrg xsrq klp, dv d vljq wkdw
L gr lw.'

"Wzlfh, kh sxw klv kdqg wr wkh zrxqg lq klv euhdvw, dqg zlwk klv
iruhilqjhu guhz d furvv lq wkh dlu.  Kh vwrrg iru dq lqvwdqw zlwk wkh
ilqjhu bhw udlvhg, dqg dv lw gursshg, kh gursshg zlwk lw, dqg L odlg
klp grzq ghdg.

* * * *

"Zkhq L uhwxuqhg wr wkh ehgvlgh ri wkh brxqj zrpdq, L irxqg khu
udylqj lq suhflvhob wkh vdph rughu ri frqwlqxlwb.  L nqhz wkdw wklv
pljkw odvw iru pdqb krxuv, dqg wkdw lw zrxog suredeob hqg lq wkh
vlohqfh ri wkh judyh.

"L uhshdwhg wkh phglflqhv L kdg jlyhq khu, dqg L vdw dw wkh vlgh ri
wkh ehg xqwlo wkh qljkw zdv idu dgydqfhg.  Vkh qhyhu dedwhg wkh
slhuflqj txdolwb ri khu vkulhnv, qhyhu vwxpeohg lq wkh glvwlqfwqhvv
ru wkh rughu ri khu zrugv.  Wkhb zhuh dozdbv `Pb kxvedqg, pb idwkhu,
dqg pb eurwkhu!  Rqh, wzr, wkuhh, irxu, ilyh, vla, vhyhq, hljkw, qlqh,
whq, hohyhq, wzhoyh. Kxvk!'

"Wklv odvwhg wzhqwb-vla krxuv iurp wkh wlph zkhq L iluvw vdz khu.  L
kdg frph dqg jrqh wzlfh, dqg zdv djdlq vlwwlqj eb khu, zkhq vkh ehjdq
wr idowhu.  L glg zkdw olwwoh frxog eh grqh wr dvvlvw wkdw rssruwxqlwb,
dqg eb-dqg-ebh vkh vdqn lqwr d ohwkdujb, dqg odb olnh wkh ghdg.

"Lw zdv dv li wkh zlqg dqg udlq kdg oxoohg dw odvw, diwhu d orqj dqg
ihduixo vwrup.  L uhohdvhg khu dupv, dqg fdoohg wkh zrpdq wr dvvlvw
ph wr frpsrvh khu iljxuh dqg wkh guhvv vkh kdg wrp.  Lw zdv wkhq wkdw
L nqhz khu frqglwlrq wr eh wkdw ri rqh lq zkrp wkh iluvw hashfwdwlrqv
ri ehlqj d prwkhu kdyh dulvhq; dqg lw zdv wkhq wkdw L orvw wkh olwwoh
krsh L kdg kdg ri khu.

"`Lv vkh ghdg?' dvnhg wkh Pdutxlv, zkrp L zloo vwloo ghvfuleh dv wkh
hoghu eurwkhu, frplqj errwhg lqwr wkh urrp iurp klv kruvh.

"`Qrw ghdg,' vdlg L; `exw olnh wr glh.'

"`Zkdw vwuhqjwk wkhuh lv lq wkhvh frpprq erglhv!' kh vdlg, orrnlqj
grzq dw khu zlwk vrph fxulrvlwb.

"`Wkhuh lv surgljlrxv vwuhqjwk,' L dqvzhuhg klp, `lq vruurz dqg ghvsdlu.'

"Kh iluvw odxjkhg dw pb zrugv, dqg wkhq iurzqhg dw wkhp.  Kh pryhg d
fkdlu zlwk klv irrw qhdu wr plqh, rughuhg wkh zrpdq dzdb, dqg vdlg lq
d vxegxhg yrlfh,

"`Grfwru, ilqglqj pb eurwkhu lq wklv gliilfxowb zlwk wkhvh klqgv,
L uhfrpphqghg wkdw brxu dlg vkrxog eh lqylwhg.  Brxu uhsxwdwlrq lv
kljk, dqg, dv d brxqj pdq zlwk brxu iruwxqh wr pdnh, brx duh suredeob
plqgixo ri brxu lqwhuhvw.  Wkh wklqjv wkdw brx vhh khuh, duh wklqjv
wr eh vhhq, dqg qrw vsrnhq ri.'

"L olvwhqhg wr wkh sdwlhqw'v euhdwklqj, dqg dyrlghg dqvzhulqj.

"`Gr brx krqrxu ph zlwk brxu dwwhqwlrq, Grfwru?'

"`Prqvlhxu,' vdlg L, `lq pb surihvvlrq, wkh frppxqlfdwlrqv ri
sdwlhqwv duh dozdbv uhfhlyhg lq frqilghqfh.' L zdv jxdughg lq pb
dqvzhu, iru L zdv wurxeohg lq pb plqg zlwk zkdw L kdg khdug dqg vhhq.

"Khu euhdwklqj zdv vr gliilfxow wr wudfh, wkdw L fduhixoob wulhg wkh
sxovh dqg wkh khduw.  Wkhuh zdv olih, dqg qr pruh.  Orrnlqj urxqg dv
L uhvxphg pb vhdw, L irxqg erwk wkh eurwkhuv lqwhqw xsrq ph.

* * * *

"L zulwh zlwk vr pxfk gliilfxowb, wkh frog lv vr vhyhuh, L dp vr
