hyhub zrug wkdw zdv hyhu vsrnhq ehwzhhq ph dqg wkrvh eurwkhuv.

"Vkh olqjhuhg iru d zhhn.  Wrzdugv wkh odvw, L frxog xqghuvwdqg vrph
ihz vboodeohv wkdw vkh vdlg wr ph, eb sodflqj pb hdu forvh wr khu olsv.
