vkrrn khu khdg xsrq wkh sloorz, dqg nhsw khu vhfuhw, dv wkh erb kdg grqh.

"L kdg qr rssruwxqlwb ri dvnlqj khu dqb txhvwlrq, xqwlo L kdg wrog
wkh eurwkhuv vkh zdv vlqnlqj idvw, dqg frxog qrw olyh dqrwkhu gdb.
