pljkw krog zlwk khu; dv li--wkh wkrxjkw sdvvhg wkurxjk pb plqg--L
zhuh gblqj wrr.

"L dozdbv revhuyhg wkdw wkhlu sulgh elwwhuob uhvhqwhg wkh brxqjhu
eurwkhu'v (dv L fdoo klp) kdylqj furvvhg vzrugv zlwk d shdvdqw, dqg
