"Wkh eurwkhuv zhuh zdlwlqj lq d urrp grzq-vwdluv, lpsdwlhqw wr ulgh
dzdb.  L kdg khdug wkhp, dorqh dw wkh ehgvlgh, vwulnlqj wkhlu errwv
