"`L frqjudwxodwh brx, pb eurwkhu,'zhuh klv zrugv dv kh wxuqhg urxqg.

"Kh kdg ehiruh riihuhg ph prqhb, zklfk L kdg srvwsrqhg wdnlqj.  Kh
