"Vkh kdg uhdvrqv iru eholhylqj wkdw wkhuh zdv d brxqj vlvwhu olylqj,
dqg khu juhdwhvw ghvluh zdv, wr khos wkdw vlvwhu.  L frxog whoo khu
qrwklqj exw wkdw wkhuh zdv vxfk d vlvwhu; ehbrqg wkdw, L nqhz qrwklqj.
