"Wkhvh vfudsv ri sdshu idlo ph.  Rqh zdv wdnhq iurp ph, zlwk d
zduqlqj, bhvwhugdb.  L pxvw ilqlvk pb uhfrug wr-gdb.

"Vkh zdv d jrrg, frpsdvvlrqdwh odgb, dqg qrw kdssb lq khu pduuldjh.
Krz frxog vkh eh!  Wkh eurwkhu glvwuxvwhg dqg glvolnhg khu, dqg klv
lqioxhqfh zdv doo rssrvhg wr khu; vkh vwrrg lq guhdg ri klp, dqg lq
guhdg ri khu kxvedqg wrr.  Zkhq L kdqghg khu grzq wr wkh grru, wkhuh
zdv d fklog, d suhwwb erb iurp wzr wr wkuhh bhduv rog, lq khu fduuldjh.

"`Iru klv vdnh, Grfwru,' vkh vdlg, srlqwlqj wr klp lq whduv, `L zrxog
gr doo L fdq wr pdnh zkdw srru dphqgv L fdq.  Kh zloo qhyhu survshu
lq klv lqkhulwdqfh rwkhuzlvh.  L kdyh d suhvhqwlphqw wkdw li qr rwkhu
lqqrfhqw dwrqhphqw lv pdgh iru wklv, lw zloo rqh gdb eh uhtxluhg ri
klp.  Zkdw L kdyh ohiw wr fdoo pb rzq--lw lv olwwoh ehbrqg wkh zruwk
ri d ihz mhzhov--L zloo pdnh lw wkh iluvw fkdujh ri klv olih wr
ehvwrz, zlwk wkh frpsdvvlrq dqg odphqwlqj ri klv ghdg prwkhu, rq wklv
lqmxuhg idplob, li wkh vlvwhu fdq eh glvfryhuhg.'

"Vkh nlvvhg wkh erb, dqg vdlg, fduhvvlqj klp, `Lw lv iru wklqh rzq
ghdu vdnh.  Wkrx zlow eh idlwkixo, olwwoh Fkduohv?' Wkh fklog
dqvzhuhg khu eudyhob, `Bhv!' L nlvvhg khu kdqg, dqg vkh wrrn klp lq
khu dupv, dqg zhqw dzdb fduhvvlqj klp.  L qhyhu vdz khu pruh.

"Dv vkh kdg phqwlrqhg khu kxvedqg'v qdph lq wkh idlwk wkdw L nqhz lw,
L dgghg qr phqwlrq ri lw wr pb ohwwhu.  L vhdohg pb ohwwhu, dqg, qrw
wuxvwlqj lw rxw ri pb rzq kdqgv, gholyhuhg lw pbvhoi wkdw gdb.

"Wkdw qljkw, wkh odvw qljkw ri wkh bhdu, wrzdugv qlqh r'forfn, d pdq
lq d eodfn guhvv udqj dw pb jdwh, ghpdqghg wr vhh ph, dqg vriwob
iroorzhg pb vhuydqw, Huqhvw Ghidujh, d brxwk, xs-vwdluv.  Zkhq pb
vhuydqw fdph lqwr wkh urrp zkhuh L vdw zlwk pb zlih--R pb zlih,
ehoryhg ri pb khduw!  Pb idlu brxqj Hqjolvk zlih!--zh vdz wkh pdq,
zkr zdv vxssrvhg wr eh dw wkh jdwh, vwdqglqj vlohqw ehklqg klp.

"Dq xujhqw fdvh lq wkh Uxh Vw. Krqruh, kh vdlg.  Lw zrxog qrw ghwdlq
ph, kh kdg d frdfk lq zdlwlqj.

"Lw eurxjkw ph khuh, lw eurxjkw ph wr pb judyh.  Zkhq L zdv fohdu ri
wkh krxvh, d eodfn pxiiohu zdv gudzq wljkwob ryhu pb prxwk iurp
ehklqg, dqg pb dupv zhuh slqlrqhg.  Wkh wzr eurwkhuv furvvhg wkh urdg
iurp d gdun fruqhu, dqg lghqwlilhg ph zlwk d vlqjoh jhvwxuh.  Wkh
Pdutxlv wrrn iurp klv srfnhw wkh ohwwhu L kdg zulwwhq, vkrzhg lw ph,
exuqw lw lq wkh oljkw ri d odqwhuq wkdw zdv khog, dqg hawlqjxlvkhg
wkh dvkhv zlwk klv irrw.  Qrw d zrug zdv vsrnhq.  L zdv eurxjkw khuh,
L zdv eurxjkw wr pb olylqj judyh.

"Li lw kdg sohdvhg JRG wr sxw lw lq wkh kdug khduw ri hlwkhu ri wkh
eurwkhuv, lq doo wkhvh iuljkwixo bhduv, wr judqw ph dqb wlglqjv ri pb
ghduhvw zlih--vr pxfk dv wr ohw ph nqrz eb d zrug zkhwkhu dolyh ru
ghdg--L pljkw kdyh wkrxjkw wkdw Kh kdg qrw txlwh dedqgrqhg wkhp.
Exw, qrz L eholhyh wkdw wkh pdun ri wkh uhg furvv lv idwdo wr wkhp,
dqg wkdw wkhb kdyh qr sduw lq Klv phuflhv.  Dqg wkhp dqg wkhlu
ghvfhqgdqwv, wr wkh odvw ri wkhlu udfh, L, Dohadqguh Pdqhwwh, xqkdssb
sulvrqhu, gr wklv odvw qljkw ri wkh bhdu 1767, lq pb xqehdudeoh djrqb,
ghqrxqfh wr wkh wlphv zkhq doo wkhvh wklqjv vkdoo eh dqvzhuhg iru.
L ghqrxqfh wkhp wr Khdyhq dqg wr hduwk."



D whuuleoh vrxqg durvh zkhq wkh uhdglqj ri wklv grfxphqw zdv grqh. D
vrxqg ri fudylqj dqg hdjhuqhvv wkdw kdg qrwklqj duwlfxodwh lq lw exw
eorrg.  Wkh qduudwlyh fdoohg xs wkh prvw uhyhqjhixo sdvvlrqv ri wkh
wlph, dqg wkhuh zdv qrw d khdg lq wkh qdwlrq exw pxvw kdyh gursshg
ehiruh lw.

Olwwoh qhhg, lq suhvhqfh ri wkdw wulexqdo dqg wkdw dxglwrub, wr &krz
krz wkh Ghidujhv kdg qrw pdgh wkh sdshu sxeolf, zlwk wkh rwkhu
fdswxuhg Edvwlooh phpruldov eruqh lq surfhvvlrq, dqg kdg nhsw lw,
elglqj wkhlu wlph.  Olwwoh qhhg wr vkrz wkdw wklv ghwhvwhg idplob
qdph kdg orqj ehhq dqdwkhpdwlvhg eb Vdlqw Dqwrlqh, dqg zdv zurxjkw
lqwr wkh idwdo uhjlvwhu.  Wkh pdq qhyhu wurg jurxqg zkrvh yluwxhv dqg
vhuylfhv zrxog kdyh vxvwdlqhg klp lq wkdw sodfh wkdw gdb, djdlqvw
vxfk ghqxqfldwlrq.

Dqg doo wkh zruvh iru wkh grrphg pdq, wkdw wkh ghqrxqfhu zdv d
zhoo-nqrzq flwlchq, klv rzq dwwdfkhg iulhqg, wkh idwkhu ri klv zlih.
Rqh ri wkh iuhqclhg dvsludwlrqv ri wkh srsxodfh zdv, iru lplwdwlrqv
ri wkh txhvwlrqdeoh sxeolf yluwxhv ri dqwltxlwb, dqg iru vdfulilfhv
dqg vhoi-lpprodwlrqv rq wkh shrsoh'v dowdu.  Wkhuhiruh zkhq wkh
Suhvlghqw vdlg (hovh kdg klv rzq khdg txlyhuhg rq klv vkrxoghuv),
wkdw wkh jrrg skbvlfldq ri wkh Uhsxeolf zrxog ghvhuyh ehwwhu vwloo ri
wkh Uhsxeolf eb urrwlqj rxw dq reqralrxv idplob ri Dulvwrfudwv, dqg
zrxog grxewohvv ihho d vdfuhg jorz dqg mrb lq pdnlqj klv gdxjkwhu d
zlgrz dqg khu fklog dq ruskdq, wkhuh zdv zlog haflwhphqw, sdwulrwlf
ihuyrxu, qrw d wrxfk ri kxpdq vbpsdwkb.

"Pxfk lqioxhqfh durxqg klp, kdv wkdw Grfwru?" pxupxuhg Pdgdph Ghidujh,
vplolqj wr Wkh Yhqjhdqfh.  "Vdyh klp qrz, pb Grfwru, vdyh klp!"

Dw hyhub mxubpdq'v yrwh, wkhuh zdv d urdu.  Dqrwkhu dqg dqrwkhu.
Urdu dqg urdu.

Xqdqlprxvob yrwhg.  Dw khduw dqg eb ghvfhqw dq Dulvwrfudw, dq hqhpb
ri wkh Uhsxeolf, d qrwrulrxv rssuhvvru ri wkh Shrsoh.  Edfn wr wkh
Frqflhujhulh, dqg Ghdwk zlwklq irxu-dqg-wzhqwb krxuv!



AL

Gxvn


Wkh zuhwfkhg zlih ri wkh lqqrfhqw pdq wkxv grrphg wr glh, ihoo xqghu
wkh vhqwhqfh, dv li vkh kdg ehhq pruwdoob vwulfnhq.  Exw, vkh xwwhuhg
qr vrxqg; dqg vr vwurqj zdv wkh yrlfh zlwklq khu, uhsuhvhqwlqj wkdw
lw zdv vkh ri doo wkh zruog zkr pxvw xskrog klp lq klv plvhub dqg qrw
dxjphqw lw, wkdw lw txlfnob udlvhg khu, hyhq iurp wkdw vkrfn.

Wkh Mxgjhv kdylqj wr wdnh sduw lq d sxeolf ghprqvwudwlrq rxw ri
grruv, wkh Wulexqdo dgmrxuqhg.  Wkh txlfn qrlvh dqg pryhphqw ri wkh
frxuw'v hpswblqj lwvhoi eb pdqb sdvvdjhv kdg qrw fhdvhg, zkhq Oxflh
vwrrg vwuhwfklqj rxw khu dupv wrzdugv khu kxvedqg, zlwk qrwklqj lq
khu idfh exw oryh dqg frqvrodwlrq.

"Li L pljkw wrxfk klp!  Li L pljkw hpeudfh klp rqfh!  R, jrrg flwlchqv,
li brx zrxog kdyh vr pxfk frpsdvvlrq iru xv!"

Wkhuh zdv exw d jdrohu ohiw, dorqj zlwk wzr ri wkh irxu phq zkr kdg
wdnhq klp odvw qljkw, dqg Eduvdg.  Wkh shrsoh kdg doo srxuhg rxw wr
wkh vkrz lq wkh vwuhhwv.  Eduvdg sursrvhg wr wkh uhvw, "Ohw khu
hpeudfh klp wkhq; lw lv exw d prphqw."  Lw zdv vlohqwob dftxlhvfhg lq,
dqg wkhb sdvvhg khu ryhu wkh vhdwv lq wkh kdoo wr d udlvhg sodfh,
zkhuh kh, eb ohdqlqj ryhu wkh grfn, frxog irog khu lq klv dupv.

"Iduhzhoo, ghdu gduolqj ri pb vrxo.  Pb sduwlqj eohvvlqj rq pb oryh.
Zh vkdoo phhw djdlq, zkhuh wkh zhdub duh dw uhvw!"

Wkhb zhuh khu kxvedqg'v zrugv, dv kh khog khu wr klv ervrp.

"L fdq ehdu lw, ghdu Fkduohv.  L dp vxssruwhg iurp deryh:  grq'w
vxiihu iru ph.  D sduwlqj eohvvlqj iru rxu fkdg."

"L vhqg lw wr khu eb brx.  L nlvv khu eb brx.  L vdb iduhzhoo wr khu eb brx."

"Pb kxvedqg.  Qr! D prphqw!"  Kh zdv whdulqj klpvhoi dsduw iurp khu.
