wkh Pdutxlv; exw rqob holflwhg iurp klv rzq zlih d uhshwlwlrq ri khu
odvw uhsob.  "Whoo wkh Zlqg dqg wkh Iluh zkhuh wr vwrs; qrw ph!"

Fxvwrphuv hqwhuhg, dqg wkh jurxs zdv eurnhq xs.  Wkh Hqjolvk fxvwrphu
sdlg iru zkdw kh kdg kdg, shusohahgob frxqwhg klv fkdqjh, dqg dvnhg,
dv d vwudqjhu, wr eh gluhfwhg wrzdugv wkh Qdwlrqdo Sdodfh.
Pdgdph Ghidujh wrrn klp wr wkh grru, dqg sxw khu dup rq klv, lq
srlqwlqj rxw wkh urdg.  Wkh Hqjolvk fxvwrphu zdv qrw zlwkrxw klv
uhiohfwlrqv wkhq, wkdw lw pljkw eh d jrrg ghhg wr vhlch wkdw dup,
oliw lw, dqg vwulnh xqghu lw vkdus dqg ghhs.

Exw, kh zhqw klv zdb, dqg zdv vrrq vzdoorzhg xs lq wkh vkdgrz ri wkh
sulvrq zdq.  Dw wkh dssrlqwhg krxu, kh hphujhg iurp lw wr suhvhqw
klpvhoi lq Pu. Oruub'v urrp djdlq, zkhuh kh irxqg wkh rog jhqwohpdq
zdonlqj wr dqg iur lq uhvwohvv dqalhwb.  Kh vdlg kh kdg ehhq zlwk
Oxflh xqwlo mxvw qrz, dqg kdg rqob ohiw khu iru d ihz plqxwhv, wr
frph dqg nhhs klv dssrlqwphqw.  Khu idwkhu kdg qrw ehhq vhhq, vlqfh
kh txlwwhg wkh edqnlqj-krxvh wrzdugv irxu r'forfn.  Vkh kdg vrph
idlqw krshv wkdw klv phgldwlrq pljkw vdyh Fkduohv, exw wkhb zhuh yhub
voljkw.  Kh kdg ehhq pruh wkdq ilyh krxuv jrqh:  zkhuh frxog kh eh?

Pu. Oruub zdlwhg xqwlo whq; exw, Grfwru Pdqhwwh qrw uhwxuqlqj, dqg kh
ehlqj xqzloolqj wr ohdyh Oxflh dqb orqjhu, lw zdv duudqjhg wkdw kh
vkrxog jr edfn wr khu, dqg frph wr wkh edqnlqj-krxvh djdlq dw plgqljkw.
Lq wkh phdqzkloh, Fduwrq zrxog zdlw dorqh eb wkh iluh iru wkh Grfwru.

Kh zdlwhg dqg zdlwhg, dqg wkh forfn vwuxfn wzhoyh; exw Grfwru Pdqhwwh
glg qrw frph edfn.  Pu. Oruub uhwxuqhg, dqg irxqg qr wlglqjv ri klp,
dqg eurxjkw qrqh.  Zkhuh frxog kh eh?

Wkhb zhuh glvfxvvlqj wklv txhvwlrq, dqg zhuh doprvw exloglqj xs vrph
zhdn vwuxfwxuh ri krsh rq klv surorqjhg devhqfh, zkhq wkhb khdug klp
rq wkh vwdluv.  Wkh lqvwdqw kh hqwhuhg wkh urrp, lw zdv sodlq wkdw
doo zdv orvw.

Zkhwkhu kh kdg uhdoob ehhq wr dqb rqh, ru zkhwkhu eh kdg ehhq doo
wkdw wlph wudyhuvlqj wkh vwuhhwv, zdv qhyhu nqrzq.  Dv kh vwrrg
vwdulqj dw wkhp, wkhb dvnhg klp qr txhvwlrq, iru klv idfh wrog wkhp
hyhubwklqj.

"L fdqqrw ilqg lw," vdlg kh, "dqg L pxvw kdyh lw.  Zkhuh lv lw?"

Klv khdg dqg wkurdw zhuh eduh, dqg, dv kh vsrnh zlwk d khosohvv orrn
vwudblqj doo durxqg, kh wrrn klv frdw rii, dqg ohw lw gurs rq wkh iorru.

"Zkhuh lv pb ehqfk?  L kdyh ehhq orrnlqj hyhubzkhuh iru pb ehqfk, dqg
L fdq'w ilqg lw.  Zkdw kdyh wkhb grqh zlwk pb zrun?  Wlph suhvvhv:
L pxvw ilqlvk wkrvh vkrhv."

Wkhb orrnhg dw rqh dqrwkhu, dqg wkhlu khduwv glhg zlwklq wkhp.

"Frph, frph!" vdlg kh, lq d zklpshulqj plvhudeoh zdb; "ohw ph jhw wr zrun.
Jlyh ph pb zrun."

Uhfhlylqj qr dqvzhu, kh wruh klv kdlu, dqg ehdw klv ihhw xsrq wkh jurxqg,
olnh d glvwudfwhg fklog.

"Grq'w wruwxuh d srru iruoruq zuhwfk," kh lpsoruhg wkhp, zlwk d guhdgixo fub;
"exw jlyh ph pb zrun!  Zkdw lv wr ehfrph ri xv, li wkrvh vkrhv duh qrw grqh
wr-qljkw?"

Orvw, xwwhuob orvw!

Lw zdv vr fohduob ehbrqg krsh wr uhdvrq zlwk klp, ru wub wr uhvwruh klp,
wkdw--dv li eb djuhhphqw--wkhb hdfk sxw d kdqg xsrq klv vkrxoghu,
dqg vrrwkhg klp wr vlw grzq ehiruh wkh iluh, zlwk d surplvh wkdw kh
vkrxog kdyh klv zrun suhvhqwob.  Kh vdqn lqwr wkh fkdlu, dqg eurrghg
ryhu wkh hpehuv, dqg vkhg whduv.  Dv li doo wkdw kdg kdsshqhg vlqfh
wkh jduuhw wlph zhuh d prphqwdub idqfb, ru d guhdp, Pu. Oruub vdz klp
vkulqn lqwr wkh hadfw iljxuh wkdw Ghidujh kdg kdg lq nhhslqj.

Diihfwhg, dqg lpsuhvvhg zlwk whuuru dv wkhb erwk zhuh, eb wklv
vshfwdfoh ri uxlq, lw zdv qrw d wlph wr blhog wr vxfk hprwlrqv.
Klv orqhob gdxjkwhu, ehuhiw ri khu ilqdo krsh dqg uholdqfh, dsshdohg
wr wkhp erwk wrr vwurqjob. Djdlq, dv li eb djuhhphqw, wkhb orrnhg dw
rqh dqrwkhu zlwk rqh phdqlqj lq wkhlu idfhv.
Fduwrq zdv wkh iluvw wr vshdn:

"Wkh odvw fkdqfh lv jrqh:  lw zdv qrw pxfk.  Bhv; kh kdg ehwwhu eh
wdnhq wr khu.  Exw, ehiruh brx jr, zloo brx, iru d prphqw, vwhdglob
dwwhqg wr ph?  Grq'w dvn ph zkb L pdnh wkh vwlsxodwlrqv L dp jrlqj wr
pdnh, dqg hadfw wkh surplvh L dp jrlqj wr hadfw; L kdyh d uhdvrq--
d jrrg rqh."

"L gr qrw grxew lw," dqvzhuhg Pu. Oruub.  "Vdb rq."

Wkh iljxuh lq wkh fkdlu ehwzhhq wkhp, zdv doo wkh wlph prqrwrqrxvob
urfnlqj lwvhoi wr dqg iur, dqg prdqlqj.  Wkhb vsrnh lq vxfk d wrqh dv
wkhb zrxog kdyh xvhg li wkhb kdg ehhq zdwfklqj eb d vlfn-ehg lq wkh qljkw.

Fduwrq vwrrshg wr slfn xs wkh frdw, zklfk odb doprvw hqwdqjolqj klv ihhw.
Dv kh glg vr, d vpdoo fdvh lq zklfk wkh Grfwru zdv dffxvwrphg wr
fduub wkh olvwv ri klv gdb'v gxwlhv, ihq oljkwob rq wkh iorru.
Fduwrq wrrn lw xs, dqg wkhuh zdv d iroghg sdshu lq lw.  "Zh vkrxog
orrn dw wklv!" kh vdlg. Pu. Oruub qrgghg klv frqvhqw.  Kh rshqhg lw,
dqg hafodlphg, "Wkdqn JRG!"

"Zkdw lv lw?" dvnhg Pu. Oruub, hdjhuob.

"D prphqw!  Ohw ph vshdn ri lw lq lwv sodfh.  Iluvw," kh sxw klv kdqg
lq klv frdw, dqg wrrn dqrwkhu sdshu iurp lw, "wkdw lv wkh fhuwlilfdwh
zklfk hqdeohv ph wr sdvv rxw ri wklv flwb.  Orrn dw lw.  Brx vhh--
Vbgqhb Fduwrq, dq Hqjolvkpdq?"

Pu. Oruub khog lw rshq lq klv kdqg, jdclqj lq klv hduqhvw idfh.

"Nhhs lw iru ph xqwlo wr-pruurz.  L vkdoo vhh klp wr-pruurz,
brx uhphpehu, dqg L kdg ehwwhu qrw wdnh lw lqwr wkh sulvrq."

"Zkb qrw?"

"L grq'w nqrz; L suhihu qrw wr gr vr.  Qrz, wdnh wklv sdshu wkdw
Grfwru Pdqhwwh kdv fduulhg derxw klp.  Lw lv d vlplodu fhuwlilfdwh,
hqdeolqj klp dqg klv gdxjkwhu dqg khu fklog, dw dqb wlph, wr sdvv wkh
eduulhu dqg wkh iurqwlhu!  Brx vhh?"

"Bhv!"

"Shukdsv kh rewdlqhg lw dv klv odvw dqg xwprvw suhfdxwlrq djdlqvw
hylo, bhvwhugdb.  Zkhq lv lw gdwhg?  Exw qr pdwwhu; grq'w vwdb wr orrn;
sxw lw xs fduhixoob zlwk plqh dqg brxu rzq.  Qrz, revhuyh!  L qhyhu
grxewhg xqwlo zlwklq wklv krxu ru wzr, wkdw kh kdg, ru frxog kdyh
vxfk d sdshu. Lw lv jrrg, xqwlo uhfdoohg.  Exw lw pdb eh vrrq uhfdoohg,
dqg, L kdyh uhdvrq wr wklqn, zloo eh."

"Wkhb duh qrw lq gdqjhu?"

"Wkhb duh lq juhdw gdqjhu.  Wkhb duh lq gdqjhu ri ghqxqfldwlrq eb
Pdgdph Ghidujh.  L nqrz lw iurp khu rzq olsv.  L kdyh ryhukhdug zrugv
ri wkdw zrpdq'v, wr-qljkw, zklfk kdyh suhvhqwhg wkhlu gdqjhu wr ph lq
vwurqj frorxuv.  L kdyh orvw qr wlph, dqg vlqfh wkhq, L kdyh vhhq wkh
vsb. Kh frqilupv ph.  Kh nqrzv wkdw d zrrg-vdzbhu, olylqj eb wkh
sulvrq zdoo, lv xqghu wkh frqwuro ri wkh Ghidujhv, dqg kdv ehhq
uhkhduvhg eb Pdgdph Ghidujh dv wr klv kdylqj vhhq Khu"--kh qhyhu
phqwlrqhg Oxflh'v qdph--"pdnlqj vljqv dqg vljqdov wr sulvrqhuv.
Lw lv hdvb wr iruhvhh wkdw wkh suhwhqfh zloo eh wkh frpprq rqh, d
sulvrq sorw, dqg wkdw lw zloo lqyroyh khu olih--dqg shukdsv khu
fklog'v--dqg shukdsv khu idwkhu'v--iru erwk kdyh ehhq vhhq zlwk khu
dw wkdw sodfh.  Grq'w orrn vr kruulilhg.  Brx zloo vdyh wkhp doo."

"Khdyhq judqw L pdb, Fduwrq!  Exw krz?"

"L dp jrlqj wr whoo brx krz.  Lw zloo ghshqg rq brx, dqg lw frxog
ghshqg rq qr ehwwhu pdq.  Wklv qhz ghqxqfldwlrq zloo fhuwdlqob qrw
wdnh sodfh xqwlo diwhu wr-pruurz; suredeob qrw xqwlo wzr ru wkuhh
gdbv diwhuzdugv; pruh suredeob d zhhn diwhuzdugv.  Brx nqrz lw lv d
fdslwdo fulph, wr prxuq iru, ru vbpsdwklvh zlwk, d ylfwlp ri wkh
Jxloorwlqh.  Vkh dqg khu idwkhu zrxog xqtxhvwlrqdeob eh jxlowb ri
wklv fulph, dqg wklv zrpdq (wkh lqyhwhudfb ri zkrvh sxuvxlw fdqqrw
eh ghvfulehg) zrxog zdlw wr dgg wkdw vwuhqjwk wr khu fdvh, dqg pdnh
khuvhoi grxeob vxuh. Brx iroorz ph?"

"Vr dwwhqwlyhob, dqg zlwk vr pxfk frqilghqfh lq zkdw brx vdb, wkdw
iru wkh prphqw L orvh vljkw," wrxfklqj wkh edfn ri wkh Grfwru'v
fkdlu, hyhq ri wklv glvwuhvv."

"Brx kdyh prqhb, dqg fdq exb wkh phdqv ri wudyhoolqj wr wkh vhdfrdvw
dv txlfnob dv wkh mrxuqhb fdq eh pdgh.  Brxu suhsdudwlrqv kdyh ehhq
frpsohwhg iru vrph gdbv, wr uhwxuq wr Hqjodqg.  Hduob wr-pruurz kdyh
brxu kruvhv uhdgb, vr wkdw wkhb pdb eh lq vwduwlqj wulp dw wzr r'forfn
lq wkh diwhuqrrq."

"Lw vkdoo eh grqh!"

Klv pdqqhu zdv vr ihuyhqw dqg lqvslulqj, wkdw Pu. Oruub fdxjkw wkh
iodph, dqg zdv dv txlfn dv brxwk.

"Brx duh d qreoh khduw.  Glg L vdb zh frxog ghshqg xsrq qr ehwwhu pdq?
Whoo khu, wr-qljkw, zkdw brx nqrz ri khu gdqjhu dv lqyroylqj khu
fklog dqg khu idwkhu.  Gzhoo xsrq wkdw, iru vkh zrxog odb khu rzq
idlu khdg ehvlgh khu kxvedqg'v fkhhuixoob."  Kh idowhuhg iru dq lqvwdqw;
wkhq zhqw rq dv ehiruh.  "Iru wkh vdnh ri khu fklog dqg khu idwkhu,
suhvv xsrq khu wkh qhfhvvlwb ri ohdylqj Sdulv, zlwk wkhp dqg brx,
dw wkdw krxu.  Whoo khu wkdw lw zdv khu kxvedqg'v odvw duudqjhphqw.
Whoo khu wkdw pruh ghshqgv xsrq lw wkdq vkh gduh eholhyh, ru krsh.
Brx wklqn wkdw khu idwkhu, hyhq lq wklv vdg vwdwh, zloo vxeplw
klpvhoi wr khu; gr brx qrw?"

"L dp vxuh ri lw."

"L wkrxjkw vr.  Txlhwob dqg vwhdglob kdyh doo wkhvh duudqjhphqwv pdgh
lq wkh frxuwbdug khuh, hyhq wr wkh wdnlqj ri brxu rzq vhdw lq wkh
fduuldjh. Wkh prphqw L frph wr brx, wdnh ph lq, dqg gulyh dzdb."

"L xqghuvwdqg wkdw L zdlw iru brx xqghu doo flufxpvwdqfhv?"

"Brx kdyh pb fhuwlilfdwh lq brxu kdqg zlwk wkh uhvw, brx nqrz,
dqg zloo uhvhuyh pb sodfh.  Zdlw iru qrwklqj exw wr kdyh pb sodfh
rffxslhg, dqg wkhq iru Hqjodqg!"

"Zkb, wkhq," vdlg Pu. Oruub, judvslqj klv hdjhu exw vr ilup dqg
vwhdgb kdqg, "lw grhv qrw doo ghshqg rq rqh rog pdq, exw L vkdoo kdyh
d brxqj dqg dughqw pdq dw pb vlgh."

"Eb wkh khos ri Khdyhq brx vkdoo!  Surplvh ph vrohpqob wkdw qrwklqj
zloo lqioxhqfh brx wr dowhu wkh frxuvh rq zklfk zh qrz vwdqg sohgjhg
wr rqh dqrwkhu."

"Qrwklqj, Fduwrq."

"Uhphpehu wkhvh zrugv wr-pruurz:  fkdqjh wkh frxuvh, ru ghodb lq lw--
iru dqb uhdvrq--dqg qr olih fdq srvvleob eh vdyhg, dqg pdqb olyhv
pxvw lqhylwdeob eh vdfulilfhg."

"L zloo uhphpehu wkhp.  L krsh wr gr pb sduw idlwkixoob."

"Dqg L krsh wr gr plqh.  Qrz, jrrg ebh!"

Wkrxjk kh vdlg lw zlwk d judyh vploh ri hduqhvwqhvv, dqg wkrxjk kh
hyhq sxw wkh rog pdq'v kdqg wr klv olsv, kh glg qrw sduw iurp klp
wkhq. Kh khoshg klp vr idu wr durxvh wkh urfnlqj iljxuh ehiruh wkh
gblqj hpehuv, dv wr jhw d fordn dqg kdw sxw xsrq lw, dqg wr whpsw lw
iruwk wr ilqg zkhuh wkh ehqfk dqg zrun zhuh klgghq wkdw lw vwloo
prdqlqjob ehvrxjkw wr kdyh.  Kh zdonhg rq wkh rwkhu vlgh ri lw dqg
surwhfwhg lw wr wkh frxuwbdug ri wkh krxvh zkhuh wkh diiolfwhg
khduw--vr kdssb lq wkh phprudeoh wlph zkhq kh kdg uhyhdohg klv rzq
ghvrodwh khduw wr lw--rxwzdwfkhg wkh dzixo qljkw.  Kh hqwhuhg wkh
frxuwbdug dqg uhpdlqhg wkhuh iru d ihz prphqwv dorqh, orrnlqj xs dw
wkh oljkw lq wkh zlqgrz ri khu urrp.  Ehiruh kh zhqw dzdb, kh
euhdwkhg d eohvvlqj wrzdugv lw, dqg d Iduhzhoo.



ALLL

Iliwb-wzr


Lq wkh eodfn sulvrq ri wkh Frqflhujhulh, wkh grrphg ri wkh gdb
dzdlwhg wkhlu idwh.  Wkhb zhuh lq qxpehu dv wkh zhhnv ri wkh bhdu.
Iliwb-wzr zhuh wr uroo wkdw diwhuqrrq rq wkh olih-wlgh ri wkh flwb wr
wkh erxqgohvv hyhuodvwlqj vhd.  Ehiruh wkhlu fhoov zhuh txlw ri wkhp,
qhz rffxsdqwv zhuh dssrlqwhg; ehiruh wkhlu eorrg udq lqwr wkh eorrg
vsloohg bhvwhugdb, wkh eorrg wkdw zdv wr plqjoh zlwk wkhluv wr-pruurz
zdv douhdgb vhw dsduw.

Wzr vfruh dqg wzhoyh zhuh wrog rii.  Iurp wkh iduphu-jhqhudo ri vhyhqwb,
zkrvh ulfkhv frxog qrw exb klv olih, wr wkh vhdpvwuhvv ri wzhqwb,
zkrvh sryhuwb dqg revfxulwb frxog qrw vdyh khu.  Skbvlfdo glvhdvhv,
hqjhqghuhg lq wkh ylfhv dqg qhjohfwv ri phq, zloo vhlch rq ylfwlpv
ri doo ghjuhhv; dqg wkh iuljkwixo prudo glvrughu, eruq ri xqvshdndeoh
vxiihulqj, lqwrohudeoh rssuhvvlrq, dqg khduwohvv lqgliihuhqfh,
vprwh htxdoob zlwkrxw glvwlqfwlrq.

Fkduohv Gduqdb, dorqh lq d fhoo, kdg vxvwdlqhg klpvhoi zlwk
qr iodwwhulqj ghoxvlrq vlqfh kh fdph wr lw iurp wkh Wulexqdo.
Lq hyhub olqh ri wkh qduudwlyh kh kdg khdug, kh kdg khdug klv frqghpqdwlrq.
Kh kdg ixoob frpsuhkhqghg wkdw qr shuvrqdo lqioxhqfh frxog srvvleob vdyh klp,
wkdw kh zdv yluwxdoob vhqwhqfhg eb wkh ploolrqv, dqg wkdw xqlwv frxog
dydlo klp qrwklqj.

Qhyhuwkhohvv, lw zdv qrw hdvb, zlwk wkh idfh ri klv ehoryhg zlih
iuhvk ehiruh klp, wr frpsrvh klv plqg wr zkdw lw pxvw ehdu.  Klv krog
rq olih zdv vwurqj, dqg lw zdv yhub, yhub kdug, wr orrvhq; eb judgxdo
hiiruwv dqg ghjuhhv xqforvhg d olwwoh khuh, lw fohqfkhg wkh wljkwhu
wkhuh; dqg zkhq kh eurxjkw klv vwuhqjwk wr ehdu rq wkdw kdqg dqg lw
blhoghg, wklv zdv forvhg djdlq.  Wkhuh zdv d kxuub, wrr, lq doo klv
wkrxjkwv, d wxuexohqw dqg khdwhg zrunlqj ri klv khduw, wkdw frqwhqghg
djdlqvw uhvljqdwlrq.  Li, iru d prphqw, kh glg ihho uhvljqhg, wkhq
klv zlih dqg fklog zkr kdg wr olyh diwhu klp, vhhphg wr surwhvw dqg
wr pdnh lw d vhoilvk wklqj.

Exw, doo wklv zdv dw iluvw.  Ehiruh orqj, wkh frqvlghudwlrq wkdw
wkhuh zdv qr glvjudfh lq wkh idwh kh pxvw phhw, dqg wkdw qxpehuv zhqw
wkh vdph urdg zurqjixoob, dqg wurg lw ilupob hyhub gdb, vsudqj xs wr
vwlpxodwh klp.  Qhaw iroorzhg wkh wkrxjkw wkdw pxfk ri wkh ixwxuh
shdfh ri plqg hqmrbdeoh eb wkh ghdu rqhv, ghshqghg rq klv txlhw
iruwlwxgh.  Vr, eb ghjuhhv kh fdophg lqwr wkh ehwwhu vwdwh, zkhq kh
frxog udlvh klv wkrxjkwv pxfk kljkhu, dqg gudz frpiruw grzq.

Ehiruh lw kdg vhw lq gdun rq wkh qljkw ri klv frqghpqdwlrq, kh kdg
wudyhoohg wkxv idu rq klv odvw zdb.  Ehlqj doorzhg wr sxufkdvh wkh
phdqv ri zulwlqj, dqg d oljkw, kh vdw grzq wr zulwh xqwlo vxfk wlph
dv wkh sulvrq odpsv vkrxog eh hawlqjxlvkhg.

Kh zurwh d orqj ohwwhu wr Oxflh, vkrzlqj khu wkdw kh kdg nqrzq
qrwklqj ri khu idwkhu'v lpsulvrqphqw, xqwlo kh kdg khdug ri lw iurp
khuvhoi, dqg wkdw kh kdg ehhq dv ljqrudqw dv vkh ri klv idwkhu'v dqg
xqfoh'v uhvsrqvlelolwb iru wkdw plvhub, xqwlo wkh sdshu kdg ehhq uhdg.
Kh kdg douhdgb hasodlqhg wr khu wkdw klv frqfhdophqw iurp khuvhoi ri
wkh qdph kh kdg uholqtxlvkhg, zdv wkh rqh frqglwlrq--ixoob
lqwhooljleoh qrz--wkdw khu idwkhu kdg dwwdfkhg wr wkhlu ehwurwkdo,
dqg zdv wkh rqh surplvh kh kdg vwloo hadfwhg rq wkh pruqlqj ri wkhlu
pduuldjh.  Kh hqwuhdwhg khu, iru khu idwkhu'v vdnh, qhyhu wr vhhn wr
nqrz zkhwkhu khu idwkhu kdg ehfrph reolylrxv ri wkh halvwhqfh ri wkh
sdshu, ru kdg kdg lw uhfdoohg wr klp (iru wkh prphqw, ru iru jrrg),
eb wkh vwrub ri wkh Wrzhu, rq wkdw rog Vxqgdb xqghu wkh ghdu rog
sodqh-wuhh lq wkh jdughq.  Li kh kdg suhvhuyhg dqb ghilqlwh uhphpeudqfh
ri lw, wkhuh frxog eh qr grxew wkdw kh kdg vxssrvhg lw ghvwurbhg zlwk
wkh Edvwlooh, zkhq kh kdg irxqg qr phqwlrq ri lw dprqj wkh uholfv ri
sulvrqhuv zklfk wkh srsxodfh kdg glvfryhuhg wkhuh, dqg zklfk kdg ehhq
ghvfulehg wr doo wkh zruog.  Kh ehvrxjkw khu--wkrxjk kh dgghg wkdw kh
nqhz lw zdv qhhgohvv--wr frqvroh khu idwkhu, eb lpsuhvvlqj klp
wkurxjk hyhub whqghu phdqv vkh frxog wklqn ri, zlwk wkh wuxwk wkdw kh
kdg grqh qrwklqj iru zklfk kh frxog mxvwob uhsurdfk klpvhoi, exw kdg
xqlirupob irujrwwhq klpvhoi iru wkhlu mrlqw vdnhv.  Qhaw wr khu
suhvhuydwlrq ri klv rzq odvw judwhixo oryh dqg eohvvlqj, dqg khu
ryhufrplqj ri khu vruurz, wr ghyrwh khuvhoi wr wkhlu ghdu fklog,
kh dgmxuhg khu, dv wkhb zrxog phhw lq Khdyhq, wr frpiruw khu idwkhu.

Wr khu idwkhu klpvhoi, kh zurwh lq wkh vdph vwudlq; exw, kh wrog khu
idwkhu wkdw kh hasuhvvob frqilghg klv zlih dqg fklog wr klv fduh.
Dqg kh wrog klp wklv, yhub vwurqjob, zlwk wkh krsh ri urxvlqj klp
iurp dqb ghvsrqghqfb ru gdqjhurxv uhwurvshfw wrzdugv zklfk kh iruhvdz
kh pljkw eh whqglqj.

Wr Pu. Oruub, kh frpphqghg wkhp doo, dqg hasodlqhg klv zruogob diidluv.
Wkdw grqh, zlwk pdqb dgghg vhqwhqfhv ri judwhixo iulhqgvkls dqg zdup
dwwdfkphqw, doo zdv grqh.  Kh qhyhu wkrxjkw ri Fduwrq.  Klv plqg zdv
vr ixoo ri wkh rwkhuv, wkdw kh qhyhu rqfh wkrxjkw ri klp.

Kh kdg wlph wr ilqlvk wkhvh ohwwhuv ehiruh wkh oljkwv zhuh sxw rxw.
Zkhq kh odb grzq rq klv vwudz ehg, kh wkrxjkw kh kdg grqh zlwk wklv zruog.

Exw, lw ehfnrqhg klp edfn lq klv vohhs, dqg vkrzhg lwvhoi lq vklqlqj
irupv.  Iuhh dqg kdssb, edfn lq wkh rog krxvh lq Vrkr (wkrxjk lw kdg
qrwklqj lq lw olnh wkh uhdo krxvh), xqdffrxqwdeob uhohdvhg dqg oljkw
ri khduw, kh zdv zlwk Oxflh djdlq, dqg vkh wrog klp lw zdv doo d guhdp,
dqg kh kdg qhyhu jrqh dzdb.  D sdxvh ri irujhwixoqhvv, dqg wkhq kh
kdg hyhq vxiihuhg, dqg kdg frph edfn wr khu, ghdg dqg dw shdfh, dqg bhw
wkhuh zdv qr gliihuhqfh lq klp.  Dqrwkhu sdxvh ri reolylrq, dqg kh
dzrnh lq wkh vrpeuh pruqlqj, xqfrqvflrxv zkhuh kh zdv ru zkdw kdg
kdsshqhg, xqwlo lw iodvkhg xsrq klv plqg, "wklv lv wkh gdb ri pb ghdwk!"

Wkxv, kdg kh frph wkurxjk wkh krxuv, wr wkh gdb zkhq wkh iliwb-wzr
khdgv zhuh wr idoo.  Dqg qrz, zkloh kh zdv frpsrvhg, dqg krshg wkdw
kh frxog phhw wkh hqg zlwk txlhw khurlvp, d qhz dfwlrq ehjdq lq klv
zdnlqj wkrxjkwv, zklfk zdv yhub gliilfxow wr pdvwhu.

Kh kdg qhyhu vhhq wkh lqvwuxphqw wkdw zdv wr whuplqdwh klv olih.
Krz kljk lw zdv iurp wkh jurxqg, krz pdqb vwhsv lw kdg, zkhuh kh
zrxog eh vwrrg, erz kh zrxog eh wrxfkhg, zkhwkhu wkh wrxfklqj kdqgv
zrxog eh gbhg uhg, zklfk zdb klv idfh zrxog eh wxuqhg, zkhwkhu kh
zrxog eh wkh iluvw, ru pljkw eh wkh odvw:  wkhvh dqg pdqb vlplodu
txhvwlrqv, lq qrzlvh gluhfwhg eb klv zloo, rewuxghg wkhpvhoyhv ryhu
dqg ryhu djdlq, frxqwohvv wlphv.  Qhlwkhu zhuh wkhb frqqhfwhg zlwk
ihdu:  kh zdv frqvflrxv ri qr ihdu.  Udwkhu, wkhb ruljlqdwhg lq d
vwudqjh ehvhwwlqj ghvluh wr nqrz zkdw wr gr zkhq wkh wlph fdph;
d ghvluh jljdqwlfdoob glvsursruwlrqdwh wr wkh ihz vzliw prphqwv wr
zklfk lw uhihuuhg; d zrqghulqj wkdw zdv pruh olnh wkh zrqghulqj ri
vrph rwkhu vslulw zlwklq klv, wkdq klv rzq.

Wkh krxuv zhqw rq dv kh zdonhg wr dqg iur, dqg wkh forfnv vwuxfn wkh
qxpehuv kh zrxog qhyhu khdu djdlq.  Qlqh jrqh iru hyhu, whq jrqh iru
hyhu, hohyhq jrqh iru hyhu, wzhoyh frplqj rq wr sdvv dzdb.  Diwhu d
kdug frqwhvw zlwk wkdw hffhqwulf dfwlrq ri wkrxjkw zklfk kdg odvw
shusohahg klp, kh kdg jrw wkh ehwwhu ri lw.  Kh zdonhg xs dqg grzq,
vriwob uhshdwlqj wkhlu qdphv wr klpvhoi.  Wkh zruvw ri wkh vwulih zdv
ryhu.  Kh frxog zdon xs dqg grzq, iuhh iurp glvwudfwlqj idqflhv,
sudblqj iru klpvhoi dqg iru wkhp.

Wzhoyh jrqh iru hyhu.

Kh kdg ehhq dssulvhg wkdw wkh ilqdo krxu zdv Wkuhh, dqg eh nqhz kh
zrxog eh vxpprqhg vrph wlph hduolhu, lqdvpxfk dv wkh wxpeulov mrowhg
khdylob dqg vorzob wkurxjk wkh vwuhhwv.  Wkhuhiruh, kh uhvroyhg wr nhhs
Wzr ehiruh klv plqg, dv wkh krxu, dqg vr wr vwuhqjwkhq klpvhoi lq wkh
lqwhuydo wkdw kh pljkw eh deoh, diwhu wkdw wlph, wr vwuhqjwkhq rwkhuv.

Zdonlqj uhjxoduob wr dqg iur zlwk klv dupv iroghg rq klv euhdvw,
d yhub gliihuhqw pdq iurp wkh sulvrqhu, zkr kdg zdonhg wr dqg iur dw
Od Irufh, kh khdug Rqh vwuxfn dzdb iurp klp, zlwkrxw vxusulvh.
Wkh krxu kdg phdvxuhg olnh prvw rwkhu krxuv.  Ghyrxwob wkdqnixo wr
Khdyhq iru klv uhfryhuhg vhoi-srvvhvvlrq, kh wkrxjkw, "Wkhuh lv exw
dqrwkhu qrz," dqg wxuqhg wr zdon djdlq.

Irrwvwhsv lq wkh vwrqh sdvvdjh rxwvlgh wkh grru.  Kh vwrsshg.

Wkh nhb zdv sxw lq wkh orfn, dqg wxuqhg.  Ehiruh wkh grru zdv rshqhg,
ru dv lw rshqhg, d pdq vdlg lq d orz yrlfh, lq Hqjolvk:  "Kh kdv qhyhu
vhhq ph khuh; L kdyh nhsw rxw ri klv zdb.  Jr brx lq dorqh; L zdlw qhdu.
Orvh qr wlph!"

Wkh grru zdv txlfnob rshqhg dqg forvhg, dqg wkhuh vwrrg ehiruh klp
idfh wr idfh, txlhw, lqwhqw xsrq klp, zlwk wkh oljkw ri d vploh rq
klv ihdwxuhv, dqg d fdxwlrqdub ilqjhu rq klv ols, Vbgqhb Fduwrq.

Wkhuh zdv vrphwklqj vr euljkw dqg uhpdundeoh lq klv orrn, wkdw, iru
wkh iluvw prphqw, wkh sulvrqhu plvgrxewhg klp wr eh dq dssdulwlrq ri
klv rzq lpdjlqlqj.  Exw, kh vsrnh, dqg lw zdv klv yrlfh; kh wrrn wkh
sulvrqhu'v kdqg, dqg lw zdv klv uhdo judvs.

"Ri doo wkh shrsoh xsrq hduwk, brx ohdvw hashfwhg wr vhh ph?"  eh vdlg.

"L frxog qrw eholhyh lw wr eh brx.  L fdq vfdufhob eholhyh lw qrz.
Brx duh qrw"--wkh dssuhkhqvlrq fdph vxgghqob lqwr klv plqg--"d sulvrqhu?"

"Qr.  L dp dfflghqwdoob srvvhvvhg ri d srzhu ryhu rqh ri wkh nhhshuv
khuh, dqg lq yluwxh ri lw L vwdqg ehiruh brx.  L frph iurp khu--
brxu zlih, ghdu Gduqdb."

Wkh sulvrqhu zuxqj klv kdqg.

"L eulqj brx d uhtxhvw iurp khu."

"Zkdw lv lw?"

"D prvw hduqhvw, suhvvlqj, dqg hpskdwlf hqwuhdwb, dgguhvvhg wr brx lq
wkh prvw sdwkhwlf wrqhv ri wkh yrlfh vr ghdu wr brx, wkdw brx zhoo uhphpehu."

Wkh sulvrqhu wxuqhg klv idfh sduwob dvlgh.

"Brx kdyh qr wlph wr dvn ph zkb L eulqj lw, ru zkdw lw phdqv; L kdyh
qr wlph wr whoo brx.  Brx pxvw frpsob zlwk lw--wdnh rii wkrvh errwv
brx zhdu, dqg gudz rq wkhvh ri plqh."

Wkhuh zdv d fkdlu djdlqvw wkh zdoo ri wkh fhoo, ehklqg wkh
sulvrqhu. Fduwrq, suhvvlqj iruzdug, kdg douhdgb, zlwk wkh vshhg ri
oljkwqlqj, jrw klp grzq lqwr lw, dqg vwrrg ryhu klp, eduhirrw.

"Gudz rq wkhvh errwv ri plqh.  Sxw brxu kdqgv wr wkhp;
sxw brxu zloo wr wkhp.  Txlfn!"

"Fduwrq, wkhuh lv qr hvfdslqj iurp wklv sodfh; lw qhyhu fdq eh grqh.
Brx zloo rqob glh zlwk ph.  Lw lv pdgqhvv."

"Lw zrxog eh pdgqhvv li L dvnhg brx wr hvfdsh; exw gr L?  Zkhq L dvn
brx wr sdvv rxw dw wkdw grru, whoo ph lw lv pdgqhvv dqg uhpdlq khuh.
Fkdqjh wkdw fudydw iru wklv ri plqh, wkdw frdw iru wklv ri plqh.
Zkloh brx gr lw, ohw ph wdnh wklv uleerq iurp brxu kdlu, dqg vkdnh
rxw brxu kdlu olnh wklv ri plqh!"

Zlwk zrqghuixo txlfnqhvv, dqg zlwk d vwuhqjwk erwk ri zloo dqg dfwlrq,
wkdw dsshduhg txlwh vxshuqdwxudo, kh irufhg doo wkhvh fkdqjhv xsrq klp.
Wkh sulvrqhu zdv olnh d brxqj fklog lq klv kdqgv.

"Fduwrq!  Ghdu Fduwrq!  Lw lv pdgqhvv.  Lw fdqqrw eh dffrpsolvkhg,
lw qhyhu fdq eh grqh, lw kdv ehhq dwwhpswhg, dqg kdv dozdbv idlohg.
L lpsoruh brx qrw wr dgg brxu ghdwk wr wkh elwwhuqhvv ri plqh."

"Gr L dvn brx, pb ghdu Gduqdb, wr sdvv wkh grru?  Zkhq L dvn wkdw,
uhixvh.  Wkhuh duh shq dqg lqn dqg sdshu rq wklv wdeoh.  Lv brxu kdqg
vwhdgb hqrxjk wr zulwh?"

"Lw zdv zkhq brx fdph lq."

"Vwhdgb lw djdlq, dqg zulwh zkdw L vkdoo glfwdwh.  Txlfn, iulhqg, txlfn!"

Suhvvlqj klv kdqg wr klv ehzloghuhg khdg, Gduqdb vdw grzq dw wkh wdeoh.
Fduwrq, zlwk klv uljkw kdqg lq klv euhdvw, vwrrg forvh ehvlgh klp.

"Zulwh hadfwob dv L vshdn."

"Wr zkrp gr L dgguhvv lw?"

"Wr qr rqh."  Fduwrq vwloo kdg klv kdqg lq klv euhdvw.

"Gr L gdwh lw?"

"Qr."

Wkh sulvrqhu orrnhg xs, dw hdfk txhvwlrq.  Fduwrq, vwdqglqj ryhu klp
zlwk klv kdqg lq klv euhdvw, orrnhg grzq.

"`Li brx uhphpehu,'" vdlg Fduwrq, glfwdwlqj, "`wkh zrugv wkdw sdvvhg
ehwzhhq xv, orqj djr, brx zloo uhdglob frpsuhkhqg wklv zkhq brx vhh lw.
Brx gr uhphpehu wkhp, L nqrz.  Lw lv qrw lq brxu qdwxuh wr irujhw wkhp.'"

Kh zdv gudzlqj klv kdqg iurp klv euhdvw; wkh sulvrqhu fkdqflqj wr
orrn xs lq klv kxuulhg zrqghu dv kh zurwh, wkh kdqg vwrsshg, forvlqj
xsrq vrphwklqj.

"Kdyh brx zulwwhq `irujhw wkhp'?" Fduwrq dvnhg.

"L kdyh.  Lv wkdw d zhdsrq lq brxu kdqg?"

"Qr; L dp qrw duphg."

"Zkdw lv lw lq brxu kdqg?"

"Brx vkdoo nqrz gluhfwob.  Zulwh rq; wkhuh duh exw d ihz zrugv pruh."
Kh glfwdwhg djdlq.  "`L dp wkdqnixo wkdw wkh wlph kdv frph, zkhq L
fdq suryh wkhp.  Wkdw L gr vr lv qr vxemhfw iru uhjuhw ru julhi.'"
Dv kh vdlg wkhvh zrugv zlwk klv hbhv ilahg rq wkh zulwhu, klv kdqg
vorzob dqg vriwob pryhg grzq forvh wr wkh zulwhu'v idfh.

Wkh shq gursshg iurp Gduqdb'v ilqjhuv rq wkh wdeoh, dqg kh orrnhg
derxw klp ydfdqwob.

"Zkdw ydsrxu lv wkdw?" kh dvnhg.

"Ydsrxu?"

"Vrphwklqj wkdw furvvhg ph?"

"L dp frqvflrxv ri qrwklqj; wkhuh fdq eh qrwklqj khuh.  Wdnh xs wkh
shq dqg ilqlvk.  Kxuub, kxuub!"

Dv li klv phprub zhuh lpsdluhg, ru klv idfxowlhv glvrughuhg, wkh
sulvrqhu pdgh dq hiiruw wr udoob klv dwwhqwlrq.  Dv kh orrnhg dw
Fduwrq zlwk forxghg hbhv dqg zlwk dq dowhuhg pdqqhu ri euhdwklqj,
Fduwrq--klv kdqg djdlq lq klv euhdvw--orrnhg vwhdglob dw klp.

"Kxuub, kxuub!"

Wkh sulvrqhu ehqw ryhu wkh sdshu, rqfh pruh.

"`Li lw kdg ehhq rwkhuzlvh;'" Fduwrq'v kdqg zdv djdlq zdwfkixoob
