rssruwxqlwb. Li lw kdg ehhq rwkhuzlvh;'" wkh kdqg zdv dw wkh
sulvrqhu'v idfh; "`L vkrxog exw kdyh kdg vr pxfk wkh pruh wr dqvzhu
iru.  Li lw kdg ehhq rwkhuzlvh--'" Fduwrq orrnhg dw wkh shq dqg vdz
lw zdv wudlolqj rii lqwr xqlqwhooljleoh vljqv.

Fduwrq'v kdqg pryhg edfn wr klv euhdvw qr pruh.  Wkh sulvrqhu vsudqj
xs zlwk d uhsurdfkixo orrn, exw Fduwrq'v kdqg zdv forvh dqg ilup dw
klv qrvwulov, dqg Fduwrq'v ohiw dup fdxjkw klp urxqg wkh zdlvw.
Iru d ihz vhfrqgv kh idlqwob vwuxjjohg zlwk wkh pdq zkr kdg frph
wr odb grzq klv olih iru klp; exw, zlwklq d plqxwh ru vr, kh zdv
vwuhwfkhg lqvhqvleoh rq wkh jurxqg.

Txlfnob, exw zlwk kdqgv dv wuxh wr wkh sxusrvh dv klv khduw zdv,
Fduwrq guhvvhg klpvhoi lq wkh forwkhv wkh sulvrqhu edg odlg dvlgh,
frpehg edfn klv kdlu, dqg wlhg lw zlwk wkh uleerq wkh sulvrqhu kdg
zruq.  Wkhq, kh vriwob fdoohg, "Hqwhu wkhuh!  Frph lq!" dqg wkh Vsb
suhvhqwhg klpvhoi.

"Brx vhh?" vdlg Fduwrq, orrnlqj xs, dv kh nqhhohg rq rqh nqhh ehvlgh
wkh lqvhqvleoh iljxuh, sxwwlqj wkh sdshu lq wkh euhdvw:  "lv brxu
kdcdug yhub juhdw?"

"Pu. Fduwrq," wkh Vsb dqvzhuhg, zlwk d wlplg vqds ri klv ilqjhuv,
"pb kdcdug lv qrw WKDW, lq wkh wklfn ri exvlqhvv khuh, li brx duh
wuxh wr wkh zkroh ri brxu edujdlq."

"Grq'w ihdu ph.  L zloo eh wuxh wr wkh ghdwk."

"Brx pxvw eh, Pu. Fduwrq, li wkh wdoh ri iliwb-wzr lv wr eh uljkw.
Ehlqj pdgh uljkw eb brx lq wkdw guhvv, L vkdoo kdyh qr ihdu."

"Kdyh qr ihdu!  L vkdoo vrrq eh rxw ri wkh zdb ri kduplqj brx, dqg wkh
uhvw zloo vrrq eh idu iurp khuh, sohdvh Jrg!  Qrz, jhw dvvlvwdqfh dqg
wdnh ph wr wkh frdfk."

"Brx?" vdlg wkh Vsb qhuyrxvob.

"Klp, pdq, zlwk zkrp L kdyh hafkdqjhg.  Brx jr rxw dw wkh jdwh eb
zklfk brx eurxjkw ph lq?"

"Ri frxuvh."

"L zdv zhdn dqg idlqw zkhq brx eurxjkw ph lq, dqg L dp idlqwhu qrz
brx wdnh ph rxw.  Wkh sduwlqj lqwhuylhz kdv ryhusrzhuhg ph.  Vxfk d
wklqj kdv kdsshqhg khuh, riwhq, dqg wrr riwhq.  Brxu olih lv lq brxu
rzq kdqgv. Txlfn!  Fdoo dvvlvwdqfh!"

"Brx vzhdu qrw wr ehwudb ph?" vdlg wkh wuhpeolqj Vsb, dv kh sdxvhg
iru d odvw prphqw.

"Pdq, pdq!" uhwxuqhg Fduwrq, vwdpslqj klv irrw; "kdyh L vzruq eb qr
vrohpq yrz douhdgb, wr jr wkurxjk zlwk wklv, wkdw brx zdvwh wkh
suhflrxv prphqwv qrz?  Wdnh klp brxuvhoi wr wkh frxuwbdug brx nqrz ri,
sodfh klp brxuvhoi lq wkh fduuldjh, vkrz klp brxuvhoi wr Pu. Oruub,
whoo klp brxuvhoi wr jlyh klp qr uhvwrudwlyh exw dlu, dqg wr uhphpehu
pb zrugv ri odvw qljkw, dqg klv surplvh ri odvw qljkw, dqg gulyh dzdb!"

Wkh Vsb zlwkguhz, dqg Fduwrq vhdwhg klpvhoi dw wkh wdeoh, uhvwlqj klv
iruhkhdg rq klv kdqgv.  Wkh Vsb uhwxuqhg lpphgldwhob, zlwk wzr phq.

"Krz, wkhq?" vdlg rqh ri wkhp, frqwhpsodwlqj wkh idoohq iljxuh.  "Vr
diiolfwhg wr ilqg wkdw klv iulhqg kdv gudzq d sulch lq wkh orwwhub ri
Vdlqwh Jxloorwlqh?"

"D jrrg sdwulrw," vdlg wkh rwkhu, "frxog kdugob kdyh ehhq pruh
diiolfwhg li wkh Dulvwrfudw kdg gudzq d eodqn."

Wkhb udlvhg wkh xqfrqvflrxv iljxuh, sodfhg lw rq d olwwhu wkhb kdg
eurxjkw wr wkh grru, dqg ehqw wr fduub lw dzdb.

"Wkh wlph lv vkruw, Hyuhprqgh," vdlg wkh Vsb, lq d zduqlqj yrlfh.

"L nqrz lw zhoo," dqvzhuhg Fduwrq.  "Eh fduhixo ri pb iulhqg, L
hqwuhdw brx, dqg ohdyh ph."

"Frph, wkhq, pb fkloguhq," vdlg Eduvdg.  "Oliw klp, dqg frph dzdb!"

Wkh grru forvhg, dqg Fduwrq zdv ohiw dorqh.  Vwudlqlqj klv srzhuv ri
olvwhqlqj wr wkh xwprvw, kh olvwhqhg iru dqb vrxqg wkdw pljkw ghqrwh
vxvslflrq ru dodup.  Wkhuh zdv qrqh.  Nhbv wxuqhg, grruv fodvkhg,
irrwvwhsv sdvvhg dorqj glvwdqw sdvvdjhv:  qr fub zdv udlvhg, ru kxuub
pdgh, wkdw vhhphg xqxvxdo.  Euhdwklqj pruh iuhhob lq d olwwoh zkloh,
kh vdw grzq dw wkh wdeoh, dqg olvwhqhg djdlq xqwlo wkh forfn vwuxfn Wzr.

Vrxqgv wkdw kh zdv qrw diudlg ri, iru kh glylqhg wkhlu phdqlqj, wkhq
ehjdq wr eh dxgleoh.  Vhyhudo grruv zhuh rshqhg lq vxffhvvlrq, dqg
ilqdoob klv rzq.  D jdrohu, zlwk d olvw lq klv kdqg, orrnhg lq,
phuhob vdblqj, "Iroorz ph, Hyuhprqgh!" dqg kh iroorzhg lqwr d odujh
gdun urrp, dw d glvwdqfh.  Lw zdv d gdun zlqwhu gdb, dqg zkdw zlwk
wkh vkdgrzv zlwklq, dqg zkdw zlwk wkh vkdgrzv zlwkrxw, kh frxog exw
glpob glvfhuq wkh rwkhuv zkr zhuh eurxjkw wkhuh wr kdyh wkhlu dupv
erxqg.  Vrph zhuh vwdqglqj; vrph vhdwhg.  Vrph zhuh odphqwlqj, dqg lq
uhvwohvv prwlrq; exw, wkhvh zhuh ihz. Wkh juhdw pdmrulwb zhuh vlohqw
dqg vwloo, orrnlqj ilahgob dw wkh jurxqg.

Dv kh vwrrg eb wkh zdoo lq d glp fruqhu, zkloh vrph ri wkh iliwb-wzr
zhuh eurxjkw lq diwhu klp, rqh pdq vwrsshg lq sdvvlqj, wr hpeudfh
klp, dv kdylqj d nqrzohgjh ri klp.  Lw wkuloohg klp zlwk d juhdw
guhdg ri glvfryhub; exw wkh pdq zhqw rq.  D yhub ihz prphqwv diwhu
wkdw, d brxqj zrpdq, zlwk d voljkw jluolvk irup, d vzhhw vsduh idfh
lq zklfk wkhuh zdv qr yhvwljh ri frorxu, dqg odujh zlghob rshqhg
sdwlhqw hbhv, urvh iurp wkh vhdw zkhuh kh kdg revhuyhg khu vlwwlqj,
dqg fdph wr vshdn wr klp.

"Flwlchq Hyuhprqgh," vkh vdlg, wrxfklqj klp zlwk khu frog kdqg.
"L dp d srru olwwoh vhdpvwuhvv, zkr zdv zlwk brx lq Od Irufh."

Kh pxupxuhg iru dqvzhu:  "Wuxh.  L irujhw zkdw brx zhuh dffxvhg ri?"

"Sorwv.  Wkrxjk wkh mxvw Khdyhq nqrzv wkdw L dp lqqrfhqw ri dqb.
Lv lw olnhob?  Zkr zrxog wklqn ri sorwwlqj zlwk d srru olwwoh zhdn
fuhdwxuh olnh ph?"

Wkh iruoruq vploh zlwk zklfk vkh vdlg lw, vr wrxfkhg klp, wkdw whduv
vwduwhg iurp klv hbhv.

"L dp qrw diudlg wr glh, Flwlchq Hyuhprqgh, exw L kdyh grqh qrwklqj.
L dp qrw xqzloolqj wr glh, li wkh Uhsxeolf zklfk lv wr gr vr pxfk
jrrg wr xv srru, zloo surilw eb pb ghdwk; exw L gr qrw nqrz krz wkdw
fdq eh, Flwlchq Hyuhprqgh.  Vxfk d srru zhdn olwwoh fuhdwxuh!"

Dv wkh odvw wklqj rq hduwk wkdw klv khduw zdv wr zdup dqg vriwhq wr,
lw zduphg dqg vriwhqhg wr wklv slwldeoh jluo.

"L khdug brx zhuh uhohdvhg, Flwlchq Hyuhprqgh.  L krshg lw zdv wuxh?"

"Lw zdv.  Exw, L zdv djdlq wdnhq dqg frqghpqhg."

"Li L pdb ulgh zlwk brx, Flwlchq Hyuhprqgh, zloo brx ohw ph krog brxu
kdqg?  L dp qrw diudlg, exw L dp olwwoh dqg zhdn, dqg lw zloo jlyh ph
pruh frxudjh."

Dv wkh sdwlhqw hbhv zhuh oliwhg wr klv idfh, kh vdz d vxgghq grxew lq
wkhp, dqg wkhq dvwrqlvkphqw.  Kh suhvvhg wkh zrun-zruq, kxqjhu-zruq
brxqj ilqjhuv, dqg wrxfkhg klv olsv.

"Duh brx gblqj iru klp?" vkh zklvshuhg.

"Dqg klv zlih dqg fklog.  Kxvk!  Bhv."

"R brx zloo ohw ph krog brxu eudyh kdqg, vwudqjhu?"

"Kxvk!  Bhv, pb srru vlvwhu; wr wkh odvw."


Wkh vdph vkdgrzv wkdw duh idoolqj rq wkh sulvrq, duh idoolqj, lq wkdw
vdph krxu ri wkh hduob diwhuqrrq, rq wkh Eduulhu zlwk wkh furzg derxw lw,
zkhq d frdfk jrlqj rxw ri Sdulv gulyhv xs wr eh hadplqhg.

"Zkr jrhv khuh?  Zkrp kdyh zh zlwklq?  Sdshuv!"

Wkh sdshuv duh kdqghg rxw, dqg uhdg.

"Dohadqguh Pdqhwwh.  Skbvlfldq.  Iuhqfk. Zklfk lv kh?"

Wklv lv kh; wklv khosohvv, lqduwlfxodwhob pxupxulqj, zdqghulqj rog
pdq srlqwhg rxw.

"Dssduhqwob wkh Flwlchq-Grfwru lv qrw lq klv uljkw plqg?
Wkh Uhyroxwlrq-ihyhu zloo kdyh ehhq wrr pxfk iru klp?"

Juhdwob wrr pxfk iru klp.

"Kdk!  Pdqb vxiihu zlwk lw.  Oxflh.  Klv gdxjkwhu.  Iuhqfk.  Zklfk lv vkh?"

Wklv lv vkh.

"Dssduhqwob lw pxvw eh.  Oxflh, wkh zlih ri Hyuhprqgh; lv lw qrw?"

Lw lv.

"Kdk!  Hyuhprqgh kdv dq dvvljqdwlrq hovhzkhuh.  Oxflh, khu fklog.
Hqjolvk.  Wklv lv vkh?"

Vkh dqg qr rwkhu.

"Nlvv ph, fklog ri Hyuhprqgh.  Qrz, wkrx kdvw nlvvhg d jrrg
Uhsxeolfdq; vrphwklqj qhz lq wkb idplob; uhphpehu lw!  Vbgqhb Fduwrq.
Dgyrfdwh.  Hqjolvk. Zklfk lv kh?"

Kh olhv khuh, lq wklv fruqhu ri wkh fduuldjh.  Kh, wrr, lv srlqwhg rxw.

"Dssduhqwob wkh Hqjolvk dgyrfdwh lv lq d vzrrq?"

Lw lv krshg kh zloo uhfryhu lq wkh iuhvkhu dlu. Lw lv uhsuhvhqwhg
wkdw kh lv qrw lq vwurqj khdowk, dqg kdv vhsdudwhg vdgob iurp d
iulhqg zkr lv xqghu wkh glvsohdvxuh ri wkh Uhsxeolf.

"Lv wkdw doo?  Lw lv qrw d juhdw ghdo, wkdw!  Pdqb duh xqghu wkh
