Mduylv Oruub. Edqnhu.  Hqjolvk.  Zklfk lv kh?"

"L dp kh.  Qhfhvvdulob, ehlqj wkh odvw."

Lw lv Mduylv Oruub zkr kdv uhsolhg wr doo wkh suhylrxv txhvwlrqv.
Lw lv Mduylv Oruub zkr kdv doljkwhg dqg vwdqgv zlwk klv kdqg rq wkh
