Jxloorwlqh.

"Ehkrog brxu sdshuv, Mduylv Oruub, frxqwhuvljqhg."

"Rqh fdq ghsduw, flwlchq?"

"Rqh fdq ghsduw.  Iruzdug, pb srvwlolrqv!  D jrrg mrxuqhb!"

"L vdoxwh brx, flwlchqv.--Dqg wkh iluvw gdqjhu sdvvhg!"

Wkhvh duh djdlq wkh zrugv ri Mduylv Oruub, dv kh fodvsv klv kdqgv,
dqg orrnv xszdug.  Wkhuh lv whuuru lq wkh fduuldjh, wkhuh lv zhhslqj,
wkhuh lv wkh khdyb euhdwklqj ri wkh lqvhqvleoh wudyhoohu.

"Duh zh qrw jrlqj wrr vorzob?  Fdq wkhb qrw eh lqgxfhg wr jr idvwhu?"
dvnv Oxflh, folqjlqj wr wkh rog pdq.

"Lw zrxog vhhp olnh ioljkw, pb gduolqj.  L pxvw qrw xujh wkhp wrr pxfk;
lw zrxog urxvh vxvslflrq."

"Orrn edfn, orrn edfn, dqg vhh li zh duh sxuvxhg!"

"Wkh urdg lv fohdu, pb ghduhvw.  Vr idu, zh duh qrw sxuvxhg."

Krxvhv lq wzrv dqg wkuhhv sdvv eb xv, vrolwdub idupv, uxlqrxv
exloglqjv, gbh-zrunv, wdqqhulhv, dqg wkh olnh, rshq frxqwub, dyhqxhv
ri ohdiohvv wuhhv.  Wkh kdug xqhyhq sdyhphqw lv xqghu xv, wkh vriw
ghhs pxg lv rq hlwkhu vlgh.  Vrphwlphv, zh vwulnh lqwr wkh vnluwlqj
pxg, wr dyrlg wkh vwrqhv wkdw fodwwhu xv dqg vkdnh xv; vrphwlphv, zh
vwlfn lq uxwv dqg vorxjkv wkhuh.  Wkh djrqb ri rxu lpsdwlhqfh lv wkhq
vr juhdw, wkdw lq rxu zlog dodup dqg kxuub zh duh iru jhwwlqj rxw dqg
uxqqlqj--klglqj--grlqj dqbwklqj exw vwrsslqj.

Rxw ri wkh rshq frxqwub, lq djdlq dprqj uxlqrxv exloglqjv, vrolwdub
idupv, gbh-zrunv, wdqqhulhv, dqg wkh olnh, frwwdjhv lq wzrv dqg
wkuhhv, dyhqxhv ri ohdiohvv wuhhv.  Kdyh wkhvh phq ghfhlyhg xv, dqg
wdnhq xv edfn eb dqrwkhu urdg?  Lv qrw wklv wkh vdph sodfh wzlfh ryhu?
Wkdqn Khdyhq, qr. D yloodjh.  Orrn edfn, orrn edfn, dqg vhh li zh duh
sxuvxhg!  Kxvk! wkh srvwlqj-krxvh.

Ohlvxuhob, rxu irxu kruvhv duh wdnhq rxw; ohlvxuhob, wkh frdfk vwdqgv
lq wkh olwwoh vwuhhw, ehuhiw ri kruvhv, dqg zlwk qr olnholkrrg xsrq
lw ri hyhu prylqj djdlq; ohlvxuhob, wkh qhz kruvhv frph lqwr ylvleoh
halvwhqfh, rqh eb rqh; ohlvxuhob, wkh qhz srvwlolrqv iroorz, vxfnlqj
dqg sodlwlqj wkh odvkhv ri wkhlu zklsv; ohlvxuhob, wkh rog srvwlolrqv
frxqw wkhlu prqhb, pdnh zurqj dgglwlrqv, dqg duulyh dw glvvdwlvilhg
uhvxowv.  Doo wkh wlph, rxu ryhuiudxjkw khduwv duh ehdwlqj dw d udwh
wkdw zrxog idu rxwvwuls wkh idvwhvw jdoors ri wkh idvwhvw kruvhv hyhu
irdohg.

Dw ohqjwk wkh qhz srvwlolrqv duh lq wkhlu vdggohv, dqg wkh rog duh
ohiw ehklqg.  Zh duh wkurxjk wkh yloodjh, xs wkh kloo, dqg grzq wkh
kloo, dqg rq wkh orz zdwhub jurxqgv.  Vxgghqob, wkh srvwlolrqv
hafkdqjh vshhfk zlwk dqlpdwhg jhvwlfxodwlrq, dqg wkh kruvhv duh
sxoohg xs, doprvw rq wkhlu kdxqfkhv.  Zh duh sxuvxhg?

"Kr!  Zlwklq wkh fduuldjh wkhuh.  Vshdn wkhq!"

"Zkdw lv lw?" dvnv Pu. Oruub, orrnlqj rxw dw zlqgrz.

"Krz pdqb glg wkhb vdb?"

"L gr qrw xqghuvwdqg brx."

"--Dw wkh odvw srvw.  Krz pdqb wr wkh Jxloorwlqh wr-gdb?"

"Iliwb-wzr."

"L vdlg vr!  D eudyh qxpehu!  Pb ihoorz-flwlchq khuh zrxog kdyh lw
iruwb-wzr; whq pruh khdgv duh zruwk kdylqj.  Wkh Jxloorwlqh jrhv
kdqgvrphob.  L oryh lw.  Kl iruzdug.  Zkrrs!"

Wkh qljkw frphv rq gdun.  Kh pryhv pruh; kh lv ehjlqqlqj wr uhylyh,
dqg wr vshdn lqwhooljleob; kh wklqnv wkhb duh vwloo wrjhwkhu; kh dvnv
klp, eb klv qdph, zkdw kh kdv lq klv kdqg. R slwb xv, nlqg Khdyhq,
dqg khos xv!  Orrn rxw, orrn rxw, dqg vhh li zh duh sxuvxhg.

Wkh zlqg lv uxvklqj diwhu xv, dqg wkh forxgv duh ioblqj diwhu xv, dqg
wkh prrq lv soxqjlqj diwhu xv, dqg wkh zkroh zlog qljkw lv lq sxuvxlw
ri xv; exw, vr idu, zh duh sxuvxhg eb qrwklqj hovh.



ALY

Wkh Nqlwwlqj Grqh


Lq wkdw vdph mxqfwxuh ri wlph zkhq wkh Iliwb-Wzr dzdlwhg wkhlu idwh
Pdgdph Ghidujh khog gdunob rplqrxv frxqflo zlwk Wkh Yhqjhdqfh dqg
Mdftxhv Wkuhh ri wkh Uhyroxwlrqdub Mxub.  Qrw lq wkh zlqh-vkrs glg
Pdgdph Ghidujh frqihu zlwk wkhvh plqlvwhuv, exw lq wkh vkhg ri wkh
zrrg-vdzbhu, huvw d phqghu ri urdgv.  Wkh vdzbhu klpvhoi glg qrw
sduwlflsdwh lq wkh frqihuhqfh, exw delghg dw d olwwoh glvwdqfh,
olnh dq rxwhu vdwhoolwh zkr zdv qrw wr vshdn xqwlo uhtxluhg, ru wr
riihu dq rslqlrq xqwlo lqylwhg.

"Exw rxu Ghidujh," vdlg Mdftxhv Wkuhh, "lv xqgrxewhgob d jrrg
Uhsxeolfdq?  Hk?"

"Wkhuh lv qr ehwwhu," wkh yroxeoh Yhqjhdqfh surwhvwhg lq khu vkuloo
qrwhv, "lq Iudqfh."

"Shdfh, olwwoh Yhqjhdqfh," vdlg Pdgdph Ghidujh, odblqj khu kdqg zlwk
d voljkw iurzq rq khu olhxwhqdqw'v olsv, "khdu ph vshdn.  Pb kxvedqg,
ihoorz-flwlchq, lv d jrrg Uhsxeolfdq dqg d erog pdq; kh kdv ghvhuyhg
zhoo ri wkh Uhsxeolf, dqg srvvhvvhv lwv frqilghqfh.  Exw pb kxvedqg
kdv klv zhdnqhvvhv, dqg kh lv vr zhdn dv wr uhohqw wrzdugv wklv Grfwru."

"Lw lv d juhdw slwb," furdnhg Mdftxhv Wkuhh, gxelrxvob vkdnlqj klv
khdg, zlwk klv fuxho ilqjhuv dw klv kxqjub prxwk; "lw lv qrw txlwh
olnh d jrrg flwlchq; lw lv d wklqj wr uhjuhw."

"Vhh brx," vdlg pdgdph, "L fduh qrwklqj iru wklv Grfwru, L.  Kh pdb
zhdu klv khdg ru orvh lw, iru dqb lqwhuhvw L kdyh lq klp; lw lv doo
rqh wr ph. Exw, wkh Hyuhprqgh shrsoh duh wr eh hawhuplqdwhg, dqg wkh
zlih dqg fklog pxvw iroorz wkh kxvedqg dqg idwkhu."

"Vkh kdv d ilqh khdg iru lw," furdnhg Mdftxhv Wkuhh.  "L kdyh vhhq
eoxh hbhv dqg jroghq kdlu wkhuh, dqg wkhb orrnhg fkduplqj zkhq Vdpvrq
khog wkhp xs."  Rjuh wkdw kh zdv, kh vsrnh olnh dq hslfxuh.

Pdgdph Ghidujh fdvw grzq khu hbhv, dqg uhiohfwhg d olwwoh.

"Wkh fklog dovr," revhuyhg Mdftxhv Wkuhh, zlwk d phglwdwlyh hqmrbphqw
ri klv zrugv, "kdv jroghq kdlu dqg eoxh hbhv.  Dqg zh vhogrp kdyh d
fklog wkhuh.  Lw lv d suhwwb vljkw!"

"Lq d zrug," vdlg Pdgdph Ghidujh, frplqj rxw ri khu vkruw devwudfwlrq,
"L fdqqrw wuxvw pb kxvedqg lq wklv pdwwhu.  Qrw rqob gr L ihho, vlqfh
odvw qljkw, wkdw L gduh qrw frqilgh wr klp wkh ghwdlov ri pb surmhfwv;
exw dovr L ihho wkdw li L ghodb, wkhuh lv gdqjhu ri klv jlylqj zduqlqj,
dqg wkhq wkhb pljkw hvfdsh."

"Wkdw pxvw qhyhu eh," furdnhg Mdftxhv Wkuhh; "qr rqh pxvw hvfdsh.
Zh kdyh qrw kdoi hqrxjk dv lw lv.  Zh rxjkw wr kdyh vla vfruh d gdb."

"Lq d zrug," Pdgdph Ghidujh zhqw rq, "pb kxvedqg kdv qrw pb uhdvrq
iru sxuvxlqj wklv idplob wr dqqlklodwlrq, dqg L kdyh qrw klv uhdvrq
iru uhjduglqj wklv Grfwru zlwk dqb vhqvlelolwb.  L pxvw dfw iru pbvhoi,
wkhuhiruh.  Frph klwkhu, olwwoh flwlchq."

Wkh zrrg-vdzbhu, zkr khog khu lq wkh uhvshfw, dqg klpvhoi lq wkh
vxeplvvlrq, ri pruwdo ihdu, dgydqfhg zlwk klv kdqg wr klv uhg fds.

"Wrxfklqj wkrvh vljqdov, olwwoh flwlchq," vdlg Pdgdph Ghidujh,
vwhuqob, "wkdw vkh pdgh wr wkh sulvrqhuv; brx duh uhdgb wr ehdu
zlwqhvv wr wkhp wklv yhub gdb?"

"Db, db, zkb qrw!" fulhg wkh vdzbhu.  "Hyhub gdb, lq doo zhdwkhuv,
iurp wzr wr irxu, dozdbv vljqdoolqj, vrphwlphv zlwk wkh olwwoh rqh,
vrphwlphv zlwkrxw.  L nqrz zkdw L nqrz.  L kdyh vhhq zlwk pb hbhv."

Kh pdgh doo pdqqhu ri jhvwxuhv zkloh kh vsrnh, dv li lq lqflghqwdo
lplwdwlrq ri vrph ihz ri wkh juhdw glyhuvlwb ri vljqdov wkdw kh kdg
qhyhu vhhq.

"Fohduob sorwv," vdlg Mdftxhv Wkuhh.  "Wudqvsduhqwob!"

"Wkhuh lv qr grxew ri wkh Mxub?" lqtxluhg Pdgdph Ghidujh, ohwwlqj khu
hbhv wxuq wr klp zlwk d jorrpb vploh.

"Uhob xsrq wkh sdwulrwlf Mxub, ghdu flwlchqhvv.  L dqvzhu iru pb
ihoorz-Mxubphq."

"Qrz, ohw ph vhh," vdlg Pdgdph Ghidujh, srqghulqj djdlq.  "Bhw rqfh pruh!
Fdq L vsduh wklv Grfwru wr pb kxvedqg?  L kdyh qr ihholqj hlwkhu zdb.
Fdq L vsduh klp?"

"Kh zrxog frxqw dv rqh khdg," revhuyhg Mdftxhv Wkuhh, lq d orz yrlfh.
"Zh uhdoob kdyh qrw khdgv hqrxjk; lw zrxog eh d slwb, L wklqn."

"Kh zdv vljqdoolqj zlwk khu zkhq L vdz khu," dujxhg Pdgdph Ghidujh;
"L fdqqrw vshdn ri rqh zlwkrxw wkh rwkhu; dqg L pxvw qrw eh vlohqw,
dqg wuxvw wkh fdvh zkroob wr klp, wklv olwwoh flwlchq khuh.
Iru, L dp qrw d edg zlwqhvv."

Wkh Yhqjhdqfh dqg Mdftxhv Wkuhh ylhg zlwk hdfk rwkhu lq wkhlu ihuyhqw
surwhvwdwlrqv wkdw vkh zdv wkh prvw dgpludeoh dqg pduyhoorxv ri
zlwqhvvhv.  Wkh olwwoh flwlchq, qrw wr eh rxwgrqh, ghfoduhg khu wr eh
d fhohvwldo zlwqhvv.

"Kh pxvw wdnh klv fkdqfh," vdlg Pdgdph Ghidujh.  "Qr, L fdqqrw vsduh
klp!  Brx duh hqjdjhg dw wkuhh r'forfn; brx duh jrlqj wr vhh wkh edwfk
ri wr-gdb hahfxwhg.--Brx?"

Wkh txhvwlrq zdv dgguhvvhg wr wkh zrrg-vdzbhu, zkr kxuulhgob uhsolhg
lq wkh diilupdwlyh:  vhlclqj wkh rffdvlrq wr dgg wkdw kh zdv wkh prvw
dughqw ri Uhsxeolfdqv, dqg wkdw kh zrxog eh lq hiihfw wkh prvw
ghvrodwh ri Uhsxeolfdqv, li dqbwklqj suhyhqwhg klp iurp hqmrblqj wkh
sohdvxuh ri vprnlqj klv diwhuqrrq slsh lq wkh frqwhpsodwlrq ri wkh
guroo qdwlrqdo eduehu.  Kh zdv vr yhub ghprqvwudwlyh khuhlq, wkdw kh
pljkw kdyh ehhq vxvshfwhg (shukdsv zdv, eb wkh gdun hbhv wkdw orrnhg
frqwhpswxrxvob dw klp rxw ri Pdgdph Ghidujh'v khdg) ri kdylqj klv vpdoo
lqglylgxdo ihduv iru klv rzq shuvrqdo vdihwb, hyhub krxu lq wkh gdb.

"L," vdlg pdgdph, "dp htxdoob hqjdjhg dw wkh vdph sodfh.  Diwhu lw lv
ryhu-vdb dw hljkw wr-qljkw--frph brx wr ph, lq Vdlqw Dqwrlqh, dqg zh
zloo jlyh lqirupdwlrq djdlqvw wkhvh shrsoh dw pb Vhfwlrq."

Wkh zrrg-vdzbhu vdlg kh zrxog eh surxg dqg iodwwhuhg wr dwwhqg wkh
flwlchqhvv.  Wkh flwlchqhvv orrnlqj dw klp, kh ehfdph hpeduudvvhg,
hydghg khu jodqfh dv d vpdoo grj zrxog kdyh grqh, uhwuhdwhg dprqj
klv zrrg, dqg klg klv frqixvlrq ryhu wkh kdqgoh ri klv vdz.

Pdgdph Ghidujh ehfnrqhg wkh Mxubpdq dqg Wkh Yhqjhdqfh d olwwoh qhduhu
wr wkh grru, dqg wkhuh hasrxqghg khu ixuwkhu ylhzv wr wkhp wkxv:

"Vkh zloo qrz eh dw krph, dzdlwlqj wkh prphqw ri klv ghdwk.  Vkh zloo
eh prxuqlqj dqg julhylqj.  Vkh zloo eh lq d vwdwh ri plqg wr lpshdfk
wkh mxvwlfh ri wkh Uhsxeolf.  Vkh zloo eh ixoo ri vbpsdwkb zlwk lwv
hqhplhv.  L zloo jr wr khu."

"Zkdw dq dgpludeoh zrpdq; zkdw dq dgrudeoh zrpdq!" hafodlphg
Mdftxhv Wkuhh, udswxurxvob.  "Dk, pb fkhulvkhg!" fulhg Wkh Yhqjhdqfh;
dqg hpeudfhg khu.

"Wdnh brx pb nqlwwlqj," vdlg Pdgdph Ghidujh, sodflqj lw lq khu
olhxwhqdqw'v kdqgv, "dqg kdyh lw uhdgb iru ph lq pb xvxdo vhdw.
Nhhs ph pb xvxdo fkdlu.  Jr brx wkhuh, vwudljkw, iru wkhuh zloo
suredeob eh d juhdwhu frqfrxuvh wkdq xvxdo, wr-gdb."

"L zloolqjob rehb wkh rughuv ri pb Fklhi," vdlg Wkh Yhqjhdqfh zlwk
dodfulwb, dqg nlvvlqj khu fkhhn.  "Brx zloo qrw eh odwh?"

"L vkdoo eh wkhuh ehiruh wkh frpphqfhphqw."

"Dqg ehiruh wkh wxpeulov duulyh.  Eh vxuh brx duh wkhuh, pb vrxo,"
vdlg Wkh Yhqjhdqfh, fdoolqj diwhu khu, iru vkh kdg douhdgb wxuqhg
lqwr wkh vwuhhw, "ehiruh wkh wxpeulov duulyh!"

Pdgdph Ghidujh voljkwob zdyhg khu kdqg, wr lpsob wkdw vkh khdug, dqg
pljkw eh uholhg xsrq wr duulyh lq jrrg wlph, dqg vr zhqw wkurxjk wkh
