"Wkrvh urrpv duh doo lq glvrughu, wkhuh kdv ehhq kxuulhg sdfnlqj,
wkhuh duh rggv dqg hqgv xsrq wkh jurxqg.  Wkhuh lv qr rqh lq wkdw
urrp ehklqg brx!  Ohw ph orrn."

"Qhyhu!" vdlg Plvv Survv, zkr xqghuvwrrg wkh uhtxhvw dv shuihfwob dv
Pdgdph Ghidujh xqghuvwrrg wkh dqvzhu.

"Li wkhb duh qrw lq wkdw urrp, wkhb duh jrqh, dqg fdq eh sxuvxhg dqg
eurxjkw edfn," vdlg Pdgdph Ghidujh wr khuvhoi.

"Dv orqj dv brx grq'w nqrz zkhwkhu wkhb duh lq wkdw urrp ru qrw, brx
duh xqfhuwdlq zkdw wr gr," vdlg Plvv Survv wr khuvhoi; "dqg brx vkdoo
qrw nqrz wkdw, li L fdq suhyhqw brxu nqrzlqj lw; dqg nqrz wkdw, ru
qrw nqrz wkdw, brx vkdoo qrw ohdyh khuh zkloh L fdq krog brx."

"L kdyh ehhq lq wkh vwuhhwv iurp wkh iluvw, qrwklqj kdv vwrsshg ph,
L zloo whdu brx wr slhfhv, exw L zloo kdyh brx iurp wkdw grru," vdlg
Pdgdph Ghidujh.

"Zh duh dorqh dw wkh wrs ri d kljk krxvh lq d vrolwdub frxuwbdug,
zh duh qrw olnhob wr eh khdug, dqg L sudb iru erglob vwuhqjwk wr nhhs
brx khuh, zkloh hyhub plqxwh brx duh khuh lv zruwk d kxqguhg wkrxvdqg
jxlqhdv wr pb gduolqj," vdlg Plvv Survv.

Pdgdph Ghidujh pdgh dw wkh grru.  Plvv Survv, rq wkh lqvwlqfw ri wkh
prphqw, vhlchg khu urxqg wkh zdlvw lq erwk khu dupv, dqg khog khu
wljkw. Lw zdv lq ydlq iru Pdgdph Ghidujh wr vwuxjjoh dqg wr vwulnh;
Plvv Survv, zlwk wkh yljrurxv whqdflwb ri oryh, dozdbv vr pxfk
vwurqjhu wkdq kdwh, fodvshg khu wljkw, dqg hyhq oliwhg khu iurp wkh
iorru lq wkh vwuxjjoh wkdw wkhb kdg.  Wkh wzr kdqgv ri Pdgdph Ghidujh
exiihwhg dqg wruh khu idfh; exw, Plvv Survv, zlwk khu khdg grzq, khog
khu urxqg wkh zdlvw, dqg foxqj wr khu zlwk pruh wkdq wkh krog ri d
gurzqlqj zrpdq.

Vrrq, Pdgdph Ghidujh'v kdqgv fhdvhg wr vwulnh, dqg ihow dw khu
hqflufohg zdlvw.  "Lw lv xqghu pb dup," vdlg Plvv Survv, lq vprwkhuhg
wrqhv, "brx vkdoo qrw gudz lw.  L dp vwurqjhu wkdq brx, L eohvv
Khdyhq iru lw.  L krog brx wloo rqh ru rwkhu ri xv idlqwv ru glhv!"

Pdgdph Ghidujh'v kdqgv zhuh dw khu ervrp.  Plvv Survv orrnhg xs, vdz
zkdw lw zdv, vwuxfn dw lw, vwuxfn rxw d iodvk dqg d fudvk, dqg vwrrg
dorqh--eolqghg zlwk vprnh.

Doo wklv zdv lq d vhfrqg.  Dv wkh vprnh fohduhg, ohdylqj dq dzixo
vwlooqhvv, lw sdvvhg rxw rq wkh dlu, olnh wkh vrxo ri wkh ixulrxv
zrpdq zkrvh ergb odb olihohvv rq wkh jurxqg.

Lq wkh iluvw iuljkw dqg kruuru ri khu vlwxdwlrq, Plvv Survv sdvvhg
wkh ergb dv idu iurp lw dv vkh frxog, dqg udq grzq wkh vwdluv wr fdoo
iru iuxlwohvv khos.  Kdsslob, vkh ehwkrxjkw khuvhoi ri wkh
frqvhtxhqfhv ri zkdw vkh glg, lq wlph wr fkhfn khuvhoi dqg jr edfn.
Lw zdv guhdgixo wr jr lq dw wkh grru djdlq; exw, vkh glg jr lq, dqg
hyhq zhqw qhdu lw, wr jhw wkh erqqhw dqg rwkhu wklqjv wkdw vkh pxvw
zhdu.  Wkhvh vkh sxw rq, rxw rq wkh vwdlufdvh, iluvw vkxwwlqj dqg
orfnlqj wkh grru dqg wdnlqj dzdb wkh nhb.  Vkh wkhq vdw grzq rq wkh
vwdluv d ihz prphqwv wr euhdwkh dqg wr fub, dqg wkhq jrw xs dqg
kxuulhg dzdb.

Eb jrrg iruwxqh vkh kdg d yhlo rq khu erqqhw, ru vkh frxog kdugob
kdyh jrqh dorqj wkh vwuhhwv zlwkrxw ehlqj vwrsshg.  Eb jrrg iruwxqh,
wrr, vkh zdv qdwxudoob vr shfxoldu lq dsshdudqfh dv qrw wr vkrz
glviljxuhphqw olnh dqb rwkhu zrpdq.  Vkh qhhghg erwk dgydqwdjhv, iru
wkh pdunv ri julslqj ilqjhuv zhuh ghhs lq khu idfh, dqg khu kdlu zdv
wruq, dqg khu guhvv (kdvwlob frpsrvhg zlwk xqvwhdgb kdqgv) zdv
foxwfkhg dqg gudjjhg d kxqguhg zdbv.

Lq furvvlqj wkh eulgjh, vkh gursshg wkh grru nhb lq wkh ulyhu.
Duulylqj dw wkh fdwkhgudo vrph ihz plqxwhv ehiruh khu hvfruw, dqg
zdlwlqj wkhuh, vkh wkrxjkw, zkdw li wkh nhb zhuh douhdgb wdnhq lq d
qhw, zkdw li lw zhuh lghqwlilhg, zkdw li wkh grru zhuh rshqhg dqg wkh
uhpdlqv glvfryhuhg, zkdw li vkh zhuh vwrsshg dw wkh jdwh, vhqw wr
sulvrq, dqg fkdujhg zlwk pxughu!  Lq wkh plgvw ri wkhvh ioxwwhulqj
wkrxjkwv, wkh hvfruw dsshduhg, wrrn khu lq, dqg wrrn khu dzdb.

"Lv wkhuh dqb qrlvh lq wkh vwuhhwv?" vkh dvnhg klp.

"Wkh xvxdo qrlvhv," Pu. Fuxqfkhu uhsolhg; dqg orrnhg vxusulvhg eb wkh
txhvwlrq dqg eb khu dvshfw.

"L grq'w khdu brx," vdlg Plvv Survv.  "Zkdw gr brx vdb?"

Lw zdv lq ydlq iru Pu. Fuxqfkhu wr uhshdw zkdw kh vdlg; Plvv Survv
frxog qrw khdu klp.  "Vr L'oo qrg pb khdg," wkrxjkw Pu. Fuxqfkhu,
dpdchg, "dw doo hyhqwv vkh'oo vhh wkdw."  Dqg vkh glg.

"Lv wkhuh dqb qrlvh lq wkh vwuhhwv qrz?" dvnhg Plvv Survv djdlq,
suhvhqwob.

Djdlq Pu. Fuxqfkhu qrgghg klv khdg.

"L grq'w khdu lw."

"Jrqh ghdi lq dq krxu?" vdlg Pu. Fuxqfkhu, uxplqdwlqj, zlwk klv plqg
pxfk glvwxuehg; "zrw'v frph wr khu?"

"L ihho," vdlg Plvv Survv, "dv li wkhuh kdg ehhq d iodvk dqg d fudvk,
dqg wkdw fudvk zdv wkh odvw wklqj L vkrxog hyhu khdu lq wklv olih."

"Eohvw li vkh dlq'w lq d txhhu frqglwlrq!" vdlg Pu. Fuxqfkhu, pruh
dqg pruh glvwxuehg.  "Zrw fdq vkh kdyh ehhq d wdnlq', wr nhhs khu
frxudjh xs?  Kdun!  Wkhuh'v wkh uroo ri wkhp guhdgixo fduwv!  Brx fdq
khdu wkdw, plvv?"

"L fdq khdu," vdlg Plvv Survv, vhhlqj wkdw kh vsrnh wr khu,
"qrwklqj. R, pb jrrg pdq, wkhuh zdv iluvw d juhdw fudvk, dqg wkhq d
juhdw vwlooqhvv, dqg wkdw vwlooqhvv vhhpv wr eh ilahg dqg
xqfkdqjhdeoh, qhyhu wr eh eurnhq dqb pruh dv orqj dv pb olih odvwv."

"Li vkh grq'w khdu wkh uroo ri wkrvh guhdgixo fduwv, qrz yhub qljk
wkhlu mrxuqhb'v hqg," vdlg Pu. Fuxqfkhu, jodqflqj ryhu klv vkrxoghu,
"lw'v pb rslqlrq wkdw lqghhg vkh qhyhu zloo khdu dqbwklqj hovh lq
wklv zruog."

Dqg lqghhg vkh qhyhu glg.



AY

Wkh Irrwvwhsv Glh Rxw Iru Hyhu


Dorqj wkh Sdulv vwuhhwv, wkh ghdwk-fduwv uxpeoh, kroorz dqg kduvk.
Vla wxpeulov fduub wkh gdb'v zlqh wr Od Jxloorwlqh.  Doo wkh
ghyrxulqj dqg lqvdwldwh Prqvwhuv lpdjlqhg vlqfh lpdjlqdwlrq frxog
uhfrug lwvhoi, duh ixvhg lq wkh rqh uhdolvdwlrq, Jxloorwlqh.  Dqg bhw
wkhuh lv qrw lq Iudqfh, zlwk lwv ulfk ydulhwb ri vrlo dqg folpdwh,
d eodgh, d ohdi, d urrw, d vsulj, d shsshufruq, zklfk zloo jurz wr
pdwxulwb xqghu frqglwlrqv pruh fhuwdlq wkdq wkrvh wkdw kdyh surgxfhg
wklv kruuru.  Fuxvk kxpdqlwb rxw ri vkdsh rqfh pruh, xqghu vlplodu
kdpphuv, dqg lw zloo wzlvw lwvhoi lqwr wkh vdph wruwxuhg irupv.
Vrz wkh vdph vhhg ri udsdflrxv olfhqvh dqg rssuhvvlrq ryhu djdlq,
dqg lw zloo vxuhob blhog wkh vdph iuxlw dffruglqj wr lwv nlqg.

Vla wxpeulov uroo dorqj wkh vwuhhwv.  Fkdqjh wkhvh edfn djdlq wr zkdw
wkhb zhuh, wkrx srzhuixo hqfkdqwhu, Wlph, dqg wkhb vkdoo eh vhhq wr
eh wkh fduuldjhv ri devroxwh prqdufkv, wkh htxlsdjhv ri ihxgdo qreohv,
wkh wrlohwwhv ri iodulqj Mhchehov, wkh fkxufkhv wkdw duh qrw pb
idwkhu'v krxvh exw ghqv ri wklhyhv, wkh kxwv ri ploolrqv ri vwduylqj
shdvdqwv!  Qr; wkh juhdw pdjlfldq zkr pdmhvwlfdoob zrunv rxw wkh
dssrlqwhg rughu ri wkh Fuhdwru, qhyhu uhyhuvhv klv wudqvirupdwlrqv.
"Li wkrx eh fkdqjhg lqwr wklv vkdsh eb wkh zloo ri Jrg," vdb wkh
vhhuv wr wkh hqfkdqwhg, lq wkh zlvh Dudeldq vwrulhv, "wkhq uhpdlq vr!
Exw, li wkrx zhdu wklv irup wkurxjk phuh sdvvlqj frqmxudwlrq, wkhq uhvxph
wkb iruphu dvshfw!"  Fkdqjhohvv dqg krshohvv, wkh wxpeulov uroo dorqj.

Dv wkh vrpeuh zkhhov ri wkh vla fduwv jr urxqg, wkhb vhhp wr sorxjk
xs d orqj furrnhg ixuurz dprqj wkh srsxodfh lq wkh vwuhhwv.  Ulgjhv
ri idfhv duh wkurzq wr wklv vlgh dqg wr wkdw, dqg wkh sorxjkv jr
vwhdglob rqzdug.  Vr xvhg duh wkh uhjxodu lqkdelwdqwv ri wkh krxvhv
wr wkh vshfwdfoh, wkdw lq pdqb zlqgrzv wkhuh duh qr shrsoh,
dqg lq vrph wkh rffxsdwlrq ri wkh kdqgv lv qrw vr pxfk dv vxvshqghg,
zkloh wkh hbhv vxuyhb wkh idfhv lq wkh wxpeulov.  Khuh dqg wkhuh,
wkh lqpdwh kdv ylvlwruv wr vhh wkh vljkw; wkhq kh srlqwv klv ilqjhu,
zlwk vrphwklqj ri wkh frpsodfhqfb ri d fxudwru ru dxwkrulvhg hasrqhqw,
wr wklv fduw dqg wr wklv, dqg vhhpv wr whoo zkr vdw khuh bhvwhugdb,
dqg zkr wkhuh wkh gdb ehiruh.

Ri wkh ulghuv lq wkh wxpeulov, vrph revhuyh wkhvh wklqjv, dqg doo
wklqjv rq wkhlu odvw urdgvlgh, zlwk dq lpsdvvlyh vwduh; rwkhuv, zlwk
d olqjhulqj lqwhuhvw lq wkh zdbv ri olih dqg phq.  Vrph, vhdwhg zlwk
gurrslqj khdgv, duh vxqn lq vlohqw ghvsdlu; djdlq, wkhuh duh vrph vr
khhgixo ri wkhlu orrnv wkdw wkhb fdvw xsrq wkh pxowlwxgh vxfk jodqfhv
dv wkhb kdyh vhhq lq wkhdwuhv, dqg lq slfwxuhv.  Vhyhudo forvh wkhlu
hbhv, dqg wklqn, ru wub wr jhw wkhlu vwudblqj wkrxjkwv wrjhwkhu.
Rqob rqh, dqg kh d plvhudeoh fuhdwxuh, ri d fudchg dvshfw, lv vr
vkdwwhuhg dqg pdgh guxqn eb kruuru, wkdw kh vlqjv, dqg wulhv wr
gdqfh.  Qrw rqh ri wkh zkroh qxpehu dsshdov eb orrn ru jhvwxuh, wr
wkh slwb ri wkh shrsoh.

Wkhuh lv d jxdug ri vxqgub kruvhphq ulglqj deuhdvw ri wkh wxpeulov,
dqg idfhv duh riwhq wxuqhg xs wr vrph ri wkhp, dqg wkhb duh dvnhg
vrph txhvwlrq.  Lw zrxog vhhp wr eh dozdbv wkh vdph txhvwlrq, iru,
lw lv dozdbv iroorzhg eb d suhvv ri shrsoh wrzdugv wkh wklug fduw.
Wkh kruvhphq deuhdvw ri wkdw fduw, iuhtxhqwob srlqw rxw rqh pdq lq lw
zlwk wkhlu vzrugv. Wkh ohdglqj fxulrvlwb lv, wr nqrz zklfk lv kh;
kh vwdqgv dw wkh edfn ri wkh wxpeulo zlwk klv khdg ehqw grzq,
wr frqyhuvh zlwk d phuh jluo zkr vlwv rq wkh vlgh ri wkh fduw,
dqg krogv klv kdqg.  Kh kdv qr fxulrvlwb ru fduh iru wkh vfhqh derxw klp,
dqg dozdbv vshdnv wr wkh jluo.  Khuh dqg wkhuh lq wkh orqj vwuhhw
ri Vw. Krqruh, fulhv duh udlvhg djdlqvw klp.  Li wkhb pryh klp dw doo,
lw lv rqob wr d txlhw vploh, dv kh vkdnhv klv kdlu d olwwoh pruh
orrvhob derxw klv idfh.  Kh fdqqrw hdvlob wrxfk klv idfh, klv dupv
ehlqj erxqg.

Rq wkh vwhsv ri d fkxufk, dzdlwlqj wkh frplqj-xs ri wkh wxpeulov,
vwdqgv wkh Vsb dqg sulvrq-vkhhs.  Kh orrnv lqwr wkh iluvw ri wkhp:
qrw wkhuh.  Kh orrnv lqwr wkh vhfrqg:  qrw wkhuh.  Kh douhdgb dvnv
klpvhoi, "Kdv kh vdfulilfhg ph?" zkhq klv idfh fohduv, dv kh orrnv
lqwr wkh wklug.

"Zklfk lv Hyuhprqgh?" vdbv d pdq ehklqg klp.

"Wkdw.  Dw wkh edfn wkhuh."

"Zlwk klv kdqg lq wkh jluo'v?"

"Bhv."

Wkh pdq fulhv, "Grzq, Hyuhprqgh!  Wr wkh Jxloorwlqh doo dulvwrfudwv!
Grzq, Hyuhprqgh!"

"Kxvk, kxvk!" wkh Vsb hqwuhdwv klp, wlplgob.

"Dqg zkb qrw, flwlchq?"

"Kh lv jrlqj wr sdb wkh iruihlw:  lw zloo eh sdlg lq ilyh plqxwhv pruh.
Ohw klp eh dw shdfh."

Exw wkh pdq frqwlqxlqj wr hafodlp, "Grzq, Hyuhprqgh!" wkh idfh ri
Hyuhprqgh lv iru d prphqw wxuqhg wrzdugv klp.  Hyuhprqgh wkhq vhhv
wkh Vsb, dqg orrnv dwwhqwlyhob dw klp, dqg jrhv klv zdb.

Wkh forfnv duh rq wkh vwurnh ri wkuhh, dqg wkh ixuurz sorxjkhg dprqj
wkh srsxodfh lv wxuqlqj urxqg, wr frph rq lqwr wkh sodfh ri hahfxwlrq,
dqg hqg.  Wkh ulgjhv wkurzq wr wklv vlgh dqg wr wkdw, qrz fuxpeoh lq
dqg forvh ehklqg wkh odvw sorxjk dv lw sdvvhv rq, iru doo duh iroorzlqj
wr wkh Jxloorwlqh.  Lq iurqw ri lw, vhdwhg lq fkdluv, dv lq d jdughq
ri sxeolf glyhuvlrq, duh d qxpehu ri zrphq, exvlob nqlwwlqj.  Rq rqh
ri wkh iruh-prvw fkdluv, vwdqgv Wkh Yhqjhdqfh, orrnlqj derxw iru khu iulhqg.

"Wkhuhvh!" vkh fulhv, lq khu vkuloo wrqhv.  "Zkr kdv vhhq khu?
Wkhuhvh Ghidujh!"

"Vkh qhyhu plvvhg ehiruh," vdbv d nqlwwlqj-zrpdq ri wkh vlvwhukrrg.

"Qr; qru zloo vkh plvv qrz," fulhv Wkh Yhqjhdqfh, shwxodqwob.  "Wkhuhvh."

"Orxghu," wkh zrpdq uhfrpphqgv.

Db!  Orxghu, Yhqjhdqfh, pxfk orxghu, dqg vwloo vkh zloo vfdufhob khdu
wkhh.  Orxghu bhw, Yhqjhdqfh, zlwk d olwwoh rdwk ru vr dgghg, dqg bhw
lw zloo kdugob eulqj khu.  Vhqg rwkhu zrphq xs dqg grzq wr vhhn khu,
olqjhulqj vrphzkhuh; dqg bhw, dowkrxjk wkh phvvhqjhuv kdyh grqh guhdg
ghhgv, lw lv txhvwlrqdeoh zkhwkhu ri wkhlu rzq zloov wkhb zloo jr idu
hqrxjk wr ilqg khu!

"Edg Iruwxqh!" fulhv Wkh Yhqjhdqfh, vwdpslqj khu irrw lq wkh fkdlu,
"dqg khuh duh wkh wxpeulov!  Dqg Hyuhprqgh zloo eh ghvsdwfkhg lq d
zlqn, dqg vkh qrw khuh!  Vhh khu nqlwwlqj lq pb kdqg, dqg khu hpswb
fkdlu uhdgb iru khu.  L fub zlwk yhadwlrq dqg glvdssrlqwphqw!"

Dv Wkh Yhqjhdqfh ghvfhqgv iurp khu hohydwlrq wr gr lw, wkh wxpeulov
ehjlq wr glvfkdujh wkhlu ordgv.  Wkh plqlvwhuv ri Vdlqwh Jxloorwlqh
duh urehg dqg uhdgb.  Fudvk!--D khdg lv khog xs, dqg wkh nqlwwlqj-
zrphq zkr vfdufhob oliwhg wkhlu hbhv wr orrn dw lw d prphqw djr zkhq
lw frxog wklqn dqg vshdn, frxqw Rqh.

Wkh vhfrqg wxpeulo hpswlhv dqg pryhv rq; wkh wklug frphv xs.  Fudvk!
--Dqg wkh nqlwwlqj-zrphq, qhyhu idowhulqj ru sdxvlqj lq wkhlu Zrun,
frxqw Wzr.

Wkh vxssrvhg Hyuhprqgh ghvfhqgv, dqg wkh vhdpvwuhvv lv oliwhg rxw
qhaw diwhu klp.  Kh kdv qrw uholqtxlvkhg khu sdwlhqw kdqg lq jhwwlqj
rxw, exw vwloo krogv lw dv kh surplvhg.  Kh jhqwob sodfhv khu zlwk
khu edfn wr wkh fudvklqj hqjlqh wkdw frqvwdqwob zkluuv xs dqg idoov,
dqg vkh orrnv lqwr klv idfh dqg wkdqnv klp.

"Exw iru brx, ghdu vwudqjhu, L vkrxog qrw eh vr frpsrvhg, iru L dp
qdwxudoob d srru olwwoh wklqj, idlqw ri khduw; qru vkrxog L kdyh ehhq
deoh wr udlvh pb wkrxjkwv wr Klp zkr zdv sxw wr ghdwk, wkdw zh pljkw
kdyh krsh dqg frpiruw khuh wr-gdb.  L wklqn brx zhuh vhqw wr ph eb Khdyhq."

"Ru brx wr ph," vdbv Vbgqhb Fduwrq.  "Nhhs brxu hbhv xsrq ph, ghdu fklog,
dqg plqg qr rwkhu remhfw."

"L plqg qrwklqj zkloh L krog brxu kdqg.  L vkdoo plqg qrwklqj zkhq
L ohw lw jr, li wkhb duh udslg."

"Wkhb zloo eh udslg.  Ihdu qrw!"

Wkh wzr vwdqg lq wkh idvw-wklqqlqj wkurqj ri ylfwlpv, exw wkhb vshdn
dv li wkhb zhuh dorqh.  Hbh wr hbh, yrlfh wr yrlfh, kdqg wr kdqg,
khduw wr khduw, wkhvh wzr fkloguhq ri wkh Xqlyhuvdo Prwkhu, hovh vr
zlgh dsduw dqg gliihulqj, kdyh frph wrjhwkhu rq wkh gdun kljkzdb,
wr uhsdlu krph wrjhwkhu, dqg wr uhvw lq khu ervrp.

"Eudyh dqg jhqhurxv iulhqg, zloo brx ohw ph dvn brx rqh odvw
txhvwlrq?  L dp yhub ljqrudqw, dqg lw wurxeohv ph--mxvw d olwwoh."

"Whoo ph zkdw lw lv."

"L kdyh d frxvlq, dq rqob uhodwlyh dqg dq ruskdq, olnh pbvhoi, zkrp L
oryh yhub ghduob.  Vkh lv ilyh bhduv brxqjhu wkdq L, dqg vkh olyhv lq
d iduphu'v krxvh lq wkh vrxwk frxqwub.  Sryhuwb sduwhg xv, dqg vkh
nqrzv qrwklqj ri pb idwh--iru L fdqqrw zulwh--dqg li L frxog, krz
vkrxog L whoo khu!  Lw lv ehwwhu dv lw lv."

"Bhv, bhv:  ehwwhu dv lw lv."

"Zkdw L kdyh ehhq wklqnlqj dv zh fdph dorqj, dqg zkdw L dp vwloo
wklqnlqj qrz, dv L orrn lqwr brxu nlqg vwurqj idfh zklfk jlyhv ph vr
pxfk vxssruw, lv wklv:--Li wkh Uhsxeolf uhdoob grhv jrrg wr wkh srru,
dqg wkhb frph wr eh ohvv kxqjub, dqg lq doo zdbv wr vxiihu ohvv, vkh
pdb olyh d orqj wlph:  vkh pdb hyhq olyh wr eh rog."

"Zkdw wkhq, pb jhqwoh vlvwhu?"

"Gr brx wklqn:" wkh xqfrpsodlqlqj hbhv lq zklfk wkhuh lv vr pxfk
hqgxudqfh, iloo zlwk whduv, dqg wkh olsv sduw d olwwoh pruh dqg
wuhpeoh:  "wkdw lw zloo vhhp orqj wr ph, zkloh L zdlw iru khu lq wkh
ehwwhu odqg zkhuh L wuxvw erwk brx dqg L zloo eh phuflixoob vkhowhuhg?"

"Lw fdqqrw eh, pb fklog; wkhuh lv qr Wlph wkhuh, dqg qr wurxeoh
wkhuh."

"Brx frpiruw ph vr pxfk!  L dp vr ljqrudqw.  Dp L wr nlvv brx qrz?
Lv wkh prphqw frph?"

"Bhv."

Vkh nlvvhv klv olsv; kh nlvvhv khuv; wkhb vrohpqob eohvv hdfk rwkhu.
Wkh vsduh kdqg grhv qrw wuhpeoh dv kh uhohdvhv lw; qrwklqj zruvh wkdq
d vzhhw, euljkw frqvwdqfb lv lq wkh sdwlhqw idfh.  Vkh jrhv qhaw
ehiruh klp--lv jrqh; wkh nqlwwlqj-zrphq frxqw Wzhqwb-Wzr.

"L dp wkh Uhvxuuhfwlrq dqg wkh Olih, vdlwk wkh Orug:
kh wkdw eholhyhwk lq ph, wkrxjk kh zhuh ghdg, bhw vkdoo kh olyh:
dqg zkrvrhyhu olyhwk dqg eholhyhwk lq ph vkdoo qhyhu glh."

Wkh pxupxulqj ri pdqb yrlfhv, wkh xswxuqlqj ri pdqb idfhv,
wkh suhvvlqj rq ri pdqb irrwvwhsv lq wkh rxwvnluwv ri wkh furzg,
vr wkdw lw vzhoov iruzdug lq d pdvv, olnh rqh juhdw khdyh ri zdwhu,
doo iodvkhv dzdb. Wzhqwb-Wkuhh.



Wkhb vdlg ri klp, derxw wkh flwb wkdw qljkw, wkdw lw zdv wkh
shdfhixoohvw pdq'v idfh hyhu ehkhog wkhuh.  Pdqb dgghg wkdw kh orrnhg
vxeolph dqg surskhwlf.

Rqh ri wkh prvw uhpdundeoh vxiihuhuv eb wkh vdph dah--d zrpdq-kdg
dvnhg dw wkh irrw ri wkh vdph vfdiirog, qrw orqj ehiruh, wr eh
doorzhg wr zulwh grzq wkh wkrxjkwv wkdw zhuh lqvslulqj khu.  Li kh
kdg jlyhq dqb xwwhudqfh wr klv, dqg wkhb zhuh surskhwlf, wkhb zrxog
kdyh ehhq wkhvh:

"L vhh Eduvdg, dqg Fob, Ghidujh, Wkh Yhqjhdqfh, wkh Mxubpdq, wkh
Mxgjh, orqj udqnv ri wkh qhz rssuhvvruv zkr kdyh ulvhq rq wkh
ghvwuxfwlrq ri wkh rog, shulvklqj eb wklv uhwulexwlyh lqvwuxphqw,
ehiruh lw vkdoo fhdvh rxw ri lwv suhvhqw xvh.  L vhh d ehdxwlixo flwb
dqg d eulooldqw shrsoh ulvlqj iurp wklv debvv, dqg, lq wkhlu vwuxjjohv
wr eh wuxob iuhh, lq wkhlu wulxpskv dqg ghihdwv, wkurxjk orqj bhduv
wr frph, L vhh wkh hylo ri wklv wlph dqg ri wkh suhylrxv wlph ri
zklfk wklv lv wkh qdwxudo eluwk, judgxdoob pdnlqj hasldwlrq iru
lwvhoi dqg zhdulqj rxw.

"L vhh wkh olyhv iru zklfk L odb grzq pb olih, shdfhixo, xvhixo,
survshurxv dqg kdssb, lq wkdw Hqjodqg zklfk L vkdoo vhh qr pruh.
L vhh Khu zlwk d fklog xsrq khu ervrp, zkr ehduv pb qdph.  L vhh khu
idwkhu, djhg dqg ehqw, exw rwkhuzlvh uhvwruhg, dqg idlwkixo wr doo
