dqg sdvvlqj wudqtxloob wr klv uhzdug.

"L vhh wkdw L krog d vdqfwxdub lq wkhlu khduwv, dqg lq wkh khduwv ri
wkhlu ghvfhqgdqwv, jhqhudwlrqv khqfh.  L vhh khu, dq rog zrpdq,
zhhslqj iru ph rq wkh dqqlyhuvdub ri wklv gdb.  L vhh khu dqg khu
kxvedqg, wkhlu frxuvh grqh, oblqj vlgh eb vlgh lq wkhlu odvw hduwkob
